hadiths[504]{hadithnumber,text}:
4474,"mein masjid mein Namaz padh raha tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey usi haalat mein bulaya , maine koi jawab nahi diya ( phir baad mein, maine hazir ho kar) arz kya : ya Rasulullah! main Namaz padh raha tha. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya Allah Taala ne tum se nahi farmaya hai) استجيبوا لله وللرسول إذا دعاكم‏ ( ''Allah aur uske rasool jab tumhen balaaein to haan mein jawab do. '' phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya ke aaj main tumhen masjid se nikalney se pahley aik aisi sura ki taleem doonga jo Quran ki sabse badi sura hai. phir aap ne mera hath apne hath mein liya aur jab aap bahar nikalney lagey to maine yad dilaya ke aap ne mujhey Quran ki sabse badi sura bataaney ka wada kya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ( الحمد لله رب العالمين ( yahi wo ""saba'-masaanii"" aur Quran azeem hai jo mujhey ata kya gaya hai."
4475,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab imaam (غير المغضوب عليهم wla الضالين) kahey to tum (aameen) kaho kyonke jiska ye kehna malaaika ke kehney ke sath ho jaey uski tamam pichhli khataein maaf ho jati hain.''
4476,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''momineen qiyamat ke din pareshan ho kar jama hongey aur (aapas mein) kahengey, behtar ye tha ke apne rab ke huzoor mein aaj kisi ko ham apna sifarishi banaatey. chunanche sab log Adam (Alaihissalam) ki khidmat mein hazir hongey aur arz karengey ke aap insanon ke bap hain. Allah Taala ne aapko apne hath se banaya. aap ke liye farishton ko sajde ka hukm diya aur aapko har cheez ke naam sikhaaey. aap hamarey liye apne rab ke huzoor mein sifarish kar dein taake aaj ki museebat se hamein nijat miley. Adam (Alaihissalam) kahengey, main iske laaiq nahi hun, wo apni khata ko yad karengey aur unko parwardigar ke huzoor mein janey se sharm aaeygii . kahengey ke tum log Nuh (Alaihissalam) ke paas jao. wo sabse pahley Nabi hain jinhein Allah Taala ne ( mere baad) zameen walon ki taraf maboos kya tha. sab log Nuh (Alaihissalam) ki khidmat mein hazir hongey. wo bhi kahengey ke main is qaabil nahi aur wo apne rab se apne sawal ko yad karengey jiske mutaalliq unhein koi ilm nahi tha. unko bhi sharm aaeygii aur kahengey ke Allah ke khaleel (Alaihissalam) ke paas jao. log unki khidmat mein hazir hongey lekin wo bhi yahi kahengey ke main is qaabil nahi, Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas jao, unse Allah Taala ne kalam farmaya tha aur Taurait di thi. log unke paas aaeingey lekin wo bhi uzr kar dengey ke mujh mein uski jur'at nahi. unko baghair kisi haq ke aik shakhs ko qatl karna yad aa jaeyga aur apne rab ke huzoor mein jatey huey sharm aaeygi. kahengey tum Esa (Alaihissalam) ke paas jao, wo Allah ke bandey aur uske rasool, iska kalima aur uski Rooh hain lekin Esa (Alaihissalam) bhi yahi kahengey ke mujh mein uski himmat nahi, tum Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jao, wo Allah ke maqbool bandey hain aur Allah ne unke tamam agley aur pichhley gunah maaf kar diye hain. chunanche log mere paas aaeingey, main unke sath jaaunga aur apne rab se ijazat chaahoonga. mujhey ijazat mil jaeygi, phir main apne rab ko dekhtey hi sajde mein gir padoonga aur jab tak Allah chaahega mein sajde mein rahunga , phir mujh se kaha jaeyga ke apna sar uthao aur jo chaho maango, tumhen diya jaeyga jo chaho kaho tumhari baat suni jaeygi. shafaat karo, tumhari shafaat qabool ki jaeygi. main apna sar uthaaoonga aur Allah ki wo hamd bayan karunga jo mujhey uski taraf se sikhai gaee hogi. uske baad shafaat karunga aur mere liye aik had muqarrar kar di jaeygi. mein unhein jannat mein dakhil karaaoonga chothi martaba jab main wapas aaoonga to arz karunga ke jahannam mein un logon ke siwa aur koi ab baqi nahi raha jinhein Quran ne hamesha ke liye jahannam mein rehna zaroori qarar de diya hai. abu-Adbullah imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke Quran ki ro se dozakh mein qaid rehney se murad wo log hain jinke liye (khaaledeen feehaa) kaha gaya hai. ke wo hamesha dozakh mein rahengey."
4477,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se poochha, Allah ke nazdeek kon sa gunah sabse bada hai? farmaya aur ye ke tum Allah ke sath kisi ko barabar thehrao halanke Allah hi ne tum ko paid kiya hai. maine arz kya ye to waqei sabse bada gunah hai, phir iske baad kon sa gunah sabse bada hai? farmaya ye ke tum apni aulad ko is khof se mar dalo ke wo tumharey sath khaaengey. maine puchha aur uske baad ? farmaya ye ke tum apne padosi ki aurat se zina karo."
4478,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' ( كمأة ( (yani کھنبی ( bhi) من ( ki qism hai aur iska pani aankh ki dawaa hai.''
4479,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Bani-Israeel ko ye hukm hua tha ke Shahar ke darwazey mein jhuktey huey dakhil hon aur) حطة‏ ( kehtey huey (yani ( ''aey Allah ! hamarey gunah maaf kar de. '' lekin wo ultey koolhon ke bal ghisattey huey dakhil huey aur kalima ( حطة‏ ( ko bhi badal diya aur kaha ke (حبة في شعرة) yani dil lagi ke taur par kehney lagey ke ''daana baal ke andar hona chaahiye.''
4480,"jab Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) (jo yahood ke badey aalim they) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki (Madina ( tashrif laney ki khabar suni to wo apne baagh mein phal tod rahe they. wo usi waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya ke main aap se aisi teen chizon ke mutaalliq poochhta hun, jinhein Nabi ke siwa aur koi nahi janta. batlaaiye ! qiyamat ki nishaniyon mein sabse pehli nishani kya hai? ahle-jannat ki dawat ke liye sabse pahley kya cheez pesh ki jaeygi ? bachcha Kab apne bap ki sura mein hoga aur Kab apni maa ki sura par? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey abhi Jibraeel ne aa kar unke mutaalliq bataya hai. Abdullaah-bin-Salaam boley Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne ! farmaya : haan , Abdullaah-bin-Salaam ne kaha ke wo to yahudiyon ke dushman hain. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat ki ( من كان عدوا لجبريل فإنه نزله على قلبك‏) aur unke sawalat ke jawab mein farmaya, qiyamat ki sabse pehli nishani aik aag hogi jo insanon ko mashriq se maghrib ki taraf jama kar laaeygii. ahle-jannat ki dawat mein jo khana sabse pahley pesh kya jaeyga wo machhli ke jigar ka badha hua hissey hoga aur jab mard ka pani aurat ke pani par ghalba kar jata hai to bachcha bap ki shakl par hota hai aur jab aurat ka pani mard ke pani par ghalba kar jata hai to bachcha maa ki shakl par hota hai. Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) bol uthey (أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله ، Mina وأشهد أنك رسول الله) ''main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur gawahi deta hun ke aap Allah ke rasool hain.''(phir arz kya (ya Rasulullah ! Yahudi badi bohtan baaz qaum hai, agar us se pahley ke aap mere mutaalliq unse kuchh poochhein, unhein mere Islam ka pata chal gaya to mujh par bohtan lagaaney shuru kar dengey. baad mein jab Yahudi aaey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke Abdullah tumharey yahan kaisey aadmi samjhey jatey hain? wo kehney lagey, ham mein sabse behtar aur ham mein sabse behtar ke betey! hamarey sardaar aur hamarey sardaar ke betey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar wo Islam ley aaein phir tumhara kya khayal hoga? kehney lagey, Allah Taala us se unhein panah mein rakhey. itney mein Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne zahir ho kar kahaa (أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله ، Mina وأشهد أنك رسول الله) ke ''main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa aur koi maabood nahi aur gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad Allah ke sachey rasool hain.'' ab wahi Yahudi unke barey mein kehney lagey ke ye ham mein sabse badtar hai aur sabse badtar shakhs ka betaa hai aur unki tauheen shuru kar di. Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! yahi wo cheez thi jis se main darta tha."
4481,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya, ham mein Quran ke sabse behtar qaari Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) hain aur ham mein sabse zyada Ali (Raziallahu anhu) mein qaza yani faisley karne ki salahiyatein hai. iske bawajud ham Ubii (Raziallahu anhu) ki is baat ko taslim nahi kartey jo Ubii (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jin aayatein ki bhi tilawat suni hai, main unhein nahi chhod sakta. halanke Allah Taala ne khud farmaya hai) ما ننسخ من آية أو ننسأها‏ ( الخ ke ''ham ne jo aayat bhi mansukh ki ya usey bhulaayaa to phir us se achi aayat laaey.''"
4482,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala irshad farmata hai, ibne-Aadam ne mujhey jhutlaayaa halanke uske liye ye munasib na tha. usne mujhey gali di, halanke uske liye ye munasib na tha. uska mujhey jhutlana to ye hai ke wo kehta hai ke main usey dobara zinda karne par qaadir nahi hun aur uska mujhey gali dena ye hai ke mere liye aulad bataataa hai, meri zaat us se paak hai ke main apne liye biwi ya aulad banaaun.''"
4483,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya, teen mauqon par Allah Taala ke nazil hone-waale hukm se meri raey ne pahley hi muwafiqat ki ya mere rab ne teen mauqon par meri raey ke muwafiq hukm nazil farmaya, maine arz kya tha ke ya Rasulullah! kya achchha hota ke aap maqaame-Ibraaheem ko tawaaf ke baad Namaz padhney ki jagah banatey to baad mein yahi aayat nazil hui aur maine arz kya tha ke ya Rasulullah ! aap ke ghar mein achchhey aur burey har tarah ke log aatey hain. kya achchha hota ke aap ummahaatul momeneen (nabi ki beeviyon) ko parde ka hukm de detey. is par Allah Taala ne aayat hijaab ( parde ki aayat ( nazil farmai aur unhon-ne bayan kya aur mujhey kuchh paak beeviyon se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki narazgi ki khabar milii. main unke yahan gaya aur unse kaha ke tum baaz aa jao, warna Allah Taala tum se behtar beeviyan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye badal dega. baad mein paak beeviyon mein se aik ke yahan gaya to wo mujh se kehney lagein ke umr ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to apni beeviyon ko itni naseehatein nahi kartey jitni tum unhein kartey rahtey ho. aakhir Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki(عسى ربه إن طلقكن أن يبدله أزواجا خيرا منكن مسلمات) ''koii tajjub na hona chahiye agar us Nabi ka rab tumhen talaaq dila de aur dusri musalman beeviyan tum se behtar badal de.'' aakhir aayat tak aur ibne-abi Maryam ne bayan kya, unhein Yahya bin Ayub ne khabar di, unse Humaid ne bayan kya aur unhon-ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) se naql kya."
4484,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' dekhti nahi ho ke jab tumhari qaum ( Quraish ( ne Kaba ki tameer ki to Ibrahim ki buniyaadon se usey kam kar diya. '' maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! phir aap Ibrahim ki buniyaadon ke mutabiq phir se Kaba ki tameer kyon nahi karwaa detey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar tumhari qaum abhi nai naii kufr se nikli na hoti (to mein aisa hi karta ( . Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, jabke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke maine ye hadis Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni hai to main samajhta hun ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un 2 ruknon ka jo Hateem ke qareeb hain (tawaaf ke waqt) chhoonaa usi liye chhoda tha ke Baitullah ki tameer Ibrahim ki buniyad ke mutabiq mukammal nahi thi."
4485,unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke ahle-kitab ( Yahudi ( Taurah ko khud Ibranii zaban mein padhtey hain lekin musalmanon ke liye uski tafseer arabii mein kartey hain. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum ahle-kitab ki na tasdeeq karo aur na tum takzeeb karo balke ye kaha karo (آمنا بالله وما أنزل إلينا) yaanii ham eman laey Allah par aur us cheez par jo hamari taraf nazil ki gaee hai.''
4486,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne baitul-maqdis ki taraf rukh karke sola ya satrah mahiney tak Namaz padhi lekin aap chahtey they ke aap ka qibla Baitullah ( Kaba (ho jaey (aakhir aik din Allah ke hukm se) aap ne Asr ki Namaz (Baitullaah ki taraf rukh karke) padhi aur aap ke sath bahut se sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi padhi. jin sahaba ne ye Namaz aap ke sath padhi thi, unmein se aik sahabi Madina ki aik masjid ke qareeb se guzrey. us masjid mein log rukoo mein they, unhon-ne is par kaha ke main Allah ka naam lekar gawahi deta hun ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Makka ki taraf munh karke Namaz padhi hai, tamam namazi usi haalat mein Baitullah ki taraf phir gaey. iske baad logon ne kaha ke jo log Kaba ke qibla honey se pahley intiqal kar gaey, unke mutaalliq ham kya kahein. (unki namazein qabool huin ya nahi ? ( is par ye aayat nazil hui ''Allah aisa nahi ke tumhari ibaadaton ko zaaye karey, beshak Allah apne bandon par bahut bada meharban aur bada Rahim hai.''"
4487,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat ke din Nuh (Alaihissalam) ko bulaya jaeyga wo arz karengey, ( لبيك وسعديك ( : ya rab! Allah rabbul-izzat farmaeyga, kya tum ne mera paigham pahuncha diya tha? Nuh (Alaihissalam) arz karengey ke maine pahuncha diya tha, phir unki ummat se puchha jaeyga, kya unhon-ne tumhen mera paigham pahuncha diya tha? wo log kahengey ke hamarey yahan koi daraane wala nahi aaya. Allah Taala farmaeyga ( Nuh (Alaihissalam) se) ke aap ke haq mein koi gawahi bhi de sakta hai? wo kahengey ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur unki ummat meri gawah hai. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ummat unke haq mein gawahi degi ke unhon-ne paigham pahuncha diya tha aur rasool (yani Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) apni ummat ke haq mein gawahi dengey (ke unhon-ne sachchii gawahi di hai) yahi murad hai Allah ke us irshad se (وكذلك جعلناكم أمة وسطا لتكونوا شهداء على Naas ويكون الرسول عليكم شهيدا‏) ke ''aur isi tarah ham ne tum ko ummat beech banaya taake tum logon ke liye gawahi 2 aur rasool tumharey liye gawahi dein.'' aayat mein lafz ( beech (ke mana aadil, munsif, behtar ke hain."
4488,"log masjide-Qubaa mein subah ki Namaz padh hi rahe they ke aik sahib aaey aur unhon-ne kaha ke Allah Taala ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par Quran nazil kya hai ke aap Namaz mein Kaba ki taraf munh karein, lihaza aap log bhi Kaba ki taraf rukh kar lein. sab namazi usi waqt Kaba ki taraf phir gaey."
4489,mere siwa un sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) mein se jinhoney donon qiblon ki taraf Namaz padhi thi aur koi ab zinda nahi raha.
4490,"log masjide-Qubaa mein subah ki Namaz padh rahe they ke aik sahib wahan aaey aur kaha ke raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par Quran nazil hua hai ke (namaz mein) Kaba ki taraf munh karein, to aap log bhi ab Kaba ki taraf rukh kar lein. rawi ne bayan kya ke logon ka munh us waqt Sham (Syria) ( baitul-maqdis ( ki taraf tha, usi waqt log Kaba ki taraf phir gaey."
4491,log masjide-Qubaa mein subah ki Namaz padh rahe they ke aik sahib (Madina se) aaey aur kaha ke raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par Quran nazil hua hai aur aapko hukm hua hai ke Kaba ki taraf munh kar lein. isliye aap log bhi Kaba ki taraf phir jaaein. us waqt unka munh Sham (Syria) ki taraf tha. chunanche sab namazi Kaba ki taraf phir gaey.
4492,ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sola ya satrah mahiney tak baitul-maqdis ki taraf munh karke Namaz padhi. phir Allah Taala ne hamein Kaba ki taraf munh karne ka hukm diya.
4493,"log Quba mein subah ki Namaz padh rahe they ke aik sahib aaey aur kaha ke raat Quran nazil hua hai aur Kaba ki taraf munh kar leney ka hukm hua hai. isliye aap log bhi Kaba ki taraf munh kar lein aur jis haalat mein hain, isi tarah uski taraf mutwajjeh ho jayen (ye suntey hi ( tamam sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) Kaba ki taraf mutwajjeh ho gaey. us waqt logon ka munh Sham (Syria) ki taraf tha."
4494,abhi log masjide-Qubaa mein subah ki Namaz padh hi rahe they ke aik aaney waley sahib aaey aur kaha ke raat ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par Quran nazil hua hai aur aapko Kaba ki taraf munh karne ka hukm hua hai. isliye aap log bhi usi taraf munh kar lein. wo log Sham (Syria) ki taraf munh karke Namaz padh rahe they lekin usi waqt Kaba ki taraf phir gaey.
4495,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha (un dinon mein nau-umr tha) ke Allah tabarak w taala ke us irshad ke barey mein aap ka kya khayal hai إن الصفا والمروة من شعائر الله فمن حج البيت أو اعتمر فلا جناح عليه أن يطوف بهما‏'' Safa aur Marwa beshak Allah ki yaadgaar chizon mein se hain. to jo koi Baitullah ka Haj karey ya Umra karey to is par koi gunah nahi ke un donon ke darmyan aamad-o-raft (yani saee) kare. '' mera khayal hai ke agar koi unki saee na karey to is par bhi koi gunah nahi hona chahiye Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke hargiz nahi jaisa ke tumhara khayal hai. agar masla yahi hota to phir waqei unke saee na karne mein koi gunah na tha. lekin ye aayat Ansar ke barey mein nazil hui thi (Islam se pahley) Ansar manaat but ke naam se ehram baandhtey they, ye but maqam qudaid mein rakha hua tha aur Ansar Safa aur Marwa ki saee ko achchha nahi samajhtey they. jab Islam aaya to unhon-ne saee ke mutaalliq Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha : is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki إن الصفا والمروة من شعائر الله فمن حج البيت أو اعتمر فلا جناح عليه أن يطوف بهما‏'' Safa aur Marwa beshak Allah ki yaadgaar chizon mein se hain, so jo koi Baitullah ka Haj karey ya Umra karey to is par koi bhi gunah nahi ke un donon ke darmyan ( saee ( kare. ''"
4496,"usey ham jahiliyat ke kaamon mein se samajhtey they. jab Islam aaya to ham unki saee se ruk gaey, is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki) إن الصفا والمروة ( se irshad ( أن يطوف بهما‏ ( tak. yani beshak Safa aur Marwa Allah ki nishaniyon mein se hain. to unki saee karne mein Haj aur Umra ke doran koi gunah nahi hai."
4497,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik kalima irshad farmaya aur maine aik aur baat kahi . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs is haalat mein mar jaey ke wo Allah ke siwa auron ko bhi iska Sharik thahraataa raha ho to wo jahannam mein jata hai aur maine yun kaha ke jo shakhs us haalat mein marey ke Allah ka kisi ko Sharik na thahraataa raha to wo jannat mein jata hai.
4498,"Bani-Israeel mein qisaas yani badla tha lekin diyat nahi thi. isliye Allah Taala ne is ummat se kaha ke ''tum par maqtoolon ke baare mein qisaas farz kya gaya, aazad ke badley mein aazad aur ghulam ke badley mein ghulam aur aurat ke badley mein aurat, haan jis kisi ko iske fareeq maqtool ki taraf se kuchh maafi mil jaaey.'' to maafi se murad yahi diyat qabool karna hai. so mutalba ma'qool aur narm tariqa se ho aur mutalba ko us fareeq ke paas khoobi se pahunchaya jaey. ye tumharey parwardigar ki taraf se riaayat aur meherbani hai.'' yani uske muqable mein jo tum se pehli ummaton par farz tha.'' so jo koi iske baad bhi zyadti karega, uske liye aakhirat mein dardnak azab hoga.'' (zyaadtii se murad ye hai ke) diyat bhi ley li aur phir iske baad qatl bhi kar diya."
4499,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kitabullah ka hukm qisaas ka hai.
4500,"meri phoophii Rabe ne aik ladki ke daant tod diye, phir us ladki se logon ne maafi ki darkhaast ki lekin us ladki ke qabeeley waley maafi dene ko taiyaar nahi huey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur qisaas ke siwa aur kisi cheez par razi nahi they. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qisaas ka hukm de diya. is par Anas-bin-Nazar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! kya Rabe (Raziallahu anhu) ke daant tod diye jaaeinge, nahi, us zaat ki qism jisne aapko haq ke sath maboos kya hai, unke daant na todey jaengey. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Anas! kitabullah ka hukm qisaas ka hi hai. phir ladki waley razi ho gaey aur unhon-ne maaf kar diya. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kuchh Allah ke bandey aisey hain ke agar wo Allah ka naam lekar qism khaaein to Allah unki qism poori kar hi deta hai."
4501,Aashooraa ke din jahiliyat mein ham roza rakhtey they lekin jab Ramazan ke rozey nazil ho gaey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jiska ji chahey Aashooraa ka roza rakhey aur jiska ji chahey na rakhey .
4502,Aashooraa ke din jahiliyat mein ham roza rakhtey they lekin jab Ramazan ke rozey nazil ho gaey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jiska ji chahey Aashooraa ka roza rakhey aur jiska ji chahey na rakhey.
4503,"Ashas unke yahan aaey, wo us waqt khana kha rahe they, Ashas ne kaha ke aaj to Aashooraa ka din hai. ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke un dinon mein Aashooraa ka roza Ramazan ke rozon ke nazil honey se pahley rakha jata tha lekin jab Ramazan ke rozey ka hukm nazil hua to ye roza chhod diya gaya. aao tum bhi khaney mein Sharik ho jao."
4504,"Aashooraa ke din Quraish zamana jahiliyat mein rozey rakhtey they aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi us din roza rakhtey they. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to yahan bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us din roza rakha aur sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi iske rakhney ka hukm diya, lekin jab Ramazan ke rozon ka hukm nazil hua to Ramazan ke rozey farz ho gaey aur Aashooraa ke roza (ki farziyat) baqi nahi rahi. ab jiska ji chahey us din bhi roza rakhey aur jiska ji chahey na rakhey."
4505,"wo yun qirat kar rahe they ( وعلى الذين يطوقونه فدية طَعام مسكين ( ) تفعیل se) ( فدية طَعام مسكين )''ibne-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ye aayat mansukh nahi hai. us se murad bahut boodha mard ya bahut boodhi aurat hai. jo rozey ki taqat na rakhti ho, unhein chahiye ke har roza ke badley aik miskeen ko khana khilaa dein."
4506,unhon-ne yun qirat ki) فدية ( baghair تنوین (taa'm masaakeen) batlaya ke ye aayat mansukh hai.
4507,jab ye aayat nazil huii. ( وعلى الذين يطيقونه فدية طَعام مسكين‏ ) to jiska ji chahta tha roza chhod deta tha aur uske badley mein fidya de deta tha. yahan tak ke iske baad wali aayat nazil hui aur us ne pehli aayat ko mansukh kar diya. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke Bukair ka intiqal Yazeed se pahley ho gaya tha. Bukair jo Yazeed ke shagird they Yazeed se pahley 120 hijri mein mar gaey they.
4508,jab Ramazan ke rozey ka hukm nazil hua to musalman poorey Ramazan main apni beeviyon ke qareeb nahi jatey they aur kuchh logon ne apne ko khayanat mein mubtala kar liya tha. is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaaii علم الله أنكم كنتم تختانون أنفسكم فتاب عليكم وعفا عنكم‏''Allaah ne jaan liya ke tum apne ko khayanat mein mubtala kartey rahtey they. to us ne tum par rehmat se tawajjoh farmai aur tum ko maaf kar diyaa.''
4509,"unhon-ne aik safaid dhaagaa aur aik siyah dhaagaa liya (aur sotey huey apne sath rakh liyaa). jab raat ka kuchh hissey guzar gaya to unhon-ne usey dekha, wo donon mein tameez nahi hui. jab subah hui to arz kya : ya Rasulullah! maine apne takiye ke nichey ( safaid w siyah dhaagey rakhey they aur kuchh nahi hua) to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par bataur mazaaq ke farmaya ke phir to tumhara takiya bahut lambaa-chaudaa hoga ke subah ka safed khat aur siyah khat uske nichey aa gaya tha."
4510,maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ( aayat mein) ( الخيط الأبيض (aur ( الخيط الأسود ( se kya murad hai? kya unse murad 2 dhaagey hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhari khopdi phir to badi lambii-chaudii hogi. agar tum ne raat ko 2 dhaagey dekhey hain. phir farmaya ke unse murad raat ki siyaahii aur subah ki safedi hai.
4511,"ham se Saeed bin abi Maryam ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha ham se abu-Ghassaan Muhammad-bin Mutarrif ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha mujh se abu-Hazim Salma bin-Dinar ne bayan kya, unse Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke jab ye aayat nazil hui ke) کلوا واشربوا حتٰی یتبین لکم الخیط الابیض من الخیط الاسود (aur «من الفجر» ‘‘ ke alfaz abhi nazil nahi huey they too kaii log jab roza rakhney ka irada kartey too apney donon paon mein safaid aur siyah dhaaga baandh letey aur phir jab tuk wo donon dhaagey saaf dikhai dene na lag jatey barabar khaatey rahtey, phir Allah Taala ne ’’ «من الفجر» ‘‘ ke alfaz utaarey tab unko malum hua ke kaley dhaagey se raat aur safaid dhaagey se din murad hai."
4512,"jab log jahiliyat mein ehram baandh letey to gharon mein peechhey ki taraf se chhat par chadh kar dakhil hotey. is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki وليس البر بأن تأتوا البيوت من ظهورها ولكن البر من اتقى وأتوا البيوت من أبوابهاke ''aur ye neki nahi hai ke tum gharon mein unke peechhey ki taraf se aao, albatta neki ye hai ke koi shakhs taqwa ikhtiyar karey aur gharon mein unke darwazon se aao.''"
4513,"unke paas ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ke fitney ke zamane mein (jab un par Hajjaj zaalim ne hamla kya aur Makka ka muhaasra kya ( 2 aadmi (Alaa-bin-Araar aur Hibban salmaa) aaey aur kaha ke log aapas mein lad kar tabah ho rahe hain. aap umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke sahibzadey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahabi hain phir aap kyon khamosh hain? us fasaad ko rafa' kyon nahi kartey? ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke meri khamoshi ki wjah sirf ye hai ke Allah Taala ne mere kisi bhi bhai musalman ka khoon mujh par haram qarar diya hai. is par unhon-ne kaha : kya Allah Taala ne ye irshad nahi farmaya hai (وقاتلوهم حتى لا تكون فتنة) ke ''aur unse lado yahan tak ke fasaad baqi na rahe.'' ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke ham ( Quran ke hukm ke mutabiq ( ladey hain, yahan tak ke fitna yani shirk w kufr baqi nahi raha aur Deen khalis Allah ke liye ho gaya, lekin tum log chahtey ho ke tum isliye lado ke fitna aur fasaad paida ho aur deene-Islam zaeef ho, kaafiron ko jeet ho aur Allah ke bar-khilaf dusron ka hukm suna jaey."
4514,"aik shakhs ( hakeem ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha ke aey abu-Abdur-Rehman ! tum ko kya ho gaya hai ke tum aik saal Haj kartey ho aur aik saal Umra aur izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ke rastey mein jihad mein Sharik nahi hotey . aapko khud malum hai ke Allah Taala ne jihad ki taraf kitni raghbat dilai hai. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke mere bhatijey ! Islam ki buniyad panch chizon par hai. Allah aur uske rasool par eman lana , panch waqt ki Namaz padhnaa, Ramazan ke rozey rakhna , zakat dena aur Haj karna. '' unhon-ne kaha : aey abba Abdur-Rehman ! kitabullah mein jo Allah Taala ne irshad farmaya kya aapko wo malum nahi hai ( وإن طائفتان من المؤمنين اقتتلوا فأصلحوا بينهما‏ ) ke ''muslmaanon ki 2 jamatein agar aapas mein jang karein to unmein suleh karao . Allah Taala ke irshad ( إلى أمر الله‏ ( tak (aur Allah Taala ka irshad ke unse jang karo) yahan tak ke fasaad baqi na rahe. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) boley ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein ham ye farz anjam de chukey hain us waqt musalman bahut thodey they, kaafiron ka hujoom tha to kaafir log musalmanon ka Deen kharaab kartey they, kahin musalmanon ko mar daaltey, kahin takleef detey yahan tak ke musalman bahut ho gaey fitna jata raha."
4515,phir us shakhs ne puchha achchha ye to kaho ke Usman aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke barey main tumhara kya maanna hai. unhon-ne kaha Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ka qasoor Allah ne maaf kar diya lekin tum us maafi ko achchha nahi samajhtey ho. ab rahe Ali (Raziallahu anhu) to wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chacha zaad bhai aur aap ke daamaad they aur hath ke ishaarey se batlaya ke ye dekho unka ghar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar se mila hua hai.
4516,"aur Allah ki raah mein kharch kartey raho aur apne aapko apne hathon se halaakat mein na daalo. ''Allah ke rastey mein kharch karne ke barey mein nazil hui thii."""
4517,"mein Kab-bin-Ujra (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein us masjid mein hazir hua, unki murad Kufa ki masjid se thi aur unse rozey ke fidye ke mutaalliq poochha. unhon-ne bayan kya ke mujhey ehram main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein log le gaey aur juein (sar se) mere chehrey par gir rahi thin. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mera khayal ye nahi tha ke tum us had tak takleef mein mubtala ho gaey ho. tum koi bakri nahi muhaiya kar saktey? maine arz kya ke nahi. farmaya, phir teen din ke rozey rakh lo ya chh miskinon ko khana khilaa do, har miskeen ko aadha saa khana khilaanaa aur apna sar mundwaa lo. Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha to ye aayat khas mere barey mein nazil hui thi aur iska hukm tum sab ke liye aam hai."
4518,"(Haj mein) tamatto ka hukm Quran mein nazil hua aur ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath tamatto ke sath ( Haj ( kya, phir iske baad Quran ne us se nahi rokaa aur na us se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rokaa, yahan tak ke aap ki wafat ho gaee ( lihaza tamatto ab bhi jaaiz hai) ye to aik sahib ne apni raey se jo chaha keh diya hai."
4519,"Ukaaz , Mujanna aur zul-Majaaz zamana jahiliyat ke bazar (meley) they, isliye (Islam ke baad) Haj ke mausam mein sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne wahan karobar ko bura samjha to aayat nazil hui ( ليس عليكم جناح أن تبتغوا فضلا من ربكم‏ (ke '' tumhen is barey mein koi harj nahi ke tum apne parwardigar ke yahan se talaashe-muaash karo.'' yani mausame-Haj mein tijarat ke liye mazkura (uper zikr) mandiyon mein jao."
4520,"Quraish aur unke tareeqey ki pairwi karne waley Arab (Haj ke liye) Muzdalfa mein hi waquf kya kartey they, iska naam unhon al-Hims rakha tha aur baqi Arab Arafaat ke maidan mein waquf kartey they. phir jab Islam aaya to Allah Taala ne apne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hukm diya ke aap Arafaat mein aaein aur wahin waquf karein aur phir wahan se Muzdalfa aaein . aayat ثم أفيضوا من حيث أفاض الناس se yahi murad hai."
4521,"(jo koi tamatto karey Umra karke ehram khol daley wo ( jab tak Haj ka ehram na baandhey Baitullah ka nafl tawaaf karta rahe. jab Haj ka ehram baandhey aur Arafaat janey ko Sawar ho to Haj ke baad jo qurbani ho sakey wo karey, oont ho ya gaaey ya bakrii. in teenon mein se jo ho sakey agar qurbani muyassar na ho to teen rozey Haj ke dinon mein rakhey Arfa ke din se pahley agar aakhiri roza Arfa ke din aa jaey tab bhi koi qabahat nahi. Shahar Makka se chal kar Arafaat ko jaey wahan Asr ki Namaz se raat ka andhera honey tak thahrey, phir Arafaat se us waqt lautey jab doosrey log lautiin aur sab logon ke sath raat Muzdalfa mein guzaarey aur Allah ki yaad, takbeer aur tahleel bahut karta rahe subah honey tak. subah ko logon ke sath Muzdalfa se Mina ko lautey jaisey Allah ne farmaayaa ثم أفيضوا من حيث أفاض Naas واستغفروا الله إن الله ghafoor رحيم‏ yaanii kankariyaan maarney tak isi tarah Allah ki yad aur takbeer w tahleel kartey raho."
4522,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dua kartey they اللهم ربنا آتنا في الدنيا حسنة وفي الآخرة حسنة وقنا عذاب النار ''aey parwardigar hamaarey! ham ko duniya mein bhi behtri de aur aakhirat mein bhi behtri aur ham ko dozakh ke azab se bachaaiyo.''
4523,"Allah Taala ke nazdeek sabse zyada na-pasandida shakhs wo hai jo sakht jhagdaalu ho aur Abdullah ( Abdullah-bin Waleed Adni) ne bayan kya ke ham se Sufiyan Sory ne bayan kya, kaha mujh se ibne-Juraij ne bayan kya, unse ibne-abi-Mulaika ne, unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ( wahi hadis jo uper guzri ( ."
4524,"Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sura Yusuf ki aayat حتى إذا استيأس الرسل وظنوا أنهم قد كذبوا (main ( كذبوا ( ko zaal ki) kami ke sath qirat kya kartey they. aayat ka jo mafhoom wo murad ley saktey they liya, iske baad yun tilawat kartey حتى يقول الرسول والذين آمنوا معه متى نصر الله ألا إن نصر الله قريب phir meri mulaqat Urwa-bin-Zubair se hui, to maine unse Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki tafseer ka zikr kya."
4525,"unhon-ne bayan kya ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) to kehti thin Allah ki panah ! paighambar , to jo wada Allah ne unse kya hai usko samajhtey hain ke wo marney se pahley zaroor pura hoga. baat ye ke hai paighambaron ki aazmaish barabar hoti rahi hai. ( madad aaney mein itni der hui (ke paighambar dar gaey. aisa na ho unki ummat ke log unko jhoota samajh lein to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) is aayat sura yoosuf) ko yun padhti thiin وظنوا أنهم قد كذبوا‏"
4526,"jab ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Quran padhtey to aur koi lafz zaban par nahi latey yahan tak ke tilawat se farigh ho jatey. aik din main ( Quran Majeed lekar ( unke samney baith gaya aur unhon-ne sura al-Baqara ki tilawat shuru ki. jab is aayat (نساؤكم حرث لكم) par pahunchey to farmaya, malum hai ye aayat kis ke barey mein nazil hui thi? maine arz kya ke nahi, farmaya ke falan-falan cheez, yani aurat se peechhey ki taraf se hambistari karne ke barey mein nazil hui thi aur phir tilawat karne lagey."
4527,"aayat ( فأتوا حرثكم أنى شئتم‏ ( ''so tum apne khet mein aao jis tarah chaaho.'' ke barey mein farmaya ke (peechhey se bhi) aa sakta hai. aur is hadis ko Muhammad-bin Yahya-bin-Saeed bin qattaan ne bhi apne walid se, unhon-ne Ubaidullah se, unhon-ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai."
4528,"Yahudi kehtey they ke agar aurat se ham-bistarii ke liye koi peechhey se aayega to bachcha bhengaa paida hoga. is par ye aayat nazil huii (نساؤكم حرث لكم فأتوا حرثكم أنى شئتم‏) ke '' tumhari beeviyan tumhari kheti hain, so apne khet mein aao jidhar se chaaho.''"
4529,"meri aik behan thin. unko unke agley khawind ne nikah ka paigham diya. (doosri sanad) aur Ibrahim bin tahmaan ne bayan kya, unse Yunus ne, unse imam Hasan Basri ne aur unse Ma'qil-bin-Yasaar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya. (teesrii sanad) aur imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke ham se abu-Ma'mar ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Abdul-Waris ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Yunus ne bayan kya aur unse imam Hasan Basri ne ke Ma'qil-bin-Yasaar (Raziallahu anhu) ki behan ko unke shauhar ne talaaq de di thi lekin jab iddat guzar gaee aur talaaq baain ho gaee to unhon-ne phir unke liye paighaame-nikaah bhejaa. Maaqil (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par inkar kya, magar aurat chahti thi to ye aayat nazil huii ( فلا تعضلوهن أن ينكحن أزواجهن‏ ) ke ''tum unhein us se mat roko ke wo apne pahley shauhar se dobara nikah karein.''"
4530,maine aayat ( والذين يتوفون منكم ويذرون أزواجا‏ ( yani ''aur tum mein se jo log wafat pa jatey hain aur beeviyan chhod jatey hain.'' ke mutaalliq Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se arz kya ke us aayat ko dusri aayat ne mansukh kar diya hai. isliye aap usey (musahaf mein) na likhein ya (ye kaha ke) na rehney dein. is par Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke betey! main (qur'aan ka ( koi harf uski jagah se nahi hata sakta.
4531,"aayat ( والذين يتوفون منكم ويذرون أزواجا‏ ( ''aur tum mein se jo log wafat pa jatey hain aur beeviyan chhod jatey hain.'' ke barey mein) zamana jahiliyat ki tarah) kaha ke iddat (yani char mahiney das din ki) thi jo shauhar ke ghar aurat ko guzaarnii zaroori thi. phir Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki والذين يتوفون منكم ويذرون أزواجا وصية لأزواجهم متاعا إلى الحول غير إخراج فإن خرجن فلا جناح عليكم فيما فعلن في أنفسهن من معروف‏''aur jo log tum mein se wafat pa jayen aur beeviyan chhod jayen unko chahiye ke apni beeviyon ke haq mein nafa uthaney ki wasiiyat (kar jaaein) ke wo aik saal tak ghar se na nikaalii jaaein, lekin agar wo (khud) nikal jayen to koi gunah tum par nahi. agar wo dastoor ke muwafiq apne liye koi kaam karein.'' farmaya ke Allah Taala ne aurat ke liye saat (7) mahiney aur bees din wasiiyat ke qarar diye ke agar wo us muddat mein chahey to apne liye wasiiyat ke mutabiq (shauhar ke ghar mein hi) thahrey aur agar chahey to kahin aur chali jaey ke agar aisi aurat kahin aur chali jaey to tumharey haq mein koi gunah nahi. to iddat ke din to wahi hain jinhein guzaarnaa is par zaroori hai (yani char mahiney das din). Shabal ne kaha ibne-abii-Najeeh ne Mujahid se aisa hi naql kya hai aur ataa-bin-Abii Ribah ne kaha ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, is aayat ne us rasm ko mansukh kar diya ke aurat apne khawind ke ghar walon ke paas iddat guzaarey. is aayat ke mutabiq aurat ko ikhtiyar mila jahan chahey wahan iddat guzaarey aur Allah paak ke qaul ( ghair ikhraaj (ka yahi matlab hai. Ata ne kaha, aurat agar chahey to apne khawind ke ghar walon mein iddat guzaarey aur khawind ki wasiiyat ke muwafiq usi ke ghar mein rahe aur agar chahey to wahan se nikal jaey kyonke Allah Taala ne farmaya ( فلا جناح عليكم فيما فعلن‏ ( ''agar wo nikal jayen to dastoor ke muwafiq apne haq mein jo baat karein usmein koi gunah tum par na hoga.'' Ata ne kaha ke phir meeraas ka hukm nazil hua jo sura Nisa mein hai aur us ne (aurat ke liye) ghar mein rakhney ke hukm ko mansukh qarar diya. ab aurat jahan chahey iddat guzaar sakti hai. usey makan ka kharcha dena zaroori nahi aur Muhammad-bin Yusuf ne riwayat kya, unse Warqaa-bin-Amr ne bayan kya, unse ibne-abii-Najeeh ne aur unse Mujahid ne, yahi qaul bayan kya aur farzandaane-ibne-abii-Najeeh se naql kya, unse Ataa-bin-abii-Ribaah ne bayan kya aur unse Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke us aayat ne sirf shauhar ke ghar mein iddat ke hukm ko mansukh qarar diya hai. ab wo jahan chahey iddat guzaar sakti hai. jaisa ke Allah Taala ke irshad (ghair ikhraaj) wghaira se Sabit hai."
4532,"mein Ansar ki aik majlis mein hazir hua. badey-badey Ansari wahan maujood they aur Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-abii-Laila bhi maujood they. maine wahan Sabeeaa-binte-Haaris ke baab se mutaalliq Abdullah-bin Utba ki hadis ka zikr kya. Abdur-Rehman ne kaha lekin Abdullah-bin Utba ke chacha (Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) aisa nahi kehtey they. (Muhammad-bin Sirin ne kaha) ke maine kaha ke phir to maine aik aisey buzurg Abdullah-bin Utba ke mutaalliq jhoot bolney mein dilairi ki hai ke jo Kufa mein abhi zinda maujood hain. meri awaz buland ho gaee thi. Ibne-Sirin ne kaha ke phir jab main bahar nikla to rastey mein Maalik-bin-Aamir ya Maalik-bin-Auf se mulaqat ho gaee. ( rawi ko shak hai ke ye ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke rafeeqon mein se they) maine unse puchha ke jis aurat ke shauhar ka intiqal ho jaey aur wo hamal se ho to ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) uski iddat ke mutaalliq kya fatwa detey they? unhon-ne kaha ke ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey they ke tum log us haamla par sakhti ke mutaalliq kyon sochtey ho is par aasani nahi kartey ( usko lambi ( iddat ka hukm detey ho. sura Nisa chhoti ( sura talaaq) lambi sura Nisa ke baad nazil hui hai aur Ayub sakhtiyan ne bayan kya, unse Muhammad-bin Sirin ne ke main abu-Atiya Malik bin Aamir se mila."
4533,"(doosri sanad) imam Bukhari ne kaha ke mujh se Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Basheer bin Hakam ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Yahya-bin-Saeed qattaan ne bayan kya, unse Hisham bin Hassan ne, kaha ke mujh se Muhammad-bin Sirin ne bayan kya, unse Ubaida-bin Amr ne aur unse Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Khandaq ki jang ke mauqe par farmaya tha, un kuffaar ne hamein darmyani Namaz nahi padhney di, yahan tak ke suraj ghurub ho gaya, Allah unki qabron aur gharon ko ya unke peton ko aag se bhar de. qabron aur gharon ya peton ke lafzon mein shak Yahya-bin-Saeed rawi ki taraf se hai."
4534,"pahley ham Namaz padhtey huey baat bhi kar liya kartey they, koi bhi shakhs apne doosrey bhai se apni kisi zarurat ke liye baat kar leta tha. yahan tak ke ye aayat nazil huii حافظوا على الصلوات والصلاة الوسطى وقوموا لله قانتين‏''sab hi namazon ki pabandi rakho aur khas taur par beech wali Namaz ki aur Allah ke samney farmaan-bardaaron ki tarah khadey hua karo.'' is aayat ke zariey hamein Namaz mein chup rehney ka hukm diya gaya."
4535,"jab Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se Namaz khof ke mutaalliq puchha jata to wo farmatey ke imam musalmanon ki aik jamat ko lekar khud aagey badhey aur unhein aik rakaat Namaz padhaaey . us doran mein musalmanon ki dusri jamat unke aur dushman ke darmyan mein rahe. ye log Namaz mein abhi Sharik na hon, phir jab imam un logon ko aik rakaat padha chukey jo pahley iske sath they, to ab ye log peechhey hat jayen aur unki jagah ley lein, jinhoney ab tak Namaz nahi padhi hai, lekin ye log salam na pherein . ab wo log aagey badhiin jinhoney Namaz nahi padhi hai aur imam unhein bhi aik rakaat Namaz padhaaey , ab imam 2 rakaat padh chikney ke baad Namaz se farigh ho chuka . phir donon jamatein (jinhon ne alag alag imam ke sath eik-eik rakaat Namaz padhi thi) apni baqi eik-eik rakaat ada kar lein. jabke imam apni Namaz se farigh ho chuka hai. is tarah donon jamaton ki 2-2 rakaat poori ho jaeyngi . lekin agar khof is se bhi zyada hai to har shakhs tanha Namaz padh ley, paidal ho ya sawaar, qible ki taraf rukh ho ya na ho. Imam Malik ne bayan kya, unse Naafe ne ke mujh ko yaqin hai ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye baatein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sun kar hi bayan ki hain."
4536,"ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke sura al-Baqara ki aayat ( والذين يتوفون منكم ويذرون أزواجا‏ ( yani ''jo log tum mein se wafat pa jayen aur beeviyan chhod jaaein. ''Allah taala ke farman ( ghair ikhraaj ( tak ko dusri aayat ne mansukh kar diya hai. usko aap ne musahaf mein kyon likhwaayaa , chhod kyon nahi diya? unhon-ne kaha : mere bhateejey! mein kisi aayat ko iske thikaaney se badalney wala nahi. ye Humaid ne kaha ya kuchh aisa hi jawab diya."
4537,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' shak karne ka hamein Ibrahim se zyada haq hai, jab unhon-ne arz kya tha ke aey mere rab! mujhey dikhaa de ke to mardon ko kis tarah zinda karega, Allah ki taraf se irshad hua, kya tujh ko yaqin nahi hai? kaha yaqin zaroor hai, lekin maine ye darkhaast isliye ki hai ke mere dil ko aur itminan hasil ho jaaey.''"
4538,"aik din umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab se malum kya ke aap log jantey ho ye aayat kis silsiley mein nazil hui hai ( أيود أحدكم أن تكون له جنة‏ )''kya tum mein se koi ye pasand karta hai ke iska aik baagh ho.'' sab ne kaha ke Allah zyada jaanney wala hai. ye sun kar umr (Raziallahu anhu) bahut khafa ho gaey aur kaha, saaf jawab dein ke aap logon ko is silsiley mein kuchh malum hai ya nahi. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ameerul-momineen ! mere dil mein aik baat aati hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : betey! tumhiin kaho aur apne ko haqeer na samjho. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke usmein amal ki misal bayan ki gaee hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne poochha, kaisey amal ki? Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke amal ki. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ye aik maaldaar shakhs ki misal hai jo Allah ki itaat mein nek amal karta rehta hai. phir Allah shaitan ko is par ghalib kar deta hai, wo gunahon mein masroof ho jata hai aur uske agley nek aamaal sab ghaarat ho jatey hain."
4539,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''miskeen wo nahi hai jisey aik ya 2 khajoor , aik ya do luqmey dar badr liye phirein, balke miskeen wo hai jo maangney se bachta rahe aur agar tum daleel chaho to (qur'aan se) us aayat ko padh lo (لا يسألون Naas إلحافا) ke ''wo logon se chimat kar nahi maangtey .''"
4540,jab sood ke silsiley mein sura al-Baqara ki aakhiri aayatein nazil huin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein padh kar logon ko sunaya aur uske baad sharab ki tijarat bhi haram qarar paaii.
4541,jab sura al-Baqara ki aakhiri aayatein nazil huin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey aur masjid mein unhein padh kar sunaya iske baad sharab ki tijarat haram ho gaee.
4542,jab sura al-Baqara ki aakhiri aayatein nazil huin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein masjid mein padh kar sunaya aur sharab ki tijarat haram qarar di gaee.
4543,jab sura al-Baqara ki aakhiri aayatein nazil hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur hamein padh kar sunaya phir sharab ki tijarat haram kar di.
4544,aakhiri aayat jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par nazil hui wo sood ki aayat thi.
4545,aayat ( وإن تبدوا ما في أنفسكم أو تخفوه‏ ( ''aur jo kuchh tumharey nafson ke andar hai agar tum unko zahir karo ya chhipaaey rakho.'' aakhir tak mansukh ho gaee thi.
4546,wo ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) hain. unhon-ne aayat ( إن تبدوا ما في أنفسكم أو تخفوه‏ ) ke mutaalliq batlaya ke is aayat ko iske baad ki aayat لا يكلف الله نفسا إلا وسعها ne mansukh kar diya hai.
4547,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us aayat ki tilawat ki هو الذي أنزل عليك الكتاب منه آيات محكمات هن أم الكتاب وأخر متشابهات فأما الذين في قلوبهم زيغ فيتبعون ما تشابه منه ابتغاء الفتنة وابتغاء تأويله‏ yaanii ''wo wahi Allah hai jisne tujh par kitab utari hai, usmein mohkam aayatein hain aur wahi kitab ka asl daro-madar hain aur dusri aayatein mutshaabe hain. so wo log jinke dilon mein chidpan hai. wo uske usi hissey ke peechhey lag jatey hain jo mutshaabe hain, fitney ki talash mein aur uski ghalat taaweel ki talash mein.'' aakhir aayat ( أولو الألباب‏ ( tak. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum aisey logon ko dekho jo mutshaabe aayaton ke peechhey padey huey hon to yad rakho ke ye wahi log hain jinka Allah Taala ne ( aayat bula mein) zikr farmaya hai. isliye unse bachtey raho."
4548,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke har bachcha jab paida hota hai to shaitan usey paida hotey hi chhootaa hai, jis se wo bachcha chillaataa hai, siwa Maryam aur unke betey (Eisaa (Alaihissalam) ( ke. phir Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke agar tumhara ji chahey to ye aayat padh lo ( وإني أعيذها بك وذريتها من الشيطان الرجيم ( ye kalima Maryam (Alaihissalam) ki maan ne kaha tha, Allah ne unki dua qabool ki aur Maryam aur Esa (Alaihissalam) ko shaitan ke hath lagaaney se bacha liya."
4549,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jis shakhs ne isliye qism khaaii ke kisi musalman ka maal (jhoot bol kar wo) mar ley to jab wo Allah se milega , Allah Taala is par bahut hi ghussa hoga, phir Allah Taala ne aap ke us farman ki tasdeeq mein ye aayat nazil ki إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا أولئك لا خلاق لهم في الآخرة '' beshak jo log Allah ke ahad aur apni qasmon ko thodi qeemat par bechtey hain, ye wahi log hain jinke liye aakhirat mein koi bhalai nahi hai.'' aakhir aayat tak. abu-Waeil ne bayan kya ke Ashas bin Qais Kandi (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laey aur puchha : abu-Abdur-Rehman ( Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ne aap logon se koi hadis bayan ki hai? ham ne bataya ke yahaan, is-is tarah se hadis bayan ki hai. Ashas (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par kaha ke ye aayat to mere hi barey mein nazil hui thi. mere aik chacha ke betey ki zameen mein mera aik kunwaan tha (ham donon ka is barey mein jhagdaa hua aur muqaddima Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh hua to (aap ne mujh se farmaya ke to gawah pesh kar ya phir uski qism par faisla hoga. maine kaha phir to ya Rasulullah wo ( jhooti ( qism kha lega . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs jhooti qism isliye khaaey ke iske zariey kisi musalman ka maal ley aur uski niyat buri ho to wo Allah Taala se us haalat mein milega ke Allah is par bahut hi ghazabnaak hoga."
4550,"rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jis shakhs ne isliye qism khaaii ke kisi musalman ka maal (jhoot bol kar wo) mar ley to jab wo Allah se milega , Allah Taala is par bahut hi ghussa hoga, phir Allah Taala ne aap ke us farman ki tasdeeq mein ye aayat nazil ki إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا أولئك لا خلاق لهم في الآخرة '' beshak jo log Allah ke ahad aur apni qasmon ko thodi qeemat par bechtey hain, ye wahi log hain jinke liye aakhirat mein koi bhalai nahi hai.'' aakhir aayat tak. abu-Waeil ne bayan kya ke Ashas bin Qais Kandi (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laey aur puchha : abu-Abdur-Rehman ( Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ne aap logon se koi hadis bayan ki hai? ham ne bataya ke yahaan, is-is tarah se hadis bayan ki hai. Ashas (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par kaha ke ye aayat to mere hi barey mein nazil hui thi. mere aik chacha ke betey ki zameen mein mera aik kunwaan tha (ham donon ka is barey mein jhagdaa hua aur muqaddima Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh hua to (aap ne mujh se farmaya ke to gawah pesh kar ya phir uski qism par faisla hoga. maine kaha phir to ya Rasulullah wo ( jhooti ( qism kha lega . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs jhooti qism isliye khaaey ke iske zariey kisi musalman ka maal ley aur uski niyat buri ho to wo Allah Taala se us haalat mein milega ke Allah is par bahut hi ghazabnaak hoga."
4551,"aik shakhs ne bazar mein saman bechtey huey qism khaaii ke falan shakhs us saman ka itna rupya de raha tha, halanke kisi ne itni qeemat nahi lagai thi, balke iska maqsad ye tha ke is tarah kisi musalman ko wo dhokaa de kar usey thag ley to is par ye aayat nazil huii ( إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا‏ ) ke '' beshak jo log Allah ke ahad aur apni qasmon ko thodi qeemat par bechtey hain.'' aakhir aayat tak."
4552,"2 auratein kisi ghar ya hujre mein baith kar mozey banaya karti thin. unmein se aik aurat bahar niklii. uske hath mein mozey seeney ka suwaa chubho diya gaya tha. us ne dusri aurat par dawa kya. ye muqaddima Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya to unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke agar sirf dawa ki wjah se logon ka mutalba maan liya janey lagey to bahut son ka khoon aur maal barbad ho jaeyga jab gawah nahi hai to dusri aurat ko jis par ye ilzam hai, Allah se daraao aur uske samney ye aayat padho ( إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله‏ ) chunaanche jab logon ne usey Allah se daraayaa to usne iqrar kar liya. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai, qism is par hai jis par daawaa kiya gaya hai. agar wo jhooti qism kha kar kisi ka maal hadap karega to usko us dhamki ke barabar qarar diya jaeyga jo aayat mein bayan ki gaee hai."
4553,"jis muddat mein mere aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke darmyan suleh (Suleh Hudaibiya ke muaahida ke mutabiq ( thi, mein (safar tijarat par Sham (Syria) mein) gaya hua tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka khat Hiraql ke paas pahuncha. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Dahiya Kalbi (Raziallahu anhu) wo khat laey they aur azeem Basra ke hawale kar diya tha aur Hiraql ke paas usi se pahuncha tha. Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Hiraql ne puchha kya hamarey hudood saltanat mein us shakhs ki qaum ke bhi kuchh log hain jo Nabi honey ka dawedar hai? darbaariyon ne bataya ke ji haan maujood hain. Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir mujhey Quraish ke chand doosrey aadmiyon ke sath bulaya gaya. ham Hiraql ke darbar mein dakhil huey aur uske samney hamein bitha diya gaya. us ne poochha, tum logon mein us shakhs se zyada qaribi kon hai jo Nabi honey ka dawa karta hai? Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine kaha ke main zyada qareeb hun. ab darbaariyon ne mujhey badshah ke bilkul qareeb bitha diya aur mere doosrey sathiyon ko mere peechhey bitha diya. iske baad tarjuman ko bulaya aur us se Hiraql ne kaha ke unhein bataao ke main us shakhs ke barey main tum se kuchh sawalat karunga, jo Nabi honey ka dawedar hai, agar ye (yani Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu)) jhoot boley to tum iske jhoot ko zahir kar dena. Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan tha ke Allah ki qism ! agar mujhey iska khof na hota ke mere sathi kahin mere mutaalliq jhoot bolnaa naql na kar dein to main (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke barey mein) zaroor jhoot boltaa . phir Hiraql ne apne tarjuman se kaha ke us se poochho ke jisne Nabi honey ka dawa kya hai wo apne nasb mein kaisey hain? Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ne batlaya ke unka nasb ham mein bahut hi izzat wala hai. us ne puchha kya unke bap dada mein koi badshah bhi hua hai? bayan kya ke maine kaha, nahi. us ne poochha, tum ne dawa-e-nabwooat se pahley kabhi un par jhoot ki tohmat lagai thi? maine kaha nahi. puchha unki pairwi muazzaz log zyada kartey hain ya kamzor ? maine kaha ke qaum ke kamzor log zyada hain. us ne poochha, unke manney walon mein zyadti hoti rehti hai ya kami ? maine kaha ke nahi balke zyadti hoti rehti hai. puchha kabhi aisa bhi koi waqia pesh aaya hai ke koi shakhs unke Deen ko qabool karne ke baad phir unse bd-gumaan ho kar unse phir gaya ho? maine kaha aisa bhi kabhi nahi hua. us ne poochha, tum ne kabhi unse jang bhi ki hai? maine kaha ke haan. us ne poochha, tumhari unke sath jang ka kya nateeja raha ? maine kaha ke hamari jang ki misal aik dol ki hai ke kabhi unke hath main aur kabhi hamarey hath mein. us ne poochha, kabhi unhon-ne tumharey sath koi dhokaa bhi kiya? maine kaha ke ab tak to nahi kya, lekin aaj kal bhi hamara unse aik muaahida chal raha hai, nahi kaha ja sakta ke usmein unka tarze-amal kya rahega. Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Allah ki qism ! is jumle ke siwa aur koi baat mein is poori guftgu main apni taraf se nahi mila sakaa, phir us ne puchha is se pahley bhi ye dawa tumharey yahan kisi ne kya tha? maine kaha ke nahi. iske baad Hiraql ne apne tarjuman se kaha, us se kaho ke maine tum se Nabi ke nasb ke barey mein puchha to tum ne bataya ke wo tum logon mein baa-izzat aur oonchey nasb ke samjhey jatey hain, anbiya ka bhi yahi haal hai. unki bea'sat hamesha qaum ke saahibe-hasab w nasb khandan mein hoti hai aur maine tum se puchha tha ke kya koi unke bap daadon mein badshah guzra hai, to tum ne iska inkar kya main us se us faisla par pahuncha ke agar unke bap daadon mein koi badshah guzra hota to mumkin tha ke wo apni khaandaanii saltanat ko is tarah wapas lena chahtey hon aur maine tum se unki ittaba (pairvi) karne walon ke mutaalliq puchha ke aaya wo qaum ke kamzor log hain ya ashraaf, to tum ne bataya ke kamzor log unki pairwi karne walon main (zyaada) hain. yahi tabqa hamesha se anbiya ki ittaba (pairvi) karta raha hai aur maine tum se puchha tha ke kya tum ne dawa-e-nabwooat se pahley un par jhoot ka kabhi shuba kya tha, to tum ne iska bhi inkar kya. maine us se ye samjha ke jis shakhs ne logon ke maamle mein kabhi jhoot na bola ho, wo Allah ke mamley mein kis tarah jhoot bol dega aur maine tum se puchha tha ke unke Deen ko qabool karne ke baad phir unse bd-gumaan ho kar koi shakhs unke Deen se kabhi phiraa bhi hai, to tum ne iska bhi inkar kya. eman ka yahi asar hota hai jab wo dil ki gahraaiyon mein utar jaey. maine tum se puchha tha ke unke manney walon ki tadaad badhtii rehti hai ya kam hoti hai, to tum ne bataya ke unmein izafa hi hota hai, eman ka yahi mamla hai, yahan tak ke wo kamaal ko pahunch jaey. maine tum se puchha tha ke kya tum ne kabhi unse jang bhi ki hai? to tum ne bataya ke jang ki hai aur tumharey darmyan ladai ka nateeja aisa raha hai ke kabhi tumharey haq main aur kabhi unke haq mein. anbiya ka bhi yahi mamla hai, unhein aazmaish mein daala jata hai aur aakhir anjam unhiin ke haq mein hota hai aur maine tum se puchha tha ke usne tumharey sath kabhi khilaf ahad bhi mamla kya hai to tum ne us se bhi inkar kya. anbiya kabhi ahad ke khilaf nahi kartey aur maine tum se puchha tha ke kya tumharey yahan is tarah ka dawa pahley bhi kisi ne kya tha to tum ne kaha ke pahley kisi ne is tarah ka dawa nahi kya, main us se is faisley par pahuncha ke agar kisi ne tumharey yahan is se pahley is tarah ka dawa kya hota to ye kaha ja sakta tha ke ye bhi usi ki naql kar rahe hain. bayan kya ke phir Hiraql ne puchha wo tumhen kin chizon ka hukm detey hain? maine kaha Namaz , zakat , sila rehmii aur paakdaamnii kaa. aakhir usne kaha ke jo kuchh tum ne bataya hai agar wo sahi hai to yaqinan wo Nabi hain iska ilm to mujhey bhi tha ke unki nabwooat ka zamana qareeb hai lekin ye khayal na tha ke wo tumhari qaum mein hongey. agar mujhey un tak pahunch sakney ka yaqin hota to main zaroor unse mulaqat karta aur agar main unki khidmat mein hota to unke qadmon ko dhota aur unki hukumat mere un 2 qadmon tak pahunch kar rahegi . Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir us ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka khat mangwaya aur usey padha , usmein ye likha hua thaa, Allaah, Rehmaan, Rahim ke naam se shuru karta hoon. Allaah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se azeem Rome (mojooda Itly) Hiraql ki taraf, salaamatii ho is par jo hidayat ki ittaba (pairvi) kare. ammaa ba'd! main tumhen Islam ki taraf bulata hun, Islam lao to salamati paogey aur Islam lao to Allah tumhen dohra ajr dega. lekin tum ne agar munh modaa to tumhari riaya (ke kufr ka baar bhi sab ( tum par hoga aur aey kitab waalo! aik aisi baat ki taraf aa jao jo ham main aur tum mein barabar hai, wo ye ke ham siwaey Allah ke aur kisi ki ibadat na karein. Allah Taala ke farmaan (اشهدوا بأنا مسلمون) tak.jab Hiraql khat padh chuka to darbar mein bada shor barpa ho gaya aur phir hamein darbar se bahar kar diya gaya. bahar aa kar maine apne sathiyon se kaha ke ibne-abii-Kabsha ka mamla to ab us had tak pahunch chuka hai ke mulk bani-asfar ( Hiraql ( bhi unse darney laga. is waqia ke baad mujhey yaqin ho gaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghalib aa kar rahengey aur aakhir Allah Taala ne Islam ki roshni mere dil mein bhi daal hi di. Zohri ne kaha ke phir Hiraql ne Rome (mojooda Itly) ke sardaaron ko bula kar aik khas kamrey mein jama kya, phir unse kaha aey roomiyon ! kya tum hamesha ke liye apni falaah aur bhalai chahtey ho aur ye ke tumhara mulk tumharey hi hath mein rahe (agar tum aisa chahtey ho to Islam qabool kar lo ( rawi ne bayan kya ke ye suntey hi wo sab wahshii janwaron ki tarah darwazey ki taraf bhaagey, dekha to darwaza band tha, phir Hiraql ne sab ko apne paas bulaya ke unhein mere paas lao aur unse kaha ke maine to tumhen aazmaya tha ke tum apne Deen mein kitney pukhta ho, ab maine us cheez ka mushaahida kar liya jo mujhey pasand thi. chunanche sab darbaariyon ne usey sajda kya aur us se razi ho gaey."
4554,"Madina mein abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas Ansar mein sabse zyada khajooron ke darakht they aur beerhaa ka baagh apni tamam jaaidaad mein unhein sabse zyada azeez tha. ye baagh masjide-Nabawi ke samney hi tha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi usmein tashrif ley jatey aur uske meethey aur umda pani ko peetey, phir jab aayat ( لن تنالوا البر حتى تنفقوا مما تحبون‏ ) ''jab tak tum apni azeez tareen chizon ko na kharch karogey neki ke martaba ko na pahunch sakogey.'' nazil hui to abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) uthey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah! Allah Taala farmata hai ke jab tak tum apni azeez chizon ko kharch na karogey neki ke martabe ko na pahunch sakogey aur mera sabse zyada azeez maal beerhaa hai aur ye Allah ki raah mein sadqa hai. Allah hi se main iske sawab w ajr ki tawaqqoa' rakhta hun, to ya Rasulullah ! jahan aap munasib samjhein usey istemal karein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke khub ye faanii hi daulat thi, ye faanii hi daulat thi. jo kuchh tum ne kaha hai wo maine sun liya aur mera khayal hai ke tum apne azeez w aqrabaa ko usey de do. abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main aisa hi karunga, ya Rasulullah! chunanche unhon-ne wo baagh apne azeezon aur apne nataa walon mein baant diya. Abdullah-bin Yusuf aur Rooh bin Ubada ne (ذلك مال رايح) ( ربح ( se) bayan kya hai. yani ye maal bahut nafa dene wala hai. mujh se Yahya-bin-Yahya ne bayan kya, kaha ke maine Imam Malik ke samney ( مال رايح) ( rawahu ( se) padha tha."
4555,phir abu-Talha ne wo baagh Hassan aur abi (Raziallahu anhu) ko de diya tha. main un donon se unka zyada qaribi tha lekin mujhey nahi diya.
4556,"kuchh Yahudi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas apne qabeele ke aik mard aur aik aurat ko lekar aaey, jinhoney zina kya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse puchha agar tum mein se koi zina karey to tum usko kya saza detey ho? unhon-ne kaha ke ham iska munh kala karke usey maartey peet'tey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya Taurait mein rajm (sangsaar) ka hukm nahi hai? unhon-ne kaha ke ham ne Taurait mein rajm (sangsaar) ka hukm nahi dekha. Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) boley ke tum jhoot bol rahe ho, Taurait lao aur usey padho, agar tum sachey ho. (jab Taurait laai gai) to unke aik bahut badey mudarris ne jo unhein Taurait ka dars diya karta tha, aayat rajm (sangsaar) par apni hatheli rakh li aur us se pahley aur uske baad ki ibaarat padhney laga aur aayat rajm (sangsaar) nahi padhta tha. Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne iske hath ko aayat rajm (sangsaar) se hata diya aur us se puchha ke ye kya hai? jab yahudiyon ne dekha to kehney lagey ke ye aayat rajm (sangsaar) hai. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya aur un donon ko masjide-Nabawi ke qareeb hi jahan janazey la kar rakhey jatey they, rajm (sangsaar) kar diya gaya. maine dekha ke us aurat ka sathi aurat ko patthar se bachaney ke liye is par jhuk jhuk padta tha."
4557,aayat ( كنتم خير أمة أخرجت للناس‏ ) ''tum log logon ke liye sab logon se behtar ho ''aur kaha unko gardanon mein zanjeerein daal kar) ladai mein giraftaar karke ( latey ho phir wo Islam mein dakhil ho jatey hain.
4558,"ham se Ali-bin-Abdullaah madeenii ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne bayan kya, kaha Amr-bin-Dinar ne kaha, unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke hamaarey hi barey mein ye aayat nazil hui thi, jab ham se do jamatein is ka khayal kar baithi thin ke himmat haar dein, halanke Allah donon ka madadgaar tha. Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke ham do jamatein bano Harisa aur bano Salma they. halanke is aayat mein hamarey bodeypan ka zikr hai, magar ham ko ye pasand nahi ke ye aayat na utartii kyonke is mein ye zikr kiya gaya hai ke in donon girohon ka madadgaar (sarparast) hai."
4559,"aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap ne fajr ki dusri rakaat ke rukoo se sar utha kar ye baddua ki. ''aey Allah ! falan , falan aur falan kaafir par laanat kar. ye baddua aap ne ( سمع الله لمن حمده (aur ( ربنا ولك الحمد (ke baad ki thi. is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat utari ( ليس لك من الأمر شىء‏ ( '' aapko usmein koi dakhal nahi. '' aakhir aayat ( فإنهم ظالمون‏ ( tak. is riwayat ko Ishaq bin Rashid ne Zohri se naql kya hai."
4560,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab kisi par baddua karna chahtey ya kisi ke liye dua karna chahtey to rukoo ke baad kartey سمع الله لمن حمده ، Mina اللهم ربنا لك الحمد ke ba'd. kabhi-kabhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye dua bhi ki ''aey Allah ! Waleed bin Waleed, Salma bin Hisham aur Ayash bin abi Rabee ko nijat de, aey Allaah! Muzar walon ko sakhti ke sath pakad ley aur unmein aisi qahat saalii laa, jaisi Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke zamaney mein hui thii.'' Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) buland awaz se ye dua kartey aur aap namaze-Fajr ki kuchh rakaat mein ye dua kartey. aey Allaah, falan aur falan ko apni rehmat se door kar de. Arab ke chand khas qabaayel ke haq mein aap (ye baddua kartey they) yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne aayat nazil ki ( ليس لك من الأمر شىء‏ (ke ''aapko is baat mein koi dakhal nahi.''"
4561,"Uhud ki ladai main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (teerandaazon ke) paidal dastey par Abdullaah-bin-Jubair (Raziallahu anhu) ko afsar muqarrar kya tha, phir bahut se musalmanon ne peeth pher li, aayat ( فذاك إذ يدعوهم الرسول في أخراهم ( ''aur rasool tum ko pukar rahe they tumharey peechhey se.'' main usi ki taraf ishara hai, us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath baara sahaabiyon ke siwa aur koi maujood na tha."
4562,"abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, Uhud ki ladai mein jab ham saf baandhey khadey they, to ham par ghunoodgi taarii ho gaee thi. abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke kaifiyat ye ho gaee thi ke neend se meri talwaar hath se baar-baar girtii aur main usey uthaataa."
4563,"kalima ( حسبنا الله ونعم الوكيل‏ ( Ibrahim ne kaha tha, us waqt jab unko aag mein daala gaya tha aur yahi kalima Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us waqt kaha tha jab logon ne musalmanon ko daraane ke liye kaha tha ke logon (yani Quraish ( ne tumharey khilaf bada saamaane-jang ikattha kar rakha hai, unse daro lekin is baat ne un musalmanon ka ( josh ( eman aur badha diya aur ye musalman boley ke hamarey liye Allah kafi hai aur wahi behtreen kaam banaaney wala hai."
4564,jab Ibrahim ko aag mein daala gaya to aakhiri kalima jo aap ki zaban Mubarak se nikla ( حسبي الله ونعم الوكيل‏) tha yani meri madad ke liye Allah kafi hai aur wahi behtreen kaam banaaney wala hai.
4565,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jisey Allah Taala ne maal diya aur phir usne uski zakat nahi ada ki to (aakhirat mein) iska maal bahut hi zyada zahreeley sanp bin kar jiski aankhon ke uper 2 nuqtey hongey. uski gardan mein tauq ki tarah pehna diya jaeyga phir wo sanp iske donon jabdon ko pakad kar kahega ke main hi tera maal hun, main hi tera khazaana hun, phir aap ne us aayat ki tilaawat ( wla يحسبن الذين يبخلون بما آتاهم الله من فضله‏ ) ki ''aur jo log ke us maal mein kanjoosii kartey hain jo Allah ne unhein apne Fazal se de rakha hai, wo ye na samjhein ke ye maal unke haq mein behtar hai.'' aakhir tak."
4566,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik gadhey ki pusht par fidak ki bani hui aik motii chadar rakhney ke baad sawar huey aur Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ko apne peechhey bithaayaa. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) banu-Haaris bin khazraj mein Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ki mizaaj pursi ke liye tashrif ley ja rahe they. ye jange-badr se pahley ka waqia hai. raaste mein aik majlis se aap guzrey jis mein Abdullah-bin-Ubai ibne-salool ( munafiq ( bhi maujood tha, ye Abdullah-bin-Ubai ke zahiri Islam laney se bhi pahley ka qissa hai. majlis mein musalman aur mushrekeen yani but parast aur Yahudi sab hi tarah ke log they, unhein mein Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. sawari ki) taapon se gard udii aur) majlis walon par padi to Abdullah-bin-Ubai ne chadar se apni naak band kar li aur bataur tahqeer kehney laga ke ham par gard na udaao, itney mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi qareeb pahunch gaey aur unhein salam kya, phir aap sawari se utar gaey aur majlis walon ko Allah ki taraf bulaya aur Quran ki aayatein padh kar sunain . is par Abdullaah-bin-Ubaii-ibne-salool kehney laga, jo kalam aap ne padh kar sunaya hai, us se umda koi kalam nahi ho sakta. agarche ye kalam bahut achchha, phir bhi hamari majlison mein aa aa kar aap hamein takleef na diya karein, apne ghar baithein , agar koi aap ke paas jaey to usey apni baatein sunaya karein. (ye sun kar) Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, zaroor ya Rasulullah ! aap hamari majlison mein tashrif laya karein, ham isi ko pasand kartey hain. iske baad muslmaan, mushrekeen aur Yahudi aapas mein aik doosrey ko bura bhala kehney lagey aur qareeb tha ke fasaad aur ladai tak ki naubat pahunch jati lekin aap ne unhein khamosh aur thanda kar diya aur aakhir sab log khamosh ho gaey, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni sawari par Sawar ho kar wahan se chaley aaey aur Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan tashrif ley gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi iska zikr kya ke Sad ! tum ne nahi suna, abu-Hubaab, aap ki murad Abdullah-bin-Ubai ibne-Salool se thi, kya keh raha tha? us ne is tarah ki baatein ki hain. Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aap usey maaf farma dein aur us se darguzar kar dein. us zaat ki qism ! jisne aap par kitab nazil ki hai Allah ne aap ke zariey wo haq bheja hai jo usney aap par nazil kya hai. is Shahar (Madina (ke log (pahley ( is par muttafiq ho chukey they ke us ( Abdullah-bin-Ubai ( ko taaj pehna dein aur) shahi ( amama uske sar par baandh dein lekin jab Allah Taala ne us haq ke zariey jo aapko us ne ata kya hai, us baatil ko rok diya to ab wo chid gaya hai aur us wjah se wo mamla us ne aap ke sath kya jo aap ne dekha hai. aap ne usey maaf kar diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) mushrekeen aur ahle-kitab se darguzar kya kartey they aur unki takleefon par sabr kya kartey they. usi ke barey mein ye aayat nazil hui ''aur yaqinan tum bahut si dil aazaari ki baatein unse bhi sunogey, jinhein tum se pahley kitab mil chuki hai aur unse bhi jo mushrik hain aur agar tum sabr karo aur taqwa ikhtiyar karo to ye badey azm w hosla ki baat hai'' aur Allah Taala ne farmaya ''bahut se ahle-kitab to dil hi se chahtey hain ke tumhen eman ( ley aaney (ke baad phir se kaafir bana lein, hasad ki raah se jo unke dilon mein hai.'' aakhir aayat tak. jaisa ke Allah Taala ka hukm tha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamesha kuffaar ko maaf kar diya kartey they. aakhir Allah Taala ne aapko unke sath jang ki ijazat de di aur jab aap ne jange-badr ki to Allah Taala ki mansha ke mutabiq Quraish ke kaafir sardaar usmein maarey gaey to Abdullah-bin-Ubai ibne-Salool aur uske doosrey mushrik aur but parast sathiyon ne aapas mein mashwara karke un sab ne bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Islam par bait kar li aur zaahiran Islam mein dakhil ho gaey."
4567,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein chand munaafeqeen aisey they ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jihad ke liye tashrif ley jatey to ye Madina mein peechhey reh jatey aur peechhey reh janey par bahut khush hua kartey they lekin jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas aatey to uzr bayan kartey aur qasmein kha letey balke unko aisey kaam par tareef hona pasand aata jis ko unhon-ne na kya hota aur baad mein chiknii chipdii baton se apni baat banaanaa chaahtey. Allah Taala ne usi par ye aayat (لا يحسبن الذين يفرحون‏) aakhir aayat tak utaarii.
4568,"Marwaan-bin-Hakam ne (jab wo Madina ke ameer they) apne darbaan se kaha ke raafe'! Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan jao aur unse poochho ke aayat (لا يحسبن الذين يفرحون‏) ki ro se to ham sab ko azab hona chahiye kyonke har aik aadmi un ne'maton par jo usko mili hain, khush hai aur ye chahta hai ke jo kaam us ne kya nahi is par bhi uski tareef ho. abu-Raafe ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se ja kar poochha, to Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, tum musalmanon se is aayat ka kya talluq ! ye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahudiyon ko bulaya tha aur unse aik Deen ki baat poochhi thi. (jo unki aasmani kitab mein maujood thi) unhon-ne asl baat ko to chhipaayaa aur dusri ghalat baat bayan kar di, phir bhi is baat ke khaahishmand rahe ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sawal ke jawab mein jo kuchh unhon-ne bataya hai is par unki tareef ki jaey aur idhar asl haqiqat ko chipa kar bhi badey khush they. phir Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne us aayat ki tilawat ( وإذ أخذ الله ميثاق الذين أوتوا الكتاب‏ ( ki ''aur wo waqt yad karo jab Allah ne ahle-kitab se ahad liya tha ke kitab ko poori zahir kar dena logon par, aayat ( يفرحون بما أتوا ويحبون أن يحمدوا بما لم يفعلوا‏ ( ''jo log apne kartooton par khush hain aur chahtey hain ke jo kaam nahi kiye hain, un par bhi unki tareef ki jaaey'' tak. Hishaam-bin-Yoosuf ke sath is hadis ko Abdur-Razzaq ne bhi ibne-Juraij se riwayat kya. ham se Muhammad-bin-Muqaatil ne bayan kya, kaha ham ko hujjaaj-bin-Muhammad ne khabar di, unhon-ne ibne-Juraij se kaha mujh ko ibne-abi-Mulaika ne khabar di, unko Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke Marwan ne apne darbaan Raafe se kaha, phir yahi hadis bayan ki."
4569,"main aik raat apni khala ( Ummul-Momenin ( Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar reh gaya. pahley Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni biwi ( Memuna (Raziallahu anha) (ke sath thodi der tak baat cheet ki phir so gaey. jab raat ka tesraa hissey baqi raha to aap uth kar baith gaey aur aasman ki taraf nazar ki aur ye aayat tilawat ki (إن في خلق السموات والأرض واختلاف الليل والنهار لآيات لأولي الألباب)''beshak aasmanon aur zameen ki paidaaish aur din w raat ke mukhtalif honey mein aqlmandon ke liye ( badi ( nishaniyan hain.''iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur wuzu kya aur miswak ki, phir gyara (11) rakatein tahajjud aur witr padhin. jab Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( fajr ki) azan di to aap ne 2 rakaat (fajr ki sunnat) padhi aur bahar masjid mein tashrif laey aur fajr ki Namaz padhai."
4570,"mein aik raat apni khala Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan so gaya, irada ye tha ke aaj Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz dekhoonga. meri khala ne aap ke liye gaddaa bichhaa diya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iske lambaan mein let gaey phir (jab aakhiri raat mein bedaar huey to) chehra Mubarak par hath pher kar neend ke aasaar door kiye. phir sura aale-Imraan ki aakhiri das aayatein padhin, iske baad aap aik mishkeezey ke paas aaey aur usse pani lekar wuzu kya aur Namaz padhney ke liye khadey ho gaey. main bhi khada ho gaya aur jo kuchh aap ne kya tha wahi sab kuchh maine bhi kya aur aap ke paas aa kar aap ke bazu mein main bhi khada ho gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere sar par apna dayan hath rakha aur mere hath ko) shafqat se) pakad kar malney lagey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 rakaat tahajjud ki Namaz padhi, phir 2 rakaat Namaz padhi, phir 2 rakaat Namaz padhi, phir 2 rakaat Namaz padhi, phir 2 rakaat Namaz padhi, phir 2 rakaat Namaz padhi, phir witr ki Namaz padhi."
4571,"aik raat wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar mein reh gaey jo unki khala thin. unhon-ne kaha ke main bistar ke chaudaan mein leta aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ki biwi lambaan mein letey, phir aap so gaey aur aadhi raat mein ya us se thodi der pahley ya baad mein aap bedaar huey aur chehre par hath pher kar neend ko door kya. phir sura aale-Imraan ki aakhiri das aayaton ki tilawat ki. iske baad aap uth kar mishkeezey ke qareeb gaey jo latkaa hua tha. uske pani se aap ne wuzu bahut hi achi tarah se poorey aadaab ke sath kya aur Namaz padhney ke liye khadey ho gaey. maine bhi aap hi ki tarah (wuzoo wghaira) kya aur Namaz ke liye aap ke bazu mein ja kar khada ho gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna daahinaa hath mere sar par rakha aur usi hath se ( bataur shafqat ( mera kaan pakad kar malney lagey, phir aap ne 2 rakaat Namaz padhi, phir 2 rakaat padhi, phir 2 rakaat padhi, phir 2 rakaat padhi, phir 2 rakaat padhi aur phir 2 rakaat padhi aur aakhir mein witr ki Namaz padhi. us se farigh ho kar aap let gaey, phir jab muazzan aaya to aap uthey aur 2 halki ( fajr ki sunnat ( rakatein padhein aur Namaz farz ke liye bahar tashrif (masjid mein) le gaey aur subah ki Namaz padhai."
4572,"aap aik martaba Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar reh gaey. Memuna (Raziallahu anha) unki khala thin. unhon-ne bayan kya ke main bistar ke arz (chaudaan) mein let gaya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ki biwi tool (lambaan) mein letey, phir aap so gaey aur aadhi raat mein ya us se thodi der pahley ya thodi der baad aap jaagey aur baith kar chehre par neend ke aasaar door karne ke liye hath pherney lagey aur sura Aale-Imran ki aakhiri das aayatein padhein. iske baad aap mishkeeze ke paas gaey jo latkaa hua tha, us se tamam aadaab ke sath aap ne wuzu kya, phir Namaz ke liye khadey huey. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke main bhi utha aur maine bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki tarah wuzu wghaira kya aur ja kar aap ke bazu mein khada ho gaya, to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna daahinaa hath mere sar par rakha aur) shafqat se) mere daahiney kaan ko pakad kar malney lagey. phir aap ne 2 rakaat Namaz padhi, phir 2 rakaat padhi, phir 2 rakaat padhi, phir 2 rakaat padhi, phir 2 rakaat padhi, phir 2 rakaat padhi aur aakhir mein unhein witr banaya, phir aap let gaey aur jab muazzan aap ke paas aaya to aap uthey aur 2 halki rakatein padh kar bahar masjid mein tashrif le gaey aur subah ki Namaz padhai."
4573,"aik aadmi ki parwarish mein aik yateem ladki thi, phir us ne us se nikah kar liya, us yateem ladki ki milkiyat mein khajoor ka aik baagh tha. usi baagh ki wjah se ye shakhs uski parwarish karta raha halanke dil mein us se koi khas lagaao na tha. is silsiley mein ye aayat utrii (وإن خفتم أن لا تقسطوا في اليتامى) ke ''agar tumhen andesha ho ke tum yatimon ke haq mein insaf na kar sakogey .'' Hisham bin-Yoosuf ne kaha, main samajhta hun, ibne-Juraij ne yun kaha ye ladki us darakht aur doosrey maal asbaab mein us mard ki hisse daar thi."
4574,"unhon-ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se aayat (وإن خفتم أن لا تقسطوا في اليتامى) kaa matlab poochha. unhon-ne kaha mere bhaanjey iska matlab ye hai ke aik yateem ladki apne wali ki parwarish mein ho aur uski jaaidaad ki hisse daar ho (tarkey ki ro se uska hissey ho) ab us wali ko uski maaldaarii, khoobsoortii pasand aaey. us se nikah karna chahey par insaf ke sath pura mehar jitna mehar usko doosrey log dein, na dena chaahey, to Allah Taala ne is aayat mein logon ko aisi yateem ladkiyon ke sath jab tak unka pura mehar insaf ke sath na dein, nikah karne se mana farmaya aur unko ye hukm diya ke tum dusri aurton se jo tum ko bhalii lagein nikah kar lo. (yateem ladki ka nuqsan na karo) Urwa ne kaha Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kehti thin, us aayat ke utarney ke baad logon ne phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us barey mein masla poochha, us waqt Allah ne ye aayat ( ويستفتونك في Nisa ( utari . Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha dusri aayat mein ye jo farmaya ( وترغبون أن تنكحوهن‏ ( yani wo yateem ladkiyan jinka maal w jamaal kam ho aur tum unke sath nikah karne se nafrat karo. iska matlab ye hai ke jab tum un yateem ladkiyon se jinka maal w jamaal kam ho nikah karna nahi chahtey to maal aur jamaal wali yateem ladkiyon se bhi jin se tum ko nikah karne ki raghbat hai nikah na karo, magar jab insaf ke sath unka mehar pura ada karo."
4575,Allah Taala ke irshaad (ومن كان غنيا فليستعفف ومن كان فقيرا فليأكل بالمعروف‏) ''balke jo shakhs khush'haal ho wo apne ko bilkul rokey rakhey . albatta jo shakhs naadaar ho wo waajibii taur par kha sakta hai.'' ke barey mein farmaya ke ye aayat yateem ke barey mein utri hai ke agar wali naadaar ho to yateem ki parwarish aur dekh bhaal ki ujrat mein wo waajibii taur par) yateem ke maal mein se kuchh ( kha sakta hai) basharte ke niyat mein fasaad na ho ( .
4576,"aayat (وإذا حضر القسمة أولو القربى واليتامى والمساكين)''aur jab taqseem ke waqt azeez w aqaarib aur yateem aur miskeen maujood hoon.'' ke mutaalliq farmaya ke ye mohkam hai, mansukh nahi hai. Ikrima ke sath us hadis ko Saeed-bin-Jubair ne bhi Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai."
4577,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) qabila banu- Salma tak paidal chal kar meri iyaadat ke liye tashrif laey. aap ne dekha ke mujh par be-hoshi taarii hai, isliye aap ne pani mangwaya aur wuzu karke iska pani mujh par chhidkaa , main hosh mein aa gaya, phir maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aap ka kya hukm hai, main apne maal ka kya karun? is par ye aayat nazil hui ( يوصيكم الله في أولادكم‏ (ke ''Allah tumhen tumhari aulad (ki meeraas (ke barey mein hukm deta hai.''"
4578,"shuruaat Islam mein maiyat ka Sara maal aulad ko milta tha, albatta waalidain ko wo milta jo maiyat unke liye wasiiyat kar jaey, phir Allah Taala ne jaisa munasib samjha usmein naskh kar diya. chunanche ab mard ka hissa 2 aurton ke hissey ke barabar hai aur maiyat ke waalidain yani un donon mein har aik ke liye us maal ka chhataa hissey hai. basharte ke maiyat ke koi aulad ho, lekin agar iske koi aulad na ho, balke iske waalidain hi iske waaris hon to uski maan ka aik tehai hissey hoga aur biwi ka aathwaan hissey hoga, jabke aulad ho, lekin agar aulad na ho to chothai hoga aur shauhar ka aadha hissey hoga, jabke aulad na ho lekin agar aulad ho to chothai hoga."
4579,"ye hadis abul-Hasan ata Suwaaii ne bhi bayan ki hai aur jahan tak mujhey yaqin hai Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) hi se bayan kya hai ke aayat (يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا يحل لكم أن ترثوا Nisa كرها wla تعضلوهن لتذهبوا ببعض ما آتيتموهن‏)''aey eman waalo! tumharey liye jaaiz nahi ke tum aurton ke zabardastii Malik ho jao aur na unhein us gharaz se qaid rakho ke tum ne unhein jo kuchh de rakha hai, iska kuchh hissey wsool kar lo, unhon-ne bayan kya ke jahiliyat mein kisi aurat ka shauhar mar jata to shauhar ke rishtedar us aurat ke zyada mustahiq samjhey jatey. agar unhiin mein se koi chahta to us se shadi kar letaa, ya phir wo jis se chahtey usi se uski shadi kartey aur chahtey to na bhi kartey, is tarah aurat ke ghar walon ke muqable mein bhi shauhar ke rishtedar iske zyada mustahiq samjhey jatey, usi par ye aayat (يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا يحل لكم أن ترثوا Nisa كرها) naazil hui."
4580,"(aayat mein) (ولكل جعلنا موالي‏) se murad waaris hain aur) والذين عاقدت أيمانكم‏ ( ki tafseer ye hai ke shuru mein jab muhajireen Madina aaey to qaraabat daaron ke ilawa Ansar ke waaris muhajireen bhi hotey they. us bhai chaara ki wjah se jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne muhajireen aur Ansar ke darmyan karaya tha, phir jab ye aayat nazil hui ke (ولكل جعلنا موالي‏) to pahlaa tariqa mansukh ho gaya phir bayan kya ke) والذين عاقدت أيمانكم‏ ( se wo log murad hain, jin se dosti aur madad aur khair-khahi ki qism kha kar ahad kya jaey. lekin ab unke liye meeraas ka hukm mansukh ho gaya magar wasiiyat ka hukm reh gaya. is asnaad mein abu-Usama ne Idrees se aur Idrees ne Talha bin musrif se suna hai."
4581,"kuchh sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha : ya Rasulullah ! kya qiyamat ke din ham apne rab ko dekh sakengey? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, kya suraj ko do-pahar ke waqt dekhney main tumhen koi dushwari hoti hai, jabke is par badal bhi na ho? sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke nahi. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aur kya chaudahwiin raat ke chaand ko dekhney main tumhen kuchh dushwari pesh aati hai, jabke is par badal na ho? sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke nahi. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bas isi tarah tum bila kisi diqqat aur rukawat ke Allah Taala ko dekhogey. qiyamat ke din aik manaadii awaz lagaayega ke har ummat apne jhootey ma'boodon ke sath hazir ho jaey. us waqt Allah ke siwa jitney bhi buton aur pattharon ki puja hoti thi, sab ko jahannam mein jhonk diya jaeyga phir jab wahi log baqi reh jaeinge jo sirf Allah ki puja kya kartey they, chahe nek hon ya gunahgaar aur ahle-kitab ke kuchh log, to pahley yahood ko bulaya jaeyga aur puchha jaeyga ke tum (Allah ke siwaa) kiski puja kartey they? wo arz karengey ke Uzair-ibnullaah ki, Allah Taala unse farmaeyga lekin tum jhootey they, Allah ne na kisi ko apni biwi banaya aur na betaa , ab tum kya chahtey ho? wo kahengey , hamarey rab! ham piyaasey hain, hamein pani pilaa de. unhein ishara kya jaeyga ke kya udhar nahi chaltey . chunanche sab ko jahannam ki taraf ley jaya jaeyga wahan chamaktii ret pani ki tarah nazar aaeygii, kuchh kuchh ke tukdey kiye de rahi hogi. phir sab ko aag mein daal diya jaeyga phir nasara ko bulaya jaeyga aur unse puchha jaeyga ke tum kis ki ibadat kya kartey they? wo kahengey ke ham Masih ibnullaah ki ibadat kartey they. unse bhi kaha jaeyga ke tum jhootey they. Allah ne kisi ko biwi aur betaa nahi banaya, phir unse puchha jaeyga ke kya chahtey ho? aur unke sath yahudiyon ki tarah bartaw kya jaeyga yahan tak ke jab un logon ke siwa aur koi baqi na rahega jo sirf Allah ki ibadat kartey they, chahe wo nek hon ya gunahgaar , to unke paas unka rab aik sura mein jalwa gar hoga, jo pehli sura se jis ko wo dekh chukey hongey, miltii jultii hogi (ye wo sura na hogi) ab unse kaha jaeyga ab tumhen kis ka intizar hai? har ummat apne ma'boodon ko sath lekar ja chukii, wo jawab dengey ke ham duniya mein jab logon se (jinhon ne kufr kya tha) juda huey to ham unmein sabse zyada mohtaaj they, phir bhi ham ne unka sath nahi diya aur ab hamein apne sachey rab ka intizar hai jiski ham duniya mein ibadat kartey rahe. Allah Taala farmaeyga ke tumhara rab main hi hun. is par tamam musalman bol uthengey ke ham apne rab ke sath kisi ko Sharik nahi thehratey , 2 ya teen martaba yun kahengey ham Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik karne waley nahi hain."
4582,"hadis ka kuchh hissey Amr-bin-Murra se hai) b-waaste Ibrahim) ke Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke mujh se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey Quran padh kar sunao. maine arz kya, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko main padh ke sunaun ? wo to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par hi nazil hota hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main doosrey se sunnaa chahta hun. chunanche maine aapko sura Nisa sunaanii shuru ki, jab main (فكيف إذا جئنا من كل أمة بشهيد وجئنا بك على هؤلاء شهيدا‏) par pahuncha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke thahar jao . maine dekha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aankhon se aansu bah rahe they."
4583,"(mujh se) Asma (Raziallahu anha) ka aik haar gum ho gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chand sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ko usey talash karne ke liye bhejaa. idhar Namaz ka waqt ho gaya, na log wuzu se they aur na pani maujood tha. isliye wuzu ke baghair Namaz padhi gaee is par Allah Taala ne tayammum ki aayat nazil ki."
4584,aayat ( أطيعوا الله وأطيعوا الرسول وأولي الأمر منكم‏ ( ''Allah ki itaat karo aur rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aur apne mein se haakimon ki.'' Abdullah-bin Huzafa bin Qais-bin Adi (Raziallahu anhu) ke barey mein nazil hui thi. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein aik muhim par bataur afsar ke rawaana kya tha.
4585,"Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ka aik Ansari sahabi se maqam Harra ki aik nali ke barey mein jhagdaa ho gaya (ke us se kon apne baagh ko pahley seenchney ka haq rakhta hai) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Zubair! pahley tum apne baagh seench lo phir apne padosi ko jald pani de dena. is par us Ansari sahabi ne kaha : ya Rasulullah! isliye ke ye aap ke phoophii zaad bhai hain? ye sun kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehra Mubarak ka rang badal gaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Zuber ! apne baagh ko seencho aur pani us waqt tak rokey rakho ke mundeer tak bhar jaey, phir apne padosi ke liye usey chhodo . (pahley Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansari ke sath apne faisley mein riaayat rakhi thi) lekin is martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko saaf taur par unka pura haq de diya kyonke Ansari ne aisi baat kahi thi. jis se aap ka ghussa hona qudrati tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne pahley faisle mein donon ke liye riaayat rakhi thi. Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke mera khayal hai, ye aayatein usi silsiley mein nazil hui thiin (فلا وربك لا يؤمنون حتى يحكموك فيما شجر بينهم) ''terey parwardigar ki qism hai ke ye log emaandaar na hongey jab tak ye us jhagdey mein jo unke aapas mein hon aapko hukm na bana lin aur aap ke faisley ko khuley dil ke sath khushi se taslim karne ke liye taiyaar na hoon.''"
4586,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo Nabi marzul-maut mein bimar hota hai to usey duniya aur aakhirat ka ikhtiyar diya jata hai. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki marzul-maut mein jab awaz galley mein phansney lagi to maine suna ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they (مع الذين أنعم الله عليهم من النبيين والصديقين والشهداء والصالحين) ''un logon ke sath jin par Allah ne inaam kya hai yani anbiyaa, siddeqeen, shohdaa aur saaleheen ke saath.'' isliye main samajh gaee ke aapko bhi ikhtiyar diya gaya hai (aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( اللهم بالرفيق الاعلي ( keh kar aakhirat ko pasand farmaya ( ."
4587,"maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha ke main aur meri walida ( mustaz-ifeen ( ) kamzoron ( mein se they."
4588,"ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne aayat (لا المستضعفين من الرجال والنساء والولدان‏) ki tilawat ki aur farmaya ke main aur meri walida bhi un logon mein se thin, jinhein Allah Taala ne ma'zoor rakha tha aur Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke) حصرت‏ ( mana main ( ضاقت (ke hai. ( تلووا‏ ( yani tumhari zabanon se gawahi ada hogi aur Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke siwa doosrey shakhs (abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha ( مراغم (ka mana hijrat ka maqaam. Arab log kehtey hain ( راغمت قومي‏ ( yani maine apni qaum walon ko jama kar diya. ( موقوتا‏ (ke mana aik waqt muqarrara par yani jo waqt unke liye muqarrar ho."
4589,"aayat ( فما لكم في المنافقين فئتين‏ ( ''aur tumhen kya ho gaya hai ke tum munaafeqeen ke barey mein 2 fareeq ho gaey ho.'' ke barey mein farmaya ke kuchh log munaafeqeen jo ( uper se) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they, jange-Uhud mein (aap chhod kar) wapas chaley aaey to unke barey mein musalmanon ki 2 jamatein ho gain . aik jamat to ye kehti thi ke) ya Rasulullah ! ( un ( munaafeqeen ( se qitaal kijiye aur aik jamat ye kehti thi ke unse qitaal na kijiye . is par ye aayat utri ( فما لكم في المنافقين فئتين‏ (ke '' tumhen kya ho gaya hai ke tum munaafeqeen ke barey mein 2 giroh ho gaey ho. ''aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye Madina ( طيبة ( hai. ye khabaasat ko is tarah door kar deta hai jaisey aag chandi ki mail kuchail ko door kar deti hai."
4590,koofa ke aalimon ka is aayat ke barey mein ikhtilaf ho gaya tha. chunanche main Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein uske liye safar karke gaya aur unse iske mutaalliq poochha. unhon-ne farmaya ke ye aayat ومن يقتل مؤمنا متعمدا فجزاؤه جهنم‏ ''aur jo koi musalman ko jaan-bojh kar qatl karey uski saza dozakh hai.'' nazil hui aur is baab ki ye sabse aakhiri aayat hai usey kisi aayat ne mansukh nahi kya hai.
4591,"aayat ( wla تقولوا لمن ألقى إليكم السلام لست مؤمنا‏ ( ''aur jo tumhen salam karta ho usey ye mat keh diya karo ke to to momin hi nahi hai.'' ke barey mein farmaya ke aik sahib (mirdaas naamii) apni bakriyan charaa rahe they, aik muhim par jatey huey kuchh musalman unhein miley to unhon-ne kaha '' Assalaamualaikum '' lekin musalmanon ne bahana khor jaan kar unhein qatl kar diya aur unki bakriyon par qabza kar liya. is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki thi aakhir aayat (عرض الحياة الدنيا‏) is se ishara unhiin bakriyon ki taraf tha. bayan kya ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( السلام‏ ( qirat ki hai, mashhoor qirat bhi yahi hai."
4592,"unhon-ne Marwaan-bin-Hakam bin Aas ko masjid mein dekha ( bayan kya ke) phir main unke paas aaya aur unke pahlu mein baith gaya, unhon-ne mujhey khabar di aur unhein Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse ye aayat likhwaaii لا يستوي القاعدون من المؤمنين والمجاهدون في سبيل الله''muslmaanon mein se ( ghar ( baith rehney waley aur Allah ki raah main apne maal aur apni jaan se jihad karne waley barabar nahi ho saktey.'' abhi aap ye aayat likhwaa hi rahe they ke ibn-Umme-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) aagey aur arz kya : Allah ki qasam! ya Rasulullah! agar main jihad mein shirkat kar sakta to yaqinan jihad karta. wo andhey they. iske baad Allah ne apne rasool par wahi utaarii. aap ki raan meri raan par thi (shiddat wahi ki wjah se) iska mujh par itna bojh padaa ke mujhey apni raan ke phat janey ka andesha ho gaya. aakhir ye kaifiyat khatm hui aur Allah Taala ne (غير أولي الضرر) ke alfaz aur nazil kiye."
4593,"jab aayat لا يستوي القاعدون من المؤمنين naazil hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ko kitabat ke liye bulaya aur unhon-ne wo aayat likh di. phir Abdullah-bin Umme- Maktum (Raziallahu anhu) hazir huey aur apne naa-beenaa honey ka uzr pesh kya, to Allah Taala ne (غير أولي الضرر) ke alfaz aur nazil kiye."
4594,"jab aayat لا يستوي القاعدون من المؤمنين naazil hui to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke falan (yani Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu)) ko bulao . wo apne sath dawaat aur takhtii ya shana ki haddi lekar hazir huey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya likho لا يستوي القاعدون من المؤمنين والمجاهدون في سبيل اللهibn-Umme-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) ne jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey maujood they, arz kya : ya Rasulullah! main naa-beenaa hun. chunanche wahin is tarah aayat nazil huii لا يستوي القاعدون من المؤمنين غير أولي الضرر والمجاهدون في سبيل الله."
4595,"لا يستوي القاعدون من المؤمنين se ishara hai un logon ki taraf jo badr mein Sharik they aur jinhoney bila kisi uzr ke badr ki ladai mein shirkat nahi ki thi, wo donon barabar nahi ho saktey."
4596,"ahal Madina ko (jab Makka mein ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ki khilafat ka daur tha) Sham (Syria) walon ke khilaf aik fauj nikalney ka hukm diya gaya. us fauj mein mera naam bhi likha gaya to Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghulam Ikrima se main mila aur unhein is sura haal ki itlaa ki. unhon-ne badi sakhti ke sath us se mana kya aur farmaya ke mujhey Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di thi ke kuchh musalman mushrekeen ke sath rahtey they aur is tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke khilaf unki zyadti ka sabab bantey, phir teer aata aur wo samney pad jatey to unhein lag jata aur is tarah unki jaan jati ya talwaar se (ghalatii mein) unhein qatl kar diya jata. is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaaii ( إن الذين توفاهم الملائكة ظالمي أنفسهم‏ ) ''beshak un logon ki jaan jinhoney apne uper zulm kar rakha hai (jab ( Farishtey qabz kartey hain.'' aakhir aayat tak. is riwayat ko Lais-bin-Sad ne bhi ابوالاسود se naql kya hai."
4597,aur unse Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( إلا المستضعفين‏ (ke mutaalliq farmaya ke meri maan bhi un hi logon mein thin jinhein Allah ne ma'zoor rakha tha.
4598,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isha ki Namaz main (rukoo' se uthtey huey) ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kaha aur phir sajde mein janey se pahley ye dua ki ''aey Allaah! Ayash bin abi Rabee ko nijat de. aey Allah ! Salma bin Hisham ko nijat de. aey Allah ! Waleed bin Waleed ko nijat de. aey Allah kamzor mominon ko nijat de. aey Allah ! kuffaar Muzar ko sakht saza de. aey Allah unhein aisi qahat-saalii mein mubtala kar jaisi Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke zamaney mein qahat saalii aai thi. ''
4599,aayat إن كان بكم أذى من مطر أو كنتم مرضى‏ ke silsiley mein batlaya ke Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) zakhmi ho gaey they unse mutaalliq ye aayat nazil hui.
4600,"aayat ( ويستفتونك في Nisa قل الله يفتيكم فيهن‏ ( '' log aap se aurton ke barey mein fatwa maangtey hain. aap keh dein ke Allah tumhen unke barey mein) wahi ( fatwa deta hai'' aayat ( وترغبون أن تنكحوهن‏ ( tak. unhon-ne bayan kya ke ye aayat aisey shakhs ke barey mein nazil hui ke agar uski parwarish mein koi yateem ladki ho aur wo uska wali aur waaris bhi ho aur ladki iske maal mein bhi hisse daar ho. yahan tak ke khajoor ke darakht mein bhii. ab wo shakhs khud us ladki se nikah karna chaahey, kyonke usey ye pasand nahi ke kisi doosrey se iska nikah kar de ke wo uske us maal mein hissedaar bin jaey, jis mein ladki hisse daar thi, is wjah se us ladki ka kisi doosrey shakhs se nikah na honey de to aisey shakhs ke barey mein ye aayat nazil hui thi."
4601,"aayat وإن امرأة خافت من بعلها نشوزا أو إعراضا‏‏‏ ''aur kisi aurat ko apne shauhar ki taraf se zyadti ya be raghbatii ka khof ho '' ke mutaalliq kaha ke aisa mard jiske sath uski biwi rehti hai, lekin shauhar ko uski taraf koi khas tawajjoh nahi, balke wo usey juda kar dena chahta hai, is par aurat kehti hai ke main apni baari aur apna ( naan nafqa ( maaf kar deti hun (tum mujhey talaaq na 2 ( to aisi sura ke mutaalliq ye aayat usi baab mein utri ."
4602,"ham Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke halqa dars mein baithey huey they ke Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laey aur hamarey paas khadey ho kar salam kya. phir kaha nifaq mein wo jamat mubtala ho gaee jo tum se behtar thi. is par Aswad boley, sub'haan-Allaah, Allah Taala to farmata hai) إن المنافقين في الدرك الأسفل من النار‏ (ke '' munafiq dozakh ke sabse nichley darjey mein hongey.'' Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) muskuraaney lagey aur Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) masjid ke koney mein ja kar baith gaey. iske baad Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) uth gaey aur aap ke shagird bhi idhar udhar chaley gaey. phir Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh par kankari phenkii (yani mujh ko bulaya ( mein hazir ho gaya to kaha ke mujhey Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki hansi par hairat hui halanke jo kuchh maine kaha tha usey wo khub samajhtey they. yaqinan nifaq mein aik jamat ko mubtala kya gaya tha jo tum se behtar thi, isliye ke phir unhon-ne tauba kar li aur Allah ne bhi unki tauba qabool kar li."
4603,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kisi ke liye munasib nahi ke mujhey Yoonus-bin-Matti se behtar kahey .''
4604,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo shakhs ye kehta hai main Yoonus-bin-Matti se behtar hon us ne jhoot kaha, ''"
4605,sabse aakhir mein jo sura nazil hui wo sura Bara't (Tauba) hai aur) ehkaam meeraas ke silsiley mein) sabse aakhir mein jo aayat nazil hui wo ( يستفتونك قل الله یفتیکم فى الکلالة ( hai.
4606,"aap log aik aisi aayat ki tilawat kartey hain ke agar hamarey yahan wo nazil hui hoti to ham (jis din wo nazil hui hoti (us din eid manaayaa kartey. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, mein khub achi tarah janta hun ke ye aayat ( اليوم أكملت لكم دينكم‏ ( kahan aur Kab nazil hui thi aur jab Arafaat ke din nazil hui to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kahan tashrif rakhtey they. Allah ki qism ! ham us waqt maidan Arafaat mein they. Sufiyan Sory ne kaha ke mujhey shak hai ke wo Juma ka din tha ya aur koi doosra din."
4607,"aik safar mein ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath rawaana huey. jab ham maqam beda ya zaatul-Jaish tak pahunchey to mera haar gum ho gaya. isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey talash karwaaney ke liye wahin qiyam kya aur sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath qiyam kya. wahan kahin pani nahi tha aur sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath bhi pani nahi tha. log Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur kehney lagey, dekhtey nahi, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kya kar rakha hai aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko yahin thehra liya aur hamein bhi, halanke yahan kahin pani nahi hai aur na kisi ke paas pani hai. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) mere yahan ( aaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sar Mubarak meri raan par rakh kar so gaey they aur kehney lagey tum ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aur sab ko rok liya, halanke yahan kahin pani nahi hai aur na kisi ke sath pani hai. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) mujh par bahut khafa huey aur jo Allah ko manzoor tha mujhey kaha, suna aur hath se meri kokh mein kachokey lagaey . maine sirf us khayal se koi harkat nahi ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) meri raan par apna sar rakhey huey they. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uthey aur subah tak kahin pani ka naam w nishan nahi tha, phir Allah Taala ne tayammum ki aayat utari to Usaid-bin-Huzair ne kaha ke aale-abii-bakar! ye tumhari koi pehli barkat nahi hai. bayan kya ke phir ham ne wo oont uthaya jis par main sawar thi to haar usi ke nichey mil gaya."
4608,"Amr-bin-Haris ne khabar di, unse Abdur-Rehman bin-Qasim ne bayan kya, unse unke walid Qasim ne aur unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne ke mera haar maqam beda mein gum ho gaya tha. ham Madina wapas aa rahe they, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wahin apni sawari rok di aur utar gaey, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sar Mubarak meri god mein rakh kar so rahe they ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) andar aagey aur mere seeney par zor se hath mar kar farmaya ke aik haar ke liye tum ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko rok liya lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aaraam ke khayal se main be-his w harkat baithi rahi halanke mujhey takleef hui thi. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bedaar huey aur subah ka waqt hua aur pani ki talash hui lekin kahin pani ka naam w nishan na tha. usi waqt ye aayat utri (ya أيها الذين آمنوا إذا قمتم إلى الصلاة‏ ). Usaid-bin-Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey aale-abi-Bakar ! tumhen Allah Taala ne logon ke liye baaise-barkat banaya hai. yaqinan tum logon ke liye baaise-barkat ho. tumhara haar gum hua Allah ne uski wjah se tayammum ki aayat nazil farma di jo qiyamat tak musalmanon ke liye aasani aur barkat hai."
4609,"mein Miqdaad-bin-Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) ke qareeb maujood tha (doosri sanad) aur mujh se hamdaan bin umr ne bayan kya, kaha ham se abu-Nazar (haashim bin-qaasim) ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Ubaidullah bin Abdur-Rehman Ashjai ne bayan kya, unse Sufiyan Sory ne, unse makhaariq-bin-abdullaah ne, unse Tariq bin Shahab ne aur unse Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke jange-badr ke mauqe par miqdaad-bin-Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha tha : ya Rasulullah ! ham aap se wo baat nahi kahengey jo Bani-Israeel ne Musa (Alaihissalam) se kahi thi ( فاذهب أنت وربك فقاتلا إنا ها هنا قاعدون‏ (ke '' aap khud aur aap ke khuda chaley jayen aur aap donon lad bhid lein. ham to yahan se talney ke nahi.'' nahin! aap chaliye, ham aap ke sath jaan dene ko hazir hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko unki is baat se khushi hui. is hadis ko Wakee ne bhi Sufiyan Sory se, unhon-ne makhaariq se, unhon-ne Tariq se riwayat kya hai ke Miqdad (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye arz kya (jo uper bayan hua) ."
4610,"wo (ameerul-momineen ( Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahmatullahi-alaih) khaleefa ke peechhey baithey huey they (majlis mein qasaamat ka zikr aa gaya) logon ne kaha ke qasaamat (musalmaanon aur kaafiron ke beech muaahide) mein qisaas lazim hoga. aap se pahley Khulafae-Rashedeen ne bhi usmein qisaas liya hai. phir Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahmatullahi-alaih) abu-Qilaba ki taraf mutwajjeh huey wo peechhey baithey huey they aur puchha : Abdullah-bin-Zaid tumhari kya raey hai, ya yun kaha ke abu-Qilaba ! aap ki kya raey hai? maine kaha ke mujhey to koi aisi sura malum nahi hai ke Islam mein kisi shakhs ka qatl jaaiz ho, siwa iske ke kisi ne shadi shuda honey ke bawajud zina kya ho, ya nahaq kisi ko qatl kya ho, ya ( phir ( Allah aur uske rasool se lada ho (murtad ho gaya ho). is par anbasaa ne kaha ke ham se Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne is tarah hadis bayan ki thi. abu-Qilaba boley ke mujh se bhi unhon-ne ye hadis bayan ki thi. bayan kya ke kuchh log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur Islam par bait karne ke baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke hamein us Shahar Madina ki aab w hua muwafiq nahi aai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke hamarey ye oont charney ja rahe hain tum bhi unke sath chaley jao aur unka doodh aur peshab piyo (kyonke unke marz ka yahi ilaaj tha) chunanche wo log un oonton ke sath chaley gaey aur unka doodh aur peshab piyaa. jis se unhein sihat hasil ho gaee. iske baad unhon-ne (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke charwaahey) ko pakad kar qatl kar diya aur oont lekar bhaagey. ab aisey logon se badla leney mein kya shak ho sakta tha. unhon-ne aik shakhs ko qatl kya aur Allah aur uske rasool se ladey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khaufzada karna chaha. anbasaa ne is par kaha : sub'haan-Allaah! maine kaha, kya tum mujhey jhutlana chahtey ho? unhon-ne kaha ke (nahin) yahi hadis Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se bhi bayan ki thi. maine is par tajjub kya ke tum ko hadis khub yad rehti hai. abu-Qilaba ne bayan kya ke anbasaa ne kaha, aey Sham (Syria) waalo! jab tak tumharey yahan abu-Qilaba ya un jaisey aalim maujood rahengey, tum hamesha achchhey rahogey."
4611,"Rabe ne jo Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki phoophii thin, Ansar ki aik ladki ke aagey ke daant tod diye. ladki walon ne qisaas chaha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi qisaas ka hukm diya. Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke chacha Anas-bin-Nazar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : nahi Allah ki qism ! unka daant na tod jaaeyga. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Anas ! lekin kitabullah ka hukm qisaas hi ka hai. phir ladki waley maafi par razi ho gaey aur diyat lena manzoor kar liya. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ke bahut se bandey aisey hain ke agar wo Allah ka naam lekar qism kha lein to Allah unki qism sachchii kar deta hai."
4612,"unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha, jo shakhs bhi tum se ye kehta hai ke Allah Taala ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par jo kuchh nazil kya tha, usmein se aap ne kuchh chipa liya tha, to wo jhoota hai. Allah Taala ne khud farmaya hai) ya أيها الرسول بلغ ما أنزل إليك‏ (ke ''aey paighambar ! jo kuchh aap par aap ke parwardigar ki taraf se nazil hua hai, ye (sab (aap ( logon tak) pahuncha dein.''"
4613,"aayat لا يؤاخذكم الله باللغو في أيمانكم‏ ''Allaah tum se tumhari fuzool qasmon par pakad nahi kartaa.'' kisi ke is tarah qism khaney ke barey mein nazil hui thi ke nahi, Allah ki qasam, haan Allah ki qasam!."
4614,unke walid Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) apni qism ke khilaf kabhi nahi kya kartey they. lekin jab Allah Taala ne qism ke kaffaare ka hukm nazil kar diya to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ab agar iske (yani jiske liye qism kha rakhi thi) siwa dusri cheez mujhey us se behtar malum hoti hai to main Allah Taala ki di hui rukhsat par amal karta hun aur wahi kaam karta hun jo behtar hota hai.
4615,ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ho kar jihad kya kartey they aur hamarey sath hamari beeviyan nahi hoti thin. is par ham ne arz kya ke ham apne aapko khassi kyon na kar lein. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein us se rok diya aur uske baad hamein uski ijazat di ke ham kisi aurat se kapdey (ya kisi bhi cheez (ke badley mein nikah kar saktey hain. phir Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye aayat padhii يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تحرموا طيبات ما أحل الله لكم ''aey eman waalo! apne uper un pakeeza chizon ko haram na karo jo Allah ne tumharey liye jaaiz ki hain.''
4616,jab sharab ki hurmat nazil hui to Madina mein us waqt panch qism ki sharab istemal hoti thi. lekin angoori sharab ka istemal nahi hota tha (bahar-haal wo bhi haram qarar paaii).
4617,"ham log tumhari ( فضيخ ( ) khajoor se banai hui sharab (ke siwa aur koi sharab istemal nahi kartey they, yahi jiska naam tum ne ( فضيخ ( rakh rakha hai. main khada abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ko pilaa raha tha aur falan aur falan ko, ke aik sahib aaey aur kaha : tumhen kuchh khabar bhi hai? logon ne puchha kya baat hai? unhon-ne bataya ke sharab haram qarar di ja chuki hai. fauran hi un logon ne kaha : Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ab un sharab ke matkon ko baha do. unhon-ne bayan kya ke unki itlaa ke baad un logon ne usmein se aik qatra bhi na maanga aur na phir iska istemal kya."
4618,Uhud ki jang mein bahut se sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne subah subah sharab pi thi aur isi din wo sab Shahid kar diye gaey they. us waqt sharab haram nahi hui thi (is liye wo gunahgaar nahi thahrey ( .
4619,"maine umr (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke member par khadey farma rahe they. ammaa ba'd! aey logo ! jab sharab ki hurmat nazil hui to wo panch chizon se taiyaar ki jati thi. angoor, khajoor, shahad, gehun aur jau se aur sharab har wo peeney ki cheez hai jo aql ko mitaa de."
4620,"(hurmat nazil honey ke baad) jo sharab bahaaii gaee thi wo (فضيخ‏ ( ki thi. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne bayan kya ke mujh se Muhammad ne Abu-Naumaan se us zyadti ke sath bayan kya ke Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main sahaba ki aik jamat ko abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar sharab pilaa raha tha ke sharab ki hurmat nazil hui. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne manaadii ko hukm diya aur unhon-ne elaan karna shuru kya. abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : bahar ja ke dekho ye awaz kaisi hai. bayan kya ke main bahar aaya aur kaha ke aik manaadii elaan kar raha hai ke '' khabardaar ho jao, sharab haram ho gaee hai.'' ye suntey hi unhon-ne mujh ko kaha ke jao aur sharab baha do. rawi ne bayan kya, Madina ki galiyon mein sharab bahney lagi rawi ne bayan kya ke un dinon ( فضيخ‏ ( sharab istemal hoti thi. kuchh logon ne sharab ko jo is tarah bahte dekha to kehney lagey malum hota hai ke kuchh logon ne sharab se apna pet bhar rakha tha aur usi haalat mein unhein qatl kar diya gaya hai. bayan kya ke phir Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki ليس على الذين آمنوا وعملوا الصالحات جناح فيما طعموا''jo log eman rakhtey hain aur nek kaam kartey rahtey hain, un par us cheez mein koi gunah nahi jis ko unhon-ne kha liyaa.''"
4621,"aik martaba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa khutba diya ke maine waisaa khutba kabhi nahi suna tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo kuchh main janta hun agar tumhen bhi malum hota to tum hanstey kam aur rotey zyada . bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne chehrey chipa liye, bawajud zabt ke unke roney ki awaz sunai de rahi thi. aik sahabi ne us mauqe par puchha : mere walid kon hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke fulaan. is par ye aayat nazil huii لا تسألوا an (an) أشياء إن تبد لكم تسؤكمke ''aisii baatein mat poochho ke agar tum par zahir kar di jayen to tumhen na-gawar guzrein.'' uski riwayat nazar aur Rooh bin Ubada ne Shoba se ki hai."
4622,kuchh log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mazaaq mein sawalat kya kartey they. koi shakhs yun poochhta ke mera bap kon hai? kisi ki agar ontni gum ho jati to wo ye poochhtey ke meri ontni kahan hogii? aisey hi logon ke liye Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki ( ya أيها الذين آمنوا la تسألوا an (an) أشياء إن تبد لكم تسؤكم‏ ) ke ''aey eman waalo! aisi baatein mat poochho ke agar tum par zahir kar di jayen to tumhen na-gawar guzrey.'' yahan tak ke poori aayat padh kar sunai.
4623,"(baheera) us ontni ko kehtey they jiska doodh buton ke liye rok diya jata aur koi shakhs iske doodh ko dohney ka majaaz na samjha jata aur (saayeba) us ontni ko kehtey they jisey wo apne dewtaaon ke naam par aazad chhod detey aur us se bojha dhone w sawari wghaira ka kaam na letey. Saeed rawi ne bayan kya ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine Amr bin Aamir Khuzai ko dekha ke wo apni aanton ko jahannam mein ghaseet raha tha, us ne sabse pahley saand chhodney ki rasm nikaalii thi aur (وصيلة) us jawan ontni ko kehtey they jo pehli martaba maada bachcha jantii aur phir dusri martaba bhi maada hi jantii, usey bhi wo buton ke naam par chhod detey they lekin usi sura mein jabke wo barabar 2 martaba maada bachcha jantii aur us darmyan mein koi nar bachcha na hota aur (Haam) wo nar oont jo maada par shumaar se kai baar chadhtaa (iske nutfey se das bachchey paida ho jaatey) jab wo itni sohbatein kar chuktaa to usko bhi buton ke naam par chhod detey aur bojh laadney se maaf kar detey (na sawari kartey) iska naam (Haam) rakhtey aur abul-Yamaan (hakam bin Naafe') ne kaha ham ko Shuaib ne khabar di, unhon-ne Zohri se suna, kaha maine Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se yahi hadis suni jo uper guzri. Saeed ne kaha Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna (wahi Amr bin Aamir Khuzai ka qissa jo uper guzraa) aur Yazeed bin-abdullaah-bin-Haad ne bhi us hadis ko ibne-Shahab se riwayat kya. unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, kaha maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna."
4624,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine jahannam ko dekha ke iske kuchh hissey kuchh doosrey hisson ko khaaey ja rahe hain aur maine Amr bin Aamir Khuzai ko dekha ke wo apni aantein usmein ghaseetaa phir raha tha. yahi wo shakhs hai jisne sabse pahley saand chhodney ki rasm eiijaad ki thi.
4625,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khutba diya aur farmaya ke aey logo! tum Allah ke paas jama kiye jaogey nangey paon nangey jism aur baghair khatna ke, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye aayat padhi ( كما بدأنا أول خلق نعيده وعدا علينا إنا كنا فاعلين ( ''jis tarah ham ne awwal baar paida karne ke waqt shuruaat ki thi, isi tarah usey dobara zinda kar dengey, hamarey zimme wada hai, ham zaroor usey karke hi rahengey.'' aakhir aayat tak. phir farmaya qiyamat ke din tamam makhlooq mein sabse pahley Ibrahim ko kapda pahnaayaa jaeyga haan aur meri ummat ke kuchh logon ko laya jaeyga aur unhein jahannam ki baain taraf ley jaya jaeyga main arz karunga, mere rab! ye to mere ummatii hain? mujh se kaha jaeyga aapko nahi malum hai ke unhon-ne aap ke baad naii-naii baatein shariiat mein nikaalii thin. us waqt mein bhi wahi kahunga jo abd Saleh Esa (Alaihissalam) ne kaha hoga ( وكنت عليهم شهيدا ما دمت فيهم فلما توفيتني كنت أنت الرقيب عليهم‏ (ke ''main unka haal dekhta raha jab tak mein unke darmyan raha, phir jab tu ney mujhey utha liya (jab se) to hi un par nigraan hai.'' mujhey bataya jaeyga ke aap ki judai ke baad ye log Deen se phir gaey they."
4626,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhen qiyamat ke din jama kya jaeyga aur kuchh logon ko jahannam ki taraf ley jaya jaeyga us waqt mein wahi kahunga jo nek bandey ne kaha hoga ( وكنت عليهم شهيدا ما دمت فيهم‏ ( ''main unka haal dekhta raha jab tak mein unke darmyan rahaa'' aakhir aayat ( العزيز الحكيم‏ ( tak.
4627,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ghaib ke khazaaney panch hain. jaisa ke irshad baari hai. beshak Allah hi ko qiyamat ki khabar hai aur wahi janta hai ke rahmon mein kya hai aur koi bhi nahi jaan sakta ke wo kal kya amal karega aur na koi ye jaan sakta hai ke wo kis zameen par marega, beshak Allah hi ilm wala hai, khabar rakhney wala hai.''"
4628,jab ye aayat قل هو القادر على أن يبعث عليكم عذابا من فوقكم‏naazil hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey Allah ! main terey munh ki panah mangta hun. phir ye utraa أو من تحت أرجلكم‏ Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ya Allah ! main terey munh ki panah mangta hun. phir ye utraa ( أو يلبسكم شيعا ويذيق بعضكم بأس بعض‏) us waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye pahley azaabon se halka ya aasan hai.
4629,"jab aayat ( ولم يلبسوا إيمانهم بظلم‏ ( nazil hui sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, ham mein kon hoga jiska daman zulm se paak ho. is par ye aayat utrii ( إن الشرك لظلم عظيم‏ ) ''beshak shirk zulm azeem hai.''"
4630,mujh se tumharey Nabi ke chacha zaad bhai yani Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kisi ke liye munasib nahi ke mujhey Yoonus-bin-Matti (Alaihissalam) se behtar bataaey.
4631,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kisi shakhs ke liye jaaiz nahi ke mujhey Yoonus-bin-Matti (Alaihissalam) se behtar bataaey.
4632,"unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha kya sura Swaad mein sajda hai? Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne batlaayaa, haan. phir aap ne aayat ( ووهبنا‏ ( se ( فبهداهم اقتده‏ ( tak padhi aur kaha ke Dawud (Alaihissalam) bhi un anbiya mein shamil hain (jinka zikr aayat mein hua hai). Yazeed-bin-Haaroon, Muhammad-bin Ubaid aur Sahal-bin-Yoosuf ne Awam bin Hoshab se, unse Mujahid ne bayan kya ke maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se poochha, to unhon-ne kaha tumharey Nabi bhi unmein se hain jinhein agley anbiya ki iqtida (pairvi) ka hukm diya gaya hai."
4633,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Allah yahudiyon ko ghaarat karey, jab Allah Taala ne un par murda janwaron ki charbi haram kar di to uska tel nikal kar usey bechney aur khaney lagey aur abu-Aasim ne bayan kya, unse abdul-hameed ne bayan kya, unse Yazeed ne bayan kya, unhein Ata ne likha tha ke maine Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
4634,"Allah se zyada aur koi ghairat mand nahi, yahi wjah hai ke usne be-hayaaiyon ko haram qarar diya hai. chahe wo zahir hon chahe posheeda aur Allah ko apni tareef se zyada aur koi cheez pasand nahi, yahi wjah hai ke usne apni khud madah ki hai. ( Amr-bin-Murra ne bayan kya ke) maine puchha aap ne ye hadis khud Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se suni thi unhon-ne bayan kya ke yahaan, maine puchha aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hawale se hadis bayan ki thi? kaha ke haan."
4635,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us waqt tak qiyamat qaaim na hogi, jab tak suraj maghrib se tuloo na ho ley. jab log usey dekhengey to eman laaengey lekin ye wo waqt hoga jab kisi aisey shakhs ko uska eman koi nafa na dega jo pahley se eman na rakhta ho."
4636,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qiyamat us waqt tak qaaim na hogi, jab tak suraj maghrib se na tuloo ho ley. jab maghrib se suraj tuloo hoga aur log dekh lengey to sab eman laaengey lekin ye waqt hoga jab kisi ko iska eman nafa na dega, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us aayat ki tilawat ki."
4637,"(Amr bin Murra ne bayan kya ke) maine (abu-Waeil se) poochha, kya tum ne ye hadis ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se khud suni hai? unhon-ne kaha ke ji haan aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kya, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah se zyada aur koi ghairat mand nahi hai. isi liye us ne be-hayaaiyon ko haram kya chahe zahir mein hon ya posheeda aur Allah se zyada apni madah ko pasand karne wala aur koi nahi, isi liye us ne apne nafs ki khud tareef ki hai."
4638,"aik Yahudi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, iske munh par kisi ne tamaancha maara tha. usne kaha : aey Muhammad! aap ke Ansari sahaba mein se aik shakhs ne mujhey tamaancha maara hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein bulaao. logon ne unhein bulaayaa, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse puchha tum ne usey tamaancha kyon maara hai? us ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! main yahudiyon ki taraf se guzra to maine suna ke ye keh raha tha. us zaat ki qasam! jisne Musa (Alaihissalam) ko tamam insanon par fazeelat di. maine kaha aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par bhii. mujhey uski baat par ghussa aa gaya aur maine usey tamaancha mar diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke mujhey anbiya par fazeelat na diya karo. qiyamat ke din tamam log behosh kar diye jaengey. sabse pahley mein hosh mein aaoonga lekin main Musa (Alaihissalam) ko dekhunga ke wo arsh ka aik paaya pakdey khadey hongey ab mujhey nahi malum ke wo mujh se pahley hosh mein aagey ya taur ki be-hoshi ka unhein badla diya gaya."
4639,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, khumbii ( من ( mein se hai aur iska pani aankhon ke liye shifa hai."
4640,"Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke darmyan kuchh bahas si ho gaee thi. umr (Raziallahu anhu) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) par ghussa ho gaey aur unke paas se aaney lagey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi unke peechhey peechhey ho gaey, maafi maangtey huey. lekin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein maaf nahi kya aur (ghar pahunch kar) andar se darwaza band kar liya. ab Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke ham log us waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumharey ye sahib (yani Abu-Bakar (rz)) lad aaey hain. rawi ne bayan kya ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi apne tarze-amal par naadim huey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf chaley aur salam karke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb baith gaey. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Sara waqia bayan kya. abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke aap bahut naraz huey. idhar Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) baar-baar ye arz kartey ke ya Rasulullah! waqei meri hi zyadti thi. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya tum log mujhey mere sathi se juda karna chahtey ho? kya tum log mere sathi ko mujh se juda karna chahtey ho? jab maine kaha tha ke aey insaano! beshak main Allah ka rasool hun, tum sab ki taraf, to tum logon ne kaha ke tum jhoot boltey ho, us waqt Abu-Bakar ne kaha tha ke aap sachey hain. abu-Adbullah ne kaha ( غامر (ke mana hadis mein ye hai ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhalai mein sabqat ki hai."
4641,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Bani-Israeel se kaha gaya tha ke darwazey main ( aajizii se) jhuktey huey dakhil ho aur kehtey jao ke tauba hai, to ham tumhari khataein maaf kar dengey, lekin unhon-ne hukm badal dala. koolhon ke bal ghisat'tey huey dakhil huey aur ye kaha ke (حبة في شعرة) yaanii ham ko baaliyon mein daana chaahiye."
4642,"Uena bin Hisn bin Huzefa ne apne bhatijey Hur-bin-Qais ke yahan aa kar qiyam kya. Hur, un chand khas logon mein se they jinhein umr (Raziallahu anhu) apne bahut qareeb rakhtey they jo log Quran Majeed ke zyada aalim aur qaari hotey. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki majlis mein unhein ko zyada nazdeekii hasil hoti thi aur aisey log aap ke musheer hotey. uski koi qaid nahi thi ke wo boodhey hon ya naujawaan. Uena ne apne bhatijey se kaha ke tumhen is ameer ki majlis mein bahut nazdeekii hasil hai. mere liye bhi majlis mein haziri ki ijazat ley do. Hur-bin-Qais ne kaha ke main aap ke liye bhi ijazat maangonga. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya. chunanche unhon-ne Uena ke liye bhi ijazat mangi aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein majlis mein aaney ki ijazat de di. majlis mein jab wo pahunchey to kehney lagey : aey Khattab ke betey! Allah ki qasam! na to tum hamein maal hi detey ho aur na adl w insaf ke sath faisla kartey ho. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko unki is baat par bada ghussa aaya aur aagey badh hi rahe they ke Hur-bin-Qais ne arz kya : ya ameerul-momineen ! Allah Taala ne apne Nabi se Khattab karke farmaya hai'' maafi ikhtiyar kar aur nek kaam ka hukm de aur jaahilon se kinara kash! ho jaya keejiye.'' aur ye bhi jaahilon mein se hain. Allah ki qism ! ke jab Hur ne Quran Majeed ki tilawat ki to umr (Raziallahu anhu) bilkul thandey pad gaey aur kitabullah ke hukm ke samney aap ki yahi haalat hoti thi."
4643,aayat ( خذ العفو وأمر بالعرف‏ ( '' maafi ikhtiyar kijiye aur nek kaam ka hukm detey rahiye.'' logon ke akhlaq ki islaah ke liye hi nazil hui hai.
4644,"Allah Taala ne apne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hukm diya hai ke logon ke akhlaq theek karne ke liye darguzar ikhtiyar karein ya kuchh aisa hi kaha,"
4645,"maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se sura anfaal ke mutaalliq poochha. unhon-ne batlaya ke jange-badr mein nazil hui thi. ( الشوكة (ka mana dhaar nauk. ( مردفين‏ (ke mana fauj dar fauj. kehtey hain ( ردفني وأردفني ( yani mere baad aayaa. ( ذلكم فذوقوه ذوقوا‏ ) kaa mana ye hai ke ye azab uthao iska tajriba karo, munh se chakhnaa murad nahi hai. ( فيركمه‏ (ka mana iska jama kare. ( sharad (ka mana juda kar de (ya sakht saza de) .) جنحوا‏ (ke mana talab karein. (يثخن‏) ka mana ghalib hua aur Mujahid ne kaha (مكاء‏) ka mana ungliyan munh par rakhna. ( تصدية‏ ( seetii bajaana ( يثبتوك‏ (taake tujh ko qaid kar lein."
4646,aayat إن شر الدواب عند الله الصم البكم الذين لا يعقلون ''badtareen haiwaanaat Allah ke nazdeek wo behrey goongey hain jo aql se zara kaam nahi letey.'' banu-abduddaar ke kuchh logon ke barey mein utri thi.
4647,"mein Namaz padh raha tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey pukaaraa. main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein na pahunch saka balke Namaz se farigh honey ke baad hazir hua. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke aaney mein der kyon huii? kya Allah Taala ne tumhen hukm nahi diya hai) ya أيها الذين آمنوا استجيبوا لله وللرسول إذا دعاكم (ke ''aey eman waalo! Allah aur uske rasool ki awaz par labbaik kaho, jabke wo (yani rasool ( tum ko balaaein.'' phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke masjid se nikalney se pahley main tumhen Quran ki azeem tareen sura sikhaaunga. thodi der baad aap bahar tashrif ley janey lagey to maine aapko yad dilaya aur Muaaz-bin-Muaaz Anbari ne us hadis ko yun riwayat kya ke ham se Shoba ne bayan kya, unse Khubaib ne, unhon-ne Hafs se suna aur unhon-ne abu-Saeed bin Mu-alla (Raziallahu anhu) jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahabi they, suna aur unhon-ne bayan kya wo (sura faatiha) ( الحمد لله رب العالمين ( hai jis mein saat (7) aayatein hain jo har Namaz mein mukarrar (baar-baar aai hui) padhi jati hain."
4648,"abu-Jahal ne kaha tha ke aey Allaah! agar ye kalam teri taraf se waqei haq hai to ham par aasmanon se patthar barsa de ya phir koi aur hi azab dardnak ley aa!'' to is par aayat (وما كان الله ليعذبهم وأنت فيهم وما كان الله معذبهم وهم يستغفرون * وما لهم أن لا يعذبهم الله وهم يصدون an (an) المسجد الحرام‏)''haalaanke Allah aisa nahi karega ke unhein azab de, us haal mein ke aap unmein maujood hon aur na Allah un par azab laaeyga us haal mein ke wo istighfar kar rahe hun. un logon ke liye kya wjah ke Allah un par azab (hii sirey se) na laey halanke wo masjide-Haraam se roktey hain.'' aakhir aayat tak."
4649,"abu-Jahal ne kaha tha ke aey Allaah! agar ye kalam teri taraf se waqei haq hai to ham par aasmanon se patthar barsa de ya phir koi aur hi azab dardnak ley aa!'' to is par aayat (وما كان الله ليعذبهم وأنت فيهم وما كان الله معذبهم وهم يستغفرون * وما لهم أن لا يعذبهم الله وهم يصدون an (an) المسجد الحرام‏)''haalaanke Allah aisa nahi karega ke unhein azab de, us haal mein ke aap unmein maujood hon aur na Allah un par azab laaeyga us haal mein ke wo istighfar kar rahe hun. un logon ke liye kya wjah ke Allah un par azab (hii sirey se) na laey halanke wo masjide-Haraam se roktey hain.'' aakhir aayat tak."
4650,"aik shakhs (hibbaan ya Alaa-bin-Araar naamii) ne puchha : abu-Abdur-Rehmaan! aap ne Quran ki ye aayat nahi sunii ( وإن طائفتان من المؤمنين اقتتلوا‏ ) ke ''jab musalmanon ki 2 jamatein ladney lagein'' is aayat ke hotey huey tum (Ali aur Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) donon se) kyon nahi ladtey jaisey Allah ne farmaya ( فقاتلوا التي تبغيإ ). unhon-ne kaha mere bhateejey! agar main us aayat ki taaweel karke musalmanon se na ladun to ye mujh ko achchha malum hota hai b-nisbat iske ke main is aayat ( ومن يقتل مؤمنا متعمدا‏ ( ki taaweel karun. wo shakhs kehney laga achchha us aayat ko kya karogey jis mein mazkoor hai (وقاتلوهم حتى لا تكون فتنة) ke ''unse lado taake fitna baqi na rahe aur Sara Deen Allah ka ho jaaey.'' Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha (waah, waah) ye ladai to ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein kar chukey, us waqt musalman bahut thodey they aur musalman ko Islam ikhtiyar karne par takleef di jati. qatl kartey, qaid kartey yahan tak ke Islam phail gaya. musalman bahut ho gaey ab fitna jo is aayat mein mazkoor hai wo kahan raha. jab us shakhs ne dekha ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) kisi tarah ladai par iske muwafiq nahi hotey to kehney laga achchha batlao Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke barey main tumhara kya aqeeda hai? unhon-ne kaha haan ye kaho to suno, Ali aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke barey mein apna aqeeda bayan karta hun. Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ka jo qasoor tum bayan kartey ho (ke wo jange-Uhud mein bhag nikley) to Allah ne unka ye qasoor maaf kar diya magar tum ko ye maafi pasand nahi (jab to ab tak un par qasoor lagaatey jatey ho) aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) to ( Subhan-Allah ( Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chacha zaad bhai aur aap daamaad bhi they aur hath se ishara karke batlaya ye unka ghar hai jahan tum dekh rahe ho."
4651,(musalmanon ke baahamii) fitna aur jang ke barey mein aap ki kya raey hai? ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse puchha tumhen malum bhi hai'' fitna ''kya cheez hai. Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mushrekeen se jang kartey they aur unmein thahar jana hi fitna tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jang tumhari mulk w saltanat ki khaatir jang ki tarah nahi thi.
4652,"jab ye aayat nazil huii (إن يكن منكم عشرون صابرون يغلبوا مائتين‏) ke ''agar tum mein se bees aadmi bhi sabr karne waley hon to wo 200 par ghalib aa jaaengey.'' to musalmanon ke liye farz qarar de diya gaya ke aik musalman das kaafiron ke muqaabley se na bhaagey aur kai martaba Sufiyan Sory ne ye bhi kaha ke bees 200 ke muqaabley se na bhaagein. phir Allah Taala ne ye aayat utari ( الآن خفف الله عنكم‏ ( '' ab Allah ne tum par kami kar dii.'' iske baad ye farz qarar diya ke 100, 200 ke muqaabley se na bhaagein. Sufiyan Sory ne aik martaba us zyadti ke sath riwayat bayan ki ke aayat nazil huii (حرض المؤمنين على القتال إن يكن منكم عشرون صابرون) ke ''aey Nabi mominon ko qitaal par aamada karo. agar tum mein se bees aadmi sabr karne waley hongey.'' Sufiyan Sory ne bayan kya aur unse Abdullah-bin shabarma (koofa ke qaazii) ne bayan kya ke mera khayal hai Amr bil-ma'aroof aur nahii-anil-munkar mein bhi yahi hukm hai."
4653,jab ye aayat utrii (إن يكن منكم عشرون صابرون يغلبوا مائتين) ke ''agar tum mein se bees aadmi bhi sabr karne waley hongey to wo 200 par ghalib aa jaengey. '' to musalmanon par sakht guzra kyonke is aayat mein un par ye farz qarar diya gaya tha ke aik musalman das kaafiron ke muqaabley se na bhaagey. isliye iske baad kami ki gaee aur Allah Taala ne farmaayaa (الآن خفف الله عنكم وعلم أن فيكم ضعفا فإن يكن منكم مائة صابرة يغلبوا مائتين‏) ke ''ab Allah ne tum se kami kar di aur malum kar liya ke tum mein josh ki kami hai. so ab agar tum mein sabr karne waley hongey to wo 200 par ghalib aa jaengey. ''ibne-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke tadaad ki is kami se itni hi musalmanon ke sabr mein kami ho gaee.
4654,sabse aakhir mein ye aayat nazil hui thi ( يستفتونك قل الله يفتيكم في الكلالة‏ (aur sabse aakhir mein sura Bara't (Tauba) nazil hui.
4655,"Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne us Haj ke mauqe par (jiska Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ameer banaya tha) mujhey bhi elaan karne walon mein rakha tha, jinhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yaumun-nahar mein isliye bheja tha ke elaan kar dein ke aainda saal se koi mushrik Haj karne na aaey aur koi shakhs Baitullah ka tawaaf nangey ho kar na kare. Humaid-bin-Abdur-Rehmaan ne kaha ke phir iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko peechhey se bheja aur unhein sura Bara't (Tauba) ke ehkaam ke elaan karne ka hukm diya. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, chunanche hamarey sath Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi yaumun-nahar hi mein sura Bara't (Tauba) ka elaan kya aur iska ke aainda saal se koi mushrik Haj na karey aur na koi nangey ho kar tawaaf kare."
4656,"abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne us Haj ke mauqe par (jiska Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ameer banaya tha) mujhey bhi elaan karne walon mein rakha tha, jinhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yaumun-nahar mein isliye bheja tha ke elaan kar dein ke aainda saal se koi mushrik Haj karne na aaey aur koi shakhs Baitullah ka tawaaf nangey ho kar na kare. Humaid-bin-Abdur-Rehmaan ne kaha ke phir iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko peechhey se bheja aur unhein sura Bara't (Tauba) ke ehkaam ke elaan karne ka hukm diya. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, chunanche hamarey sath Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi yaumun-nahar hi mein sura Bara't (Tauba) ka elaan kya aur iska ke aainda saal se koi mushrik Haj na karey aur na koi nangey ho kar tawaaf kare."
4657,Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne us Haj ke mauqe par jiska unhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ameer banaya tha. Hijjatul-wada se (eik saal ( pahley 9 hijri mein unhein bhi un elaan karne walon mein rakha tha jinhein logon mein aap ne ye elaan karne ke liye bheja tha ke aainda saal se koi mushrik Haj karne na aaey aur na koi Baitullah ka tawaaf nangaa ho kar kare. Humaid ne kaha ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki us hadis se malum hota hai ke yaumun-nahar badey Haj ka din hai.
4658,"ham Huzefa bin Yamaan ki khidmat mein hazir they. unhon-ne kaha ye aayat jin logon ke barey mein utri unmein se ab sirf teen shakhs baqi hain, isi tarah munaafiqon mein se bhi ab char shakhs baqi hain. itney mein aik dehati kehney laga aap to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahabi hain, hamein un logon ke mutaalliq bataiye ke unka kya hashr hoga jo hamarey gharon mein chhed karke achi cheezein churaa kar ley jatey hain? unhon-ne kaha ke ye log fasiq badkaar hain. haan un munaafiqon mein char ke siwa aur koi baqi nahi raha hai aur aik to itna boodha ho chuka hai ke agar thanda pani peetaa hai to uski thand ka bhi usey pata nahi chaltaa."
4659,"mujh se Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke tumhara khazaana jis mein zakat na di gaee ho qiyamat ke din ganjey naag ki shakl ikhtiyar karega."
4660,"us jangal mein aap ne kyon qiyam ko pasand kya? farmaya ke ham Sham (Syria) mein they. (mujh main aur wahan ke Hakim Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) mein ikhtilaf ho gaya) maine ye aayat padhi ( والذين يكنزون الذهب والفضة wla ينفقونها في سبيل الله فبشرهم بعذاب أليم‏ (ke ''aur jo log sona aur chandi jama karke rakhtey hain aur usko kharch nahi kartey Allah ki raah mein, aap unhein aik dardnak azab ki khabar suna dein.'' to Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey ke ye aayat ham musalmanon ke barey mein nahi hai (jab wo zakat detey rahein) balke ahle-kitab ke barey mein hai. farmaya ke maine is par kaha ke ye hamarey barey mein bhi hai aur ahle-kitab ke barey mein bhi hai."
4661,ham Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath nikley to unhon-ne kaha ke ye (mazkoora bula aayat) zakat ke hukm se pahley nazil hui thi. phir jab zakat ka hukm ho gaya to Allah Taala ne zakat se maalon ko paak kar diya.
4662,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (hijjatul-wadaa ke khutbey mein) farmaya ke dekho zamana phir apni pehli usi haiyat par aa gaya hai jis par Allah Taala ne aasman w zameen ko paida kya tha. saal baara mahiney ka hota hai, unmein se char hurmat waley mahiney hain. teen to lagaataar yani zii-Qa'da, Zil-Hijja aur mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) aur chotha rajab Muzar jo jumaadal-Ukhra aur Shoban ke darmyan mein padta hai."
4663,mujh se Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya : unhon-ne kaha ke main ghaare-saur main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath tha. maine kaafiron ke paon dekhey (jo hamarey sar par khadey huey they) Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ghabraa gaey aur boley : ya Rasulullah! agar unmein se kisi ne zara bhi qadam uthaey to wo ham ko dekh lega. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke to kya samajhta hai un 2 aadmiyon ko (koii nuqsan pahuncha sakega) jinke sath tesraa Allah Taala ho.
4664,"jab mera Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se ikhtilaf ho gaya tha to maine kaha ke unke walid Zubair-bin-Awaam (Raziallahu anhu) they, unki walida Asma binte-abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) thin, unki khala Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) thin. unke naanaa Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) they aur unki daadi (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki phoophii) Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) thin. ( Abdullah-bin Muhammad ne bayan kya ke) maine Sufiyan (ibne-Uena) se puchha ke is riwayat ki sanad kya hai? to unhon-ne kehna shuru kya ( حدثنا ( ham se hadis bayan ki lekin abhi itna hi kehney paaey they ke unhein aik doosrey shakhs ne dusri baton mein laga diya aur (raawii ka naam) ibne-Juraij wo na bayan kar sakey."
4665,"Ibne-Abbas aur ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ke darmyan bait ka jhagdaa paida ho gaya tha. main subah ko Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya aap Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se jang karna chahtey hain, iske bawajud ke Allah ke haram ki be-hurmatii hogi ? Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Maaz-Allah ! ye to Allah Taala ne ibne-Zubair aur banu- Umayya hi ke muqaddar mein likh diya hai ke wo haram ki be-hurmatii karein. Allah ki qasam! main kisi sura mein bhi us be-hurmatii ke liye taiyaar nahi hun. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke logon ne mujh se kaha tha ke ibne-Zubair se bait kar lo. maine unse kaha ke mujhey unki khilafat ko taslim karne mein kya tammul ho sakta hai, unke walid Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hawaarii they, aap ki murad Zubair-bin-Awaam se thi. unke naanaa saahibe-ghaar they, ishara Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf tha. unki walida saahibun-nataaqain (do kamarbandon waalii) thin yani Asma (Raziallahu anha) . unki khala Ummul-Momenin thin, murad Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se thi. unki phoophii Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi thin, murad Khadija (Raziallahu anha) se thi. Ibne-Abbas ki murad in baton se ye thi ke wo bahut si khoobiyon ki Malik hain aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki phoophii unki daadi hain, ishara Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf tha. iske ilawa wo khud Islam mein hamesha saaf kirdaar aur paak daman rahe aur Quran ke aalim hain aur Allah ki qasam! agar wo mujh se achchha bartaw karein to unko karna hi chahiye wo mere bahut qareeb ke rishtedar hain aur agar wo mujh par hukumat karein to khair hukumat karein wo hamarey barabar ki izzat waley hain. lekin Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne to Tuwait, Usama aur Humaid ke logon ko ham par tarjeeh di hai. unki murad mukhtalif qabaayel yani banu-Asad, banu-Tuwait, banu-Usaama aur banu-Asad se thi. idhar ibne-abii-al-aas badi umdagii se chal raha hai yani Abdul-Malik bin Marwan musalsal pesh qadmii kar raha hai aur Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne iske samney dam daba li hai."
4666,"ham Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to unhon-ne kaha ke ibne-Zubair par tumhen hairat nahi hoti . wo ab khilafat ke liye khadey ho gaey hain to maine irada kar liya ke unke liye mehnat mashaqqat karunga ke aisi mehnat aur mashaqqat maine Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye bhi nahi ki. halanke wo donon unse har haisiyat se behtar they. maine logon se kaha ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki phoophii ki aulad mein se hain. Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ke betey aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke nawaasey, Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ke bhai ke betey, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki behan ke betey. lekin Abdullah-bin-Zubair ne kya kya wo mujh se ghurur karne lagey. unhon-ne nahi chaha ke main unke khas musaahibon mein rahoon (apne dil mein kaha) mujh ko hargiz ye guman na tha ke main to unse aisi aajizii karunga aur wo is par bhi mujh se razi na hongey. khair ab mujhey ummeed nahi ke wo mere sath bhalai karengey jo hona tha wo hua ab banii-Umayya jo mere chacha zaad bhai hain agar mujh par hukumat karein to ye mujh ko auron ke hukumat karne se zyada pasand hai."
4667,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas kuchh maal aaya to aap ne char aadmiyon mein usey taqseem kar diya. (jo nau (9) Muslim they) aur farmaya ke main ye maal de kar unki diljoii karna chahta hun is par (banu-Tameem ka ( aik shakhs bola ke aap ne insaf nahi kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us shakhs ki nasl se aisey log paida hongey jo Deen se bahar ho jaengey.
4668,jab hamein khairat karne ka hukm hua to ham mazdoorii par bojh uthatey (aur uski mazdoorii sadqe mein de detey) chunanche abu-Aqeel usi mazdoorii se aadha saa khairat lekar aaey aur aik doosrey sahabi Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf us se zyada laey. is par munaafiqon ne kaha ke Allah ko us (yani aqeel) ke sadqe ki koi zarurat nahi thi aur us doosrey (Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Auf) ne to mahz dikhawey ke liye itna bahut sa sadqa diya hai. chunanche ye aayat nazil huii الذين يلمزون المطوعين من المؤمنين في الصدقات والذين لا يجدون إلا جهدهم‏ ke ''ye aisey log hain jo sadqaat ke barey mein nafl sadqa dene waley musalmanon par ta'an kartey hain aur khususan un logon par jinhein bajuz unki mehnat mazdoorii ke kuchh nahi miltaa.'' aakhir aayat tak.
4669,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sadqe ki targheeb detey they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kuchh sahaba mazdoorii karke latey aur) badi mushkil se) aik mudd ka sadqa kar saktey lekin aaj unhein mein kuchh aisey hain jinke paas laakhon dirham hain. ghaaliban unka ishara khud apni taraf tha (Hammaad ne kaha haan sach hai)."
4670,"jab Abdullah-bin-Ubai (munaafiq) ka intiqal hua to uske ladkey Abdullah bin-Abdullah (jo pukhta musalman they) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya ke aap apni qamees unke walid ke kafan ke liye inayat farma dein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qamees inayat farmai. phir unhon-ne kaha ke aap namaaze-janaaza bhi padha dein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) namaaze-janaaza padhaaney ke liye bhi aagey badh gaey. itney mein umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka daman pakad liya aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! uski namaaze-janaaza padhaaney ja rahe hain, jabke Allah Taala ne aapko us se mana bhi farma diya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Allah Taala ne mujhey ikhtiyar diya hai farmaya hai استغفر لهم أو لا تستغفر لهم إن تستغفر لهم سبعين مرة‏ke ''aap unke liye istighfar karein chahe na karein. agar aap unke liye 70 baar bhi istighfar karengey (tab bhi Allah unhein nahi bakhshnega).'' isliye main 70 martaba se bhi zyada istighfar karunga. (mumkin hai ke Allah Taala zyada istighfar karne se maaf kar de) umr (Raziallahu anhu) boley lekin ye shakhs to munafiq hai. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke aakhir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski namaaze-janaaza padhai. iske baad Allah Taala ne ye hukm nazil farmaayaa تصل على أحد منهم مات أبدا wla تقم على قبره‏ ke ''aur unmein se jo koi mar jaey is par kabhi bhi Namaz na padhiye aur na uski qabr par khada hoiye.''"
4671,"jab Abdullah-bin-Ubai ibne-Salool ki maut hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se uski namaaze-janaaza padhaaney ke liye kaha gaya. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padhaaney ke liye khadey huey to main jaldi se khidmat nabwi mein pahuncha aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! aap ibne-abi ( munafiq ( ki namaaze-janaaza padhaaney lagey halanke us ne falan-falan din is-is tarah ki baatein (Islam ke khilaf ( ki thin ? umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke main uski kahi hui baatein eik-eik karke pesh karne laga. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tabassum karke farmaya ke umr ! mere paas se hat jao (aur saf mein ja ke khadey ho jaao). maine israar kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey ikhtiyar diya gaya hai. isliye maine (iske liye istighfar karne aur uski namaaze-janaaza padhaaney hi ko) pasand kya, agar mujhey ye malum ho jaey ke 70 martaba se zyada istighfar karne se uski maghfirat ho jaeygi to main 70 martaba se zyada istighfar karunga. bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhai aur wapas tashrif laaey, thodi der abhi hui thi ke sura Bara't (Tauba) ki 2 aayatein nazil huiin تصل على أحد منهم مات أبدا ke ''unmein se jo koi mar jaey is par kabhi bhi Namaz na padhiye.'' aakhir aayat ( وهم فاسقون‏ ( tak. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke baad mein mujhey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney apni us darja jur'at par khud bhi hairat hui aur Allah aur uske rasool behtar jaanney waley hain."
4672,"jab Abdullah-bin-Ubai ka intiqal hua to iske betey Abdullah bin-abdullaah-bin-Ubaii Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein apna kurta inayat farmaya aur farmaya ke us kurtey se usey kafan diya jaey phir aap is par Namaz padhaaney ke liye khadey huey to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap ka daman pakad liya aur arz kya aap is par Namaz padhaaney ke liye taiyaar ho gaey halanke ye munafiq hai, Allah Taala bhi aapko unke liye istighfar se mana kar chuka hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ne mujhey ikhtiyar diya hai..... Allah Taala ka irshad hai استغفر لهم أو لا تستغفر لهم إن تستغفر لهم سبعين Murra فلن يغفر الله لهم ke ''aap unke liye istighfar karein chahe na karein. agar aap unke liye 70 baar bhi istighfar karengey jab bhi Allah unhein nahi bakhshega.'' Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main 70 martaba se bhi zyada istighfar karunga. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par Namaz padhi aur ham ne bhi unke sath padhi. iske baad Allah Taala ne ye aayat utaarii ولا تصل على أحد منهم مات أبدا wla تقم على قبره إنهم كفروا بالله ورسوله وماتوا وهم فاسقون‏ke ''aur unmein se jo koi mar jaey, aap is par kabhi bhi janaaza na padhein aur na uski qabr par khadey hun. beshak unhon-ne Allah aur uske rasool ke sath kufr kya hai aur wo us haal mein marey hain ke wo naafarmaan they. ''"
4673,"unhon-ne Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se unke jange-Tabook mein Sharik na ho sakney ka waqia suna. unhon-ne batlaya , Allah ki qism ! hidayat ke baad Allah ne mujh par itna bada aur koi inaam nahi kya jitna Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney sach bolney ke baad zahir hua tha ke usne mujhey jhoot bolney se bachaayaa, warna mein bhi isi tarah halaak ho jata jis tarah doosrey log jhooti maazratein bayan karne waley halaak huey they aur Allah Taala ne unke barey mein wahi nazil ki thii سيحلفون بالله لكم إذا انقلبتم إليهم‏ ke ''an-qareeb ye log tumharey saamney, jab tum unke paas wapas jaogey. Allah ki qism kha jaaengey.'' aakhir aayat ( الفاسقين‏ ( tak."
4674,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se farmaya ke raat ( khuwab mein) mere paas 2 Farishtey aaey aur mujhey utha kar aik Shahar mein le gaey jo soney aur chandi ki enton se banaya gaya tha, wahan hamein aisey log miley jinka aadha badan bahut hi zyada khoobsoorat, itna ke kisi dekhney waley ne aisa husn na dekha hoga aur badan ka doosra aadha hissey bahut hi zyada bad-soorat tha, itna ke kisi ne bhi aisi bad-soortii nahi dekhi hogi. donon farishton ne un logon se kaha jao aur us nehar mein ghota lagaao. wo gaey aur nehar mein ghota laga aaey. jab wo hamarey paas aaey to unki bad-soortii jati rahi aur ab wo bahut hi zyada khoobsurat nazar aatey they phir farishton ne mujh se kaha ke ye ''jannate-adn'' hai aur aap ka makan yahin hai. jin logon ko abhi aap ne dekha ke jism ka aadha hissey khoobsurat tha aur aadha bad-soorat, to ye wo log they jinhoney duniya mein achchhey aur burey sab kaam kiye they aur Allah Taala ne unhein maaf kar diya tha."
4675,"jab abu-Taalib ke intiqal ka waqt hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas tashrif le gaey, us waqt wahan abu-Jahal aur Abdullah-bin-Ubai Umayya baithey huey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke (aap aik baar zaban se kalima) la ilaaha-illallaah keh dijiye mein usi ko (aap ki nijat ke liye waseela bana kar) Allah ki bargah mein pesh kar loonga. is par abu-Jahal aur Abdullah abi Umayya kehney lagey : abu-Taalib ! kya aap abdul-Muttalib ke Deen se phir jaaogey? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kaha ke ab main aap ke liye barabar maghfirat ki dua mangta rahunga jab tak mujhey us se rok na diya jaey, to ye aayat nazil huii ما كان للنبي والذين آمنوا أن يستغفروا للمشركين ولو كانوا أولي قربى من بعد ما تبين لهم أنهم أصحاب الجحيم ke ''nabii aur eman walon ke liye jaaiz nahi ke wo mushrikon ke liye bakhshish ki dua karein. agarche wo (mushrekeen) rishtedar hi kyon na hun. jab un par ye zahir ho chukey ke wo (yaqeenan) ahale-dozakh se hain.''"
4676,(unke walid ( Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) jab naa-beenaa ho gaey to unke beton mein yahi unko rastey mein sath lekar chaltey hain. unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Kab-bin-Malik se unke waaqie ke silsiley mein suna jiske barey mein aayat ( وعلى الثلاثة الذين خلفوا‏ ( nazil hui thi. aap ne aakhir mein (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se) arz kya tha ke apni tauba ke qabool honey ki khushi mein apna tamam maal Allah aur uske rasool ke rastey mein khairat karta hun. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi apna kuchh thoda maal apne paas hi rehney do. ye tumharey haq mein bhi behtar hai.
4677,"maine apne walid Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna. wo un teen sahaba mein se they jinki tauba qabool ki gaee thi. unhon-ne bayan kya ke 2 jangon, jange-Tabook aur jange-badr ke siwa aur kisi ghazwey mein kabhi main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath janey se nahi ruka tha. unhon-ne bayan kya chasht ke waqt jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (jang se wapas tashrif laaey) to maine sach bolney ka pukhta irada kar liya aur aap ka safar se wapas aaney mein mamool (routine) ye tha ke chasht ke waqt hi aap (Madeena) pahunchtey they aur sabse pahley masjid mein tashrif ley jatey aur 2 rakaat Namaz padhtey (bahar-haal) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se aur meri tarah uzr bayan karne waley 2 aur sahaba se doosrey sahaba ko baat-cheet karne se mana kar diya. hamarey ilawa aur bhi bahut se log (jo zahir mein musalman they) us jang mein Sharik nahi huey lekin aap ne unmein se kisi se bhi baat cheet ki manaahii nahi ki thi. chunanche logon ne ham se baat-cheet karna chhod diya. main usi haalat mein thehra raha. mamla bahut tool pakadta ja raha tha. idhar meri nazar mein sabse aham mamla ye tha ke agar kahin (is arse mein) main mar gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujh par namaaze-janaaza nahi padhaaeingey ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho jaey to afsos logon ka yahi tarze-amal mere sath phir hamesha ke liye baqi reh jaeyga na mujh se koi guftgu karega aur na mujh par namaaze-janaaza padheyga. aakhir Allah Taala ne hamari tauba ki bashaarat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par us waqt nazil ki jab raat ka aakhiri tehai hissey baqi reh gaya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar mein tashrif rakhtey they. Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ka mujh par bada ehsan w karam tha aur wo meri madad kya karti thin. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Umme-Salma ! Kab ki tauba qabool ho gaee. unhon-ne arz kya. phir main unke yahan kisi ko bhej kar ye khushkhabri na pahunchwaa dun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye khabar suntey hi log jama ho jaeinge aur saari raat tumhen soney nahi dengey. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fajr ki Namaz padhney ke baad bataya ke Allah ne hamari tauba qabool kar li hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab ye khushkhabri sunai to aap ka chehra Mubarak munawwar ho gaya jaisey chaand ka tukda ho aur (jang mein na Sharik hone-waale doosrey logon se) jinhoney ma'zirat ki thi aur unki ma'zirat qabool bhi ho gaee thi. ham teen sahaba ka mamla bilkul mukhtalif tha ke Allah Taala ne hamari tauba qabool honey ke mutaalliq wahi nazil ki, lekin jab un doosrey jang mein Sharik na hone-waale logon ka zikr kya, jinhoney Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney jhoot bola tha aur jhooti ma'zirat ki thi to us darja burai ke sath kya ke kisi ka bhi itni burai ke sath zikr na kya hoga. Allah Taala ne farmaayaa يعتذرون إليكم إذا رجعتم إليهم قل لا تعتذروا لن نؤمن لكم قد نبأنا الله من أخباركم وسيرى الله عملكم ورسوله‏ke ''ye log tumharey sab ke samney uzr pesh karengey, jab tum unke paas wapas jaogey to aap keh dein ke bahaney na banao ham hargiz tumhari baat na maanengey! beshak ham ko Allah tumhari khabar de chuka hai aur an-qareeb Allah aur uska rasool tumhara amal dekh lengey.'' aakhir aayat tak."
4678,"wo Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko sath lekar chaltey they. (jab wo naa-beenaa ho gaey they) Abdullah ne bayan kya ke maine Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo jange-Tabook main apni ghair haziri ka qissa bayan kar rahe they, kaha ke Allah ki qism ! sach bolney ka jitna umda phal Allah Taala ne mujhey diya, kisi ko na diya hoga. jab se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney maine is barey mein sachchii baat kahi thi, us waqt se aaj tak kabhi jhoot ka irada bhi nahi kya aur Allah ne apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par ye aayat nazil ki thii لقد تاب الله على النبي والمهاجرين ke '' beshak Allah ne Nabi par aur muhajireen w Ansar par rehmat ke sath tawajjoh farmai. aakhir aayat وكونوا مع الصادقين‏ tak."
4679,"jab (11 hijri) mein yamaama ki ladai mein (jo Musailma kazzaab se hui thi) bahut se sahaba maarey gaey to Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey bulaayaa, unke paas umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi maujood they. unhon-ne mujh se kaha, umr (Raziallahu anhu) mere paas aaey aur kaha ke jange-yamaama mein bahut zyada musalman Shahid ho gaey hain aur mujhey khatrah hai ke (kuffaar ke saath) ladaaiyon mein yoonhii Quran ke ulma aur qaari Shahid hongey aur is tarah bahut sa Quran zaaye ho jaeyga ab to aik hi sura hai ke aap Quran ko aik jagah jama kara dein aur meri raey to ye hai ke aap zaroor Quran ko jama kara dein Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke is par maine umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha, aisa kaam mein kis tarah kar sakta hun jo khud Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nahi kya tha. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, Allah ki qism ! ye to mahz aik nek kaam hai. iske baad umr (Raziallahu anhu) mujh se us maamle par baat kartey rahe aur aakhir mein Allah Taala ne is khidmat ke liye mera bhi Sina khol diya aur meri bhi raey wahi ho gaee jo umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki thi. Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) wahin khamosh baithey huey they. phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : tum jawan aur samajhdaar ho hamein tum par kisi qism ka shuba bhi nahi aur tum Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wahi likha bhi kartey they, isliye tum hi Quran Majeed ko jaa-bajaa se talash karke usey jama kar do. Allah ki qasam! ke agar Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) mujh se koi pahaad utha ke ley janey ke liye kehtey to ye mere liye utnaa bhari nahi tha jitna Quran ki tarteeb ka hukm. maine arz kya aap log aik aisey kaam ke karne par kis tarah aamada ho gaey, jisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nahi kya tha to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! ye aik nek kaam hai. phir main unse is mas'ale par guftgu karta raha, yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne is khidmat ke liye mera bhi Sina khol diya. jis tarah Abu-Bakar w umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka Sina khola tha. chunanche main utha aur maine khaal, haddi aur khajoor ki shakhon se (jin par Quran Majeed likha hua tha, us daur ke riwaaj ke mutaabiq) Quran Majeed ko jama karna shuru kar diya aur logon ke (jo Quran ke Hafiz they) haafize se bhi madad li aur sura Tauba ki 2 aayatein Khuzaima Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas mujhey miliin. unke ilawa kisi ke paas mujhey nahi mili thi. (wo aayatein ye thiin) لقد جاءكم رسول من أنفسكم عزيز عليه ما عنتم حريص عليكم aakhir tak. phir musahaf jis mein Quran Majeed jama kya gaya tha, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas raha, aap ki wafat ke baad umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas mehfooz raha, phir aap ki wafat ke baad aap ki sahibzadi (ummul-momeneen Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke paas mehfooz rahaa). Shuaib ke sath is hadis ko Usman bin umr aur Lais-bin-Sad ne bhi Yunus se, unhon-ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat kya, aur Leis ne kaha mujh se Abdur-Rehman bin Khalid ne bayan kya, unhon-ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat kya usmein Khuzaima ke badley abu-Khuzaima Ansari hai aur Musa ne Ibrahim se riwayat ki, kaha ham se ibne-Shahab ne bayan kya, is riwayat mein bhi abu-Khuzaima hai. Musa bin Ismail ke sath us hadis ko Yaqoob-bin-Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ne bhi apne walid Ibraaheem-bin-Sa'd se riwayat kya aur Abu-Saabit Muhammad-bin Ubaidullah madni ne, kaha ham se Ibrahim ne bayan kya is riwayat mein shak ke sath Khuzaima ya abu-Khuzaima mazkoor hai."
4680,jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to yahood Aashooraa ka roza rakhtey they. unhon-ne bataya ke isi din Musa (Alaihissalam) ko firaun par fateh mili thi. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba se farmaya ke Musa (Alaihissalam) ke ham unse bhi zyada mustahiq hain isliye tum bhi roza rakho .
4681,"aap aayat ki qirat is tarah kartey they ( ألا إنهم تثنوني صدورهم‏ ( maine unse aayat ke mutaalliq poochha. unhon-ne kaha ke kuchh log usmein haya kartey they ke khuli hui jagah mein haajat ke liye baithney mein, aasman ki taraf sattar kholney mein, is tarah sohbat kartey waqt aasman ki taraf kholney mein parwardigar se sharmaatey."
4682,Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) is tarah qirat kartey they ( ألا إنهم تثنوني صدورهم‏ ( Muhammad-bin Ibad ne puchha : aey abul-Abbaas ! ( تثنوني صدورهم‏ (ka kya matlab hai? batlaya ke kuchh log apni biwi se ham-bistarii karne mein haya kartey aur haajat poori karney ke liye baithtey huey bhi haya kartey they. unhiin ke barey mein ye aayat nazil hui ke) ألا إنهم تثنوني صدورهم‏ ( aakhir aayat tak. ''
4683,Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne aayat ki qirat is tarah ki thii ( ألا إنهم يثنون صدورهم ليستخفوا منه ألا حين يستغشون ثيابهم‏ (aur Amr-bin-Dinar ke ilawa auron ne bayan kya Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se ke) يستغشون‏ ( yani apne sar chipa letey hain. ( سيء بهم‏ ( yani apni qaum se wo bd-gumaan hua. ( وضاق بهم‏ ( yani apne mahmaanon ko dekh kar wo bd-gumaan hua ke unki qaum unhein bhi pareshan karegii. (بقطع من الليل‏) yani raat ki siyaahii main aur Mujahid ne kaha ( أنيب‏ (ke mana mein rujoo karta hun (mutwajjeh hota hoon).
4684,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala farmata hai ke bando! (meri raah mein) kharch karo to main bhi tum par kharch karunga aur farmaya, Allah ka hath bharaa hua hai. raat aur din musalsal ke kharch se bhi usmein kam nahi hota aur farmaya tum ne dekha nahi jab se Allah ne aasman w zameen ko paida kya hai, musalsal kharch kiye ja raha hai lekin uske hath mein koi kami nahi hui, uska arsh pani par tha aur uske hath mein meezaane-adl (insaaf ki taraazu) hai jisey wo jhukata aur uthata rehta hai."
4685,"aik shakhs naam naa-maaloom aap ke samney aaya aur puchha : aey abu-Abdur-Rehmaan! ya ye kaha ke aey ibne-Umar! kya aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sargoshi ke mutaalliq kuchh suna hai (jo Allah Taala mominon se qiyamat ke din karega). unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke momin apne rab ke qareeb laya jaeyga aur Hisham ne ( يدنو المؤمن ( ) bajaey ( يدنى المؤمن ( kaha ( matlab aik hi hai. yahan tak ke Allah Taala apna aik taraf is par rakhega aur uske gunahon ka iqrar karaaeyga ke falan gunah tujhey yad hai? banda arz karega, yad hai, mere rab! mujhey yad hai, 2 martaba iqrar karega. phir Allah Taala farmaeyga ke maine duniya main tumharey gunahon ko chhipaaey rakha aur aaj bhi tumhari maghfirat karunga. phir uski nekiyon ka daftar lapet diya jaeyga lekin doosrey log ya (ye kaha ke) kuffaar to unke mutaalliq mahshar mein elaan kya jaeyga ke yahi wo log hain jinhoney Allah par jhoot baandha tha aur Sheban ne bayan kya, unse Qatada ne ke ham se Safwan ne bayan kya."
4686,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala zaalim ko chand roz duniya mein mohlat deta rehta hai lekin jab pakadta hai to phir nahi chhodtaa. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us aayat ki tilawat ki وكذلك أخذ ربك إذا أخذ القرى وهى ظالمة إن أخذه أليم شديد‏''aur terey parwardigar ki pakad isi tarah hai, jab wo basti walon ko pakadta hai. jo (apne oopar) zulm kartey rahtey hain, beshak uski pakad badi takleef dene wali aur badi hi sakht hai.''"
4687,"aik shakhs ne kisi ghair aurat ko bosa de diya aur phir wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap se apna gunah bayan kya. is par ye aayat nazil huiiوأقم الصلاة طرفى النهار وزلفا من الليل إن الحسنات يذهبن السيئات ذلك ذكرى للذاكرين''aur tum Namaz ki pabandi karo din ke donon saron par aur raat ke kuchh hisson mein beshak nekiyan mitaa deti hain badiyon ko, ye aik nasihat hai nasihat manney walon ke liye.'' un sahib ne arz kya ye aayat sirf mere hi liye hai (ke nekiyan badiyon ko mitaa deti hain) ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke meri ummat ke har insan ke liye hai jo is par amal kare."
4688,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Karim bin Karim bin Karim bin Karim Yusuf bin Yaqoob bin Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim they.
4689,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kisi ne sawal kya ke insanon mein kon sabse zyada sharif hai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke sabse zyada sharif wo hai jo sabse zyada muttaqii ho. sahaba ne arz kya ke hamarey sawal ka maqsad ye nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir sabse zyada sharif Yusuf (Alaihissalam) hain (نبي الله ابن نبي الله ابن نبي الله ابن خليل الله). sahaba ne arz kya ke hamarey sawal ka ye bhi maqsad nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchha , Arab ke khandanon ke mutaalliq tum malum karna chahtey ho? sahaba ne arz kya ji haan. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jahiliyat mein jo log sharif samjhey jatey they, Islam laney ke baad bhi wo sharif hain, jabke Deen ki samajh bhi unhein hasil ho jaey. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) abu-Usama ne Ubaidullah se ki hai."
4690,"maine Zohri se suna, unhon-ne Urwa bin Zubair, Saeed-bin-Musaiyab, Alqama bin Waqas aur Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke us waqia ke mutaalliq suna jis mein tohmat lagaaney walon ne un par tohmat lagai thi aur phir Allah Taala ne unki paakii nazil ki. un tamam logon ne mujh se us qisse ka kuchh kuchh tukda bayan kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (Aaisha (Raziallahu anhu) se) farmaya ke agar tum barii ho to an-qareeb Allah Taala tumhari paakii nazil kar dega lekin agar to aalooda ho gaee hai to Allah se maghfirat talab kar aur uske huzoor mein tauba kar (Aaisha (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke) maine is par kaha : Allah ki qasam! meri aur aap ki misal Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke walid jaisi hai (aur unhein ki kahi hui baat mein bhi dohraatii hon ke) (فصبر جميل والله المستعان على ما تصفون‏)''so sabr karna ( hi ( achchha hai aur tum jo kuchh bayan kartey ho is par Allah hi madad karega.'' iske baad Allah Taala ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki paakii mein sura Noor ki) إن الذين جاءوا بالإفك‏ ( se aakhir tak das aayatein utaarein."
4691,main aur Aaisha baithey huey they ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko bukhar chadh gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ghaaliban ye un baton ki wjah hua hoga jinka charcha ho raha hai. umme-Roomaan (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke ji haan. iske baad Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) baith gain aur kaha ke meri aur aap logon ki misal Yaqoob (Alaihissalam) aur unke beton jaisi hai aur aap log jo kuchh bayan kartey ho is par Allah hi madad kare.
4692,"Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( هيت لك ( padha aur kaha ke jis tarah hamein ye lafz sikhaya gaya hai. isi tarah ham padhtey hain. ( مثواه‏ ( yani iska thikaanaa, darja. ( ألفيا‏ ( yani paya usi se hai. ( ألفوا آباءهم‏ (aur ( ألفينا‏ ( (doosri aayaton mein) aur ibne-Masood se (sura Saaffaat) main (بل عجبت ويسخرون) manqool hai."
4693,"Quraish ne jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par eman laney mein taakheer ki to aap ne unke haq mein baddua ki ke aey Allaah! un par Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke zamane ka sa qahat nazil farmaa. chunanche aisa qahat padaa ke koi cheez nahi miltii thi aur wo haddiyon ke khaney par majbur ho gaey they. logon ki us waqt ye kaifiyat thi ke aasman ki taraf nazar utha ke dekhtey they, to bhook w piyaas ki shiddat se dhuaan sa nazar aata tha. Allah Taala ne farmaayaa (فارتقب يوم تأتي السماء بدخان مبين‏) ''to aap intizar kijiye us roz ka jab aasman ki taraf aik nazar aaney wala dhuaan paida ho.''aur farmaya ( إنا كاشفو العذاب قليلا إنكم عائدون‏ ( '' beshak ham us azab ko hata lengey aur tum bhi (apni pehli haalat par) lot aaogey.'' ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke azab se yahi qahat ka azab murad hai kyonke aakhirat ka azab kaafiron se talney wala nahi hai."
4694,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah lot (Alaihissalam) par apni rehmat nazil farmaai ke unhon-ne aik zabardast sahaarey ki panah leney ke liye kaha tha aur agar main qaid-khaaney mein itney dinon tak reh chuka hota jitney din Yusuf (Alaihissalam) rahe they, to bulaney waley ki baat radd na karta aur ham ko to Ibrahim ke b-nisbat shak hona zyada sazawar hai. jab Allah paak ne unse farmaayaa (أولم تؤمن قال بلى ولكن ليطمئن قلبي) ke kya tujh ko yaqin nahi ? unhon-ne kaha kyon nahi yaqin to hai par main chahta hun ke aur itminan ho jaey."
4695,"Urwa ne un se aayat «حتی اذا استیأس الرسل» ke mutaalliq puchha tha. Urwa ne bayan kya ke maine puchha tha (aayat main) «کذبوا» (halkey zaal ke saath) ya «کذبوا» (tashdeed ke saath) is par Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke «کذبوا» (tashdeed ke saath) is par maine unsey kaha ke anbiya to yaqin ke sath jantey they ke unki qaum unhein jhutlaa rahi hai. phir «ظنوا» se kya murad hai, unhoney kaha apni zindagi ki qism beshak paighambaron ko is ka yaqin tha. maine kaha «کذبوا» halkey zaal ke sath padhein too kya kharabi hai. unhoney kaha Maaz-Allah kahin paighambar apney parwardigar ki nisbat aisa guman kar saktey hain. maine kaha achchha is aayat ka matlab kya hai? unhoney kaha matlab ye hai ke paighambaron ko jin logon ne maanaa unki tasdeeq ki jab un par aik lambi muddat tak aafat aur museebat aati rahi aur Allah ki madad aaney mein der hui aur paighambar unke eman laney se naa-ummeed ho gaey jinhon ne unko jhutlaayaa tha aur ye guman karney lagey ke jo log eman laey hain ab wo bhii ham ko jhoota samajhney lagengey. us waqt Allah ki madad aan pahunchii."
4696,mein ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se kaha ho sakta hai ye «کذبوا» halkey 'z' ke sath ho too unhoney farmaya : ma'aaz-Allah! phir wahii hadis bayan ki jo uper guzrii.
4697,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ghaib ki panch kunjiyaan hain jinhein Allah ke siwa koi nahi janta. Allah ke siwa koi nahi janta ke kal kya honey wala hai, Allah ke siwa koi nahi janta ke aurton ke raham mein kya kami beshi hoti rehti hai, Allah ke siwa koi nahi janta ke barish Kab barsegii, koi shakhs nahi janta ke uski maut kahan hogi aur Allah ke siwa koi nahi janta ke qiyamat Kab qaaim hogi."
4698,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya : achchha mujh ko batlao to wo kon sa darakht hai jo musalman ki manind (tarah) hai jiske pattey nahi girtey, har waqt mewa de jata hai? ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain mere dil mein aaya wo khajoor ka darakht hai magar maine dekha ke Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) baithey huey hain unhon-ne jawab nahi diya to mujh ko un buzurgon ke samney kalam karna achchha malum nahi hua. jab un logon ne kuchh jawab nahi diya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud hi farmaya wo khajoor ka darakht hai. jab ham us majlis se khadey huey to maine apne walid umr (Raziallahu anhu) se arz kya : baabaa-jaan! Allah ki qasam! mere dil mein aaya tha ke main keh dun wo khajoor ka darakht hai. unhon-ne kaha phir tu ney keh kyon na diya. maine kaha aap logon ne koi baat nahi ki maine aagey badh kar baat karna munasib na jaanaa. unhon-ne kaha waah agar to us waqt keh deta to mujh ko itney-itney (laal-laal oont ka ( maal milney se bhi zyada khushi hoti ."
4699,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke musalman se jab qabr mein sawal hoga to wo gawahi dega ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur ye ke Muhammad Allah ke rasool hain. Allah Taala ke irshaad ( يثبت الله الذين آمنوا بالقول الثابت في الحياة الدنيا وفي الآخرة‏ ) ''Allaah eman walon ki us pakkii baat (ki barkat ( se mazbut rakhta hai, duniyawii zindagi main ( bhi) aur aakhirat main ( bhi )'' ka yahi matlab hai."
4700,aayat (ألم تر إلى الذين بدلوا نعمة الله كفرا‏) mein kuffaar se ahal Makka murad hain.
4701,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jab Allah Taala aasman mein koi faisla farmata hai to malaaika aajizii se apne par maarney lagtey hain. jaisa ke Allah Taala ke irshad mein hai ke jaisey kisi saaf chikney patthar par zanjeer ke (maarney se awaz paida hoti hai) aur Ali-bin-Abdullaah al-madeenii ne bayan kya ke Sufiyan-bin-Uena ke siwa aur rawiyon ne (Safwaan) ke baad) ينفذهم ذلك ( (jis se un par dahshat taarii hoti hai) ke alfaz kahey hain. phir Allah paak apna hukm farishton tak pahuncha deta hai, jab unke dilon par se dar jata rehta hai to doosrey door waley Farishtey nazdeek waley farishton se poochhtey hain parwardigar ne kya hukm saadir farmaya, nazdeek waley Farishtey kehtey hain bajaa irshad farmaya aur wo uncha hai badaa. farishton ki ye baatein chori se baat udaaney waley shaitan pa letey hain. ye baat udaaney waley shaitan uper taley rahtey hain (eik par aik ( Sufiyan ne apne daain hath ki ungliyan khol kar aik par aik karke batlaya ke is tarah shaitan uper taley reh kar wahan jatey hain. phir bhi kabhi aisa hota hai. Farishtey khabar pa kar aag ka sho'la phainktey hain wo baat sunney waley ko us se pahley jalaa daalta hai ke wo apne peechhey waley ko wo baat pahuncha de. kabhi aisa hota hai ke wo sho'la us tak nahi pahunchtaa aur wo apne nichey waley shaitan ko wo baat pahuncha deta hai, wo us se nichey waley ko is tarah wo baat zameen tak pahuncha detey hain. yahan tak ke zameen tak aa pahunchti hai. (kabhii Sufiyan ne yun kaha) phir wo baat Nujoomi (Astrologer) ke munh par dali jati hai. wo aik baat mein so baatein jhoot apni taraf se mila kar logon se bayan karta hai. koi koii baat uski sach nikalti hai to log kehney lagtey hain dekho us Nujoomi (Astrologer) ne falan din ham ko ye khabar di thi ke aainda aisa aisaa hoga aur waisaa hi hua. uski baat sach nikli . ye wo baat hoti hai jo aasman se churaaii gaee thi."
4702,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ashaab hijr ke mutaalliq farmaya tha ke us qaum ki basti se jab guzarna hi pad gaya hai to rotey huey guzro aur agar rotey huey nahi guzar saktey to phir usmein na jao. kahin tum par bhi wahi azab na aaey jo un par aaya tha.
4703,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere paas se guzrey main us waqt Namaz padh raha tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey bulaya. main Namaz se farigh honey ke baad khidmat mein hazir hua. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke fauran hi kyon na aaey? arz kya ke Namaz padh raha tha. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya Allah ne tum logon ko hukm nahi diya hai ke aey eman waalo! jab Allah aur uske rasool tumhen balaaein to labbaik kaho, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kyon na aaj main tumhen masjid se nikalney se pahley Quran ki sabse azeem sura bataaun . phir aap ( bataaney se pahley) masjid se bahar tashrif ley janey ke liye uthey to maine baat yad dilai . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke sura Fatiha ( الحمد لله رب العالمين ( yahi سبع مثانی (saat dohraaii jaanewaaliyaan) hai aur yahi Quran azeem hai jo mujhey diya gaya hai."
4704,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ummul-Quraan (yani sura faatiha) hi سبع مثانی aur Quran azeem hai.
4705,aayat ( الذين جعلوا Quran عضين‏ ( '' jinhoney Quran ke tukdey kar rakhey hain'' ke mutaalliq kaha ke us se murad ahle-kitab hain ke unhon-ne Quran ke tukdey tukdey kar diye.
4706,aayat (كما أنزلنا على المقتسمين) mein se yahood w nasara murad hain kuchh Quran unhon-ne maanaa kuchh na maanaa.
4707,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dua kya kartey they (أعوذ بك من البخل والكسل ، Mina وأرذل العمر ، Mina وعذاب القبر ، Mina وفتنة الدجال ، Mina وفتنة المحيا والممات)ke aey Allaah! main teri panah mangta hun kanjoosii se, sustii se, arzal umr se (nikammi aur kharaab umr 80 ya 90 saal ke baad) azaabe-qabr se, dajjal ke fitney se aur zindagi aur maut ke fitney se."
4708,ye awwal darje ki umda bahut hi zyada faseeh w baleegh soortein hain aur meri puraanii yad ki hui ( aayat ( ) فسينغضون‏ (ke mutaalliq Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke apne sar hilaaengey aur doosrey logon ne kaha ke ye ( نغضت سنك ( se nikla hai yani tera daant hil gaya.
4709,meraaj ki raat main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney baitul-maqdis mein 2 pyaley pesh kiye gaey aik sharab ka aur doosra doodh kaa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne donon ko dekha phir doodh ka piyala utha liya. is par Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne kaha ke tamam hamd us Allah ke liye hai jisne aapko fitrat (Islam) ki hidayat ki. agar aap sharab ka piyala utha letey to aap ki ummat gumrah ho jati.
4710,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab Quraish ne mujh ko waqia meraaj ke silsile mein jhutlaayaa to main ( Kaba ke) maqaame-hijr mein khada hua tha aur mere samney pura baitul-maqdis kar diya gaya tha. main usey dekh dekh kar uski eik-eik alamat bayan karne laga. Yaqoob-bin-Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ne apni riwayat mein ye zyada kya ke ham se ibne-Shahab ke bhatijey ne apne chacha ibne-Shahab se bayan kya ke (rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya) jab mujhey Quraish ne baitul-maqdis ke meraaj ke silsile mein jhutlaayaa, phir pehli hadis ki tarah bayan kya. ( قاصفا‏ ( wo aandhii jo har cheez ko tabah kar de."
4711,"jab kisi qabeele ke log badh jatey to zamana jahiliyat mein ham unke mutaalliq kaha kartey they ke (Amr-banu-fulaan.) (yani falan ka khandan bahut badh gayaa). ham se Humaidi ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne bayan kya aur is riwayat mein unhon-ne bhi lafz ( أمر‏) ka zikr kya."
4712,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein gosht laya gaya aur dast ka hissa aapko pesh kya gaya. to aap ne apne daanton se usey aik baar nocha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dast ka gosht bahut pasand tha. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qiyamat ke din main sab logon ka sardaar hunga tumhen malum bhi hai ye kon sa din hoga? us din duniya ke shuru se qiyamat ke din tak ki saari khilqat aik chatiyal maidan mein jama hogi ke aik pukarney waley ki awaz sab ke kanon tak pahunch sakegi aur aik nazar sab ko dekh sakegi. suraj bilkul qareeb ho jaeyga aur logon ki pareshani aur be-qaraarii ki koi had na rahegi jo bardasht se bahar ho jaeygi. log aapas mein kahengey, dekhtey nahi ke hamari kya haalat ho gaee hai. kya aisa koi maqbool banda nahi hai jo Allah paak ki bargah mein tumhari shafaat karey? kuchh log kuchh se kahengey ke Adam (Alaihissalam) ke paas chalnaa chahiye chunanche sab log Adam (Alaihissalam) ki khidmat mein hazir hongey aur arz karengey aap insanon ke pardada hain, Allah Taala ne aapko apne hath se paida kya aur apni taraf se khusoosiyat ke sath aap mein Rooh phoonkii. farishton ko hukm diya aur unhon-ne aapko sajda kya isliye aap rab ke huzoor mein hamari shafaat kar dein, aap dekh rahe hain ke ham kis haal ko pahunch chukey hain. Adam (Alaihissalam) kahengey ke mera rab aaj intihai ghazabnaak hai. us se pahley itna ghazabnaak wo kabhi nahi hua tha aur na aaj ke baad kabhi itna ghazab naak hoga aur rabbul-izzat ne mujhey bhi darakht se rokaa tha lekin maine uski nafarmani ki, to نفسی , نفسی , نفسی mujh ko apni fikr hai tum kisi aur ke paas jao. haan Nuh (Alaihissalam) ke paas jao. chunanche sab log Nuh (Alaihissalam) ki khidmat mein hazir hongey aur arz karengey, aey Nooh! aap sabse pahley paighambar hain jo ahale-zameen ki taraf bhejey gaey they aur aapko Allah ne ''shukr guzaar banda'' (abd shukoor) ka Khattab diya. aap hi hamarey liye apne rab ke huzoor mein shafaat kar dein, aap dekh rahe hain ke ham kis haalat ko pahunch gaey hain. Nuh (Alaihissalam) bhi kahengey ke mera rab aaj itna ghazabnaak hai ke is se pahley kabhi itna ghazabnaak nahi tha aur na aaj ke baad kabhi itna ghazabnaak hoga aur mujhey aik dua ki qabooliyat ka yaqin dilaya gaya tha jo maine apni qaum ke khilaf kar li thi. نفسی , نفسی , نفسی aaj mujh ko apne hi nafs ki fikr hai tum mere siwa kisi aur ke paas jao, Ibrahim ke paas jao. sab log Ibrahim ki khidmat mein hazir hongey aur arz karengey, aey Ibrahim ! aap Allah ke Nabi aur Allah ke khaleel hain poori zameen mein muntakhab, aap hamari shafaat keejiye, aap dekh rahey hain ke ham kis haalat ko pahunch chukey hain. Ibrahim bhi kahengey ke aaj mera rab bahut ghazabnaak hai? itna ghazabnaak na wo pahley hua tha aur na aaj ke baad hoga aur maine teen jhoot boley they (raawii) abu-Hayyan ne apni riwayat mein teenon ka zikr kya hai. نفسی , نفسی , نفسی mujh ko apne nafs ki fikr hai. mere siwa kisi aur ke paas jao. haan Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas jao. sab log Musa (Alaihissalam) ki khidmat mein hazir hongey aur arz karengey aey Musa ! aap Allah ke rasool hain, Allah Taala ne aapko apni taraf se risalat aur apne kalam ke zariey fazeelat di. aap hamari shafaat apne rab ke huzoor mein karein, aap dekh saktey hain ke ham kis haalat ko pahunch chukey hain. Musa (Alaihissalam) kahengey ke aaj Allah Taala bahut ghazabnaak hai, itna ghazabnaak ke wo na pahley kabhi hua tha aur na aaj ke baad kabhi hoga aur maine aik shakhs ko qatl kar diya tha, halanke Allah ki taraf se mujhey iska koi hukm nahi mila tha. نفسی , نفسی , نفسی bas mujh ko aaj apni fikr hai, mere siwa kisi aur ke paas jao. haan Esa (Alaihissalam) ke paas jao. sab log Esa (Alaihissalam) ki khidmat mein hazir hongey aur arz karengey. aey Eisaa! aap Allah ke rasool aur uska kalima hain jisey Allah ne Maryam (Alaihissalam) par daala tha aur Allah ki taraf se Rooh hain, aap ne bachpan mein maa ki god hi mein logon se baat ki thi, hamari shafaat keejiye, aap dekh saktey hain ke hamari kya haalat ho chuki hai. Esa bhi kahengey ke mera rab aaj is darja ghazabnaak hai ke na is se pahley kabhi itna ghazabnaak hua tha aur na kabhi hoga aur aap kisi khata ka zikr nahi karengey ( sirf ( itna kahengey, نفسی , نفسی , نفسی mere siwa kisi aur ke paas jao. haan, Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jao. sab log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hongey aur arz karengey, aey Muhammad (sl)! aap Allah ke rasool aur sabse aakhiri paighambar hain aur Allah Taala ne aap ke tamam agley pichhley gunah maaf kar diye hain, apne rab ke darbar mein hamari shafaat keejiye. aap khud dekh saktey hain ke ham kis haalat ko pahunch chukey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aakhir main aagey badhonga aur arsh taley pahunch kar apne rab azz-w-jall ke liye sajde mein gir padoonga, phir Allah Taala mujh par apni hamd aur sana ke darwazey khol dega ke mujh se pahley kisi ko wo tareeqey aur wo taareefein nahi batai thin. phir kaha jaeyga aey Muhammad! apna sar uthaaiye, maangiye aapko diya jaeyga shafaat keejiye, aap ki shafaat qabool ho jaeygi. ab main apna sar uthaaoonga aur arz karunga. aey mere rab! meri ummat, aey mere rab! meri ummat par karam kar, kaha jaeyga aey Muhammad! apni ummat ke un logon ko jin par koi hisab nahi hai, jannat ke daahiney darwazey se dakhil kijiye waisey unhein ikhtiyar hai, jis darwazey se chaahein doosrey logon ke sath dakhil ho saktey hain. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us zaat ki qasam! jiske hath mein meri jaan hai. jannat ke darwazey ke donon kinaron mein itna fasla hai jitna Makka aur hameer mein hai ya jitna Makka aur Basra mein hai."
4713,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Dawud (Alaihissalam) par Zabur ki tilawat aasan kar di gaee thi. aap ghodey par zeen kasney ka hukm detey aur us se pahley ke zeen kasi ja chukey, tilawat se farigh ho jatey they."
4714,"( aayat ( ) إلى ربهم الوسيلة‏ (ka shaane-nuzool ye hai ke kuchh log jinon ki ibadat kartey they, lekin wo jin baad mein musalman ho gaey aur ye mushrik (kam bakht) un hi ki parastish kartey jaahilii shariiat par qaaim rahe. Ubaidullah Ashjai ne us hadis ko Sufiyan se riwayat kya aur unse Aamash ne bayan kya, usmein yun hai ke us aayat ( قل ادعوا الذين زعمتم‏ (ka shaan nuzool ye hai aakhir tak."
4715,aayat ( الذين يدعون يبتغون إلى ربهم الوسيلة‏ ( ki tafseer mein kaha ke kuchh jin aisey they jinki aadmi parastish kya kartey they phir wo jin musalman ho gaey.
4716,aayat ( وما جعلنا الرؤيا التي أريناك إلا فتنة للناس‏ ( main ( ru'ayaa ( se aankh ka dekhnaa murad hai) bedaarii mein na ke khuwab mein) yani wo jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko shab meraaj mein dikhaya gaya aur) شجرة الملعونة‏ ( se thoohad ka darakht murad hai.
4717,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tanha Namaz padhney ke muqaabley mein jamat se Namaz padhney ki fazeelat pachchis guna zyada hai aur subah ki Namaz mein raat ke aur din ke Farishtey ikatthey ho jatey hain. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke agar tumhara ji chahey to ye aayat padho (وقرآن الفجر إن قرآن الفجر كان مشهودا) yaanii fajr mein qirat Quran zyada kya karo kyonke ye Namaz farishton ki haziri ka waqt hai.
4718,qiyamat ke din ummatein giroh dar giroh chalengii. har ummat apne Nabi ke peechhey hogi aur) anbiya se) kahegii ke aey fulaan! hamari shafaat karo (magar wo sab hi inkar kar dengey) aakhir shafaat ke liye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hongey to yahi wo din hai jab Allah Taala Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko maqam Mehmood ata farmaeyga.
4719,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne azan sun kar ye dua padhii (اللهم رب هذه الدعوة التامة والصلاة القائمة ، Mina آت محمدا الوسيلة والفضيلة ، Mina وابعثه مقاما محمودا الذي وعدته ، Mina حلت له شفاعتي يوم القيامة) ''aey Allah ! us kaamil pukar ke rab aur khadi honey wali Namaz ke rab! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko qurb aur fazeelat ata farma aur unhein maqam Mehmood par khada kiijiyo. jiska tu ney unse wada kya hai.'' to uske liye qiyamat ke din meri shafaat zaroori hogi. is hadis ko Hamza bin-Abdullah ne bhi apne walid (Abdullaah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kya hai aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se.
4720,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Makka mein (fatah ke baad) dakhil huey to Kaba ke charon taraf teen so sath (360) but they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne hath ki lakdi se aik ko takraatey jatey aur padhtey jaatey (جاء الحق وزهق الباطل إن الباطل كان زهوقا) ‏‏‏‏ ( جاء الحق وما يبدئ الباطل وما يعيد‏) haq aaya aur jhoot naabood hua beshak jhoot naabood honey wala hi tha.
4721,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik khet mein hazir tha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt khajoor ke aik taney par tek lagaey huey they ke kuchh Yahudi us taraf se guzrey. kisi Yahudi ne apne doosrey sathi se kaha ke unse Rooh ke barey mein poochho. unmein se kisi ne is par kaha aisa kyon kartey ho? doosra Yahudi bola. kahin wo koi aisi baat na keh dein, jo tum ko na-pasand ho. raey is par ghahrii ke Rooh ke barey mein poochhna hi chahiye chunanche unhon-ne aap se iske barey mein sawal kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) thodi der ke liye khamosh ho gaey aur unki baat ka koi jawab nahi diya. main samajh gaya ke is waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi utar rahi hai. isliye main wahin khada raha. jab wahi khatm hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us aayat ki tilawat ki ( ويسألونك an (an) الروح قل الروح من أمر ربي وما أوتيتم من العلم إلا قليلا‏ ) ke ''aur ye aap se Rooh ke barey mein sawal kartey hain. aap keh dein ke Rooh mere parwardigar ke hukm hi se hai aur tumhen ilm to thoda hi diya gaya hai.''"
4722,"Allah Taala ke irshaad ( wla تجهر بصلاتك wla تخافت بها‏ ) ''aur aap Namaz mein na to bahut pukar kar padhiye aur na ( bilkul ( chupkey hi chupkey'' ke mutaalliq farmaya ke ye aayat us waqt nazil hui thi jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka main ( kaafiron ke dar se) chhipey rahtey to us zamane mein jab aap apne sahaba ke sath Namaz padhtey to Quran Majeed ki tilawat buland awaz se kartey, mushrekeen suntey to Quran ko bhi gali detey aur uske nazil karne waley aur uske laney waley ko bhii. isi liye Allah Taala ne apne Nabi se kaha ke aap Namaz na to bahut pukar kar padhein (yani qirat khub Jahar ke sath na karein) ke mushrekeen sun kar gaaliyaan dein aur na bilkul chupkey hi chupkey ke aap ke sahaba bhi na sun sakein, balke darmyani awaz mein padha karein."
4723,ye aayat dua ke silsiley mein nazil hui hai.
4724,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ke waqt unke aur Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar aaey aur farmaya, tum log tahajjud ki Namaz nahi padhtey (aakhir hadis tak)."
4725,"maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha Nauf Bakaalii kehta hai ke jin Musa ki khizr ke sath mulaqat hui thi wo Bani-Israeel ke) rasool ( Musa ke ilawa doosrey hain. (yani Musa bin meesaa bin Afraaseem bin-Yoosuf bin ya'qoob) Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha dushman khuda ne ghalat kaha, mujh se Ubai-bin-Kab ne bayan kya ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke Musa (Alaihissalam) Bani-Israeel ko waz (nasihat) sunaney ke liye khadey huey to unse puchha gaya ke insanon mein sabse zyada ilm kisey hai? unhon-ne farmaya ke mujhey . is par Allah Taala ne un par ghussa kya kyonke unhon-ne ilm ko Allah Taala ki taraf mansub nahi kya tha. Allah Taala ne unhein wahi ke zariey bataya ke 2 daryaon (faaras aur Rome (mojooda Itly) (ke sangam par mera aik banda hai jo tum se zyada ilm rakhta hai. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne arz kya : aey rab! mein un tak kaisey pahunch paaunga? Allah Taala ne bataya ke apne sath aik machhli ley lo aur usey aik zanbeel mein rakh lo, wo jahan gum ho jaey ( zinda ho kar dariya mein kood jaey) bas mera wo banda wahin milega chunanche aap ne machhli li aur zanbeel mein rakh kar rawaana huey. aap ke sath aap ke khaadim Yoosha-bin-Noon bhi they. jab ye donon chattaan ke paas aaey to sar rakh kar so gaey, idhar machhli zanbeel mein tadpii aur us se nikal gaee aur us ne dariya mein apna rasta pa liya. machhli jahan giri thi Allah Taala ne wahan pani ki rawaanii ko rok diya aur pani aik taaq ki tarah is par bin gaya (ye haal Yushaa apni aankhon se dekh rahe they) phir jab Musa (Alaihissalam) bedaar huey to Yushaa unko machhli ke mutaalliq batana bhool gaey. isliye din aur raat ka jo hissey baqi tha usmein chaltey rahe, doosrey din Musa (Alaihissalam) ne apne khaadim se farmaya ke ab khana lao , ham ko safar ne bahut thakaa diya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Musa (Alaihissalam) us waqt tak nahi thakey jab tak wo us maqam se na guzar chukey jiska Allah Taala ne unhein hukm diya tha. ab unke khaadim ne kaha aap ne nahi dekha jab ham chattaan ke paas they, to machhli ke mutaalliq batana bhool gaya tha aur sirf shaitan ne yad rehney nahi diya. us ne to ajeeb tareeqe se apna rasta bana liya tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : machhli ne to dariya mein apna rasta liya aur Musa aur unke khaadim ko) machhli ka jo nishan pani mein ab tak maujood tha) dekh kar tajjub hua. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke ye wahi jagah thi jiski talash mein ham they, chunanche donon hazraat peechhey usi rasta se lautey . bayan kya ke donon hazraat peechhey apne naqsh qadam par chaltey chaltey aakhir us chattaan tak pahunch gaey wahan unhon-ne dekha ke aik sahib ( khizr (Alaihissalam) ( kapdey mein liptey huey wahan baithey hain. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne unhein salam kya. khizr (Alaihissalam) ne kaha (tum kon ho ( tumharey mulk mein '' salam '' kahan se aa gaya. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke main Musa hun. puchha Bani-Israeel ke Moosaa? farmaya ke ji haan. aap ke paas is gharaz se hazir hua hun taake jo hidayat ka ilm aapko hasil hai wo mujhey bhi sikhaa dein. khizr (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya, Musa ! aap mere sath sabr nahi kar saktey mujhey Allah Taala ki taraf se aik khas ilm mila hai jisey aap nahi jaantey, isi tarah aapko Allah Taala ki taraf se jo ilm mila hai wo mein nahi janta. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya inshaAllah aap mujhey saabir paaengey aur main kisi mamley mein aap ke khilaf nahi karunga. khizr (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya, achchha agar aap mere sath chalein to kisi cheez ke mutaalliq sawal na karein yahan tak ke main khud aapko iske mutaalliq bata doonga. ab ye donon samandar ke kinarey kinaarey rawaana huey itney mein aik kashtii guzrii, unhon-ne kashtii walon se baat ki ke unhein bhi is par Sawar kar lein. kashtii walon ne khizr (Alaihissalam) ko pehchan liya aur kisi kiraaye ke baghair unhein sawar kar liya. jab ye donon kashtii par baith gaey to khizr (Alaihissalam) ne kulhaadey se kashtii ka aik takhta nikal dala. is par Musa (Alaihissalam) ne dekha to khizr (Alaihissalam) se kaha ke un logon ne hamein baghair kisi kiraaye ke apni kashtii mein sawar kar liya tha aur aap ne unhiin ki kashtii cheer dali taake sarey musaafir doob jaaein. bila shubah aap ne ye bada na-gawar kaam kya hai. khizr (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya, kya maine aap se pahley hi na kaha tha ke aap mere sath sabr nahi kar saktey. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya jo baat main bhool gaya tha is par mujhey maaf kar dein aur mere maamle mein tangi na karein. bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ye pehli martaba Musa (Alaihissalam) ne bhool kar unhein tokaa tha. rawi ne bayan kya ke itney mein aik chidiyaa aai aur us ne kashtii ke kinarey baith kar samandar mein aik martaba apni chaunch maari to khizr (Alaihissalam) ne Musa (Alaihissalam) se kaha ke mere aur aap ke ilm ki haisiyat Allah ke ilm ke muqaabley mein us se zyada nahi hai jitna is chidiyaa ne is samandar ke pani se kam kya hai. phir ye donon kashtii se utar gaey, abhi wo samandar ke kinarey chal hi rahe they ke khizr (Alaihissalam) ne aik bachcha ko dekha jo doosrey bachchon ke sath khel raha tha. aap ne us bachchey ka sar apne hath mein dabaayaa aur usey ( gardan se) ukhaad diya aur uski jaan ley li. Musa (Alaihissalam) is par boley, aap ne aik be-gunaah ki jaan baghair kisi jaan ke badley ke ley li, ye aap ne bada na-pasand kaam kya. khizr (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke main to pahley hi keh chuka tha ke aap mere sath sabr nahi kar saktey. Sufiyan-bin-Uena (raawii hadis) ne kaha aur ye kaam to pahley se bhi zyada sakht tha. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne aakhir is martaba bhi ma'zirat ki ke agar maine iske baad phir aap se sawal kya to aap mujhey sath na rakhiyega. aap mera baar-baar uzr sun chukey hain (iske baad mere liye bhi uzr ka koi mauqa na rahega ( phir donon rawaana huey, yahan tak ke aik basti mein pahunchey aur basti walon se kaha ke hamein apna mehman bana lo, lekin unhon-ne mezbaanii se inkar kya, phir unhein basti mein aik diwar dikhai di jo bas girney hi wali thi. bayan kya ke diwar jhuk rahi thi. khizr (Alaihissalam) khadey ho gaey aur diwar apne hath se seedhi kar di. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke un logon ke yahan ham aaey aur unse khaney ke liye kaha, lekin unhon-ne hamari mezbaanii se inkar kya, agar aap chahtey to diwar ke us seedha karne ke kaam par ujrat ley saktey they. khizr (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke bas ab mere aur aap ke darmyan judai hai, Allah Taala ke irshaad ذلك تأويل ما لم تسطع عليه صبرا tak. rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ham to chahtey they ke Musa ne sabr kya hota taake Allah Taala unke aur waaqiaat ham se bayan karta. Saeed-bin-Jubair ne bayan kya ke Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) is aayat ki tilawat kartey they (jis mein khizr (Alaihissalam) ne apne kaamon ki wjah bayan ki hai ke) kashtii walon ke aagey aik badshah tha jo har achi kashtii ko chheen liya karta tha aur uski bhi aap tilawat kartey they ke aur wo ghulam (jiski gardan khizr (Alaihissalam) ne tod di thi) to wo ( Allah ke ilm mein) kaafir tha aur uske waalidain momin they."
4726,"mujhey Yala bin Muslim aur Amr-bin-Dinar ne khabar di Saeed-bin-Jubair se, donon mein se aik apne sathi aur doosrey rawi ke muqaabla mein kuchh alfaz zyada kehta hai aur unke ilawa aik aur sahib ne bhi Saeed-bin-Jubair se sun kar bayan kya ke unhon-ne kaha ham Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein unke ghar hazir they. unhon-ne farmaya ke Deen ki baatein mujh se kuchh poochho . maine arz kya : aey abu-Abbaas ! Allah aap par mujhey qurbaan karey Kufa mein aik waaiz shakhs Nauf naam ke) Nauf Bakaalii ( hai aur wo kehta hai ke Musa , khizr (Alaihissalam) se milney waley wo nahi they jo Bani-Israeel ke paighambar Musa (Alaihissalam) huey hain (ibne-Juraij ne bayan kya ke) Amr-bin-Dinar ne to riwayat is tarah bayan ki ke Ibne-Abbas ne kaha dushmane-khudaa jhooti baat kehta hai aur Yala bin Muslim ne apni riwayat mein is tarah mujh se bayan kya ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mujh se Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Musa (Alaihissalam) Allah ke rasool they aik din aap ne logon (banii-Israaeel) ko aisa waz (nasihat) farmaya ke logon ki aankhon se aansu nikal padey aur dil paseej gaey to aap wapas janey ke liye mudey. us waqt aik shakhs ne unse puchha : aey Allah ke rasool! kya duniya mein aap se bada koi aalim hai? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi, is par Allah ne Musa (Alaihissalam) par itaab nazil kya, kyonke unhon-ne ilm ki nisbat Allah Taala ki taraf nahi ki thi. (unko yun kehna chahiye tha ke Allah hi janta hai). unse kaha gaya ke yahan tum se bhi bada aalim hai. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne arz kya, aey parwardigar ! wo kahan hai. Allah ne farmaya jahan ( Faaris aur Rome (mojooda Itly) ke) 2 dariya miley hain. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne arz kya : aey parwardigar ! mere liye unki koi nishani aisi batla de ke main un tak pahunch jaun. ab Amr-bin-Dinar ne mujh se apni riwayat is tarah bayan ki hai ke Allah Taala ne farmaya, jahan tum se machhli tumhari zanbeel se chal de ( wahin wo milengey) aur Yala ne hadis is tarah bayan ki ke aik murda machhli sath ley lo, jahan us machhli mein jaan pad jaey ( wahin wo milengey) Musa (Alaihissalam) ne machhli sath ley li aur usey aik zanbeel mein rakh liya. aap ne apne sathi Yushaa se farmaya ke main bas tumhen itni takleef deta hun ke jab ye machhli zanbeel se nikal kar chal de to mujhey batana . unhon-ne arz kya ke ye kon si badi takleef hai. usi ki taraf ishara hai Allah Taala ke irshad (وإذ قال موسى لفتاه) mein wo ( فتي ( ) rafeeq safar ( Yushaa ibne- noon they. Saeed-bin-Jubair ( rawi hadis) ne apni riwayat mein Yoosha-bin-Noon ka naam nahi liya. bayan kya ke phir Musa (Alaihissalam) aik chattaan ke saaye mein thahar gaey jahan nami aur thand thi. us waqt machhli tadpii aur dariya mein kood gaee. Musa (Alaihissalam) so rahe they isliye Yushaa ne sochaa ke aapko jagaanaa na chahiye lekin jab Musa (Alaihissalam) bedaar huey to machhli ka haal kehna bhool gaey. usi arse mein machhli tadap kar pani mein chali gaee. Allah Taala ne machhli ki jagah pani ke bahaao ko rok diya aur machhli ka nishan patthar par jis par se gaee thi bin gaya. Amr-bin-Dinar ne mujh (ibne-Juraij ( se bayan kya ke iska nishan patthar pe bin gaya aur donon angoothon aur kalime ki ungliyon ko mila kar aik halqe ki tarah usko bataya . bedaar honey ke baad Musa (Alaihissalam) baqi din aur baqi raat chaltey rahe. aakhir kehney lagey. hamein ab is safar mein thakan ho rahi hai. unke khaadim ne arz kya. Allah ne aap ki thakan ko door kar diya hai (aur machhli zinda ho gaee hai). ibne-Juraij ne bayan kya ke ye tukda Saeed-bin-Jubair ki riwayat mein nahi hai. phir Musa (Alaihissalam) aur Yushaa donon wapas lautey aur khizr (Alaihissalam) se mulaqat hui (ibne-Juraij ne kaha) mujh se Usman bin abi Sulaiman ne bayan kya ke khizr (Alaihissalam) dariya ke beech mein aik chhotey se sabz zeen posh par tashrif rakhtey they. aur Saeed-bin-Jubair ne yun bayan kya ke wo apne kapdey se tamam jism lapetey huey they. kapdey ka aik kinara unke paon ke nichey tha aur doosra sar ke taley tha. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne pahunch ko salam kya to khizr (Alaihissalam) ne apna chehra khola aur kaha, meri is zameen mein salam ka riwaaj kahan se aa gaya. aap kon hain? Musa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke main Musa hun. poochha, Musa Bani-Israeel ? farmaya ke haan! poochha, aap kyon aaey hain? farmaya ke mere aaney ka maqsad ye hai ke jo hidayat ka ilm aapko Allah ne diya hai wo mujhey bhi sikhaa dein. is par khizr (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke Musa kya aap ke liye ye kafi nahi hai iska pura seekhnaa aap ke liye munasib nahi hai. isi tarah aapko jo ilm hasil hai uska pura seekhnaa mere liye munasib nahi. is arse mein aik chidiyaa ne apni chaunch se dariya ka pani liya to khizr (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : Allah ki qism ! mera aur aap ka ilm Allah ke ilm ke muqaabley mein us se zyada nahi hai. jitna us chidiyaa ne dariya ka pani apni chaunch mein liya hai. kashtii par chadhney ke waqt unhon-ne chhoti chhotii kashtiyaan dekhiin jo aik kinarey walon ko doosrey kinarey par ley ja kar chhod aati thin. kashtii walon ne khizr (Alaihissalam) ko pehchan liya aur kaha ke ye Allah ke Saleh bandey hain ham unse kiraaya nahi lengey. lekin khizr (Alaihissalam) ne kashtii mein shigaaf kar diye aur us main ( takhton ki jagah) keelein gaad dein. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne kaha aap ne isliye usey phaad daala ke iske musaafiron ko dubo dein. bila shubah aap ne aik bada na-gawar kaam kya hai. Mujahid ne aayat main ( إمرا (ka tarjama ( منكرا ( kya hai. khizr (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya maine pahley hi na kaha tha ke aap mere sath sabr nahi kar saktey. Musa (Alaihissalam) ka pahlaa sawal to bhoolney ki wjah se tha lekin doosra bataur shart tha aur tesraa qasdan unhon-ne kya tha. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne is pahley sawal par kaha ke jo main bhool gaya is par mujh se muwaakhiza na kijiye aur mere maamle mein tangi na kijiye . phir unhein aik bachcha mila to khizr (Alaihissalam) ne usey qatl kar diya. Yala ne bayan kya ke Saeed-bin-Jubair ne kaha ke khizr (Alaihissalam) ko chand bachchey miley jo khel rahe they aap ne unmein se aik bachcha ko pakda jo kaafir aur chaalaak tha aur usey lita kar chhuri se zabah kar diya. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya, aap ne bila kisi khoon ke aik be-gunaah jaan ko jisne ke bura kaam nahi kya tha, qatl kar dala. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aayat main ( زكية ( ki jagah ( زاكية ( padha kartey they. ba-maanaa ( musallema ( jaisey ( غلاما زكيا ( mein hai. phir wo donon buzurg aagey badhey to aik diwar par nazar padi jo bas girney hi wali thi. khizr (Alaihissalam) ne usey theek kar diya. Saeed-bin-Jubair ne apne hath se ishara karke bataya ke is tarah . Yala bin Muslim ne bayan kya mera khayal hai ke Saeed-bin-Jubair ne bayan kya ke khizr ne diwar par hath pher kar usey theek kar diya. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke agar aap chahtey to is par ujrat ley saktey they. Saeed-bin-Jubair ne uski tashreeh ki ke ujrat jisey ham kha saktey. aayat ( وكان وراءهم ( ki Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne qirat ( وكان أمامهم ( ki yani kashtii jahan ja rahi thi us mulk mein aik badshah tha. Saeed ke siwa doosrey rawi se us badshah ka naam hudhud-bin-badud naql kartey hain aur jis bachche ko khizr (Alaihissalam) ne qatl kya tha iska naam log Jaisoor bayan kartey hain. wo badshah har ( nai ( kashtii ko zabardastii chheen liya karta tha. isliye maine chaha ke jab ye kashtii iske samney se guzrey to uske us aib ki wjah se usey na chheeney. jab kashtii waley us badshah ki saltanat se guzar jaeinge to wo khud usey theek kar lengey aur usey kaam mein latey rahengey. kuchh logon ka to ye khayal hai ke unhon-ne kashtii ko phir seesaa laga kar joda tha aur kuchh kehtey hain ke taarcol se joda tha (aur jis bachche ko qatl kar diya tha) to iske waalidain momin they aur wo bachcha ( Allah ki taqdeer mein) kaafir tha. isliye hamein dar tha ke kahin (badaa ho kar) wo unhein bhi kufr mein mubtala na kar de ke apne ladkey se intihai mohabbat unhein uske Deen ki ittaba (pairvi) par majbur kar de. isliye ham ne chaha ke Allah iske badley mein unhein koi nek aur us se behtar aulad de. ( وأقرب رحما ( yani uske waalidain us bachche par jo ab Allah Taala unhein dega pahley se zyada behtar meharban hon jisey khizr (Alaihissalam) ne qatl kar diya hai. Saeed-bin-Jubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke un waalidain ko us bachchey ke badley aik ladki di gaee thi. Dawud bin abi Aasim (Rahmatullahi-alaih) kai rawiyon se naql kartey hain ke wo ladki hi thi."
4727,"Musa (Alaihissalam) jo Allah ke Nabi they wo nahi hain jinhoney khizr (Alaihissalam) se mulaqat ki thi. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, dushman khuda ne ghalat baat kahi hai. ham se Ubai-bin-Kab ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Musa (Alaihissalam) Bani-Israeel ko waz (nasihat) karne ke liye khadey huey to unse puchha gaya ke sabse bada aalim kon shakhs hai. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke main hun. Allah Taala ne is par ghussa kya, kyonke unhon-ne ilm ki nisbat Allah ki taraf nahi ki thi aur unke paas wahi bheji ke yahaan, mere bandon mein se aik banda 2 daryaon ke milney ki jagah par hai aur wo tum se bada aalim hai. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne arz kya : aey parwardigaar! un tak pahunchne ka tariqa kya hoga? Allah Taala ne farmaya ke aik machhli zanbeel mein sath ley lo. phir jahan wo machhli gum ho jaey wahin unhein talash karo. bayan kya ke Musa (Alaihissalam) nikal padey aur aap ke sath aap ke rafeeq safar Yoosha-bin-Noon bhi they. machhli sath thi. jab chattaan tak pahunchey to wahan thahar gaey. Musa (Alaihissalam) apna sar rakh kar wahin so gaey, Amr ki riwayat ke siwa dusri riwayat ke hawale se Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke us chattaan ki jad mein aik chashma tha, jisey '' hayaat ''kaha jata tha. jis cheez par bhi iska pani pad jata wo zinda ho jati thi. us machhli par bhi iska pani padaa to uske andar harkat paida ho gaee aur wo apni zanbeel se nikal kar dariya mein chali gaee. Musa (Alaihissalam) jab bedaar huey to unhon-ne apne sathi se farmaayaa (قال لفتاه آتنا غداءنا‏) ke ''hamaaraa naashta laao'' الآیۃ . bayan kya ke safar mein Musa (Alaihissalam) ko us waqt tak koi thakan nahi hui jab tak wo muqarrara jagah se aagey nahi badh gaey. rafeeq safar Yoosha-bin-Noon ne is par kaha ( أرأيت إذ أوينا إلى الصخرة فإني نسيت الحوت‏ ( '' aap ne dekha jab ham chattaan ke nichey baithey huey they, to main machhli ke mutaalliq kehna bhool gaya '' الآیۃ . bayan kya ke phir wo donon ultey paon wapas lautey. dekha ke jahan machhli pani mein giri thi wahan iske guzarney ki jagah taaq ki si sura bani hui hai. machhli to pani mein chali gaee thi lekin Yoosha-bin-Noon ko is tarah pani ke ruk janey par tajjub tha. jab chattaan par pahunchey to dekha ke aik buzurg kapdey mein liptey huey wahan maujood hain. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne unhein salam kya to unhon-ne farmaya ke tumhari zameen mein salam kahan se aa gaya? aap ne farmaya ke main Musa hun. puchha Bani-Israeel ke Musa ? farmaya ke ji haan ! Musa (Alaihissalam) ne unse kaha kya aap ke sath reh sakta hun taake jo hidayat ka ilm Allah Taala ne aapko diya hai wo aap mujhey bhi sikhaa dein. khizr (Alaihissalam) ne jawab diya ke aapko Allah ki taraf se aisa ilm hasil hai jo main nahi janta aur isi tarah mujhey Allah ki taraf se aisa ilm hasil hai jo aap nahi jantey . Musa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya, lekin main aap ke sath rahunga . khizr (Alaihissalam) ne is par kaha ke agar aapko mere sath rehna hi hai to phir mujh se kisi cheez ke mutaalliq na poochhiyega, main khud aapko bataaoonga. chunanche donon hazraat dariya ke kinarey rawaana huey, unke qareeb se aik kashtii guzri to khizr (Alaihissalam) ko kashtii walon ne pehchan liya aur apni kashtii mein unko baghair kiraaya ke chadhaa liya donon kashtii mein Sawar ho gaey. bayan kya ke usi arsa mein aik chidiyaa kashtii ke kinarey aa ke baithi aur us ne apni chaunch ko dariya mein daala to khizr (Alaihissalam) ne Musa (Alaihissalam) se farmaya ke meraa, aap ka aur tamam makhlooqat ka ilm Allah ke ilm ke muqable mein us se zyada nahi hai jitna us chidiyaa ne apni chaunch mein dariya ka pani liya hai. bayan kya ke phir yakdam jab khizr (Alaihissalam) ne bisoola uthaya aur kashtii ko phaad daala to Musa (Alaihissalam) us taraf mutwajjeh huey aur farmaya un logon ne hamein baghair kisi kiraaya ke apni kashtii mein sawar kar liya tha aur aap ne iska badla ye diya hai ke unki kashtii hi cheer dali taake iske musaafir doob marein . bila shubah aap ne bada naa munasib kaam kya hai. phir wo donon aagey badhey to dekha ke aik bachcha jo bahut se doosrey bachchon ke sath khel raha tha, khizr ne iska sar pakda aur kaat dala. is par Musa (Alaihissalam) bol padey ke aap ne bila kisi khoon w badla ke aik masoom bachchey ki jaan ley li, ye to badi buri baat hai. khizr (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya, maine aap se pahley hi nahi keh diya tha ke aap mere sath sabr nahi kar saktey , Allah Taala ke irshad '' to us basti walon ne unki mezbaanii se inkar kya, phir us basti mein unhein aik diwar dikhai di jo bas girney hi wali thi. khizr (Alaihissalam) ne apna hath yun is par phera aur usey seedha kar diya. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ham us basti mein aaey to unhon-ne hamari mezbaanii se inkar kya aur hamein khana bhi nahi diya agar aap chahtey to is par ujrat ley saktey they. khizr (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya bas yahan se ab mere aur aap ke darmyan judai hai aur main aapko un kaamon ki wjah bataunga jin par aap sabr nahi kar sakey they. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, kash! Musa (Alaihissalam) ne sabr kya hota aur Allah Taala unke silsiley main aur waaqiaat ham se bayan karta. bayan kya ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) وكان وراءهم ملك ( ki bajaey ( وكان أمامهم ملك يأخذ كل سفينة صالحة غصبا ( qirat kartey they aur bachcha ( jisey qatl kya tha) iske waalidain momin they. aur ye bachcha ( marzi ilahi mein) kaafir tha."
4728,"maine apne walid ( Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu)) se aayat ( قل هل ننبئكم بالأخسرين أعمالا‏ (ke mutaalliq sawal kya ke unse kon log murad hain? kya unse khawaarij murad hain? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi, us se murad yahood w nasara hain. yahood ne to Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki takzeeb ki aur nasara ne jannat ka inkar kya aur kaha ke usmein khaaney-peeney ki koi cheez nahi milegii aur khawaarij wo hain jinhoney Allah ke ahad w meesaaq ko todaa Sad (Raziallahu anhu) unhein fasiq kaha kartey they."
4729,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bila-shubah qiyamat ke din aik bahut bhari bharkam motaa-taaza shakhs aayega lekin wo Allah ke nazdeek machchhar ke par ke barabar bhi koi qadr nahi rakhega aur farmaya ke padho ( فلا نقيم لهم يوم القيامة وزنا‏ ( ''qiyaamat ke din ham unka koi wazan na karengey. ''is hadis ko Muhammad-bin-Abdullah ne Yahya-bin-Bukair se, unhon-ne Mughira bin Abdur-Rehman se, unhon-ne abu-Zinaad se aisa hi riwayat kya hai."
4730,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qiyamat ke din maut aik chitkabrey mendhey ki shakl mein laai jaeygi. aik awaz dene wala farishta awaz dega ke aey jannat waalo! tamam jannati gardan uthaa-uthaa kar dekhengey, awaz dene wala farishta poochhega. tum us mendhey ko bhi pehchantey ho? wo boleingey ke yahaan, ye maut hai aur unse har shakhs iska zaayqa chakh chuka hoga. phir usey zabah kar diya jaeyga aur awaz dene wala jannatiyon se kahega ke ab tumharey liye hameshgii hai, maut tum par kabhi na aaeygii aur aey jahannam waalo! tumhen bhi hamesha isi tarah rehna hai, tum par bhi maut kabhi nahi aaeygi. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat ki ( وأنذرهم يوم الحسرة إذ قضي الأمر وهم في غفلة‏ ) ''aur unhein hasarat ke din se dara do. jabke akheer faisla kar diya jaeyga aur ye log ghafalat mein padey huey hain (yani duniyaadaar log) aur eman nahi laatey.''"
4731,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ''jaisaa ke ab aap hamari mulaqat ko aaya kartey hain, us se zyada aap ham se milney ke liye kyon nahi aaya kartey? is par ye aayat nazil hui ( وما نتنزل إلا بأمر ربك له ما بين أيدينا وما خلفنا‏ ( yani ''ham (farishtey) nazil nahi hotey bajuz aap ke parwardigar ke hukm ke, usi ki milk hai jo kuchh hamarey aagey hai aur jo kuchh hamarey peechhey hai.''"
4732,"main Aas-bin-Waail Sehmi ke paas apna haq maangney gaya to wo kehney laga ke jab tak tum Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kufr nahi karogey main tumhen mazdoorii nahi doonga. maine is par kaha ke ye kabhi nahi kar sakta. yahan tak ke tum marney ke baad phir zinda kiye jao. is par wo bola, kya marney ke baad phir mujhey zinda kya jaaeyga? maine kaha haan, zaroor, kehney laga ke phir wahan bhi mere paas maal-aulaad hogi aur main wahin tumhari mazdoorii bhi de doonga. is par ye aayat nazil hui ( أفرأيت الذي كفر بآياتنا وقال لأوتين مالا وولدا‏ (ke '' bhala aap ne us shakhs ko bhi dekha jo hamari nishaniyon se kufr karta hai aur kehta hai ke mujhey maal aur aulad mil kar rahengey.'' is hadis ko Sufiyan Sory aur Shoba aur Hafs aur abu-Muawia aur Wakee ne bhi Aamash se riwayat kya hai."
4733,main Makka mein lohaar tha aur Aas-bin-Waail Sehmi ke liye maine aik talwaar banai thi. meri mazdoorii baqi thi isliye aik din mein usko maangney aaya to kehney laga ke us waqt tak nahi doonga jab tak tum Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se phir nahi jaogey . maine kaha ke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hargiz nahi phiroonga yahan tak ke Allah tujhey mar de aur phir zinda kar de aur wo kehney laga ke jab Allah Taala mujhey mar kar dobara zinda kar dega to mere paas us waqt bhi maal w aulad hogi aur usi waqt tum apni mazdoorii mujh se ley lenaa. is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki) أفرأيت الذي كفر بآياتنا وقال لأوتين مالا وولدا * أطلع الغيب أم اتخذ عند الرحمن عهدا‏ (ke '' bhala tu ney us shakhs ko bhi dekha jo hamari aayaton ka inkar karta hai aur kehta hai ke mujhey to maal w aulad mil kar hi raheingey to kya ye ghaib par muttala' ho gaya hai ya us ne khudaey Rehman se koi wada ley liya hai.'' ( عهد‏ (ka mana mazbut iqraar. Ubaidullah Ashjai ne bhi us hadis ko Sufiyan Sory se riwayat kya hai lekin usmein talwaar banaaney ka zikr nahi hai na ahad ki tafseer mazkoor hai.
4734,"main zamana jahiliyat mein lohaarii ka kaam karta tha aur Aas-bin-Waail par mera kuchh qarz tha. bayan kya ke main uske paas apna qarz maangney gaya to wo kehney laga ke jab tak tum Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka inkar nahi kartey, tumhari mazdoorii nahi mil saktii. maine is par jawab diya ke Allah ki qasam! mein hargiz Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka inkar nahi kar sakta, yahan tak ke Allah Taala tujhey mar de aur phir tujhey dobara zinda kar de. Aas kehney laga ke phir marney tak mujh se qarz na maango. marney ke baad jab main zinda rahunga to mujhey maal w aulad bhi milengey aur us waqt tumhara qarz ada kar doonga. is par ye aayat nazil hui ( أفرأيت الذي كفر بآياتنا وقال لأوتين مالا وولدا‏ ( لخ ."
4735,"mein pahley lohaar tha aur Aas-bin-Waail par mera qarz chahiye tha. main uske paas taqaza karne gaya to kehney laga ke jab tak tum Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se na phir jaogey tumhara qarz nahi doonga, maine kaha ke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Deen se hargiz nahi phiroonga. yahan tak ke Allah Taala tujhey mar de aur phir zinda kar de. usne kaha kya maut ke baad main dobara zinda kya jaaunga? phir to mujhey maal w aulad bhi mil jaeinge aur usi waqt tumhara qarz bhi ada kar doonga. rawi ne bayan kya ke iske mutaalliq aayat nazil huii أفرأيت الذي كفر بآياتنا وقال لأوتين مالا وولدا * أطلع الغيب أم اتخذ عند الرحمن عهدا * كلا سنكتب ما يقول ونمد له من العذاب مدا * ونرثه ما يقول ويأتينا فرداke ''bhalaa tum ne us shakhs ko bhi dekha jo hamari aayaton ka inkar karta hai aur kehta hai ke mujhey to maal aur aulad mil kar rahengey, to kya ye ghaib par aagah ho gaya hai. ya us ne khudaey Rehman se koi ahad kar liya hai? hargiz nahi, albatta ham iska kaha hua bhi likh letey hain aur uske liye azab badhaatey hi chaley jaeinge aur uski kahi hui ke ham hi Malik hongey aur wo hamarey paas akelaa aayega.''"
4736,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Adam (Alaihissalam) aur Musa (Alaihissalam) ki mulaqat hui to Musa (Alaihissalam) ne Adam (Alaihissalam) se kaha ke aap hi ne logon ko pareshani mein daala aur unhein jannat se nikaalaa. Adam (Alaihissalam) ne jawab diya ke aap wahi hain jinhein Allah Taala ne apni risalat ke liye pasand kya aur khud apne liye pasand kya aur aap par Taurait nazil ki. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne kaha ke ji haan. is par Adam (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke phir aap ne to dekha hi hoga ke meri paidaaish se pahley hi ye sab kuchh mere liye likh diya gaya tha. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke ji haan malum hai. chunanche Adam (Alaihissalam) Musa (Alaihissalam) par ghalib aa gaey. ( اليم (ke mana dariya ke hain.
4737,jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to Yahudi aashoora ka roza rakhtey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse iske mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne bataya ke us din Musa (Alaihissalam) ne firaun par ghalba paya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke phir ham unke muqaabley mein Musa ke zyada haqdaar hain. musalmaano! tum log bhi us din roza rakho (phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahood ki mushabihat (similarity) se bchney ke liye uske sath aik roza aur milaaney ka hukm saadir farmaya jo ab bhi masnoon hai.)
4738,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Musa (Alaihissalam) ne Adam (Alaihissalam) se bahas ki aur unse kaha ke aap hi ne apni ghalati ke nateeja mein insanon ko jannat se nikala aur mashaqqat mein dala. Adam (Alaihissalam) boley ke aey Moosaa! aapko Allah ne apni risalat ke liye pasand farmaya aur ham-kalaamii ka sharf bakhshaa. kya aap aik aisi baat par mujhey malaamat kartey hain jisey Allah Taala ne meri paidaaish se bhi pahley mere liye muqarrar kar diya tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya chunanche Adam (Alaihissalam) Musa (Alaihissalam) par bahas mein ghalib aa gaey.
4739,"sura Bani-Israeel aur sura kahaf aur sura Maryam aur sura Taahaa aur sura anbiya agli bahut Faseeh Suraton mein se hain (jo Makka mein utri thiin) aur meri puraanii yad ki hui hain. Qataada ne kaha ( جذاذا‏ (ka mana tukdey tukdey aur Hasan Basri ne kaha ( كل في فلك‏ ( yani har aik taara eik-eik aasman mein gol ghoomtaa hai, jaisey soot kaatney ka charkha. ( يسبحون‏ ( yani gol ghoomtey hain. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ( نفشت‏ (ke mana char gaiin. ( يصحبون‏ (ke mana rokey jaengey. bachaaey jaengey. ( أمتكم أمة واحدة‏ ( yani tumhara Deen aur mazhab aik hi Deen aur mazhab hai. aur Ikrima ne kaha ( حصب‏ ( habshi zaban mein jalaaney ki lakdiyon iindhan ko kehtey hain. aur logon ne kaha lafz ( أحسوا‏ (ke mana tawaqqoa' paai ye ( أحسست‏ ( se nikla hai yani aahat paai .) خامدين‏ (ke mana bujhey huey (yani marey huey) .) حصيد (ke mana jad se اکھاڑا gaya, waahid aur تثنیہ aur jama sab par yahi lafz bola jata hai. ( la يستحسرون‏ (ke mana nahi thakey usi se hai lafz ( حسير ( thakaa hua aur) hasarat ba'eerii . Mina (ke mana maine apne oont ko thakaa diya. ( عميق ( Mina ke mana door daraaz .) نكسوا‏ ( ye kufr ki taraf pherey gaey. ( صنعة لبوس‏ ( zirahein banaanaa .) تقطعوا أمرهم‏ ( yani ikhtilaf kya, juda judaa tariqa ikhtiyar kya. ( la يسمعون حسيسها (ke mana aur lafz ( حس (aur ( jaras (aur ( همس (ke maana aik hi hain yani past awaz .) آذناك‏ ( ham ne tujh ko aagah kya Arab log kehtey hain. ( آذنتكم‏ ( yani maine tum ko khabar di tum ham barabar ho gaey maine koi daghaa nahi ki jab aap mukhaatab ko kisi baat ki khabar de chukey to aap aur wo donon barabar ho gaey aur aap ne us se koi daghaa nahi ki. aur Mujahid ne kaha ( لعلكم تسألون‏ (ke mana ye hain shayad tum samjho .) irtizaa (ke mana pasand kya razi hua. ( التماثيل‏ (ke mana moortein but .) السجل ( mana ke khaton ka majmooae-daftar ."
4740,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik din khutba sunaya. farmaya tum qiyamat ke din Allah ke samney nangey paon nangey badan be-khatna hashr kiye jaogey jaisa ke irshad baari hai) كما بدأنا أول خلق نعيده وعدا علينا إنا كنا فاعلين ( phir sabse pahley qiyamat ke din Ibrahim ko kapdey pehnaey jaengey. sun lo ! meri ummat ke kuchh log laey jaeinge Farishtey unko pakad kar baain taraf waley dozkhiyon mein ley jaengey. mein arz karunga parwardigar ! ye to mere sath waley hain. irshad hoga tum nahi jantey unhon-ne tumhari wafat ke baad kya kya kartoot kiye hain. us waqt main wahi kahunga jo Allah ke nek bandey Esa (Alaihissalam) ne kaha ke main jab tak un logon mein raha unka haal dekhta raha aakhir aayat tak. irshad hoga ye log apni eidiyon ke bal Islam se phir gaey jab to unse juda hua.
4741,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah paak qiyamat ke din Adam (Alaihissalam) se farmaeyga . aey Adam ! wo arz karengey, main hazir hun aey rab! teri farmaanbardaarii ke liye. parwardigar awaz se pukaarey ga (ya farishta parwardigar ki taraf se awaz dega ( Allah hukm deta hai ke apni aulad mein se dozakh ka jatthaa nikaalo . wo arz karengey aey parwardigar ! dozakh ka jatthaa kitna nikaalun . hukm hoga ( rawi ne kaha, main samajhta hun) har hazaar aadmiyon mein 999 (maano hazaar mein aik jannati hoga) ye aisa sakht waqt hoga ke pet wali ka hamal gir jaeyga aur bachcha ( fikr ke maarey ( boodha ho jaeyga (yani jo bachpan mein maraa ho (aur to qiyamat ke din logon ko aisa dekhega jaisey wo nashe mein matwaaley ho rahe hain halanke unko nasha na hoga balke Allah ka azab aisa sakht hoga (ye hadis jo sahaba hazir they un par sakht guzri. unke chehrey ( maarey dar ke) badal gaey. us waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki tasalli ke liye farmaya (tum itna kyon dartey ho ( agar yaajooj maajooj (jo kaafir hain) ki nasl tum se Mulai jaey to unmein se 999 ke muqabil tum mein se aik aadmi padega. gharaz tum log hashr ke din doosrey logon ki nisbat (jo dozakhi hongey) aisey hogey jaisey safaid bail ke jism par aik baal kala hota hai ya jaisey kaley bail ke jism par aik 2 baal safaid hotey hain aur mujh ko ummeed hai tum log sarey jannatiyon ka chothai hissey hogey (baqi teen hisson main aur sab ummatein hongi). ye sun kar ham ne Allahu-akbar kaha, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya nahi balke tum tehai hogey ham ne phir na'ra takbeer buland kya phir farmaya nahi balke aadha hissey hogey (aadhey hisse main aur ummatein hongi) ham ne phir na'ra takbeer buland kya aur abu-Usama ne Aamash se yun riwayat kya ( ترى Naas سكارى وما هم بسكارى‏ ) jaisey mashhoor qirat hai aur kaha ke har hazaar mein se 999 nikaalo (to unki riwayat Hafs bin Ghiyas ke muwafiq hai) aur Jareer-bin-Abdul-hameed aur Esa-bin-Yonus aur abu-Muawia ne yun naql kya ( سكرى وما هم بسكرى‏ ( ) Hamza aur kasaaii ki bhi yahi qirat hai)."
4742,"aayat ومن Naas من يعبد الله على حرف‏ ''aur insanon mein koi aisa bhi hota hai jo Allah ki ibadat kinare par) khada ho kar) karta hai.'' ke mutaalliq farmaya ke kuchh log Madina aatey (aur apne Islam ka izhar kartey ( iske baad agar uski biwi ke yahan ladka paida hota aur ghodii bhi bachcha deti to wo kehtey ke ye Deen (Islam) bada achchha Deen hai, lekin agar unke yahan ladka na paida hota aur ghodii bhi koi bachcha na deti to kehtey ke ye to bura Deen hai is par uper zikr ki gaee aayat nazil hui."
4743,"ye aayat (هذان خصمان اختصموا في ربهم‏) ''ye 2 fareeq hain, jinhoney apne parwardigar ke barey mein jhagdaa kya.'' Hamza aur aap ke donon sathiyon (Ali-bin abii-Taalib (Raziallahu anhu) aur Ubaida-bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) musalmanon ki taraf se) aur (mushrekeen ki taraf se) Utba aur uske donon sathiyon (Sheba aur Waleed bin utba) ke barey mein nazil hui thi, jab unhon-ne badr ki ladai mein maidan mein aa kar muqable ki dawat di thi. is riwayat ko Sufiyan ne abu-Haashim se aur Usman ne Jarir se, unhon-ne Mansoor se, unhon-ne abu-Haashim se aur unhon-ne abu-Mujliz se isi tarah naql kya hai."
4744,"ye khud un ( abu-Mujliz (ka qaul hai, unse Qais-bin Ibad ne aur unse Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke main pahlaa shakhs hunga jo Rehman ke huzoor mein qiyamat ke din apna dawa pesh karne ke liye chaar zaanu baithoonga. Qais ne kaha ke aap hi logon ke barey mein ye aayat nazil hui thi (هذان خصمان اختصموا في ربهم‏) ke ye 2 fareeq hain jinhoney apne parwardigar ke barey mein jhagdaa kya'' bayan kya ke yahi wo log hain jinhoney badr ki ladai mein dawat muqaabla di thi. yani ( musalmanon ki taraf se) Ali , Hamza aur Ubeda (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur (kuffaar ki taraf se) Sheba bin Rabee , Utba-bin- Rabee aur Waleed bin Utba ne."
4745,"Uwemir bin-Haaris bin Zaid-bin-Jad-bin-Ajlaan Aasim-bin-adii ke paas aaey. Aasim bani Ajlan ke sardaar they. unhon-ne aap se kaha ke aap logon ka aik aisey shakhs ke barey mein kya khayal hai jo apni biwi ke sath kisi ghair mard ko pa leta hai. kya wo usey qatl kar de? lekin tum phir usey qisaas mein qatl kar doge! aakhir aisi sura mein insan kya tariqa ikhtiyar karey? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske mutaalliq poochh ke mujhey bataiye . chunanche Aasim , Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ( sura mazkura (uper zikr) mein khawind kya karey) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un masayel (main sawal w jawab ( ko na-pasand farmaya, jab Uwemir ne unse puchha to unhon-ne bata diya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un masayel ko na-pasand farmaya hai. Uwemir ne unse kaha ke Allah ki qism main khud Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usey poochhoonga. chunanche wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya. ya Rasulullah ! aik shakhs apni biwi ke sath aik ghair mard ko dekhta hai kya wo usko qatl kar de ? lekin phir aap qisaas mein usko qatl karengey. aisi sura mein usko kya karna chaahiye? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ne tumharey aur tumhari biwi ke barey mein Quran ki aayat utari hai. phir aap ne unhein Quran ke bataaey huey tariqa ke mutabiq liaan ka hukm diya aur Uwemir ne apni biwi ke sath liaan kya, phir unhon-ne kaha : ya Rasulullah! agar main apni biwi ko rokey rakhoon to main zaalim hoonga. isliye Uwemir ne usey talaaq de di. iske liaan ke baad miyan biwi mein judai ka tariqa jari ho gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya ke dekhtey raho agar us aurat ke kaalaa, bahut kali putliyon waalaa, bhari peeth aur bhari hui pindliyon wala bachcha paida ho to mera khayal hai ke Uwemir ne ilzam ghalat nahi lagaya hai. lekin agar surkh surkh girgit jaisa paida ho to mera khayal hai ke Uwemir ne ghalat ilzam lagaya hai. iske baad us aurat ke jo bachcha paida hua wo unhiin sifaat ke mutabiq tha jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bayan ki thin aur jis se Uwemir ki tasdeeq hoti thi. chunanche us ladkey ka nasb uski maa ki taraf rakha gaya."
4746,"aik sahib (yani Uwemir ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah! aisey shakhs ke mutaalliq aap ka kya irshad hai jisne apni biwi ke sath aik ghair mard ko dekha ho kya wo usey qatl kar de ? lekin phir aap qisaas mein qaatil ko qatl kar dengey. phir usey kya karna chahiye ? unhiin ke mutaalliq Allah Taala ne 2 aayatein nazil kiin jin mein liaan ka zikr hai. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke tumharey aur tumhari biwi ke barey mein faisla kya ja chuka hai. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir donon miyan biwi ne liaan kya aur main us waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir tha. phir aap ne donon mein judai kara di aur 2 liaan karne walon mein iske baad yahi tariqa qaaim ho gaya ke unmein judai kara di jaey. unki biwi haamla thin, lekin unhon-ne iska bhi inkar kar diya. chunanche jab bachcha paida hua to usey maan hi ke naam se pukara janey laga. meeraas ka ye tariqa hua ke betaa maan ka waaris hota hai aur maan Allah ke muqarrar kiye huey hissey ke mutabiq betey ki waaris hoti hai."
4747,"Hilal bin Umayya ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney apni biwi par shareek-bin-Sahmaa ke sath tohmat lagai . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke iske gawah lao warna tumhari peeth par had lagai jaeygi. unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aik shakhs apni biwi ke sath aik ghair ko mubtala dekhta hai to kya wo aisi haalat mein gawah talash karne jaaeyga? lekin aap yahi farmatey rahe ke gawah lao , warna tumhari peeth par had jari ki jaeygi. is par Hilal ne arz kya. us zaat ki qism jisne aapko haq ke sath Nabi bana kar bheja hai main sachcha hun aur Allah Taala khud hi koi aisi aayat nazil farmaeyga. jiske zariey mere uper se had door ho jaeygi. itney mein Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) tashrif laey aur ye aayat nazil hui ( والذين يرمون أزواجهم‏ ( se (إن كان من الصادقين). (jis mein aisi sura mein liaan ka hukm hai) jab nuzoole-wahi ka silsile khatm hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hilal ko aadmi bhej kar bulwaya wo aaey aur aayat ke mutabiq char martaba qism khaaii. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us mauqe par farmaya ke Allah khub janta hai ke tum mein se aik zaroor jhoota hai to kya wo tauba karne par taiyaar nahi hai. iske baad unki biwi khadi huin aur unhon-ne bhi qism khaai, jab wo paanchwein par pahunchein (aur char martaba apni Bara't (Tauba) ki qism khaney ke ba'd, kehney lagiin ke agar main jhooti hun to mujh par Allah ka ghazab ho ( to logon ne unhein rokney ki koshish ki aur kaha ke (agar tum jhooti ho to) us se tum par Allah ka azab zaroor nazil hoga. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke is par wo hichkichaaiin ham ne samjha ke ab wo apna bayan wapas ley lengii. lekin ye kehtey huey ke zindagi bhar ke liye main apni qaum ko ruswa nahi karoongii. paanchwein baar qism khaaii. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke dekhnaa agar bachcha khub siyah aankhon waalaa, bhari koolhon aur bhari bharii pindliyon wala paida hua to phir wo Sharik bin Sahmaa hi ka hoga. chunanche jab paida hua to wo usi shakl w sura ka tha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar kitabullah ka hukm na aa chuka hota to main usey rajm ki saza deta."
4748,aik sahib ne apni biwi par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein aik ghair mard ke sath tohmat lagai aur kaha ke aurat ka hamal mera nahi hai. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se donon miyan biwi ne Allah ke farman ke mutabiq liaan kya. uske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bachche ke barey mein faisla kya ke wo aurat hi ka hoga aur liaan karne waley donon miyaan-beewii mein judai karwaa di.
4749,( والذي تولى كبره‏ ( yani aur jisne unmein se sabse badh kar hissey liya tha aur murad Abdullah-bin-Ubai ibne-Salool ( munafiq ( hai.
4750,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) par tohmat lagaaney ka waqia bayan kya. yani jis mein tohmat lagaaney walon ne unke mutaalliq afawaah udaaii thi aur phir Allah Taala ne unko us se barii qarar diya tha. un tamam rawiyon ne poori hadis ka eik-eik tukda bayan kya aur un rawiyon mein se kuchh ka bayan kuchh doosrey ke bayan ki tasdeeq karta hai. ye alag baat hai ke unmein se kuchh rawi ko kuchh doosrey ke muqaabla mein hadis zyada behtar tariqa par mehfooz yad thi. mujh se ye hadis Urwa ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se is tarah bayan ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) safar ka irada kartey to apni beeviyon mein se kisi ko apne sath ley janey ke liye Qura daltey jinka naam nikal jata unhein apne sath ley jatey. unhon-ne bayan kya ke aik jang ke mauqe par isi tarah aap ne Qura daala aur mera naam nikla . main aap ke sath rawaana hui. ye waqia parde ke hukm nazil honey ke baad ka hai. mujhey hodaj samet oont par chadhaa diya jata aur isi tarah utaar liya jata tha. yun hamara safar jari raha. phir jab aap us jang se farigh ho kar wapas lautey aur ham Madina ke qareeb pahunch gaey to aik raat jab kooch ka hukm hua. main (qazaaey haajat ke liye) padao se kuchh door gaee aur qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke baad apne kajaawey ke paas wapas aa gaee. Mina us waqt mujhey khayal hua ke mera zifaar ke nageenon ka bana hua haar kahin raaste mein gir gaya hai. main usey dhoondney lagi aur is mein itna kho gaee ke kooch ka khayal hi na raha. itney mein jo log mere hodaj ko sawar kya kartey they aaey aur mere hodaj ko utha kar us oont par rakh diya jo meri sawari ke liye tha. unhon-ne yahi samjha ke main usmein baithi hui hun. un dinon auratein bahut halki phulkii hua karti thin gosht se unka jism bhari nahi hota tha kyonke khaney peeney ko bahut kam milta tha. yahi wjah thi ke jab logon ne hodaj ko uthaya to iske halkepan mein unhein koi ajnabiyat nahi mehsus hui. main yun bhi us waqt kam Umr ladki thi. chunanche un logon ne us oont ko uthaya aur chal padey . mujhey haar us waqt mila jab lashkar guzar chuka tha. main jab padao par pahunchi to wahan na koi pukarney wala tha aur na koi jawab dene wala. mein wahan ja kar baith gaee jahan pahley baithi hui thi. mujhey yaqin tha ke jald hi unhein mere na honey ka ilm ho jaeyga aur phir wo mujhey talash karne ke liye yahan aaeingey. main apni usi jagah par baithi thi ke meri aankh lag gaee aur main so gaee. Safwaan-bin-Muattal Salma zakwaanii lashkar ke peechhey peechhey aa rahe they (taake agar lashkar walon se koi cheez chhoot jaey to usey utha lein safar mein ye dastoor tha) raat ka aakhiri hissey tha, jab mere maqam par pahunchey to subah ho chuki thi. unhon-ne (door se) aik insani saaya dekha ke padaa hua hai wo mere qareeb aaey aur mujhey dekhtey hi pehchan gaey. parde ke hukm se pahley unhon-ne mujhey dekha tha. jab wo mujhey pehchan gaey to ( إنا لله ( padhney lagey. mein unki awaz par jaag gaee aur chehra chadar se chipa liya. Allah ki qism ! iske baad unhon-ne mujh se aik lafz bhi nahi kaha aur na maine ( إنا لله وإنا إليه (ke siwa unki zaban se koi kalima suna. iske baad unhon-ne apna oont bitha diya aur main is par Sawar ho gaee wo (khud paidal) oont ko aagey se kheenchtey huey ley chaley. ham lashkar se us waqt miley jab wo bhari do-pahar main (dhoop se bachney ke liye) padao kiye huey they, us tohmat mein pesh-pesh Abdullah-bin-Ubai ibne-Salool munafiq tha. Mina Madina pahunch kar mein bimar pad gaee aur aik mahina tak bimar rahi. us arse mein logon mein tohmat lagaaney walon ki baton ka barabar charcha raha lekin mujhey un baton ka koi ehsas bhi nahiin tha. sirf aik maamle se mujhey shuba sa hota tha ke main apni bimari main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se lutf w mohabbat ka izhar nahi dekhti thi jo pehli beemaariyon ke dinon mein dekh chuki thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) andar tashrif latey salam karke sirf itna poochh letey ke kya haal hai? aur phir wapas chaley jatey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke isi tarze-amal se shuba hota tha lekin soorate-haal ka mujhey koi ehsas nahi tha. aik din jab ( bimari se kuchh fayda tha) kamzori baqi thi to main bahar nikli mere sath Umme- mistah (Raziallahu anhu) bhi thin ham manaasea' ki taraf gaey. qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye ham wahin jaya kartey they aur qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye ham sirf raat hi ko jaya kartey they. ye us se pahley ki baat hai jab hamarey gharon ke qareeb baitul-khala (toilets) nahi baney they. us waqt tak ham qadeem Arab ke dastoor ke mutabiq qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) aabadi se door ja kar kya kartey they. us se hamein badboo se takleef hoti thi ke baitul-khala hamarey ghar ke qareeb bana diye jaaein. khair main aur Umme- mistah qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye rawaana huey. wo abu-Raham bin abd munaaf ki beti thin aur unki walida sakhr bin Aamir ki beti thin. is tarah wo Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki khala hoti hain. unke ladkey mistah bin asaasa hain. qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke baad jab ham ghar wapas aaney lagey to mistah ki maan ka paon unhiin ki chadar mein ulajh kar phisal gaya. is par unki zaban se nikla mistah barbad ho, maine kaha tum ne buri baat kahii, tum aik aisey shakhs ko bura kehti ho jo jange-badr mein Sharik raha hai. unhon-ne kaha, waah uski baatein tu ney nahi sunii? maine puchha : unhon-ne kya kaha hai? phir unhon-ne mujhey tohmat lagaaney walon ki baatein bataein mein pahley se bimar thi hii, un baton ko sun kar mera marz aur badh gaya phir jab main ghar pahunchi aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) andar tashrif laey to aap ne salam kya aur malum farmaya ke kaisi tabeeat hai? maine arz kya ke kya aap mujhey apne maan-baap ke ghar janey ki ijazat dengey? mera maqsad maan-baap ke yahan janey se sirf ye tha ke is khabar ki haqiqat unse poori tarah malum ho jaeygi. Mina Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey janey ki ijazat de di aur main apne waalidain ke ghar aa gaee. maine walida se puchha ke ye log kis tarah ki baatein kar rahe hain? unhon-ne farmaya beti sabr karo, kam hi koi aisi Husain w jameel aurat kisi aisey mard ke nikah mein hogi jo us se mohabbat rakhta ho aur uski saukanein bhi hon aur phir bhi wo is tarah usey neecha dikhaaney ki koshish na karein. bayan kya ke is par maine kaha : Subhan-Allah ! kya is tarah ka charcha logon ne bhi kar diya ? unhon-ne bayan kya ke iske baad main roney lagi aur raat bhar roti rahi. subah ho gaee lekin mere aansu nahi thamtey they aur na neend ka naam w nishan tha. subah ho gaee aur main roey ja rahi thi usi arse main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ali-bin abi-Talib aur Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya kyonke us maamle mein aap par koi wahi nazil nahi hui thi. aap unse mere chhod dene ke liye mashwara lena chahtey they. kyonke wahi utarney mein der ho gaee thi. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko usi ke mutabiq mashwara diya jiska unhein ilm tha ke aap ki ahliya (yani khud Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) (us tohmat se barii hain. iske ilawa wo ye bhi jantey they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko unse kitna talluq khaatir hai. unhon-ne arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! aap ki biwi ke barey mein khair w bhalai ke siwa aur hamein kisi cheez ka ilm nahi aur Ali ne arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! Allah Taala ne aap par koi tangi nahi ki hai, auratein unke siwa aur bhi bahut hain, unki baandi ( Barira ( se bhi aap us maamle mein malum farma lein. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Barira ko bulaya aur malum farmaya : Barira ! kya tum ne koi aisi cheez dekhi hai jis se tujh ko shuba guzra ho? unhon-ne arz kya, nahi huzoor ! us zaat ki qism jisne aapko haq ke sath bheja hai, maine unmein koi aisi baat nahi paai jis par main aib laga sakoon, aik baat zaroor hai ke wo kam Umr ladki hain, aata goondhney mein bhi so jati hain aur itney mein koi bakri ya parinda wghaira wahan pahunch jata hai aur unka goondhaa hua aata kha jata hai. Mina iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur us din aap ne Abdullah-bin-Ubai bin salool ki shikayat ki. bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mimber par khadey ho kar farmaya ke aey musalmaanon ! aik aisey shakhs ke barey mein kon meri madad karta hai jiski takleefein ab mere ghar pahunch gaee hai. Allah ki qism ke main apni biwi ko nek paak daman honey ke siwa kuchh nahi janta aur ye log jis mard ka naam ley rahe hain unke barey mein bhi khair ke siwa main aur kuchh nahi janta. wo jab bhi mere ghar mein gaey to mere sath hi gaey hain. is par Sad-bin-Muaz Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) uthey aur kaha ke ya Rasulullah! main aap ki madad karunga aur agar wo shakhs qabila Aus se talluq rakhta hai to main uski gardan uda doonga aur agar wo hamarey bhaiyon yani khazraj mein ka koi aadmi hai to aap hamein hukm dein, ta'meel mein kotahi nahi hogi. rawi ne bayan kya ke iske baad Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey, wo qabila khazraj ke sardaar they, us se pahley wo mard Saleh they lekin aaj un par qaumii hamiiyat ghalib aa gaee thi ( Abdullah-bin-Ubai ibne-Salool munafiq ( un hi ke qabeele se talluq rakhta tha unhon-ne uth kar Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : Allah ki qism ! tum ne jhoot kaha hai tum usey qatl nahi kar saktey , tum mein uske qatl ki taqat nahi hai. phir Usaid-bin-Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey wo Sad-bin-Muaz ke chacherey bhai they unhon-ne Sad-bin-Ubada se kaha ke Allah ki qism ! tum jhoot boltey ho, ham usey zaroor qatl karengey, kya tum munafiq ho gaey ho ke munaafiqon ki tarafdaar mein ladtey ho? itney mein donon qabeeley Aus w khazraj uth khadey huey aur naubat aapas hi mein ladney tak pahunch gaee. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mimber par khadey they. aap logon ko khamosh karne lagey. aakhir sab log chup ho gaey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi khamosh ho gaey. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke us din bhi main barabar roti rahi na aansu thamtaa tha aur na neend aati thi. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke jab (doosri ( subah hui to mere waalidain mere paas hi maujood they, 2 raatein aur aik din mujhey musalsal rotey huey guzar gaya tha. us arse mein na mujhey neend aati thi aur na aansu thamtey they. Mina waalidain sochney lagey ke kahin rotey-rotey mera dil na phat jaey. unhon-ne bayan kya ke abhi wo isi tarah mere paas baithey huey they aur main roey ja rahi thi ke qabila Ansar ki aik khatun ne andar aaney ki ijazat chaahii, maine unhein andar aaney ki ijazat de di, wo bhi mere sath baith kar roney lagiin. ham usi haal mein they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) andar tashrif laey aur baith gaey. unhon-ne kaha ke jab se mujh par tohmat lagai gaee thi us waqt se ab tak Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere paas nahi baithey they, aap ne aik mahina tak us maamle mein intizar kya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par us silsile mein koi wahi nazil nahi hui. unhon-ne bayan kya ke baithney ke baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khutba padha phir farmaayaa, ammaa ba'd! aey Aaisha ! tumharey barey mein mujhey is-is tarah ki khabrein pahunchi hain to agar tum barii ho to Allah Taala tumhari Bara't (Tauba) khud kar dega. lekin agar tum se ghalati se gunah ho gaya hai to Allah se duaaey maghfirat karo aur uski bargah mein tauba karo, kyonke banda jab apne gunah ka iqrar kar leta hai aur phir Allah se tauba karta hai to Allah Taala bhi uski tauba qabool kar leta hai. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni guftgu khatm kar chukey to yakbaargii mere aansu is tarah khushk ho gaey jaisey aik qatra bhi baqi na raha ho. maine apne walid ( Abu-Bakar ( se kaha ke aap meri taraf se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jawab dijiye. unhon-ne farmaya ke Allah ki qism ! main nahi samajhta ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se is silsile mein kya kehna hai. phir maine apni walida se kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baton ka meri taraf se aap jawab dein. unhon-ne bhi yahi kaha ke Allah ki qism ! mujhey nahi malum ke main aap se kya arz karun. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir main khud hi bolii main us waqt nau-umr ladki thi, maine bahut zyada Quran bhi nahi padha tha ( maine kaha ke) Allah ki qism ! main to ye janti hun ke un afwaahon ke mutaalliq jo kuchh aap logon ne suna hai wo aap logon ke dil mein jam gaya hai aur aap log usey sahi samajhney lagey hain, ab agar main ye kehti hun ke main un tohmaton se barii hun aur Allah khub janta hai ke main waqei barii hun, to aap log meri baat ka yaqin nahi karengey, lekin agar main tohmat ka iqrar kar loon, halanke Allah ke ilm mein hai ke main us se hargiz barii hon, to aap log meri tasdeeq karne lagengey. Mina Allah ki qism ! mere paas aap logon ke liye koi misal nahi hai siwa Yusuf ke walid ke us irshad ke ke unhon-ne farmaya tha ( فصبر جميل والله المستعان) '' to sabr hi achchha hai aur tum jo kuchh bayan kartey ho is par Allah hi madad karega '' bayan kya ke phir maine apna rukh dusri taraf kar liya aur apne bistar par let gaee. kaha ke mujhey pura yaqin tha ke main barii hun aur Allah Taala meri Bara't zaroor karega lekin Allah ki qism ! mujhey iska waham w guman bhi nahi tha ke Allah Taala mere barey mein aisi wahi nazil farmaeyga jiski tilawat ki jaeygi. main apni haisiyat us se bahut kam tar samajhtii thi ke Allah Taala mere barey mein) Quran Majeed ki aayat ( nazil farmaaey. albatta mujhey uski tawaqqoa' zaroor thi ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere mutaalliq koi khuwab dekhengey aur Allah Taala iske zariey meri Bara't (Tauba) kar dega. bayan kya ke Allah ki qism Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) abhi apni usi majlis mein tashrif rakhtey they ghar walon mein se koi bahar na tha ke aap par wahi ka nuzool shuru hua aur wahi kaifiyat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par taarii hui thi jo wahi ke nazil hotey huey taarii hoti thi yani Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) paseeney-paseeney ho gaey aur paseena motiyon ki taraf aap ke jism-at'har se dhalney laga halanke sardi ke din they. ye kaifiyat aap par us wahi ki shiddat ki wjah se taarii hoti thi jo aap par nazil hoti thi. bayan kya ke phir jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki kaifiyat khatm hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tabassum farma rahe they aur sabse pahlaa kalima jo aap ki zabaane-mubaarak se nikla, ye tha ke Aaisha ! Allah ne tumhen barii qarar diya hai. meri walida ne farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney (aap ka shukr ada karne ke liye) khadi ho jao. bayan kya ke maine kaha : Allah ki qism ! main hargiz aap ke samney khadi nahi hoongii aur Allah paak ke siwa aur kisi ki tareef nahi karoongii. Allah Taala ne jo aayat nazil ki thi wo ye thii ''beshak jin logon ne tohmat lagai hai wo tum mein se aik chhota se giroh hai'' mukammal das aayaton tak. jab Allah Taala ne ye aayatein meri Bara't mein nazil kar dein to Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) jo mistah bin asaasa (Raziallahu anhu) ke kharchey unse qaraabat aur unki mohtaajii ki wjah se khud uthaya kartey they unhon-ne unke mutaalliq kaha ke Allah ki qism ! ab mistah par kabhi kuchh bhi kharch nahi karunga . us ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) par kaisi kaisii tohmatein laga di hain. Mina is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki( wla يأتل أولو al-Fazal منكم والسعة أن يؤتوا أولي القربى والمساكين والمهاجرين في سبيل الله وليعفوا وليصفحوا ألا تحبون أن يغفر الله لكم والله ghafoor رحيم‏ ) ''aur jo log tum mein buzurgi aur wusat waley hain, wo qaraabat walon ko aur miskinon ko aur Allah ke rastey mein hijrat karne walon ki madad deney se qism na kha baithein balke chahiye ke unki laghzishon ko maaf kartey rahen aur darguzar kartey rahen , kya tum ye nahi chahtey ke Allah tumharey qasoor maaf karta rahe, beshak Allah bada maghfirat waalaa, bada hi rehmat wala hai.'' abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) boley, haan Allah ki qism ! meri to yahi khahish hai ke Allah Taala meri maghfirat farma de chunanche mistah (Raziallahu anhu) ko wo tamam kharchey dene lagey jo pahley diya kartey they aur farmaya ke Allah ki qasam! ab kabhi unka kharch band nahi karunga. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ummul-Momenin Zenab bin Jahash (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi mere maamle mein puchha tha. aap ne malum farmaya ke Zenab ! tum ne bhi koi cheez kabhi dekhi hai? unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! mere kaan aur meri aankh ko Allah salamat rakhey, maine unke andar khair ke siwa aur koi cheez nahi dekhi. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke paak beeviyon mein wahi aik thin jo mujh se bhi uper rehna chahti thin lekin Allah Taala ne unki parhezgari ki wjah se unhein tohmat lagaaney se mehfooz rakha. lekin unki behan hamna unke liye ladii aur tohmat lagaaney walon ke sath wo bhi halaak ho gaee."
4751,jab Aaisha ne tohmat ki khabar suni to wo behosh ho kar gir padi thi.
4752,wo uper zikr ki gaee aayat ( إذ تلقونه بألسنتكم‏ ( (jab tum apni zabanon se usey munh dar munh naql kar rahe they) padh rahi thin.
4753,"Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki wafat se thodi der pahley, jabke wo jaan nikalney ki haalat mein thin, Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unke paas aaney ki ijazat chaahii, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke mujhey dar hai ke kahin wo meri tareef na karne lagein. kisi ne arz kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chacha zaad bhai hain aur khud bhi izzat daar hain (is liye aapko ijazat de deni chahiye ( is par unhon-ne kaha ke phir unhein andar bula lo. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse puchha ke aap kis haal mein hain? is par unhon-ne farmaya ke agar main Allah ke nazdeek achi hun to sab achchha hi achchha hai. is par Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke inshaAllah aap achi hi rahengii. aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi hain aur aap ke siwa Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi kunwari aurat se nikah nahi farmaya aur aap ki Bara't (Tauba) ( Quran Majeed mein) aasman se nazil hui. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke tashrif ley janey ke baad aap ki khidmat mein ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) hazir huey. mohtarma ne unse farmaya ke abhi Ibne-Abbas aaey they aur meri tareef ki, main to chahti hun ke kash! main aik bhoolii-bisrii gumnaam hoti."
4754,Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aaney ki ijazat chaahi. phir rawi ne uper zikr ki gaee hadis ki tarah bayan kya lekin is hadis mein rawi ne lafz ( نسيا منسيا‏ ) ka zikr nahi kya.
4755,"Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se mulaqat karne ki Hassaan-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne ijazat chahi . maine arz kya ke aap unhein bhi ijazat deti hain ( halanke unhon-ne bhi aap par tohmat lagaaney walon ka sath diya tha) is par Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha, kya unhein uski aik badi saza nahi mili hai. Sufiyan ne kaha ke unka ishara unke naa-beenaa ho janey ki taraf tha. phir Hassan ne ye sher padha . ''Afeefa aur badi aqlmand hain ke unke mutaalliq kisi ko koi shuba bhi nahi guzar saktaa. wo ghaafil aur paakdaaman aurton ka gosht khaney se mukammal parhez karti hain.'' Aaisha (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya, lekin tu ney aisa nahi kya."
4756,"Hassaan-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aaey aur ye sher padhaa Afeefa aur badi aqlmand hain, unke mutaalliq kisi ko shuba bhi nahi guzar saktaa. aap ghaafil aur paak daman aurton ka gosht khaney se kaamil parhez karti hain.'' is par Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke lekin aey Hassan ! to aisa nahi hai. baad mein, maine arz kya aap aisey shakhs ko apne paas aaney deti hain? Allah Taala to ye aayat bhi nazil kar chuka hai) والذي تولى كبره منهم‏ (ke ''aur jisne unmein se sabse bada hissey liyaa.'' Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke naa-beenaa ho janey se badh kar aur kya azab hoga, phir unhon-ne kaha ke Hassan (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se kuffaar ki hijo ka jawab diya kartey they (kya ye sharf unke liye kam hai)."
4757,"jab mere mutaalliq aisi baatein kahi gain jinka mujhey guman bhi nahi tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere maamle mein logon ko khutba dene ke liye khadey huey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne shahadat ke baad Allah ki hamd w sana uski shaan ke mutabiq bayan ki, phir farmaayaa, ammaa ba'd! tum log mujhey aisey logon ke barey mein mashwara 2 jinhoney meri biwi ko badnaam kya hai aur Allah ki qasam! ke maine apni biwi mein koi burai nahi dekhi aur tohmat bhi aisey shakhs ( Safwan bin muattal (ke sath lagai hai ke Allah ki qism ! unmein bhi maine kabhi koi burai nahi dekhi . wo mere ghar mein jab bhi dakhil hua to meri maujoodgii hi mein dakhil hua aur agar main kabhi safar ki wjah se Madina nahi hota to wo bhi nahi hota aur wo mere sath hi rahtey hain. iske baad Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! hamein hukm farmaiye ke ham aisey mardood logon ki gardanein uda dein. iske baad qabila khazraj ke aik sahib ( Sad-bin-Ubada ( khadey huey, Hassaan-bin-Saabit ki walida usi qabila khazraj se thin, unhon-ne khadey ho kar kaha ke tum jhootey ho, agar wo log ( tohmat lagaaney waale) qabila Aus ke hotey to tum kabhi unhein qatl karna pasand na kartey. naubat yahan tak pahunchi ke masjid hi mein Aus w khazraj ke qabaayel mein aapasii fasaad ka khatrah ho gaya, us fasaad ki mujh ko kuchh khabar na thi, isi din ki raat mein, main qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye bahar nikli , mere sath Umme- mistah bhi thin. wo ( rastey mein) phisal gain aur unki zaban se nikla ke mistah ko Allah ghaarat kare. maine kaha, aap apne betey ko kostii hain, is par wo khamosh ho gain, phir dobara wo phisliin aur unki zaban se wahi alfaz nikley ke mistah ko Allah ghaarat kare. maine phir kaha ke apne betey ko kostii ho, phir wo teesri martaba phisliin to maine phir unhein tokaa. unhon-ne bataya ke Allah ki qasam! main to teri hi wjah se usey kostii hun. maine kaha ke mere kis maamle mein unhein aap kos rahi hain? bayan kya. ke ab unhon-ne toofaan ka Sara qissa bayan kya maine poochha, kya waqei ye sab kuchh kaha gaya hai? unhon-ne kaha ke haan, Allah ki qism ! phir main apne ghar gaee. lekin (in waaqiaat ko sun kar gham ka ye haal tha ke) mujhey kuchh khabar nahi ke kis kaam ke liye main bahar gaee thi aur kahan se aai hun, zarra barabar bhi mujhey iska ehsas nahi raha. iske baad mujhey bukhar chadh gaya aur maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke aap mujhey zara mere walid ke ghar pahunchwaa dijiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere sath aik bachche ko kar diya. main ghar pahunchi to maine dekha ke umme-Roomaan nichey ke hisse mein hain aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) baalaa-khaaney mein Quran padh rahe hain. walida ne puchha beti is waqt kaisey aa gaiin. maine wjah batai aur waaqie ki tafseelaat sunain un baton se jitna gham mujh ko tha aisa malum hua ke unko itna gham nahi hai. unhon-ne farmaya, beti itna fikr kyon karti ho kam hi aisi koi khoobsurat aurat kisi aisey mard ke nikah mein hogi jo us se mohabbat rakhta ho aur uski saukanein bhi hon aur wo us se hasad na karein aur is mein so aib na nikaalein. is tohmat se wo us darja bilkul bhi mutassir nahi malum hoti thin jitna mein mutassir thi. maine puchha walid ke ilm mein bhi ye baatein aa gain hain? unhon-ne kaha ke haan, maine puchha aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ? unhon-ne bataya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke bhi ilm mein sab kuchh hai. main ye sun kar roney lagi to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi meri awaz sun li, wo ghar ke oopri hisse mein Quran padh rahe they, utar kar nichey aaey aur walida se puchha ke isey kya ho gaya hai? unhon-ne kaha ke wo tamam baatein usey bhi malum ho gaee hain jo iske mutaalliq kahi ja rahi hain. unki bhi aankhen bhar aaein aur farmaya : beti ! tumhen qism deta hun, apne ghar wapas chali jao chunanche main wapas chali aai. (jab main apne waalidain ke ghar aa gaee thi to ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere hujre mein tashrif laey they aur meri khaadima ( Barira ( se mere mutaalliq puchha tha. usne kaha tha ke nahi, Allah ki qism ! main unke andar koi aib nahi jaantii, albatta aisa ho jaya karta tha (kam Umri ki ghafalat ki wjah se) ke) aata goondhtey huey) so jaya kartin aur bakri aa kar unka gandhaa hua aata kha jati. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kuchh sahaba ne daant kar unse kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko baat sahi saheeh kyon nahi bata deti. phir unhon-ne khol kar saaf lafzon mein unse waaqie ki tasdeeq chahi . is par wo boliin ke sub'haan-Allaah, main to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko is tarah janti hun jis tarah sunaar kharey soney ko janta hai. us tohmat ki khabar jab un sahib ko malum hui jinke sath tohmat lagai gaee thi to unhon-ne kaha ke sub'haan-Allaah, Allah ki qism ! ke maine aaj tak kisi ( ghair ( aurat ka kapda nahi kholaa. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke phir unhon-ne Allah ke rastey mein shahadat paai . bayan kya ke subah ke waqt mere waalidain mere paas aagey aur mere paas hi rahe. aakhir Asr ki Namaz se farigh ho kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi tashrif laey. mere waalidain mujhey daain aur baain taraf se pakdey huey they, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Allah ki hamd w sana ki aur farmaya : ammaa ba'd! aey Aaisha ! agar tum ne waqei koi bura kaam kya hai aur apne uper zulm kya hai to phir Allah se tauba karo, kyonke Allah apne bandon ki tauba qabool karta hai. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke aik Ansari khatun bhi aa gaee thin aur darwazey par baithi hui thin, maine arz ki, aap un khatun ka lihaaz nahi farmatey kahin ye (apni samajh ke mutabiq koi ulti seedhi ( baat bahar keh dein. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nasihat farmai, iske baad main apne walid ki taraf mutwajjeh hui aur unse arz kya ke aap hi jawab dijiye , unhon-ne bhi yahi kaha ke main kya kahun jab kisi ne meri taraf se kuchh nahi kaha to maine shahadat ke baad Allah ki shaan ke mutabiq uski hamd w sana ki aur kaha : ammaa ba'd! Allah ki qism ! agar main aap logon se ye kahun ke maine is tarah ki koi baat nahi ki aur izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah gawah hai ke main apne us da'wey mein sachchii hun, to aap logon ke khayal ko badalney mein meri ye baat mujhey koi nafa nahi pahunchaaeygii, kyonke ye baat aap logon ke dil mein rach-bas gaee hai aur agar main ye keh dun ke maine waaqiatan ye kaam kya hai halanke Allah khub janta hai ke maine aisa nahi kya hai, to aap log kahengey ke usne to jurm ka iqrar kar liya hai. Allah ki qasam! meri aur aap logon ki misal Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke walid ki si hai ke unhon-ne farmaya tha (فصبر جميل والله المستعان ( '' to sabr hi achchha hai aur tum log jo kuchh bayan kartey ho is par Allah hi madad kare. '' maine zahan par bahut zor diya ke Yaqoob (Alaihissalam) ka naam yad aa jaey lekin nahi yad aaya. usi waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi ka nuzool shuru ho gaya aur ham sab khamosh ho gaey. phir aap se ye kaifiyat khatm hui to maine dekha ke khushi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehra Mubarak se zahir ho rahi thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( paseena se) apni peshani saaf kartey huey farmaya ke Aaisha ! tumhen bashaarat ho Allah Taala ne tumhari paakii nazil kar di hai. bayan kya ke us waqt mujhey bada ghussa aa raha tha. mere waalidain ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney khadi ho jao, maine kaha ke Allah ki qasam! main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney khadi nahi hoongii na aap ka shukriya ada karoongii aur na aap logon ka shukriya ada karoongii, main to sirf Allah ka shukr ada karoongii jisne meri Bara't nazil ki hai. aap logon ne to ye afawaah suni aur iska inkar bhi na kar sakey, iske khatm karne ki bhi koshish nahi ki. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati thin ke Zenab binte-Jahash ko Allah Taala ne unki deendaarii ki wjah se us tohmat mein padney se bacha liya. meri baabat unhon-ne khair ke siwa aur koi baat nahi kahii, albatta unki behan hamna halaak honey walon ke sath halaak huin. us toofaan ko phailaaney mein mistah aur Hassan aur munafiq Abdullah-bin-Ubai ne hissey liya tha. Abdullah-bin-Ubai munafiq hi to khod khod kar usko poochhta aur is par haashiya chadhaataa , wahi us toofaan ka baanii mabaanii tha. ( وهو الذي تولى كبره ( se wo aur hamna murad hain. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne qism khaaii ke mistah ko koi fayda aainda kabhi wo nahi pahunchaaengey. is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki) wla يأتل أولو al-Fazal منكم‏ ( ''aur jo log tum mein buzurgi waley aur faraakh-dast hain'', us se murad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) hain. ''wo qaraabat walon aur miskinon ko'' is se murad mistah hain. (deney se qism na kha baithein ( Allah Taala ke irshaad ( ألا تحبون أن يغفر الله لكم والله ghafoor رحيم‏ ) ''kya tum ye nahi chahtey ke Allah tumharey qasoor maaf karta rahe, beshak Allah badi maghfirat karne wala bada hi meharban hai'' tak. chunanche Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke haan, Allah ki qism ! aey hamarey rab! ham to usi ke khaahishmand hain ke to hamari maghfirat farmaa. phir wo pahley ki tarah mistah ko jo diya kartey they wo jari kar diya."
4758,"Allah un aurton par raham karey jinhoney pehli hijrat ki thi. jab Allah Taala ne aayat (وليضربن بخمرهن على جيوبهن‏) ''aur apne dupattey apne seenon par daley raha karein.'' (taake Sina aur gila wghaira na nazar aaey ( nazil ki, to unhon-ne apni chaadaron ko phaad kar unke dupattey bana liye."
4759,jab ye aayat nazil huii (وليضربن بخمرهن على جيوبهن‏) ke ''aur apne dupattey apne seenon par daley raha karein '' to ( Ansar ki aurton ne) apne tahbandon ko donon kinarey se phaad kar unki odhniyaan bana lein.
4760,"aik sahib ne poochha, aey Allah ke Nabi ! kaafir ko qiyamat ke din iske chehrey ke bal kis tarah chillaayaa jaeyga ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah jisne usey us duniya mein 2 paon par chillaayaa hai is par qaadir hai ke qiyamat ke din usko uske chehrey ke bal chala de. Qatada ne kaha yaqinan hamarey rab ki izzat ki qism ! yoonhii hoga."
4761,"maine poochha, ya (aap ne ye farmaya ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya ke kon sa gunah Allah ke nazdeek sabse bada hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye ke tum Allah ka kisi ko Sharik thehrao halanke usi ne tumhen paida kya hai. maine puchha iske baad kon sa ? farmaya ke iske baad sabse bada gunah ye hai ke tum apni aulad ko us khof se mar dalo ke wo tumhari rozii mein Sharik hogi. maine puchha iske baad kon sa ? farmaya ke iske baad ye ke tum apne padosi ki biwi se zina karo. rawi ne bayan kya ke ye aayat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke farman ki tasdeeq ke liye nazil huii (والذين لا يدعون مع الله إلها آخر wla يقتلون النفس التي حرم الله إلا بالحق)ke ''aur jo Allah ke sath kisi aur maabood ko nahi pukaartey aur jis ( insan ( ki jaan ko Allah ne haram qarar diya hai usey qatl nahi kartey magar haan haq par aur na wo zina kartey hain.''"
4762,"agar koi shakhs kisi musalman ko jaan-boojh kar qatl kar de to kya uski us gunah se tauba qabool ho sakti hai? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi. (ibne-Ubaii baza ne bayan kya ke) maine is par ye aayat padhii (ولا يقتلون النفس التي حرم الله إلا بالحق‏)ke ''aur jis jaan ko Allah ne haram qarar diya hai usey qatl na kartey, magar haan haq ke sath .'' Saeed-bin-Jubair ne kaha ke maine bhi ye aayat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke samney padhi thi to unhon-ne kaha tha ke Makki aayat aur madni aayat jo us silsile mein sura Nisa mein hai us se uska hukm mansukh ho gaya hai."
4763,ahale-koofa ka momin ke qatl ke masley mein ikhtilaf hua (ke iske qaatil ki tauba qabool ho sakti hai ya nahin) to main safar karke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein pahuncha to unhon-ne kaha ke (sura Nisa ki aayat jis mein ye zikr hai ke jisne kisi musalman ko jaan-bojh kar qatl kya uski saza jahannam hai.) is silsile mein sabse aakhir mein nazil hui hai aur kisi dusri se mansukh nahi hui.
4764,maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se (فجزاؤه جهنم) ke mutaalliq sawal kya to unhon-ne farmaya ke uski tauba qabool nahi hogi aur Allah Taala ke irshaad (‏‏‏‏لا يدعون مع الله إلها آخر) ke mutaalliq puchha to aap ne farmaya ke ye un logon ke mutaalliq hai jinhoney zamana jahiliyat mein qatl kya ho.
4765,"unse Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Abza ne bayan kya ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aayat ( ومن يقتل مؤمنا متعمدا فجزاؤه جهنم ) ''aur jo koi kisi momin ko jaan kar qatl karey uski saza jahannam hai.'' aur sura furqan ki aayat (‏‏‏‏لا يقتلون النفس التي حرم الله إلا بالحق) ''aur jis insan ki jaan maarney ko Allah ne haram qarar diya hai usey qatl nahi kartey magar haan haq ke saath'' (إلا من تاب) tak , maine is aayat ke mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke jab ye aayat nazil hui to ahale-Makka ne kaha ke phir to ham ne Allah ke sath Sharik bhi thehraya hai aur nahaq aisey qatl bhi kiye hain jinhein Allah ne haram qarar diya tha aur ham ne badkaariyon ka bhi irtikaab kya hai. is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki (إلا من تاب وآمن وعمل عملا صالحا) ke '' magar haan jo tauba karey aur eman laey aur nek kaam karta rahe, Allah bahut bakhshney wala bada hi meharban hai'' tak."
4766,mujhey Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Abza ne hukm diya ke main Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se 2 aayaton ke barey mein poochhoon yani ( ومن يقتل مؤمنا متعمدا‏ ( ''aur jisne kisi momin ko jaan-bojh kar qatl kya''. maine unse puchha to unhon-ne farmaya ke ye aayat kisi cheez se bhi mansukh nahi hui hai. (aur dusri aayat jiske) barey mein mujhey unhon-ne poochhney ka hukm diya wo ye thii (والذين لا يدعون مع الله إلها آخر) ''aur jo log kisi maabood ko Allah ke sath nahi pukaartey'' aap ne iske mutaalliq farmaya ke ye mushrekeen ke barey mein nazil hui thi.
4767,Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha (qiyamat ki) panch nishaniyan guzar chuki hain. dhuaan (iska zikr aayat ( يوم تأتي السماء بدخان مبين ( mein hai). chaand ka phatnaa (iska zikr aayat ( اقتربت الساعة وانشق القمر ( mein hai). Rome (mojooda Itly) ka maghloob hona ( iska zikr sura ( غلبت Rome ( mein hai). ( لبطشة ( yani Allah ki pakad jo badr mein hui ( iska zikr ( yaum نبطش البطشة الکبرى ( mein hai) aur wabaal jo Quraish par badr ke din aaya ( iska zikr aayat ( فسوف یکون لزاما ( mein hai.
4768,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Ibrahim apne walid (aazar) ko qiyamat ke din gard aalud kala kalootaa dekhengey. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ( غبرة (aur ( قترة‏ ( ham mana hain.
4769,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Ibrahim apne walid se (qiyamat ke din) jab milein gey to Allah Taala se arz karengey ke aey rab! tu ney wada kya tha ke to mujhey us din ruswa nahi karega jab sab uthaey jaeinge lekin Allah Taala jawab dega ke maine jannat ko kaafiron par haram qarar de diya hai.
4770,"jab aayat ( وأنذر عشيرتك الأقربين‏ ( ''aur aap apne khaandaanii qaraabat daaron ko daraatey rahiye'' nazil hui to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Safa pahaadii par chadh gaey aur pukarney lagey. aey bani fahar! aur aey bani Adi ! aur Quraish ke doosrey khandan waalo! us awaz par sab jama ho gaey agar koi kisi wjah se na aa saka to usne apna koi chaudhrii bhej diya, taake malum ho ke kya baat hai. abu-Lahab Quraish ke doosrey logon ke sath majme' mein tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein Khattab karke farmaya ke tumhara kya khayal hai, agar main tum se kahun ke wadi main (pahaadii ke peechhey) aik lashkar hai aur wo tum par hamla karna chahta hai to kya tum meri baat sach maanogey? sab ne kaha ke haan, ham aap ki tasdeeq karengey ham ne hamesha aapko sachcha hi paya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir suno, main tumhen us sakht azab se daraataa hun jo bilkul samney hai. is par abu-Lahab bola, tujh par sarey din tabahi nazil ho, kya tu ney hamein isi liye ikattha kya tha. isi waaqie par ye aayat nazil huii ( تبت يدا أبي لهب وتب * ما أغنى عنه ماله وما كسب‏ )''abu-Lahab ke donon hath toot gaey aur wo barbad ho gaya, na uska maal uske kaam aaya aur na uski kamaaii hi iske aadey aaii.''"
4771,"Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, jab aayat ( وأنذر عشيرتك الأقربين‏ ( ''aur apne khandan ke qaraabat daaron ko daraa'' nazil hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (Safaa pahaadii par khadey ho kar) awaz di ke aey jamat Quraish! ya isi tarah ka aur koi kalima Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ki itaat ke zariey apni jaanon ko uske azab se bachao (agar tum shirk w kufr se baaz na aaey to) Allah ke yahan main tumharey kisi kaam nahi aaoonga. aey bani abd munaaf! Allah ke yahan main tumharey liye bilkul kuchh nahi kar sakoonga. aey Abbas bin abdul-Muttalib ! Allah ki bargah mein main tumharey kuchh kaam nahi aa sakoonga. aey Safiya, Rasulullah ki phoophii ! main Allah ke yahan tumhen kuchh fayda na pahuncha sakoonga. aey Fatima ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beti ! mere maal mein se jo chaho mujh se ley lo lekin Allah ki bargah mein, main tumhen koi fayda na pahuncha sakoonga. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) asbagh ne ibne- Wahab se, unhon-ne Yunus se aur unhon-ne ibne-Shahab se ki hai."
4772,"jab abu-Taalib ki wafat ka waqt qareeb hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas aaey, abu-Jahal aur Abdullah-bin-Ubai Umayya bin Mughira wahan pahley hi se maujood they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke chacha ! aap sirf kalima ( لا إله إلا الله ( padh dijiye taake us kalime ke zariey Allah ki bargah mein aap ki shafaat karun. is par abu-Jahal aur Abdullah-bin-Ubai Umayya boley kya tum abdul-Muttalib ke mazhab se phir jaaogey? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baar-baar unse yahi kehtey rahe (ke aap sirf aik kalima padh lein) aur ye donon bhi apni baat unke samney baar-baar dohraatey rahe (ke kya tum abdul-Muttalib ke mazhab se phir jaaogey?) aakhir abu-Taalib ki zaban se jo aakhiri kalima nikla wo yahi tha ke wo abdul-Muttalib ke mazhab par hi qaaim hain. unhon-ne ( لا إله إلا الله ( padhney se inkar kar diya. rawi ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ki qasam! mein aap ke liye talab maghfirat karta rahunga yahan tak ke mujhey us se rok na diya jaey. phir Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki ما كان للنبي والذين آمنوا أن يستغفروا للمشركين''nabii aur eman walon ke liye ye munasib nahi hai ke wo mushrekeen ke liye duaaey maghfirat karein.'' aur khas abu-Taalib ke barey mein ye aayat nazil hui Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha gayaa إنك لا تهدي من أحببت ولكن الله يهدي من يشاءke ''jis ko tum chaho hidayat nahi kar saktey, albatta Allah hidayat deta hai usey jiske liye wo hidayat chahta hai.'' Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ( أولي القوة‏ ( se ye murad hai ke kai zor daar aadmi mil kar bhi uski kunjiyaan nahi utha saktey they. ( لتنوء‏ (ka matlab dhoi jati thin. ( فارغا‏ (ka mana ye hai ke Musa ki maa ke dil mein Musa ke siwa aur koi khas nahi raha thaa."
4773,( aayat uper zikr ki gaee mein) (لرادك إلى معاد‏) se murad hai ke Allah phir aapko Makka pahuncha kar rahega.
4774,"aik shakhs ne qabila kanda mein waz (nasihat) bayan kartey huey kaha ke qiyamat ke din aik dhuaan uthega jis se munaafiqon ke aankh kaan bilkul bekaar ho jaeinge lekin momin par iska asar sirf zukaam jaisa hoga. ham uski baat se bahut ghabraa gaey. phir main ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua (aur unhein un sahib ki ye baat sunaaii) wo us waqt tek lagaey baithey they, usey sun kar bahut ghussa huey aur seedhey baith gaey. phir farmaya ke agar kisi ko kisi baat ka waqei ilm hai to phir usey bayan karna chahiye lekin agar ilm nahi hai to keh dena chahiye ke Allah zyada jaanney wala hai. ye bhi ilm hi hai ke aadmi apni laa-ilmii ka iqrar kar ley aur saaf keh de ke main nahi janta. Allah Taala ne apne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se farmaya tha ( قل ما أسألكم عليه من أجر وما أنا من المتكلفين‏ ( '' aap keh dijiye ke main apni tableegh w dawat par tum se koi ajr nahi chahta aur na main banawat karta hoon.'' asl mein waqia ye hai ke Quraish kisi tarah Islam nahi latey they. isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke haq mein baddua ki ke aey Allah ! un par Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke zamaney jaisa qahat bhej kar meri madad kar phir aisa qahat padaa ke log tabah ho gaey aur murdar aur haddiyaan khaney lagey koi agar fizaa mein dekhta (to faaqa ki wjah se) usey dhuein jaisa nazar aataa. phir Abu-Sufiyan aaey aur kaha ke aey Muhammad ! aap hamein sila rehmii ka hukm detey hain lekin aap ki qaum tabah ho rahi hai, Allah se dua kijiye (ke unki ye museebat door ho). is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye aayat padhii (قل ما أسألكم عليه من أجر وما أنا من المتكلفين) se ( عائدون‏ ( tak. ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke qahat ka ye azab to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dua ke nateeje mein khatm ho gaya tha lekin kya aakhirat ka azab bhi unse tal jaaeyga? chunanche qahat khatm honey ke baad phir wo kufr se baaz na aaey, uski taraf ishara ( يوم نبطش البطشة الكبرى‏ ( mein hai, ye بطش kuffaar par jange-badr ke mauqe par nazil hui thi (ke unke badey badey sardaar qatl kar diye gaey) aur) لزاما ( ) qaid ( se ishara bhi ladaai badr hi ki taraf hai) الم * غلبت Rome ( se ( سيغلبون‏ ( tak ka waqia guzar chuka hai ke (ke Rome (mojooda Itly) walon ne Faaris walon par fateh pa li thi)."
4775,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke har paida honey wala bachcha deene-fitrat par paida hota hai lekin iske maan-baap usey yahoodii, nasrani ya majusi bana letey hain. uski misal aisi hai jaisi janwar ka bachcha sahi Salim paida hota hai kya tum ne unhein naak kaan kata hua koi bachcha dekha hai. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is aayat ki tilawat ki فطرة الله التي فطر Naas عليها لا تبديل لخلق الله ذلك الدين القيم ''Allaah ki us fitrat ki ittaba (pairvi) karo jis par us ne insan ko paida kya hai, Allah ki banai hui fitrat mein koi tabdili mumkin nahi, yahi seedha Deen hai.''"
4776,jab aayat ( الذين آمنوا ولم يلبسوا إيمانهم بظلم‏ (ke ''jo log eman laey aur apne eman ke sath zulm ki aamezish (milawat) nahi ki.'' nazil hui to ashaab rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahut ghabraaey aur kehney lagey ke ham mein kon aisa hoga jisne apne eman ke sath zulm ki milawat nahi ki hogii? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aayat mein zulm se ye murad nahi hai. tum ne luqman (Alaihissalam) ki wo nasihat nahi suni jo unhon-ne apne betey ko ki thi ( إن الشرك لظلم عظيم‏ (ke '' beshak shirk karna bada bhari zulm hai.''
4777,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik din logon ke sath tashrif rakhtey they ke aik nayaa aadmi khidmat mein hazir hua aur puchha : ya Rasulullah! eman kya hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke eman ye hai ke tum Allah aur uske farishton, rasulon aur uski mulaqat par eman lao aur qiyamat ke din par eman laao. unhon-ne puchha : ya Rasulullah ! Islam kya hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Islam ye hai ke tanha Allah ki ibadat karo aur kisi ko iska Sharik na thahraao, Namaz qaaim karo aur farz zakat ada karo aur Ramazan ke rozey rakho. unhon-ne puchha : ya Rasulullah ! ehsan kya hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ehsan ye hai ke tum Allah ki is tarah ibadat karo maano ke tum usey dekh rahe ho warna ye aqeeda laziman rakho ke agar tum usey nahi dekhtey to wo tumhen zaroor dekh raha hai. unhon-ne puchha : ya Rasulullah! qiyamat Kab qaaim hogi ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jis se puchha ja raha hai khud wo sawal karney waaley se zyada uske honey ke mutaalliq nahi janta. albatta main tumhen uski chand nishaniyan bataataa hun. jab aurat aisi aulad janey jo uske aaqa bin jayen to ye qiyamat ki nishani hai, jab nangey paaun, nangey jism waley log logon par Hakim ho jayen to ye qiyamat ki nishani hai. qiyamat bhi un panch chizon mein se hai jisey Allah ke siwa aur koi nahi janta, beshak Allah hi ke paas qiyamat ka ilm hai. wahi meenh barsata hai aur wahi janta hai ke maa ke raham mein kya hai? phir wo sahib uth kar chaley gaey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein mere paas wapas bula laao. logon ne unhein talash kya taake Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein dobara laaein lekin unka kahin pata nahi tha. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye sahib Jibraeel they (insaanii sura mein) logon ko Deen ki baatein sikhaney aaey they."
4778,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ghaib ki kunjiyaan panch hain. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us aayat ki tilawat ki إن الله عنده علم الساعة‏ ''beshak Allah hi ko qiyamat ka ilm hai aur wahi barish nazil karta hai aur wahi janta hai ke maadda ke raham mein nar hai ya maadda aur koi nafs nahi janta ke wo kal kya karega aur koi nahi janta ke wo kahan marega.
4779,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ka irshad hai ke ''maine apne Saleh aur nek bandon ke liye wo cheezein taiyaar kar rakhi hain jinhein kisi aankh ne dekha na kisi kaan ne suna aur na kisi ke guman w khayal mein wo aai hain.'' Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke agar chaho to is aayat ko padh lo فلا تعلم نفس ما أخفي لهم من قرة أعين‏ke ''so kisi ko nahi malum jo jo saman aankhon ki thandak ka unke liye jannat mein chipa kar rakha gaya hai.'' Ali-bin-Abdullaah madeenii ne bayan kya ke ham se Sufiyan ne bayan kya, unse abu-Zinaad ne bayan kya, unse Aaraj ne aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke Allah Taala ne farmaya hai, pehli hadis ki tarah . Sufiyan se puchha gaya ke ye aap Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadis riwayat kar rahe hain ya apne ijtihaad se farma rahe hain? unhon-ne farmaya ke (agar ye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadis nahi hai) to phir aur kya hai? abu-Muawia ne bayan kya, unse Aamash ne aur unse Saleh ne ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne (aayat mazkura (uper zikr) mein) qirat (seegha jama ke saath) padha hai."
4780,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala irshad farmata hai ke maine apne neku-kaar bandon ke liye wo cheezein taiyaar rakhi hain jinhein kisi aankh ne na dekha aur kisi kaan ne na suna aur na kisi insan ke dil mein unka kabhi guman w khayal paida hua. Allah ki un ne'maton se jankari aur aagaahii to alag rahi (unka kisi ko guman w khayal bhi paida nahi hua). phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is aayat ki tilawat ki فلا تعلم نفس ما أخفي لهم من قرة أعين jaza (badla) بما كانوا يعملونke ''so kisi nafse-momin ko malum nahi jo jo saman aankhon ki thandak ka (jannat mein) unke liye chipa kar rakha gaya hai, ye badla hai unke nek amalon ka jo duniya mein kartey rahe.''"
4781,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke koi momin aisa nahi ke main khud uske nafs se bhi zyada us se aur aakhirat mein talluq na rakhta hun, agar tumhara ji chahey to ye aayat padh lo ( النبي أولى بالمؤمنين من أنفسهم‏ ) ke ''nabii mominon ke sath khud unke nafs se bhi zyada talluq rakhtey hai.'' pas jo momin bhi (marney ke baad) tarka maal w asbaab chhodey aur koi unka wali waaris nahi hai iske azeez w aqaarib jo bhi hon, uske maal ke waaris hongey, lekin agar kisi momin ne koi qarz chhoda hai ya aulad chhodi hai to wo mere paas aa jayen unka zimmedaar main hun."
4782,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aazad kiye huey ghulam Zaid-bin-Haarisa ko ham hamesha Zaid-bin Muhammad keh kar pukara kartey they, yahan tak ke Quran Karim mein aayat nazil hui ( ادعوهم لآبائهم هو أقسط عند الله‏ (ke '' unhein unke baapon ki taraf mansub karo ke yahi Allah ke nazdeek sachchii aur theek baat hai.''"
4783,hamarey khayal mein ye aayat Anas-bin-Nazar ke barey mein nazil hui thii من المؤمنين رجال صدقوا ما عاهدوا الله عليه‏ke ''ahale-iimaan mein kuchh log aisey bhi hain ke unhon-ne Allah se jo ahad kya tha usmein wo sachey utrey.''
4784,"jab ham Quran Majeed ko musahaf ki sura mein jama kar rahe they, to mujhey sura Ahzaab ki aik aayat (kahiin likhi hui) nahi mil rahi thi. main wo aayat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sun chuka tha. aakhir wo mujhey Khuzaima Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas mili jinki shahadat ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 momin mardon ki shahadat ke barabar qarar diya tha. wo aayat ye thii من المؤمنين رجال صدقوا ما عاهدوا الله عليه‏''ahale-iimaan mein kuchh log aisey bhi hain ke unhon-ne Allah se jo ahad kya tha usmein wo sachey utrey.''"
4785,"jab Allah Taala ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hukm diya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni beeviyon ko (aap ke samney rehney ya aap se alehadgii ka ( ikhtiyar dein to aap Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas bhi tashrif le gaey aur farmaya ke main tum se aik mamla ke mutaalliq kehney aaya hun zaroori nahi ke tum usmein jald bazi se kaam lo, apne waalidain se bhi mashwara kar sakti ho. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to jantey hi they ke mere walid kabhi aap se judai ka mashwara nahi de saktey. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ka farman hai) ya أيها النبي قل لأزواجك‏ (ke ''aey Nabi ! apni beeviyon se farma dijiye '' aakhir aayat tak. maine arz kya, lekin kis cheez ke liye mujhey apne waalidain se mashwara ki zarurat hai, khuli hui baat hai ke main Allaah, uske rasool aur aalame-aakhirat ko chahti hun."
4786,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hukm hua ke apni beeviyon ko ikhtiyar dein to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere paas tashrif laey aur farmaya ke main tum se aik mamla ke mutaalliq kehney aaya hon, zaroori nahi ke tum jaldi karo, apne waalidain se bhi mashwara ley sakti ho. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko to malum hi tha ke mere waalidain aap se judai ka kabhi mashwara nahi de saktey. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (wo aayat jis mein ye hukm tha) padhi ke Allah paak ka irshad hai ( ya أيها النبي قل لأزواجك إن كنتن تردن الحياة الدنيا وزينتها‏ ) ''aey Nabi ! apni beeviyon se farma dijiye ke agar tum duniyawii zindagi aur uski zeenat ko chahti ho se ( أجرا عظيما‏ ( tak. Aaisha (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya lekin apne waalidain se mashwara ki kis baat ke liye zarurat hai, zahir hai ke main Allah aur uske rasool aur aalame-aakhirat ko chahti hun. bayan kya ke phir dusri paak beeviyon ne bhi wahi kaha jo main keh chuki thi. iski mutabiat (pairavi) Musa bin aa'yun ne Mamar se ki hai ke unse Zohri ne bayan kya ke unhein abu-Salma ne khabar di aur Abdur-Razzaq aur Abu-Sufiyan Ma'marii ne Mamar se bayan kya, unse Zohri ne, aur unse Urwa ne aur unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne."
4787,aayat ( وتخفي في نفسك ما الله مبديه‏ ( ''aur aap apne dil mein wo chhipaatey rahe jisey Allah zahir karne wala tha.'' Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) aur Zaid-bin-Haarisa (Raziallahu anhu) ke maamle mein nazil hui thi.
4788,"jo auratein apne nafs ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye hiba karne aati thin mujhey un par badi ghairat aati thi. main kehti ke kya aurat khud hi apne ko kisi mard ke liye pesh kar sakti hai? phir jab Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki  ترجئ من تشاء منهن وتؤوي إليك من تشاء ومن ابتغيت ممن عزلت فلا جناح عليكke ''unmein se jis ko chaahein apne se door rakhein aur jis ko chaahein apne nazdeek rakhein aur jinko aap ne alag kar rakha tha usmein se kisi ko phir talab kar lein jab bhi, aap par koi gunah nahi hai.'' to maine kaha ke main to samajhtii hun ke aap ka rab aap ki murad bila taakheer poori kar dena chahta hai."
4789,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is aayat ke nazil honey ke baad bhi  ترجئ من تشاء منهن وتؤوي إليك من تشاء ومن ابتغيت ممن عزلت فلا جناح عليكke '' unmein se aap jis ko chaahein apne se door rakhein aur jinko aap ne alag kar rakha tha unmein se kisi ko talab kar lein jab bhi aap par koi gunah nahi.'' agar ( paak beeviyon ( mein se kisi ki baari mein kisi dusri biwi ke paas jana chahtey to jinki baari hoti unse ijazat letey they ( Muaza ne bayan kya ke) maine is par Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha ke aisi sura mein aap Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya kehti thiin? unhon-ne farmaya ke main to ye arz kar deti thi ke ya Rasulullah! agar ye ijazat aap mujh se ley rahe hain to main to apni baari ka kisi doosrey par eisaar nahi kar saktii. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) ibaad-bin-ibaad ne ki, unhon-ne Aasim se suna."
4790,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! aap ke paas achchhey burey har tarah ke log aatey hain, kash! aap paak beeviyon ko parde ka hukm de dein. iske baad Allah ne parde ka hukm utaaraa."
4791,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zainab-bint-Jahash (Raziallahu anhu) se nikah kya to qaum ko aap ne dawat walima di, khana khaney ke baad log (ghar ke andar hi) baithey (der tak) baatein kartey rahe. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa kya maano aap uthna chahtey hain (taake log samajh jayen aur uth jaaein) lekin koi bhi nahi uthaa, jab aap ne dekha ke koi nahi uthtaa to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey ho gaey. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey to doosrey log bhi khadey ho gaey, lekin teen aadmi ab bhi baithey reh gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab bahar se andar janey ke liye aaey to dekha ke kuchh ab bhi baithey huey hain. iske baad wo log bhi uth gaey to maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar khabar di ke wo log bhi chaley gaey hain to aap andar tashrif laey. maine bhi chaha ke andar jaun , lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne aur mere beech mein darwaza ka parda gira liya, iske baad aayat ( mazkoora) nazil huii يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تدخلوا بيوت النبي ke ''aey eman waalo! Nabi ke gharon mein mat jaya karo. aakhir aayat tak."
4792,"us aayat yani aayat parda (ke shaane-nuzool) ke mutaalliq mein sabse zyada janta hun, jab Zenab (Raziallahu anha) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nikah kya aur wo aap ke sath aap ke ghar hi mein thin to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khana taiyaar karwaya aur qaum ko bulaya (khaaney se farigh honey ke baad) log baithey baatein kartey rahe. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar jatey aur phir andar aatey (taake log uth jaaein) lekin log baithey baatein kartey rahe. is par ye aayat nazil huii (يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تدخلوا بيوت النبي إلا أن يؤذن لكم إلى طعام غير ناظرين إناه‏)ke ''aey eman waalo! Nabi ke gharon mein mat jaya karo. siwaey us waqt ke jab tumhen (khaaney ke liye) aaney ki ijazat di jaey. aisey taur par ke uski taiyaarii ke muntazir na raho. ''Allah taala ke irshad ( من وراء حجاب‏ ( tak iske baad parda daal diya gaya aur log khadey ho gaey."
4793,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) se nikah ke baad (bataur waleema) gosht aur roti taiyaar karwai aur mujhey khaney par logon ko bulaney ke liye bhejaa, phir kuchh log aaey aur kha kar wapas chaley gaey. phir doosrey log aaey aur kha kar wapas chaley, mein bulata raha. aakhir jab koi baqi nahi raha to maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Nabi ! ab to koi baqi nahi raha jis ko main dawat dun to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ab dastar-khuwaan utha lo lekin teen ashkhaas ghar mein baatein kartey rahe. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar nikal aaey aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujre ke samney ja kar farmaya Assalaamu alaikum warahmatullah ahle-bait. unhon-ne kaha w-alaikumassalaam warahmatullah, apni ahal ko aap ne kaisa paayaa? Allah barkat ata farmaaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) isi tarah tamam paak beeviyon ke hujron ke samney gaey aur jis tarah Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se farmaya tha is tarah sabse farmaya aur unhon-ne bhi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki tarah jawab diya. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas tashrif laey to wo teen aadmi ab bhi ghar mein baithey baatein kar rahe they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahut zyada haya daar they, aap (ye dekh karke log ab bhi baithey huey hain) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujra ki taraf phir chaley gaey, mujhey yad nahi ke iske baad maine ya kisi aur ne aapko ja kar khabar ki ke ab wo teenon aadmi rawaana ho chukey hain. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ab wapas tashrif laey aur paon chaukhat par rakha. abhi aap ka aik paon andar tha aur aik paon bahar ke aap ne parda gira liya aur parde ki aayat nazil hui."
4794,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) se nikah par da'wate-waleema ki aur gosht aur roti logon ko khilaaii. phir ummahaatul momeneen (nabi ki beeviyon) ke hujron ki taraf gaey, jaisa ke aap ka mamool (routine) tha ke nikah ki subah ko aap jaya kartey they, aap unhein salam kartey aur unke haq mein dua kartey aur ummahaatul momeneen bhi aapko salam kartin aur aap ke liye dua kartin. ummahaatul momeneen ke hujron se jab aap apne hujre mein wapas tashrif laey to aap ne dekha ke 2 aadmi aapas mein guftgu kar rahe hain. jab aap ne unhein baithey huey dekha to phir aap hujre se nikal gaey. un donon ne jab dekha ke Allah ke Nabi apne hujre se wapas chaley gaey hain to badi jaldi jaldii wo uth kar bahar nikal gaey. mujhey yad nahi ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko unke chaley janey ki itlaa di ya kisi aur ne phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas aaey aur ghar mein aatey hi darwaze ka parda gira liya aur aayate-hijaab nazil hui aur Saeed-ibne-Ubaii Maryam ne bayan kya ke ham ko Yahya-bin-kaseer ne khabar di, kaha mujh se Humaid lamba ne bayan kya aur unhon-ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se naql kya."
4795,"Ummul-Momenin Sauda (Raziallahu anha) parde ka hukm nazil honey ke baad qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye niklin. wo bahut bhari bharkam thin jo unhein janta tha us se posheeda nahi reh sakti thin. rastey mein umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein dekh liya aur kaha ke aey Sauda ! haan Allah ki qism ! aap ham se apne aapko nahi chipa saktin dekhiye to aap kis tarah bahar nikli hain. bayan kya ke Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ultey paon wahan se wapas aa gain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt mere hujre mein tashrif rakhtey they aur raat ka khana kha rahe they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath mein us waqt gosht ki aik haddi thi. Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ne dakhil hotey hi kaha : ya Rasulullah! main qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye nikli thi to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se baatein kin, bayan kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi ka nuzool shuru ho gaya aur thodi der baad ye kaifiyat khatm hui, haddi ab bhi aap ke hath mein thi. aap ne usey rakha nahi tha. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhen ( Allah ki taraf se) qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye bahar janey ki ijazat de di gaee hai."
4796,"parde ka hukm nazil honey ke baad abul-Qaees ke bhai Aflah (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se milney ki ijazat chaahii, lekin maine kahalwaa diya ke jab tak is silsiley main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat hasil na ley loon, unse nahi mil saktii. maine sochaa ke unke bhai abul-Qaees ne mujhey thoda hi doodh pilaya tha, doodh pilaaney wali to abul-Qaees ki biwi thi. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to maine aap se arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! abul-Qaees ke bhai Aflah (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se milney ki ijazat chaahii, lekin maine ye kahlwaa diya ke jab tak Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat na ley loon unse mulaqat nahi kar saktii. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apne chacha se milney se tum ne kyon inkar kar diya. maine arz kya : ya rasoolullaah! abul-Qaees ne mujhey thoda hi doodh pilaya tha, doodh pilaaney wali to unki biwi thin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya unhein andar aaney ki ijazat de do wo tumharey chacha hain. Urwa ne bayan kya ke isi wjah se Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati thin ke razaat se bhi wo cheezein (maslan nikah wghaira) haram ho jati hain jo nasb ki wjah se haram hoti hain."
4797,"arz kya gaya : ya Rasulullah ! aap par salam ka tariqa to hamein malum ho gaya hai, lekin aap par) صلاة (ka kya tariqa hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke yun padha karo اللهم صل على محمد وعلى آل محمد ، Mina كما صليت على آل إبراهيم ، Mina إنك حميد مجيد ، Mina اللهم بارك على محمد وعلى آل محمد ، Mina كما باركت على آل إبراهيم ، Mina إنك حميد مجيد‏"
4798,ham ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! aap par salam bhejney ka tariqa to hamein malum ho gaya hai. lekin) صلاة ( ) durood ( bhejney ka kya tariqa hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke yun kaha karo اللهم صل على محمد عبدك ورسولك ، Mina كما صليت على آل إبراهيم ، Mina وبارك على محمد وعلى آل محمد كما باركت على إبراهيمabu-Saaleh ne bayan kya ke aur unse Lais-bin-Sad ne (un alfaz ke saath) على محمد وعلى آل محمد ، Mina كما باركت على آل إبراهيم ke alfaz riwayat kiye hain.
4799,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Musa (Alaihissalam) badey baa-hayaa they, unhiin ke mutaalliq Allah Taala ka ye irshad hai يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تكونوا كالذين آذوا موسى فبرأه الله مما قالوا وكان عند الله وجيها ke ''aey eman waalo! un logon ki tarah na ho jana jinhoney Musa (Alaihissalam) ko eiizaa pahunchai thi, so Allah ne unhein barii Sabit kar diya aur Allah ke nazdeek wo badey izzat waley they.''"
4800,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab Allah Taala aasman par kisi baat ka faisla karta hai to Farishtey Allah Taala ke faisla ko sun kar jhuktey huey aajizii kartey huey apne bazu phadphadaatey hain. Allah ka farman unhein is tarah sunai deta hai jaisey saaf chikney patthar par zanjeer chalaney se awaz paida hoti hai. phir jab unke dilon se ghabraahat door ho jati hai to wo aapas mein poochhtey hain ke tumharey rab ne kya farmaayaa? wo kehtey hain ke haq baat ka hukm farmaya aur wo bahut oonchaa, sabse bada hai phir unki yahi guftgu chori chhipey sunney waley shaitan sun bhaagtey hain, shaitan aasman ke nichey yun neechey-oopar hotey hain, Sufiyan ne is mauqe par hatheli ko mod kar ungliyan alag-alag karke shayatin ke jama honey ki kaifiyat batai ke is tarah shaitan aik ke uper aik rahtey hain. phir wo shayatin koi aik kalima sun letey hain aur apne nichey waley ko bataatey hain. is tarah wo kalima saahir ya kaahin tak pahunchtaa hai. kabhi to aisa hota hai ke is se pahley ke wo ye kalima apne se nichey waley ko bataein aag ka golaa unhein aa dabochtaa hai aur kabhi aisa hota hai ke jab wo bata letey hain to aag ka angaaraa un par padta hai, iske baad kaahin usmein so jhoot mila kar logon se bayan karta hai (eik baat jab us kaahin ki sahi ho jati hai to unke manney walon ki taraf se) kaha jata hai ke kya isi tarah ham se falan din kaahin nahi kaha tha, usi aik kalima ki wjah se jo aasman par shayatin ne suna tha kaahinon aur saahiron ki baat ko log sachcha jaanney lagtey hain."
4801,"aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Safa pahaadii par chadhey aur pukara : ya sabaahaa! (logo daudo) us awaz par Quraish jama ho gaey aur puchha kya baat hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhari kya raey hai agar main tumhen bataaun ke dushman subah ke waqt ya Sham ke waqt tum par hamla karne wala hai to kya tum meri baat ki tasdeeq nahi karogey? unhon-ne kaha ke ham aap ki tasdeeq karengey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir main tum ko sakht tareen azab (dozakh) se pahley daraane wala hun. abu-Lahab (mardood) bola to halaak ho jaa, kya tu ney usi liye hamein bulaya tha. is par Allah paak ne aayat ( تبت يدا أبي لهب‏ ) naazil farmai."
4802,"aaftaab ghurub honey ke waqt mein masjid main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath maujood tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Abu-Zar ! tumhen malum hai ye aaftaab kahan ghurub hota hai? maine arz kya Allah aur uske rasool ko zyada ilm hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye chalta rehta hai yahan tak ke arsh ke nichey sajda karta hai jaisa ke irshad baari hai) والشمس تجري لمستقر لها ذلك تقدير العزيز العليم‏ (ke ''aur aaftaab apne thikaaney ki taraf chalta rehta hai, ye zabardast ilm waley ka thehraya hua andaza hai.''"
4803,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Allah Taala ke farman ( والشمس تجري لمستقر لها‏ ( ''aur suraj apne thikaaney ki taraf chalta rehta hai.'' ke mutaalliq sawal kya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke iska thikana arsh ke nichey hai.
4804,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kisi ke liye munasib nahi ke wo Yoonus-bin-Matti (Alaihissalam) se behtar honey ka dawa kare.
4805,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs ye dawa karey ke main Yoonus-bin-Matti (Alaihissalam) se behtar hon wo jhoota hai.
4806,"ye sawal Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi kya gaya tha to unhon-ne us aayat ki tilawat ki) أولئك الذين هدى الله فبهداهم اقتده‏ ( '' yahi wo log hain jinhein Allah ne hidayat di thi to aap bhi unhi ki hidayat ki ittaba (pairvi) karein. ''aur Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) usmein sajda kya kartey they."""
4807,"maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha tha ke is sura mein aayate-sajda ke liye daleel kya hai? unhon-ne kaha kya tum (sura An'aam ( mein ye nahi padhtey (ومن ذريته Dawud وسليمان) ke ''aur unki nasl se Dawud aur Sulaiman hain, yahi wo log hain jinhein Allah ne ye hidayat di thi, so aap bhi unki hidayat ki ittaba (pairvi) karein. ''daawood (Alaihissalam) bhi unmein se they jinki ittaba (pairvi) ka Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hukm tha (choonke Dawud (Alaihissalam) ke sajde ka usmein zikr hai isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi us mauqe par sajda kya)."
4808,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke pichhli raat aik sarkash jin achcha mere paas aaya, ya isi tarah ka kalima Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya taake meri Namaz kharaab karey lekin Allah Taala ne mujhey is par qudrat de di aur maine sochaa ke usey masjid ke sutoon se baandh dun taake subah ke waqt tum sab log bhi usey dekh sako. phir mujh ko apne bhai Sulaiman (Alaihissalam) ki dua yad aa gaii رب هب لي ملكا لا ينبغي لأحد من بعديke ''aey mere rab! mujhey aisi saltanat de ke mere baad kisi ko muyassar na ho.'' Rooh ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us jin ko zillat ke sath bhagaa diya."
4809,"ham Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. unhon-ne kaha : aey logo ! jis shakhs ko kisi cheez ka ilm ho to wo usey bayan karey agar ilm na ho to kahey ke Allah hi ko zyada ilm hai kyonke ye bhi ilm hi hai ke jo cheez na janta ho iske mutaalliq keh de ke Allah hi zyada jaanney wala hai. Allah Taala ne apne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bhi keh diya tha ( قل ما أسألكم عليه من أجر وما أنا من المتكلفين‏ (ke '' aap keh dijiye ke main tum se us Quran ya tableegh wahi par koi ujrat nahi chahta hun aur na main banawat karne wala hoon.'' aur main ( Dukhan ( ) dhoein (ke barey mein bataunga (jiska zikr Quran mein aaya hai) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Quraish ko Islam ki dawat di to unhon-ne taakheer ki, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke haq mein baddua ki) اللهم أعني عليهم بسبع كسبع يوسف ( ''aey Allah ! un par Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke zamane ki si qahat saalii ke zariey meri madad kar.'' chunanche qahat padaa aur itna zabardast ke har cheez khatm ho gaee aur log murdar aur chamdey khaney par majbur ho gaey. bhook ki shiddat ki wjah se ye haal tha ke aasman ki taraf dhuaan hi dhuaan nazar aataa. usi ke barey mein Allah Taala ne farmaayaa فارتقب يوم تأتي السماء بدخان مبين * يغشى Naas هذا عذاب أليمke ""to intizar karo us din ka jab aasman khula hua dhuaan laaeyga jo logon par chhaa jaeyga ye dardnak azab hai.'' bayan kya ke phir Quraish dua karne lagey ربنا اكشف عنا العذاب إنا مؤمنون * أنى لهم الذكرى وقد جاءهم رسول مبين * ثم تولوا عنه وقالوا معلم مجنون * إنا كاشفو العذاب قليلا إنكم عائدون‏ke ''aey hamarey rab! us azab ko ham se hata ley to ham eman laaengey lekin wo nasihat sunney waley kahan hain unke paas to rasool saaf moa'jazaat w dalaayel ke sath aa chuka aur wo us se munh mod chukey hain aur keh chukey hain ke usey to sikhaya ja raha hai, ye majnoon hai, beshak ham thodey dinon ke liye unse azab hata lengey yaqinan tum phir kufr hi ki taraf lot jaogey kya qiyamat mein bhi azab hataya jaaeyga.'' ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir ye azab to unse door kar diya gaya lekin jab wo dobara kufr mein mubtala ho gaey to jange-badr mein Allah ne unhein pakdaa. Allah Taala ke us irshad mein usi taraf ishara hai ( يوم نبطش البطشة الكبرى إنا منتقمون‏ (ke ''jis din ham sakht pakad karengey, bila shubah ham badla leney waley hain.''"
4810,"mushrekeen mein kuchh ne qatl ka gunah kya tha aur kasarat se kya tha. isi tarah zinaakaarii bhi kasarat se kartey rahe they. phir wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaey aur arz kya ke aap jo kuchh kehtey hain aur jiski taraf dawat detey hain (yani Islam) yaqinan achi cheez hai, lekin hamein ye bataiye ke ab tak ham ne jo gunah kiye hain wo Islam laney se maaf hongey ya nahi? is par ye aayat nazil huii  والذين لا يدعون مع الله إلها آخر wla يقتلون النفس التي حرم الله إلا بالحق wla يزنون''aur wo log jo Allah ke siwa aur kisi doosrey maabood ko nahi pukaartey aur kisi bhi jaan ko qatl nahi kartey jiska qatl karna Allah ne haram kya hai, haan magar haq ke saath'' aur ye aayat nazil huii قل ya عبادي الذين أسرفوا على أنفسهم لا تقنطوا من رحمة الله‏ ''aap keh dein ke aey mere bando! jo apne nafson par ziyadtiyaan kar chukey ho, Allah ki rehmat se naa-ummeed mat ho, beshak Allah sarey gunahon ko maaf kar dega. beshak Allah wo bada hi bakhshney wala bahut hi meharban hai.''"
4811,"ulamaae-Yahood mein se aik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kaha : aey Muhammad ! ham Taurait mein patey hain ke Allah Taala aasmanon ko aik ungli par rakh lega is tarah zameen ko aik ungli par, darakhton ko aik ungli par, pani aur mitti ko aik ungli par aur tamam makhlooqat ko aik ungli par, phir farmaeyga ke main hi badshah hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par hans diye aur aap ke samney ke daant dikhai dene lagey. aap ka ye hansnaa us Yahudi aalim ki tasdeeq mein tha. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is aayat ki tilawat ki وما قدروا الله حق قدره والأرض جميعا قبضته يوم القيامة والسموات مطويات بيمينه سبحانه وتعالى عما يشركون‏''aur un logon ne Allah ki azmat na ki jaisi azmat karna chahiye thi aur haal ye ke saari zameen usi ki muththii mein hogi qiyamat ke din aur aasman uske daahiney hath mein liptey hongey, wo un logon ke shirk se bilkul paak aur buland tar hai.''"
4812,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke qiyamat ke din Allah saari zameen ko apni muththii mein lega aur aasman ko apne daahiney hath mein lapet lega . phir farmaeyga ( أنا الملك , أين ملوك الأرض ( '' aaj hukumat sirf meri hai, duniya ke badshah aaj kahan hain? ''"
4813,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aakhiri martaba Saur phoonkey janey ke baad sabse pahley apna sar uthaney wala main hunga lekin us waqt main Musa (Alaihissalam) ko dekhunga ke arsh ke sath liptey huey hain, ab mujhey nahi malum ke wo pahley hi se isi tarah they ya doosrey Saur ke baad (mujh se pahley) uth kar arshe-Ilaahii ko thaam lengey."
4814,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke donon sooron ke phoonkey janey ka darmyani arsa chalis (40) hai. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke shagirdon ne puchha : kya chalis (40) din murad hain? unhon-ne kaha ke mujhey malum nahi phir unhon-ne puchha : chalis (40) saal ? is par bhi unhon-ne inkar kya. phir unhon-ne puchha : chalis (40) mahiney ? iske mutaalliq bhi unhon-ne kaha ke mujh ko khabar nahi aur har cheez fana ho jaeygi, siwa reedh ki haddi ke ke usi se saari makhlooq dobara banai jaeygi."
4815,maine Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sabse zyada sakht mamla mushrekeen ne kya kya tha? Abdullah ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Kaba ke qareeb Namaz padh rahe they ke Aqba-bin-abii-Mueet aaya us ne aap ka shana Mubarak pakad kar aap ki gardan mein apna kapda lapet diya aur us kapdey se aap ka gala badi sakhti ke sath ghontney laga. itney mein Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aagey aur unhon-ne us bad-bakht ka moondhaa pakad kar usey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se juda kya aur kaha ke kya tum aik aisey shakhs ko qatl kar dena chahtey ho jo kehta hai ke mera rab Allah hai aur wo tumharey rab ke paas se apni sachchai ke liye roshan dalaayel bhi sath laya hai.
4816,"aayat (وما كنتم تستترون أن يشهد،‏‏‏‏ عليكم سمعكم) ''aur tum is baat se apne ko chipa nahi saktey they ke tumharey kaan gawahi dengey.'' ke mutaalliq kaha ke Quraish ke 2 aadmi aur biwi ki taraf se unke qabila Saqeef ka koi rishtedar ya Saqeef ke 2 afraad they aur biwi ki taraf Quraish ka koi rishtedar , ye khaana Kaba ke paas baithey huey they unmein se kuchh ne kaha ke kya tumhara khayal hai ke Allah Taala hamari baatein sunta hoga aik ne kaha ke kuchh baatein sunta hai. doosrey ne kaha ke agar kuchh baatein sun sakta hai to sab sunta hoga. is par ye aayat nazil hui ( وما كنتم تستترون أن يشهد عليكم سمعكم wla أبصاركم‏ ( ''aur tum is baat se apne ko chipa hi nahi saktey ke tumharey khilaf tumharey kaan aur tumhari aankhen gawahi dengii.'' aakhir aayat ( وذلكم ظنكم‏ ( tak."
4817,"khaana Kaba ke paas 2 qureshi aur aik Saqafi ya aik qureshi aur 2 Saqafi mard baithey huey they. unke pet bahut motey they lekin aql se korey . aik ne unmein se kaha, tumhara kya khayal hai kya Allah hamari baton ko sun raha hai? doosrey ne kaha agar ham zor se boliin to sunta hai lekin aahista boliin to nahi sunta . teesrey ne kaha agar Allah zor se bolney par sun sakta hai to aahista bolney pe bhi zaroor sunta hoga. is par ye aayat utri ( وما كنتم تستترون أن يشهد عليكم سمعكم wla أبصاركم wla جلودكم‏ (ke ''aur tum is baat se apne ko chipa hi nahi saktey ke tumharey kaan aur tumhari aankhen aur tumharey chamdey gawahi dengey.'' aakhir aayat tak. Sufiyan ham se ye hadis bayan kartey they aur kaha ke ham se Mansoor ne ya ibne- najeeh ne ya Humaid ne unmein se kisi aik ne ya kisi 2 ne ye hadis bayan ki, phir aap Mansoor hi ka zikr kartey they aur dusron ka zikr aik se zyada martaba nahi kya."
4818,maine Taaus se suna ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se Allah Taala ke irshad ( إلا المودة في القربى‏ ( '' siwa rishte-daarii ki mohabbat ke'' mutaalliq puchha gaya to Saeed-bin-Jubair ne farmaya ke aal Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qaraabatdaarii murad hai. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par kaha ke tum ne jald bazi ki. Quraish ki koi shaakh aisi nahi jis main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qarabat dari na ho. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke tum se sirf ye chahta hun ke tum is qarabat dari ki wjah se sila rehmii ka mamla karo jo mere aur tumharey darmyan mein maujood hai.
4819,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko member par ye aayat padhtey sunaa (ونادوا ya مالك ليقض علينا ربك) ''aur ye log pukaarengey ke aey Maalik! tumhara parwardigar hamara kaam hi tamam kar de. ''aur Qatada ne kaha ( maslan للآخرين ( yani pichhlon ke liye nasihat . doosrey ne kaha ( muqreneen (ka mana qaabu mein rakhney waley . Arab log kehtey hain fulaanaa fulaaney ka ( Muqrin ( hai yani is par ikhtiyar rakhta hai) usko qaabu mein laya hai). ( أكواب ( wo ghadey jin mein tauntii na ho balke munh khula hua ho jahan se aadmi chahey piey. (ان کان للرحمن ولد) kaa mana ye hai ke uski koi aulad nahi hai. (is sura main (ان نافيه) hai) ( عابدين ( se ( آنفين ( murad hai. yani sabse pahley mein us se ( aar ( karta hun. usmein 2 lughat hain (عابد وعبد) aur Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne usko ( وقال الرسول ya رب‏ ( padha hai. ( أول العابدين (ke mana sabse pahlaa inkar karne wala yani agar khuda ki aulad Sabit kartey ho to main iska sabse pahlaa inkaaii hun. is sura main ( عابدين ( baab (عبد يعبد) se aayega aur Qatada ne kaha ( في أم الكتاب‏ (ka mana ye hai ke majmooii kitab aur asl kitab (yani lauhe-mahfooz mein) .
4820,"(qiyamat ki) panch alamatein guzar chuki hain ( Dukhan ( dhuaan , ( Rome ( ghalbae-Rome (mojooda Itly) , ( القمر ( chaand ka tukdey hona, ( والبطشة ( pakad aur) واللزام‏ ( halaakat aur qaid ."
4821,"ye ( qahat ( isliye padaa tha ke Quraish jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dawat qabool karne ki bajaey shirk par jamey rahe to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye aisey qahat ki baddua ki jaisa Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke zamane mein padaa tha. chunanche qahat ki naubat yahan tak pahunchi ke log haddiyaan tak khaney lagey. log aasman ki taraf nazar uthatey lekin bhook aur faaqa ki shiddat ki wjah se dhuein ke siwa aur kuchh nazar na aata usi ke mutaalliq Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki (فارتقب يوم تأتي السماء بدخان مبين * يغشى Naas هذا عذاب أليم)''to aap intizar karein us roz ka jab aasman ki taraf nazar aaney wala dhuaan paida ho jo logon par chhaa jaey, ye aik dardnak azab hoga.'' bayan kya ke phir aik sahib Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha ya Rasulullah ! qabila Muzar ke liye barish ki dua kijiye ke wo barbad ho chukey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Muzar ke haq mein dua karne ke liye kehtey ho, tum badey jari ho. aakhir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye dua farmai aur barish hui. is par aayat ( إنكم عائدون‏ ( nazil hui (yani agarche tum ne eman ka wada kya hai lekin tum kufr ki taraf phir lot jaaogey) chunanche jab phir unmein khush'haalii hui to shirk ki taraf lot gaey (aur apne eman ke waadey ko bhulaa diyaa) is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki) يوم نبطش البطشة الكبرى إنا منتقمون‏‏ ( ''jis roz ham badi sakht pakad pakdein gey (is roz ( ham pura badla ley lengey. '' bayan kya us aayat se murad badr ki ladai hai."
4822,"ye bhi ilm hi hai ke tumhen agar koi baat malum nahi hai to iske mutaalliq yun keh do ke Allah hi zyada jaanney wala hai. Allah Taala ne apne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se farmaya ke aap apni qaum se keh dein ke main tum se kisi ujrat ka taalib nahi hun aur na main bnaawati baatein karta hun jab Quraish Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko takleef pahunchaney aur aap ke sath dushmani ki ravish mein barabar badhtey hi rahe to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye baddua ki ke aey Allah ! unke khilaf meri madad aisey qahat ke zariey kar jaisa ke Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke zamane mein padaa tha. chunanche qahat padaa aur bhook ki shiddat ka ye haal hua ke log haddiyaan aur murdar khaney lag gaey. log aasman ki taraf dekhtey they lekin faaqa ki wjah se dhuein ke siwa aur kuchh nazar na aataa. aakhir unhon-ne kaha ke ''aey hamarey parwardigaar! ham se is azab ko door kar, ham zaroor eman ley aaeingey. lekin Allah Taala ne unse keh diya tha ke agar ham ne ye azab door kar diya to phir bhi tum apni pehli haalat par lot aaogey.'' Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke haq mein dua ki aur ye azab unse hat gaya lekin wo phir bhi kufr w shirk par hi jamey rahe, iska badla Allah Taala ne badr ki ladai mein liya. yahi waqia aayat (يوم تأتي السماء بدخان مبين‏) aakhir tak mein bayan hua hai."
4823,"mein Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. unhon-ne farmaya ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Quraish ko Islam ki dawat di to unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jhutlaayaa aur aap ke sath sarkashi ki. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye baddua ki ke aey Allaah! meri unke khilaf Yusuf (Alaihissalam) jaisey qahat ke zariey madad farmaa. chunanche qahat padaa aur har cheez khatm ho gaee. log murdar khaney lagey. koi shakhs khada ho kar aasman ki taraf dekhta to bhook aur faaqa ki wjah se aasman aur uske darmyan dhuaan hi dhuaan nazar aataa. phir aap ne us aayat ki tilawat shuru ki (فارتقب يوم تأتي السماء بدخان مبين * يغشى Naas هذا عذاب أليم‏)''to aap intizar karein us roz ka jab aasman ki taraf se nazar aaney wala aik dhuaan paida ho jo logon par chhaa jaey, ye aik dardnak azab hoga. beshak ham chandey us azab ko hata lengey aur tum bhi apni pehli haalat par lot aaogey.'' Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke kya qiyamat ke azab se bhi wo bach sakengey? farmaya ke sakht pakad badr ki ladai mein hui thi."
4824,"Allah Taala ne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Nabi banaakar bheja aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ( قل ما أسألكم عليه من أجر وما أنا من المتكلفين‏ (ke '' keh do ke main tum se kisi ajr ka taalib nahi hun aur na main bnaawati baatein karne walon mein se hoon.'' phir jab aap ne dekha ke Quraish dushmanii se baaz nahi aatey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye baddua ki ke ''aey Allah ! unke khilaf meri madad aisey qahat se kar jaisa Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke zamane mein padaa tha.'' ( phir ( qahat padaa aur har cheez khatm ho gaee. log haddiyaan aur chamdey khaney par majbur ho gaey (Sulaimaan aur Mansoor) hadis ke raviyon mein se aik ne bayan kya ke wo chamdey aur murdar khaney par majbur ho gaey aur zameen se dhuaan sa nikalney laga. aakhir Abu-Sufiyan aaey aur kaha ke aey Muhammad (sl)! aap ki qaum halaak ho chukii, Allah se dua kijiye ke unse qahat ko door kar de. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua farmai aur qahat khatm ho gaya. lekin iske baad wo phir kufr ki taraf lot gaey. Mansoor ki riwayat mein hai ke phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye aayat padhii (فارتقب يوم تأتي السماء بدخان مبين‏)''to aap us roz ka intizar karein jab aasman ki taraf aik nazar aaney wala dhuaan paida ho.'' ( عائدون‏ ( tak. kya aakhirat ka azab bhi unse door ho sakega ?'' dhuaan ''aur '' sakht pakad ''aur '' halaakat '' guzar chukey. kuchh ne '' chaand ''aur kuchh ne '' ghalba Rome (mojooda Itly) '' ka bhi zikr kya hai ke ye bhi guzar chuka hai."
4825,"panch (Qur'aan Majeed ki pesheen goiyaan) guzar chuki hain. ( اللزام ( (badr ki ladai ki halaakat), ( Rome ( (ghalba Rome (mojooda Itly) ( ) البطشة ( (sakht pakad), (القمر) (chaand ke tukdey honaa) aur) والدخان‏ ( dhuaan, shiddat faaqa ki wjah se."
4826,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala farmata hai ke ibne-Aadam mujhey takleef pahunchata hai wo zamana ko gali deta hai halanke main hi zamana hun, mere hi hath mein sab kuchh hai. main raat aur din ko adalta-badaltaa rehta hun."
4827,"Marwan ko Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne hijaaz ka ameer (governer) banaya tha. us ne aik mauqe par khutba diya aur khutbe mein Yazeed bin Muawiya ka baar-baar zikr kya, taake iske walid (Muaawiya (Raziallahu anhu)) ke baad us se log bait karein. is par Abdur-Rehman -bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ne aitiraazan kuchh farmaya, Marwan ne kaha usey pakad lo. Abdur-Rehman apni behan Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar mein chaley gaey to wo log pakad nahi sakey. is par Marwan bola ke isi shakhs ke barey mein Quran ki ye aayat nazil hui thii والذي قال لوالديه أف لكما أتعدانني ke ''aur jis shakhs ne apne maan-baap se kaha ke tuff hai tum par kya tum mujhey khabar detey ho.'' is par Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke hamarey (aale-abii-bakar ke) barey mein Allah Taala ne koi aayat nazil nahi ki balke tohmat se meri Bara't zaroor nazil ki thi."
4828,"aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kabhi is tarah hanstey nahi dekha ke aap ke halaq ka kowa nazar aa jaey balke aap tabassum farmaya kartey they, bayan kya ke jab bhi aap badal ya hawa dekhtey to ( ghabraahat aur Allah ka khauf) aap ke chehre se pehchan liya jata."
4829,ya Rasulullah ! jab log badal dekhtey hain to khush hotey hain ke us se barish barsegii lekin iske bar-khilaf aapko main dekhti hon ke aap badal dekhtey hain to na-gawari ka asar aap ke chehre par numaayaan ho jata hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Aaisha ! kya zamaanat hai ke usmein azab na ho. aik qaum ( aad ( par hawa ka azab aaya tha. unhon-ne jab azab dekha to boley ke ye to badal hai jo ham par barsega.
4830,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ne makhlooq paida ki, jab wo uski paidaaish se farigh hua to raham ne khadey ho kar raham karne waley Allah ke daman mein panah li. Allah Taala ne us se farmaya kya tujhey ye pasand nahi ke jo tujh ko jodey main bhi usey judun aur jo tujhey todey mein bhi usey tod dun. raham ne arz kya, haan aey mere rab! Allah Taala ne farmaya, phir aisa hi hoga. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke agar tumhara ji chahey to ye aayat padh lo ( فهل عسيتم إن توليتم أن تفسدوا في الأرض وتقطعوا أرحامكم ) ''agar tum kinara kash! raho to aaya tum ko ye ehtimaal bhi hai ke tum log Deen mein fasaad machaa doge aur aapas mein qata' talluq kar logey.''"
4831,Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne pichhli hadis ki tarah. phir (abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar tumhara ji chahey to aayat ( فهل عسيتم ( agar tum kinara kash! raho padh lo.
4832,"pichhli hadis ki tarah (aur ye ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, agar tumhara ji chahey to aayat agar tum kinara kash! raho padh lo."
4833,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik safar mein ja rahe they. umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aap ke sath they. raat ka waqt tha umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne sawal kya lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne koi jawab nahi diya. phir unhon-ne sawal kya aur us martaba bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jawab nahi diya, teesri martaba bhi unhon-ne sawal kya lekin aap ne jawab nahi diya. is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, umr ki maan usey roey! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se tum ne teen martaba sawal mein israar kya, lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tumhen kisi martaba jawab nahi diya. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir maine apne oont ko harkat di aur logon se aagey badh gaya. mujhey khof tha ke kahin mere barey mein Quran Majeed ki koi aayat na nazil ho. abhi thodi hi der hui thi ke aik pukarney waley ki awaz maine suni jo mujhey hi pukar raha tha. maine kaha ke mujhey to khof tha hi ke mere barey mein koi aayat na nazil ho jaey. main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur salam kya, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujh par aaj raat aik sura nazil hui hai jo mujhey us saari kaaynaat se zyada azeez hai jis par suraj tuloo hota hai phir aap ne sura fateh ki tilawat farmai ."
4834,sura fateh suleh Hudaibiya ke barey mein nazil hui thi.
4835,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fateh Makka ke din sura fateh khoobsooat awaz se padhi. Muawiya bin Qurra ne kaha ke agar main chaahoon ke tumharey samney Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki us mauqe par tarze-qir'at ki naql karun to kar sakta hun.
4836,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz mein raat bhar khadey rahe yahan tak ke aap ke donon paon sooj gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya gaya ke Allah Taala ne to aap ki agli pichhli tamam khataein maaf kar di hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya main shukr-guzar banda na banoon?
4837,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ki Namaz mein itna lamba qiyam kartey ke aap ke qadam phat jatey. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne aik martaba arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! aap itni zyada mashaqqat kyon uthatey hain. Allah Taala ne to aapki aglii-pichhlii khataein maaf kar di hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya phir main shukr-guzar banda bannaa pasand na karun. umr ke aakhiri hisse mein (jab lamba qiyam dushwar ho gaya to) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baith kar raat ki Namaz padhtey aur jab rukoo ka waqt aata to khadey ho jatey (aur taqriban tees ya chalis (40) aayatein aur padhtey ( phir rukoo kartey.
4838,"ye aayat jo Quran mein hai  يا أيها النبي إنا أرسلناك شاهدا ومبشرا ونذيرا‏ ''aey Nabi ! beshak ham ne aapko gawahi dene wala aur daraane wala bana kar bheja hai.'' to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke mutaalliq yahi Allah Taala ne Taurait mein bhi farmaya tha ''aey Nabi ! beshak ham ne aapko gawahi dene wala aur bashaarat dene wala aur un padhun ( Arbon ( ki hifazat karne wala bana kar bheja hai. aap mere bandey hain aur mere rasool hain. maine aap ka naam mutawakkil rakhaa, aap na badkhoo hain aur na sakht dil aur na bazaron mein shor karne waley aur na wo burai ka badla burai se dengey balke maafi aur darguzar se kaam lengey aur Allah unki Rooh us waqt tak qabz nahi karega jab tak ke wo kaj qaum (arabii) ko seedha na kar lein yani jab tak wo unse ( لا إله إلا الله (ka iqrar na kara lein to us kalima tauheed ke zariey wo andhii aankhon ko aur behrey kanon ko aur parda padey huey dilon ko khol dengey.''"
4839,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aik sahabi (Usaid-bin-Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) raat mein sura Kahaf) padh rahe they. unka aik ghoda jo ghar mein bandhaa hua tha bidakney laga to wo sahabi nikley unhon-ne koi khas cheez nahi dekhi wo ghoda phir bhi bidak raha tha. subah ke waqt wo sahabi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur raat ka waqia bayan kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo cheez (jis se ghoda bidkaa tha) sakeenat thi jo Quran ki wjah se nazil hui.
4840,Suleh Hudaibiya ke mauqe par lashkar mein ham (muslmaan) aik hazaar char so they.
4841,"mein darakht ke nichey bait mein maujood tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 ungliyon ke darmyan kankari lekar phainkney se mana farmaayaa."
4842,maine Abdullah-bin Mughaffal Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) se ghusl khaane mein peshab karne ke mutaalliq suna. yani ye ke aap ne us se mana farmaayaa.
4843,aur unse Sabit bin Suhak ne aur wo (Suleh Hudaibiya ke din) darakht ke nichey bait karne walon mein shamil they.
4844,"mein abu-Waeil (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein aik masla poochhney ke liye (khawaarij ke mutaalliq) gaya, unhon-ne farmaya ke ham maqam siffiin mein padao daley huey they (jahaan Ali aur Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki jang hui thi) aik shakhs ne kaha ke aap ka kya khayal hai agar koi shakhs kitabullah ki taraf suleh ke liye bulaaey? Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya theek hai. lekin khawaarij ne Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke khilaf Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath they iske khilaf awaz uthaaii. is par Sahal-bin-Haneef ne farmaya tum pahley apna jaaiza lo. ham log Hudaibiya ke mauqe par maujood they aap ki murad us suleh se thi jo maqam Hudaibiya main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur mushrekeen ke darmyan hui thi aur jang ka mauqa aata to ham us se peechhey hatney waley nahi they. (lekin suleh ki baat chali to ham ne usmein bhi sabr w sabaat ka daman hath se nahi chhoda ( itney mein umr (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya kya ham haq par nahi hain? aur kya kuffaar baatil par nahi hain? kya hamarey maqtooleen jannat mein nahi jaeinge aur kya unke maqtooleen dozakh mein nahi jaaeinge? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kyon nahi ! umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha phir ham apne Deen ke barey mein zillat ka muzaahira kyon karein (yani dab kar suleh kyon karein (aur kyon wapas jayen, jabke Allah Taala ne hamein iska hukm farmaya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey ibne- khattaab! main Allah ka rasool hun aur Allah Taala mujhey kabhi zaaye nahi karega. umr (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas se wapas aagey unko ghussa aa raha tha, sabr nahi aaya aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur kaha, aey abu-Bakar! kya ham haq par aur wo baatil par nahi hain? Abu-Bakar ne bhi wahi jawab diya ke aey ibne-khattaab! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke rasool hain aur Allah unhein hargiz zaaye nahi karega . phir sura fateh nazil hui."
4845,qareeb tha ke wo sabse behtar afraad tabah ho jayen yani Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) un donon hazraat ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney apni awaz buland kar di thi. ye us waqt ka waqia hai jab bani Tameem ke sawar aaey they (aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se unhon-ne darkhaast ki ke hamara koi ameer bana dein) unmein se aik (Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne majaashea' ke Aqra-bin-Habis ke intikhab ke liye kaha tha aur doosrey (abu-Bakar (rz)) ne aik doosrey ka naam pesh kya tha. Naafe ne kaha ke unka naam mujhey yad nahi. is par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke aap ka irada mujh se ikhtilaf karna hi hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mera irada aap se ikhtilaf karna nahi hai. is par un donon ki awaz buland ho gaee. phir Allah Taala ne ye aayat utaarii ( ya أيها الذين آمنوا la ترفعوا أصواتكم‏ ) ''aey eman waalo! apni awaz ko Nabi ki awaz se buland na kya karo''. Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke us aayat ke nazil honey ke baad umr (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney itni ahista-ahista baat kartey ke aap saaf sun bhi na saktey they aur dobara poochhna padta tha. unhon-ne apne naanaa yani Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke mutaalliq is silsiley mein koi cheez bayan nahi ki.
4846,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Saabit-bin-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ko nahi paya. aik sahabi ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! main aap ke liye unki khabar laataa hun. phir wo Saabit-bin-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan aaey dekha ke wo ghar mein sar jhukaaey baithey hain puchha kya haal hai? kaha ke bura haal hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki awaz ke muqaabla mein buland awaz se bola karta tha ab sarey nek amal akaarat huey aur ahale-dozakh mein qarar de diya gaya hun. wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur unhon-ne jo kuchh kaha tha uski itlaa aapko di. Musa bin Anas ne bayan kya ke wo shakhs ab dobara unke liye aik azeem bashaarat lekar unke paas aaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke unke paas jao aur kaho ke tum ahale-dozakh mein se nahi ho balke tum ahle-jannat mein se ho.
4847,qabila bani Tameem ke sawaaron ka wafad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke unka ameer aap Qaaqaa bin Mabad ko bana dein aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha balke Aqra-bin-Habis ko ameer banaaein Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par kaha ke maqsad to sirf meri mukhalifat hi karna hai. umr ne kaha ke maine aap ke khilaf karne ki gharaz se ye nahi kaha hai. is par donon mein bahas chali aur awaz bhi buland ho gaee. isi ke mutaalliq ye aayat nazil huii يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تقدموا بين يدى الله ورسوله‏ke ''aey eman waalo! tum Allah aur uske rasool se pahley kisi kaam mein jaldi mat kya karo.'' aakhir aayat tak.
4848,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jahannam mein dozkhiyon ko daala jaeyga aur wo kahegii (هل من مزيد) ke kuchh aur bhi hai? yahan tak ke Allah rabbul-izzat apna qadam is par rakhega aur wo kahegii ke bas-bas.
4849,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hawale se Abu-Sufiyan Himyari aksar us hadis ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mauqoofan zikr kartey they ke jahannam se puchha jaeyga to bhar bhi gaii? wo kahegii (هل من مزيد) ke kuchh aur bhi hai? phir Allah tabarak taala apna qadam is par rakhega aur kahegii ke bas bas.
4850,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jannat aur dozakh ne bahas ki, dozakh ne kaha, main mutakabbiron aur zaalimon ke liye khas ki gaee hun. jannat ne kaha mujhey kya hua ke mere andar sirf kamzor aur kam rutbe waley log dakhil hongey. Allah Taala ne is par jannat se kaha ke to meri rehmat hai, terey zariey main apne bandon mein jis par chaahoon raham karun aur dozakh se kaha ke to azab hai terey zariey main apne bandon mein se jisey chaahoon azab dun. jannat aur dozakh donon bharengii. dozakh to us waqt tak nahi bharegii jab tak Allah rabbul-izzat apna qadam is par rakh dega. us waqt wo bolegii ke bas bas bas! aur us waqt bhar jaeygi aur iska kuchh hissey kuchh doosrey hissey par chadh jaeyga aur Allah Taala apne bandon mein kisi par zulm nahi karega aur jannat ke liye Allah Taala aik makhlooq paida karega وسبح بحمد ربك قبل طلوع الشمس وقبل الغروب ''aur apne rab ki hamd w tasbeeh kartey rahiye, suraj ke nikalney se pahley aur uske chhipney se pahley.''"
4851,ham aik raat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath baithey huey they chaudahween raat thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chaand ki taraf dekha aur phir farmaya ke yaqinan tum apne rab ko isi tarah dekhogey jis tarah is chaand ko dekh rahe ho. iske dekhney main tum dhakkam-peil nahi karogey ( balke badey itminan se aik doosrey ko dhakka diye baghair dekhogey) isliye agar tumharey liye mumkin ho to suraj nikalney aur doobney se pahley Namaz na chhodo. phir aap ne aayat وسبح بحمد ربك قبل طلوع الشمس وقبل الغروب''aur apne rab ki hamd w tasbeeh kartey rahiye suraj nikalney se pahley aur chhipney se pahley.'' ki tilawat ki.
4852,Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein tamam namazon ke baad tasbeeh padhney ka hukm diya tha. aap ka maqsad Allah Taala ka irshad ( وأدبار السجود‏ ( ki tashreeh karna tha.
4853,( Haj ke mauqe par) maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke main bimar hun Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir sawari par baith kar logon ke peechhey se tawaaf karey chunanche maine tawaaf kya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt khaana Kaba ke pahlu mein Namaz padhtey huey sura taur ki tilawat kar rahe they.
4854,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maghrib ki Namaz mein sura taur padh rahe they. jab aap sura taur ki is aayat par pahunchey أم خلقوا من غير شىء أم هم الخالقون * أم خلقوا السموات والأرض بل لا يوقنون * أم عندهم خزائن ربك أم هم المسيطرون‏ ''kya ye log baghair kisi ke paida kiye paida ho gaey ya ye khud (apne ( khaaliq hain? ya unhon-ne aasman aur zameen ko paida kar liya hai. asl ye hai ke unmein yaqin hi nahi. kya un logon ke paas aap ke parwardigar ke khazaaney hain ya ye log Hakim hain.'' to mera dil udney laga. Sufiyan ne bayan kya lekin maine Zohri se suna hai wo Muhammad-bin-Jubair-bin-Mut'im se riwayat kartey they, unse unke walid ( Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu)) ne bayan kya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko maghrib mein sura taur padhtey suna (Sufiyaan ne kaha ke) mere sathiyon ne iske baad jo izafa kya hai wo maine Zohri se nahi suna."
4855,maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha : aey eman walon ki maan! kya Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne meraaj ki raat main apne rab ko dekha tha? Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha tum ne aisi baat kahi ke mere raungtey khadey ho gaey. kya tum un teen baton se bhi na-waqif ho? jo shakhs bhi tum mein se ye teen baatein bayan karey wo jhoota hai jo shakhs ye kehta ho ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne meraaj ki raat main apne rab ko dekha tha wo jhoota hai. phir unhon-ne aayat لا تدركه الأبصار وهو يدرك الأبصار وهو اللطيف الخبير se lekar ( من وراء حجاب‏ ( tak ki tilawat ki aur kaha ke kisi insan ke liye mumkin nahi ke Allah se baat karey siwa iske ke wahi ke zariey ho ya phir pardey ke peechhey se ho aur jo shakhs tum se kahey ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aaney waley kal ki baat jantey they wo bhi jhoota hai. uske liye unhon-ne aayat وما تدري نفس ماذا تكسب غدا‏yaanii ''aur koi shakhs nahi janta ke kal kya karega.'' ki tilawat farmai aur jo shakhs tum mein se kahey ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tableeghe-deen mein koi baat chhipaaii thi wo bhi jhoota hai. phir unhon-ne ye aayat tilawat ki ( ya أيها الرسول بلغ ما أنزل إليك من ربك‏ ) yaanii aey rasool! pahuncha dijiye wo sab kuchh jo aap ke rab ki taraf se aap par utara gaya hai. haan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ko unki asl sura mein 2 martaba dekha tha.
4856,maine zar bin Habish se suna aur unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se aayat فكان قاب قوسين أو أدنى * فأوحى إلى عبده ما أوحى yaanii '' sirf 2 kamaanon ka fasla reh gaya tha balke aur bhi kam. phir Allah ne apne bande par wahi nazil ki jo kuchh bhi nazil kya'' ke mutaalliq bayan kya ke ham se Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ko unki asl sura mein dekha tha unke chh so par they.
4857,maine zar bin Habish se us aayat ke barey mein poochhaa فكان قاب قوسين أو أدنى * فأوحى إلى عبده ما أوحى yaanii 2 kamaanon ka fasla reh gaya balke aur bhi kam. phir Allah ne apne bandey par wahi ki jo kuchh bhi nazil kya to unhon-ne bayan kya ke hamein Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ko dekha tha jinke chh so par they.
4858,aayat ( لقد رأى من آيات ربه الكبرى‏ ( yani '' aap ne apne rab ki azeem nishaniyan dekhein'' ke mutaalliq batlaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( رفرف ( ) sabz farsh ( ko dekha jisne aasman ke kinaron ko dhanp liya tha.
4859,ham se abul-Jauzaa ne bayan kya aur unse Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne laat aur uzzaa ke haal mein kaha ke laat aik shakhs ko kehtey they wo haajiyon ke liye sattu gholtaa tha.
4860,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs qism khaaey aur kahey ke qism hai laat aur uzzaa ki to usey eman ko taazaa karney ke liye kehna chahiye ( لا إله إلا الله (aur jo shakhs apne sathi se ye kahey ke aao juwa khelein to usey sadqa dena chahiye
4861,"maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke kuchh log manaat but ke naam par ehram baandhtey jo maqam Mushallal mein tha, wo Safa aur Marwa ke darmyan (Haj w Umre mein) saee nahi kartey they is par Allah Taala ne aayat nazil ki (إن الصفا والمروة من شعائر الله‏) ''beshak Safa aur Marwa Allah ki nishaniyon mein se hain'' chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke darmyan tawaaf kya aur musalmanon ne bhi tawaaf kya. Sufiyan ne kaha ke '' مناۃ '' maqam qudaid par Mushallal mein tha aur Abdur-Rehman bin Khalid ne bayan kya ke unse ibne-Shahab ne, unse Urwa ne bayan kya aur unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke ye aayat Ansar ke barey mein nazil hui thi. Islam se pahley Ansar aur ghassaan ke log manaat ke naam par ehram baandhtey they, pehli hadis ki tarah aur Mamar ne Zohri se bayan kya, unse Urwa ne, unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne ke qabila Ansar ke kuchh log manaat ke naam ka ehram baandhtey they. manaat aik but tha jo Makka aur Madina ke darmyan rakha hua tha (Islam laney ke baad) un logon ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah! ham manaat ki ta'zeem ke liye Safa aur Marwa ke darmyan saee nahi kya kartey they."
4862,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sura Najm mein sajda kya aur aap ke sath musalmanon ne aur tamam mushrikon aur jinnon aur insanon ne bhi sajda kya. Abdul-Waris ke sath us hadis ko Ibrahim bin tahmaan ne bhi Ayub se riwayat kya aur Ismaaeel-bin-Ulaih ne apni riwayat mein Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr nahi kya.
4863,"sabse pahley nazil honey wali sajde wali sura sura Najm hai. bayan kya ke phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (uskii tilawat ke baad) sajda kya aur jitney log aap ke peechhey they sab hi ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sajda kya, siwa aik shakhs ke, maine dekha ke usne apni hatheli mein mitti uthai aur usi par sajda kar liya. baad main (badr ki ladai mein) maine usey dekha ke kufr ki haalat mein wo qatl kya hua padaa hai. wo shakhs Umayya-bin-Khalaf tha."
4864,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein chaand 2 tukdey ho gaya tha aik tukda pahaad ke uper aur doosra uske peechhey chala gaya tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usi mauqe par ham se farmaya tha ke gawah rehna.
4865,"chaand phat gaya tha aur us waqt ham bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they. chunanche iske 2 tukdey ho gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se farmaya ke logo gawah rehna, gawah rehna."
4866,Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein chaand phat gaya tha.
4867,Makka walon ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se moa'jza dikhaaney ko kaha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein chaand ke phat janey ka moa'jza dikhaya .
4868,chaand 2 tukdon mein phat gaya tha.
4869,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( فهل من مدكر ( padha kartey they.
4870,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( فهل من مدكر ( ) so hai koi nasihat hasil karne wala ? ( padha kartey they.
4871,unhon-ne aik shakhs ko Aswad se poochhtey suna ke sura Qamar mein aayat ( فهل من مدكر ( hai ya (فهل من مذكر) ? unhon-ne kaha ke maine ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo ( فهل من مدكر ( padhtey they. unhon-ne kaha ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bhi) فهل من مدكر ( padhtey suna hai) daal mohmila se) .
4872,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( فهل من مدكر ( (daal mohmila se) .
4873,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( فهل من مدكر ( (daal mohmila se) padha tha.
4874,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney ( فهل من مذكر ( padha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) فهل من مدكر ( (yani daal mohmila se padho ( .
4875,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jabke aap badr ki ladai ke din aik khemey mein they aur ye dua kar rahe they ke aey Allaah! mein tujhey tera ahad aur wada nusrat yad dilata hun. aey Allaah! teri marzii hai agar to chahey (un thodey se musalmanon ko bhi halaak kar de) phir aaj ke baad teri ibadat baqi nahi rahegii. phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka hath pakad liya aur arz kya : bas ya Rasulullah ! aap ne apne rab se bahut hi al-haajj w zaarii se dua kar li hai. us waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zirah pahney huey chal phir rahe they aur aap kheme se nikley to zaban Mubarak par ye aayat thi ( سيهزم الجمع ويولون الدبر‏ ( '' so an-qareeb ( kaafiron ki) jamat shikast khaaegii aur ye sab peeth pher kar bhaagengey.''
4876,mein Ummul-Momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir tha. aap ne farmaya ke jis waqt aayat بل الساعة موعدهم والساعة أدهى وأمر''lekin unka asl wada to qiyamat ke din ka hai aur qiyamat badi sakht aur talkh cheez hai'' Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par Makka mein nazil hui to main bachchii thi aur khelaa karti thi.
4877,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jabke aap badr ki ladai ke mauqe par maidan mein aik khemey mein ye dua kar rahe they ke ''aey Allaah! mein tujhey tera ahad aur wa'dae-Nusrat yad dilata hun. aey Allaah! agar to chahey ke (musalmanon ko fana kar de) to aaj ke baad phir kabhi teri ibadat nahi ki jaaeygii.'' aur is par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka hath pakad kar arz kya : bas ya Rasulullah! aap apne rab se khub al-haajj w zaarii ke sath dua kar chukey hain. Nabi Karim us waqt zirah pahney huey they. aap bahar tashrif laey to aap ki zaban Mubarak par ye aayat thii سيهزم الجمع ويولون الدبر * بل الساعة موعدهم والساعة أدهى وأمر yaanii ''an-qareeb kaafiron ki ye jamat haar jaeygi aur ye sab peeth pher kar bhaagengey. lekin unka asl wada to qiyamat ke din ka hai aur qiyamat badi sakht aur bahut hi kadwii cheez hai.''
4878,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke (jannat mein) 2 baagh hongey jinke bartan aur tamam dusri cheezein chandi ki hongi aur 2 doosrey baagh hongey jinke bartan aur tamam dusri cheezein soney ke hongey aur jannate-adn se jannatiyon ke apne rab ke deedaar mein koi cheez siwaey badai ki chadar ke jo iske munh par hogi, haail na hogi."
4879,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jannat mein khokhley motii ka khema hoga, uski chaudai sath miil hogi aur uske har kinarey par musalman ki aik biwi hogi aik kinarey wali doosrey kinarey wali ko na dekh sakegi."
4880,aur momin unke paas baari-baari jaeinge aur 2 baagh hongey jinke bartan aur tamam dusri cheezein chandi ki hongi aur aisey bhi 2 baagh hongey jabke bartan aur tamam dusri cheezein soney ki hongii. jannate-adn walon ko Allah paak ke deedaar mein sirf aik jalaal ki chadar haail hogi jo iske ( Mubarak ( munh par padi hogi.
4881,unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jannat mein aik darakht lamba hoga (itnaa bada ke) sawar uske saaye mein 100 saal tak chalega aur phir bhi uska saaya khatm na hoga agar tumhara ji chahey to is aayat (وظل ممدود‏) ki qirat kar lo.
4882,maine Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se sura Tauba ke mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne kaha ye sura Tauba ki hai ya fazeehat karne wali hai is sura mein barabar yahi utartaa raha kuchh log aisey hain aur kuchh log aisey hain yahan tak ke logon ko guman hua ye sura kisi ka kuchh bhi nahi chhodegii balke sab ke bhed khol degi. bayan kya ke maine sura al-Anfaal ke mutaalliq puchha to farmaya ke ye jange-badr ke barey mein nazil hui thi. bayan kya ke maine sura Hashr ke mutaalliq puchha to farmaya ke qabila banu-nazeer ke yahood ke barey mein nazil hui thi.
4883,maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se sura Hashr ke mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne kaha balke usey sura Nazeer kahaa
4884,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banu- nazeer ke khajooron ke darakht jalaa diye they aur unhein kaat daala tha. ye darakht maqam buwera mein they phir iske mutaalliq Allah Taala ne aayat nazil ki (ما قطعتم من لينة أو تركتموها قائمة على أصولها فبإذن الله وليخزي الفاسقين) ke ''jo khajooron ke darakht tum ne kaatey ya unhein unki jadon par qaaim rehney diya so ye donon Allah hi ke hukm ke muwafiq hain aur taake naafarmaanon ko zaleel kare.''
4885,banii-Nazeer ke amwaal ko Allah Taala ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko baghair ladai ke diya tha. musalmanon ne uske liye ghodey aur oont nahi daudaaey. un amwaal ka kharch karna khas taur se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath mein tha. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usmein se paak beeviyon ka saalaana kharch detey they aur jo baqi bachta tha us se saamaane-jang aur ghodon ke liye kharch kartey they taake Allah rabbul-izzat ke raaste mein jihad ke mauqe par kaam aaein.
4886,"Allah Taala ne godwaaney waaliyon aur godney waaliyon par laanat bheji hai chehrey ke baal ukhaadney waaliyon aur Husn ke liye aagey ke daanton mein kushadgi karne waaliyon par laanat bheji hai ke ye Allah ki paida ki hui sura mein tabdili karti hain. Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ka ye kalam qabila bani Asad ki aik aurat ko malum hua jo umme-ya'qoob ke naam se Maruf thi wo aai aur kaha ke mujhey malum hua hai ke aap ne is tarah ki aurton par laanat bheji hai? Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha aakhir kyon na main unhein laanat karun jinhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne laanat ki hai aur jo kitabullah ke hukm ke mutabiq maloon hai. us aurat ne kaha ke Quran Majeed to maine bhi padha hai lekin aap jo kuchh kehtey hain maine to usmein kahin ye baat nahi dekhi . unhon-ne kaha ke agar tum ne b-ghaur padha hota to tumhen zaroor mil jata kya tum ne ye aayat nahi padhi ( وما آتاكم الرسول فخذوه وما نهاكم عنه فانتهوا‏ (ke '' rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tumhen jo kuchh dein ley liya karo aur jis se tumhen rok dein, ruk jaya karo. usne kaha ke padhi hai Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un chizon se rokaa hai. is par aurat ne kaha ke mera khayal hai ke aap ki biwi bhi aisa karti hain. unhon-ne kaha ke achchha jao aur dekh lo. wo aurat gaee aur us ne dekha lekin is tarah ki unke yahan koi ma'yoob cheez usey nahi milii. phir Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke agar meri biwi isi tarah karti to bhala wo mere sath reh sakti thi? hargiz nahi."
4887,maine Abdur-Rehman bin Aabis se Mansoor bin Motamir ki hadis ka zikr kya jo wo Ibrahim se bayan kartey they ke unse Alqama ne aur unse Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sar ke qudrati baalon ke sath masnooii baal lagaaney waaliyon par laanat bheji thi. Abdur-Rehman bin Aabis ne kaha ke maine bhi umme-ya'qoob naam ke aik aurat se suna tha wo Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) Mansoor ki hadis ke misl bayan karti thi.
4888,umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( zakhmi honey ke baad intiqal se pahley) farmaya tha main apne baad hone-waale khaleefa ko muhajireen awwaleen ke barey mein wasiiyat karta hun ke wo unka haq pahchaaney aur main apne baad hone-waale khaleefa ko Ansar ke barey mein wasiiyat karta hun jo daarus-Salaam aur eman main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hijrat se pahley hi se qarar pakdey huey hain ye ke unmein jo neku-kaar hain unki izzat karey aur unke ghalat kaaron se darguzar kare.
4889,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik sahib khud (abu-Huraira (rz)) hazir huey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah! main faaqe se hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein paak beeviyon ke paas bheja (ke wo aap ki dawat karein) lekin unke paas koi cheez khaney ki nahi thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya koi shakhs aisa nahi jo aaj raat is mehman ki mezbaanii karey? Allah is par raham karega. is par aik Ansari sahabi ( abu-Talha ( khadey huey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ye aaj mere mehman hain phir wo unhein apne sath ghar le gaey aur apni biwi se kaha ke ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke mehman hain, koi cheez unse bacha ke na rakhna. biwi ne kaha Allah ki qism mere paas is waqt bachchon ke khaney ke siwa aur koi cheez nahi hai. Ansari sahabi ne kaha agar bachchey khana maangein to unhein sulaa do aur aao ye charagh bhi bujhaa do, aaj raat ham bhookey hi reh lengey. biwi ne aisa hi kya. phir wo Ansari sahabi subah ke waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ne falan ( Ansari sahabi (aur unki biwi (ke amal ( ko pasand farmaya, ya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya ke) Allah Taala muskuraayaa phir Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki (ويؤثرون على أنفسهم ولو كان بهم خصاصة‏) yaanii aur apne se muqaddam rakhtey hain agarche khud faaqe mein hi hon."
4890,"maine Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se suna unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey, Zuber aur Miqdad (Raziallahu anhu) ko rawaana kya aur farmaya ke chaley jao aur jab maqam khaakh ke baagh par pahunch jaogey (jo Makka aur Madina ke darmyan tha) to wahan tumhen hodaj mein aik aurat milegii, uske sath aik khat hoga, wo khat tum us se ley lenaa. chunanche ham rawaana huey hamarey ghodey hamein tez raftaarii ke sath ley ja rahe they. aakhir jab ham us baagh par pahunchey to waqei wahan ham ne hodaj mein us aurat ko pa liya ham ne us se kaha ke khat nikaal. usne kaha mere paas koi khat nahi hai hamne usse kaha ke khat nikal de warna ham tera Sara kapda utaar kar talashi lengey. aakhir us ne apni choti se khat nikala ham log wo khat lekar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. us khat mein likha hua tha ke Haatib bin abi Balta' ki taraf se mushrekeen ke chand aadmiyon ki taraf jo Makka mein they us khat mein unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taiyaarii ka zikr likha tha (ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik badi fauj lekar aatey hain tum apna bachao kar lo). Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya : Haatib! ye kya hai? unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! mere maamle mein jaldi na farmaein mein Quraish ke sath bataur haleef (zamaanae-qiyaame-Makka mein) raha karta tha lekin unke qabeele w khandan se mera koi talluq nahi tha. iske bar-khilaf aap ke sath jo doosrey muhajireen hain unki Quraish mein rishte daariyaan hain aur unki riaayat se Quraish Makka mein reh janey waley unke ahal w ayaal aur maal ki hifazat kartey hain. maine chaha ke jabke unse mera koi nasbi (rishtey ka ( talluq nahi hai to us mauqe par un par aik ehsan kar dun aur uski wjah se wo mere rishte-daaron ki Makka mein hifazat karein. ya Rasulullah ! maine ye amal kufr ya apne Deen se phir janey ki wjah se nahi kya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke yaqinan unhon-ne tum se sachchii baat keh di hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) boley ke ya Rasulullah ! mujhey ijazat dein mein uski gardan mar dun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye badr ki jang mein hamarey sath maujood they. tumhen kya malum , Allah Taala badr walon ke tamam halaat se waaqif tha aur uske bawajud unke mutaalliq farma diya ke jo ji chahey karo ke maine tumhen maaf kar diya. Amr-bin-Dinar ne kaha ke Haatib-bin-abii Balta' (Raziallahu anhu) hi ke barey mein ye aayat nazil hui thii (يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تتخذوا عدوي وعدوكم‏) ke. ''aey eman waalo! tum mere dushman aur apne dushman ko dost na bana lenaa.'' Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne kaha ke mujhey iska ilm nahi ke us aayat ka zikr hadis mein dakhil hai ya nahi ye Amr-bin-Dinar ka qaul hai. ham se Ali-bin-Abdullaah madeenii ne bayan kya ke Sufiyan-bin-Uena se Haatib bin abi Balta' (Raziallahu anhu) ke barey mein puchha gaya ke kya aayat لا تتخذوا عدوي‏ unhein ke barey mein nazil hui thi? Sufiyan ne kaha ke logon ki riwayat main to yoonhii hai lekin maine Amr se hadis yad ki usmein se aik harf bhi maine nahi chhoda aur main nahi samajhta ke mere siwa aur kisi ne us hadis ko Amr se khub yad rakha ho."
4891,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us aayat ke nazil honey ke baad un momin aurton ka imtihaan liya kartey they jo hijrat karke Madina aati thin. Allah Taala ne irshad farmaya thaa ( ya أيها النبي إذا جاءك المؤمنات يبايعنك‏ ) ke ''aey nabii! jab aap se musalman auratein bait karne ke liye aaein'' irshad ( ghafoor رحيم‏ ( tak. Urwa ne bayan kya ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha chunanche jo aurat is shart (aayat mein mazkoor yani eman wghaira) ka iqrar kar leti Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us se zabani taur par farmatey ke maine tumhari bait qabool kar li aur hargiz nahi, Allah ki qasam! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath ne kisi aurat ka hath bait letey waqt kabhi nahi chhuwa sirf aap unse zabani bait letey they ke aayat mein mazkura (uper zikr) baton par qaaim rehna. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Younus, Mamar aur Abdur-Rehman bin Ishaq ne Zohri se ki aur Ishaq bin Rashid ne Zohri se bayan kya ke unse Urwa aur Umra binte-Abdur-Rehman ne kahaa."
4892,"ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki to aap ne hamarey samney is aayat ki tilawat ki (أن لا يشركن بالله شيئا‏) ke Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik na karengii aur hamein nauha (yani maiyat par zor-zor se ronaa peetnaa) karne se mana farmaya, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki is manaahii par aik aurat (khud umme-Atiya (rz)) ne apna hath kheench liya aur arz kya ke falan aurat ne nauha mein meri madad ki thi, main chahti hun ke iska badla chuka aaoon Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iska koi jawab nahi diya chunanche wo gain aur phir dobara aa kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki."
4893,"maine Zuber se suna, unhon-ne Ikrima se aur unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se Allah Taala ke irshaad (ولا يعصينك في معروف) yaanii ''aur bhalii baton (aur achchhey kaamon mein) aap ki nafarmani na karengii.'' ke barey mein unhon-ne kaha ke ye bhi aik shart thi jisey Allah Taala ne (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ke waqt) aurton ke liye zaroori qarar diya tha."
4894,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya tum mujh se is baat par bait karogey ke Allah Taala ke sath kisi ko Sharik na thahraaogey aur na zina karogey aur na chori karogey.'' Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sura Nisa ki aayatein padhin. Sufiyan ne is hadis mein aksar yun kaha ke aap ne ye aayat padhi. phir tum mein se jo shakhs is shart ko pura karega to uska ajr Allah par hai aur jo koi unmein se kisi shart ki khilaf warzi kar betha aur is par usey saza bhi mil gaee to saza uske liye kaffara bin jaeygi lekin kisi ne apne kisi ahad ke khilaf kya aur Allah ne usey chipa liya to wo Allah ke hawale hai Allah chahey to usey is par azab de aur agar chahey maaf kar de, Sufiyan ke sath is hadis ko Abdur-Razzaq ne bhi Mamar se riwayat kya unhon-ne Zohri se aur yun hi kaha aayat padhi."
4895,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar aur umr aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath eidul-fitr ki Namaz padhi hai. un tamam buzurgon ne Namaz khutbe se pahley padhi thi aur khutba baad mein diya tha (eik martaba khutbe se farigh honey ke baad) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) utrey maano ab bhi main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh raha hun, jab aap logon ko apne hath ke ishaarey se bitha rahe they phir aap saf cheertey huey aagey badhey aur aurton ke paas tashrif laey. Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke sath they phir aap ne ye aayat tilawat ki (يا أيها النبي إذا جاءك المؤمنات يبايعنك على أن لا يشركن بالله شيئا wla يسرقن wla يزنين wla يقتلن أولادهن wla يأتين ببهتان يفترينه بين أيديهن وأرجلهن‏) yaanii ''aey nabii! jab momin auratein aap ke paas aaein ke aap se un baton par bait karein ke Allah ke sath na kisi ko Sharik karengii aur na chori karengii aur na badkaarii karengii aur na apne bachchon ko qatl karengii aur na bohtan lagaaengii jisey apne hath aur paon ke darmyan ghad lein '' aap ne poori aayat aakhir tak padhi. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aayat padh chukey to farmaya tum un sharaait par qaaim rehney ka wada karti ho? unmein se aik aurat ne jawab diya ji haan ya Rasulullah ! unke siwa aur kisi aurat ne ( sharm ki wjah se) koi baat nahi kahi . Hasan ko us aurat ka naam malum nahi tha bayan kya ke phir aurton ne sadqa dena shuru kya aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna kapda phaila liya. auratein Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke kapdey mein chhalley aur anguthiyan dalney lagiin."
4896,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke mere kai naam hain. main Muhammad hun, main Ahmed hun, main maahii hun ke jiske zariey Allah Taala kufr ko mitaa dega aur main haashir hun ke Allah Taala sab ko hashr mein mere baad jama karega aur main aaqib hun. yani sab paighambaron ke baad duniya mein aaney wala hun."
4897,ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas baithey huey they ke sura Juma ki ye aayatein nazil huin ( وآخرين منهم لما يلحقوا بهم‏ (aur dusron ke liye bhi jo abhi unmein shamil nahi huey hain. (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) haadii aur muallim hain) bayan kya maine kaha ya Rasulullah! ye doosrey kon log hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne koi jawab nahi diya. aakhir yahi sawal teen martaba kya. majlis mein Salman Farsi (Raziallahu anhu) bhi maujood they Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un par hath rakh kar farmaya agar eman surayyaa par bhi hoga tab bhi un logon (yani Faaris walon ( mein se us tak pahunch jaeinge ya yun farmaya ke aik aadmi un logon mein se us tak pahunch jaeyga
4898,unki qaum ke kuchh log usey pa lengey.
4899,Juma ke din saamaane-tijaarat liye huey oont aaey ham us waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they unhein dekh kar siwaey baara aadmi ke sab log udhar hi daud padey. is par Allah tabarak w taala ne ye aayat nazil ki ( وإذا رأوا تجارة أو لهوا انفضوا إليها‏ ) yaanii aur kuchh logon ne jab kabhi aik saudey ya tamashey ki cheez ko dekha to uski taraf daudey huey phail gaey.
4900,mein aik jang ( jange-Tabook ( mein tha aur maine ( munaafiqon ke sardaar ( Abdullah-bin-Ubai ko ye kehtey suna ke jo log ( muhajireen ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jama hain un par kharch na karo taake wo khud hi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se juda ho jaengey. us ne ye bhi kaha ab agar ham Madina lot kar jaeinge to izzat wala wahan se zillat walon ko nikal bahar karega. maine iska zikr apne chacha ( Sad-bin-Ubada Ansari ( se kya ya umr (Raziallahu anhu) se iska zikr kya. ( rawi ko shak tha) unhon-ne iska zikr Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey bulaya. maine tamam baatein aapko suna din. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abdullah-bin-Ubai aur uske sathiyon ko bula bhejaa. unhon-ne qism kha li kaha ke unhon-ne is tarah ki koi baat nahi kahi thi. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh ko jhoota samjha aur Abdullah ko sachcha samjhaa. mujhey iska itna sadma hua ke aisa kabhi na hua tha. phir main ghar mein baith raha. mere chacha ne kaha ke mera khayal nahi tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tumhari takzeeb karengey aur tum par naraz hongey. phir Allah Taala ne ye sura nazil ki) إذا جاءك المنافقون‏ ( ''jab munafiq aap ke paas aatey hain ''iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey bulwaya aur is sura ki tilawat ki aur farmaya ke aey Zaid ! Allah Taala ne tum ko sachcha kar diya hai.
4901,main apne chacha (Sa'd-bin-Ubaada ya Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu)) ke sath tha maine Abdullah-bin-Ubai ibne-Salool ko kehtey suna ke jo log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hain un par kharch mat karo taake wo unke paas se bhag jaaein. ye bhi kaha ke agar ab ham Madina lot kar jaeinge to izzat wala wahan se zaleelon ko nikal kar bahar kar dega. maine uski ye baat chacha se aa kar kahi aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska zikr kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abdullah-bin-Ubai aur uske sathiyon ko bulwaya unhon-ne qism kha li ke aisi koi baat unhon-ne nahi kahi thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi unko sachcha jana aur mujh ko jhoota samjha . mujhey itna sadma pahuncha ke aisa kabhi nahi pahuncha hoga phir main ghar ke andar baith gaya. phir Allah Taala ne ye sura nazil ki ( إذا جاءك المنافقون‏ ( se (هم الذين يقولون لا تنفقوا على من عند رسول الله) aur aayat ( ليخرجن الأعز منها الأذل‏ ( to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey bulwaya aur mere samney is sura ki tilawat ki phir farmaya ke Allah ne tumharey bayan ko sachcha kar diya hai.
4902,"jab Abdullah-bin-Ubai ibne-Salool ne kaha ke jo log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hain un par kharch na karo ye bhi kaha ke ab agar ham Madina wapas gaey to ham se izzat wala daleelon ko nikal bahar karega to maine ye khabar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchaaii. is par kuffaar ne mujhey malaamat ki aur Abdullah-bin-Ubai ne qism kha li ke usne ye baat nahi kahi thi phir main ghar wapas aa gaya aur so gaya. iske baad mujhey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey talab farmaya aur main hazir hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ne tumhari tasdeeq mein aayat nazil kar di hai aur ye aayat utri hai هم الذين يقولون لا تنفقوا aakhir tak aur ibne-abi-Zayda ne Aamash se bayan kya, unse Amr ne, unse ibn-abii-Lailaa ne aur unse Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah naql kya."
4903,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar ( jange-Tabook ya bani mustaliq ( mein they jis mein logon par badey tang oqaat aaey they. Abdullah-bin-Ubai ne apne sathiyon se kaha ke jo log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jama hain un par kuchh kharch mat karo taake wo unke paas se muntashir ho jaengey. us ne ye bhi kaha ke agar ham ab Madina lot kar jaeinge to izzat wala wahan se zaleelon ko nikal bahar karega. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar unki is guftgu ki itlaa di to aap ne Abdullah-bin-Ubai ibne-Salool ko bula kar poochha. us ne badi qasmein kha kar kaha ke maine aisi koi baat nahi kahi . logon ne kaha ke Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney jhoot bola hai. logon ki is tarah ki baton se main bada ranjeeda hua yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne meri tasdeeq farmai aur ye aayat nazil hui ( إذا جاءك المنافقون‏ ( yani jab aap ke paas munafiq aaey phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein bulaya taake unke liye maghfirat ki dua karein lekin unhon-ne apne sar pher liye. Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Allah Taala ke irshad ""maano wo bahut badey lakdi ke khambey hain"" (unke mutaalliq isliye kaha gaya ke) wo badey khoobsurat aur deel-dol waaley they, magar dil se munafiq they."
4904,"maine apne chacha ke sath tha maine Abdullah-bin-Ubai ibne-Salool ko kehtey suna ke jo log rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hain un par kuchh kharch na karo taake wo muntashir ho jayen aur agar ab ham Madina wapas lautengey to ham mein se jo izzat waley hain un zaleelon ko nikal bahar kar dengey. maine iska zikr apne chacha se kya aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un hi ki tasdeeq kar di to mujhey iska itna afsos hua ke pahley kabhi kisi baat par na hua hoga, main gham se apne ghar mein baith gaya. mere chacha ne kaha ke tumhara kya aisa khayal tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tumhen jhutlaayaa aur tum par khafa huey hain? phir Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki) إذا جاءك المنافقون قالوا نشهد إنك لرسول الله‏ ( '' jab munafiq aap ke paas aatey hain to kehtey hain ke aap beshak Allah ke rasool hain ''nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey bulwa kar is aayat ki tilawat farmai aur farmaya ke Allah Taala ne tumhari tasdeeq nazil kar di hai."
4905,"ham aik jang ( jange-Tabook ( mein they. Sufiyan ne aik martaba ( bajaey jang ke) jaish ( lashakr) ka lafz kaha, muhajireen mein se aik aadmi ne Ansar ke aik aadmi ko laat mar di. Ansari ne kaha ke aey ansaariyo ! daudo aur muhajir ne kaha aey muhajireen ! daudo . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi usey suna aur farmaya kya qissa hai? ye jahiliyat ki pukar kaisi hai? logon ne bataya ke ya Rasulullah ! aik muhajir ne aik Ansari ko laat se mar diya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is tarah jahiliyat ki pukar ko chhod do ke ye bahut hi napak baatein hain. Abdullah-bin-Ubai ne bhi ye baat suni to kaha achchha ab yahan tak naubat pahunch gaee. khuda ki qasam! jab ham Madina lautengey to ham se izzat wala zaleelon ko nikal kar bahar kar dega. uski khabar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko pahunch gaee. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne khadey ho kar arz kya : ya Rasulullah! mujhey ijazat dein ke main us munafiq ko khatm kar dun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey chhod do taake log ye na kahin ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne sathiyon ko qatl kara detey hain. jab muhajireen Madina Munawra mein aaey to Ansar ki tadaad se unki tadaad kam thi. lekin baad mein un muhajireen ki tadaad zyada ho gaee thi. Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke maine hadis Amr-bin-Dinar se yad ki, Amr ne bayan kya ke maine Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they."
4906,"mujh se Abdullah-bin Fazal ne bayan kya aur unhon-ne Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se unka bayan naql kya ke maqam Harra mein jo log Shahid kar diye gaey they un par mujhey bada ranj hua. Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) ko mere gham ki itlaa pahunchi to unhon-ne mujhey likha ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke aey Allah ! Ansar ki maghfirat farma aur unke beton ki bhi maghfirat farmaa. Abdullah-bin Fazal ko ismein shak tha ke aap ne Ansar ke beton ke beton ka bhi zikr kya tha ya nahi. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se unki majlis ke haaziriin mein se kisi ne sawal kya to unhon-ne kaha ke Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) hi wo hain jinke sunney ki Allah Taala ne tasdeeq ki thi."
4907,"maine Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo bayan kartey they ke ham aik jang mein they, achcha muhajireen ke aik aadmi ne Ansari ke aik aadmi ko mar diya. Ansar ne kaha : aey ansaariyo ! daudo aur muhajir ne kaha : aey muhajireen ! daudo. Allah Taala ne ye apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bhi sunaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya kya baat hai? logon ne bataya ke aik muhajir ne aik Ansari ko mar diya hai. is par Ansari ne kaha ke aey ansaariyo! daudo aur muhajir ne kaha ke aey muhaajireen! daudo. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is tarah pukaarnaa chhod do ke ye bahut hi napak baatein hain. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to shuru mein Ansar ki tadaad zyada thi lekin baad mein muhajireen zyada ho gaey they. Abdullah-bin-Ubai ne kaha achchha ab naubat yahan tak pahunch gaee hai. Allah ki qism ! Madina wapas ho kar izzat waley zaleelon ko bahar nikal dengey. umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ya Rasulullah! ijazat ho to is munafiq ki gardan uda dun. to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi warna log yun kahengey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne sathiyon ko qatl karaaney lagey hain."
4908,"unhon-ne apni biwi aamna binte-ghifaar ko jabke wo haaiza thin talaaq de di. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska zikr kya. aap is par bahut ghussa huey aur farmaya ke wo unse (apni biwi se) rujoo kar lein aur apne nikah mein rakhein yahan tak ke wo maahwaarii se paak ho jaey phir maahwaarii aaey aur phir wo us se paak ho, ab agar wo talaaq dena munasib samjhein to uski paakii ( tuhur (ke zamane mein unke sath ham-bistarii se pahley talaaq de saktey hain bas yahi wo waqt hai jis mein Allah Taala ne (mardon ko) hukm diya hai ke usmein yani haalate-tuhur mein talaaq dein."
4909,aik shakhs Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bhi unke paas baithey huey they. aaney waley ne puchha ke aap mujhey us aurat ke mutaalliq masla bataiye jisne apne shauhar ki wafat ke char mahiney baad bachcha janaa ? Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke jiska khawind faut ho wo iddat ki 2 muddaton mein jo muddat lambi ho uski riaayat kare. ( abu-Salma ne bayan kya ke) maine arz kya ke) Quran Majeed main to unki iddat ka ye hukm hai) hamal waaliyon ki iddat unke hamal ka paida ho jana hai. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main bhi is mas'ale main apne bhatijey ke sath hun. unki murad abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se thi aakhir Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne ghulam Kureb ko Ummul-Momenin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein bheja yahi masla poochhney ke liye. Ummul-Momenin ne bataya ke sabeeaa Aslamiya ke shauhar (Sa'd bin Khaula (Raziallahu anhu)) Shahid kar diye gaey they wo us waqt haamla thin shauhar ki maut ke chalis (40) din baad unke yahan bachcha paida hua phir unke paas nikah ka paigham pahuncha aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka nikah kar diya. abu-Sanaabil bhi unke paas paighaame-nikaah bhejney walon mein se they.
4910,"mein aik majlis mein jis mein Abdur-Rehman bin abi Leilaa bhi they maujood tha. unke shagird unki bahut izzat kya kartey they. maine wahan sabeeaa binte- al-Haaris ka Abdullah-bin Utba-bin- Masood se bayan kya ke is par unke shagird ne zaban aur aankhon ke ishaarey se hont kaat kar mujhey tanbeeh ki Muhammad-bin Sirin ne bayan kya ke main samajh gaya aur kaha ke Abdullah-bin Utba Kufa mein abhi zinda maujood hain. agar main unki taraf bhi jhoot jodtaa hun to badi jur'at ki baat hogi mujhey tanbeeh karne waley sahib is par sharminda ho gaey aur Abdur-Rehman bin abi Leilaa ne kaha lekin unke chacha to ye baat nahi kartey they. (ibne-Siiriin ne bayan kya ke) phir main abu-Atiiya Malik bin Aamir se mila aur unse ye masla puchha wo bhi sabeeaa wali hadis bayan karne lagey lekin maine unse kaha aap ne Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi is silsile mein kuchh suna hai? unhon-ne bayan kya ke ham Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir they, to unhon-ne kaha kya tum is par (jiske shauhar ka intiqal ho gaya aur wo haamla ho. iddat ki muddat ko lamba karkey) sakhti karna chahtey ho aur rukhsat w sahoolat dene ke liye taiyaar nahi, baat ye hai ke chhoti sura Nisa yani (sura talaaq) badi sura Nisa ke baad nazil hui hai aur kaha ( وأولات الأحمال أجلهن أن يضعن حملهن‏ (aur hamal waaliyon ki iddat unke hamal ka paida ho jana hai."
4911,"agar kisi ne apne uper koi halal cheez haram kar li to uska kaffara dena hoga. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ""beshak tumharey liye tumharey Rasulullah ki zindagi mein behtreen namoona hai.''"
4912,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar mein shehad peetey aur wahan thahartey they phir maine aur Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne aisey kya ke ham mein se jiske paas bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( Zenab ke yahan se shehad pi kar aaney ke baad) dakhil hon to wo kahey ke kya aap ne piyaz khaaii hai. aap ke munh se maghaafeer ki bo aati hai. chunanche jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to mansooba-bandii ke tehet yahi kaha gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) badboo ko bahut na-pasand farmatey they. isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine maghaafeer nahi khaaii hai albatta Zenab binte-Jahash ke yahan se shehad piyaa tha lekin ab usey bhi hargiz nahi piyunga. maine uski qism kha li hai lekin tum kisi se iska zikr na karna.
4913,"aik aayat ke mutaalliq umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se poochhney ke liye aik saal tak main tardeed mein raha, unka itna dar ghalib tha ke main unse na poochh saka. aakhir wo Haj ke liye gaey to main bhi unke sath ho liya, waapsii mein jab ham raaste mein they, to rafa haajat (peshab-pakhaney se farigh honey) ke liye wo peelu ke darakht mein gaey. bayan kya ke main unke intizar mein khada raha jab wo farigh ho kar aaey to phir main unke sath chala us waqt maine arz kya. ameerul-momineen! ummahaatul momeneen (nabi ki beeviyon) mein wo kon 2 auratein thin jinhoney Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye muttafiqa mansoobaa banaya tha? unhon-ne batlaya ke Hafsa aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) thin. bayan kya ke maine arz kya Allah ki qism mein ye sawal aap se karne ke liye aik saal se irada kar raha tha lekin aap ke raub ki wjah se poochhney ki himmat nahi hoti thi. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha aisa na kya karo jis masla ke mutaalliq tumhara khayal ho ke mere paas is silsiley mein koi ilm hai to usey poochh liya karo, agar mere paas uska koi ilm hoga to tumhen bata diya karunga . bayan kya ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! jahiliyat mein hamari nazar mein aurton ki koi izzat na thi. yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne unke barey mein wo ehkaam nazil kiye jo nazil karne they aur unke huquq muqarrar kiye jo muqarrar karne they. batlaya ke aik din main soch raha tha ke meri biwi ne mujh se kaha ke behtar hai agar tum us maamle falan-falan tarah karo, maine kaha tumhara usmein kya kaam . mamla mujh se mutaalliq hai tum usmein dakhal dene wali kon hoti ho? meri biwi ne is par kaha : Khattab ke betey ! tumharey is tarze-amal par hairat hai tum apni baton ka jawab bardasht nahi kar saktey tumhari ladki ( Hafsa ( to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bhi jawab de deti hain aik din to usne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ghussa bhi kar diya tha. ye sun kar umr (Raziallahu anhu) khadey ho gaey aur apni chadar odh kar Hafsa ke ghar pahunchey aur farmaya beti ! kya tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baton ka jawab de deti ho yahan tak ke aik din tum ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko din bhar naraz bhi rakha hai. Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne arz kya : ji haan , Allah ki qism ! ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kabhi jawab de detey hain. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine kaha jaan lo main tumhen Allah ki saza aur uske rasool ki saza ( narazagi ( se daraataa hun. betii! us aurat ki wjah se dhoke mein na aa jana jisne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki mohabbat hasil kar li hai. unka ishara Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf tha. kaha ke phir main wahan se nikal kar Ummul-Momenin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aaya kyonke wo bhi meri rishtedar thin. maine unse bhi guftgu ki unhon-ne kaha ibne-khattaab ! tajjub hai ke aap har maamle mein dakhal-andaazii kartey hain aur aap chahtey hain ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur unki beeviyon ke maamlaat mein bhi dakhal dein. Allah ki qism ! unhon-ne meri aisi giraft ki ke mere ghussa ko thanda karke rakh diya. main unke ghar se bahar nikal aaya. mere aik Ansari dost they, jab main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki majlis mein hazir na hota to wo majlis ki tamam baatein mujh se aa kar bataya kartey aur jab wo hazir na hotey to main unhein aa kar bataya karta tha. us zamane mein hamein ghassaan ke badshah ki taraf se dar tha itlaa mili thi ke wo Madina par chadhai karne ka irada kar raha hai, us zamane mein kai Esai aur Iraanii badshah aisa ghalat ghamand rakhtey they ke ye musalman kya hain ham jab chaahengey unka safaayaa kar dengey magar ye sarey khayalat ghalat Sabit huey Allah ne Islam ko ghalib kya. chunanche ham ko har waqt yahi khatrah rehta tha, aik din achcha mere Ansari dost ne darwaza khatkhataayaa aur kaha kholo ! kholo ! kholo ! maine kaha malum hota hai ghassaanii aa gaey. unhon-ne kaha balke us se bhi zyada aham mamla pesh aa gaya hai, wo ye ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon se alehadgii ikhtiyar kar li hai. maine kaha Hafsa aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki naak ghubaar aalud ho. chunanche maine apna kapda pehna aur bahar nikal aaya. main jab pahuncha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne baalaakhaane mein tashrif rakhtey they jis par seedhi se chadhaa jata tha. Nabi Karim ka aik habshi ghulam ( Ribah ( seedhi ke sirey par maujood tha, maine kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz karo ke umr bin-Khattab aaya hai aur andar aaney ki ijazat chahta hai. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunch kar apna Sara waqia sunaya. jab main Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki guftgu par pahuncha to aapko hansi aa gaee. us waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khajoor ki aik chatai par tashrif rakhtey they Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke jisme-mubaarak aur us chatai ke darmyan koi aur cheez nahi thi aap ke sar ke nichey aik chamdey ka takiya tha. jis mein khajoor ki chhaal bhari hui thi. paon ki taraf keekar ke patton ka dher tha aur sar ki taraf mishkeeza latak raha tha. maine chatai ke nishanat aap ke pahlu par dekhey to ro padaa . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, kis baat par roney lagey ho maine kaha ya Rasulullah ! qaisar w Kisraa ko duniya ka har tarah ka aaraam mil raha hai aap Allah ke rasool hain (aap phir aisi tang zindagi guzaartey hain) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya tum is par khush nahi ho ke unke hisse mein duniya hai aur hamarey hisse mein aakhirat hai."
4914,maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo bayan kartey they ke maine umr (Raziallahu anhu) se aik baat poochhney ka irada kya aur arz kya ameerul-momineen ! wo kon 2 auratein thin jinhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sataaney ke liye mansuba banaya tha? abhi maine apni baat poori bhi nahi ki thi ke unhon-ne kaha wo Aaisha aur Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) thin.
4915,"maine umr (Raziallahu anhu) se un aurton ke mutaalliq sawal karna chaha jinhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke uper zor kya tha. aik saal usi fikr mein raha aur mujhey koi mauqa nahi milta tha aakhir unke sath Haj ke liye nikla ( waapsii mein) jab ham maqam Zohraan mein they, to umr (Raziallahu anhu) zarurat se farigh honey ke liye gaey. phir kaha ke mere liye wuzu ka pani laao, main aik bartan mein pani laya aur unko wuzu karaaney laga us waqt mujh ko mauqa mila. maine arz kya ameerul-momineen ! wo auratein kon thin jinhoney Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke muqabil aisa kya tha? abhi maine apni baat poori na ki thi unhon-ne kaha ke wo Aaisha aur Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) thin."
4916,umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ghairat dilaane ke liye jama ho gain to maine unse kaha agar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) talaaq de dein to unka parwardigar tumharey badley mein unhein tum se behtar beeviyan dedega. chunanche ye aayat nazil hui ( عسى ربه إن طلقكن ( aakhir tak.
4917,aayat عتل بعد ذلك زنيم yaanii ''wo zaalim sakht mizaaj hai iske ilawa haraamii bhi hai.'' ke mutaalliq farmaya ke ye aayat Quraish ke aik shakhs ke barey mein hui thi uski gardan mein nishani thi jaisey bakri mein nishani hoti hai ke kuchh unmein ka koi uzu (khaas ang) badha hua hota hai.
4918,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke main tumhen jannati aadmi ke mutaalliq na bata dun. wo dekhney mein kamzor kamzor hota hai (lekin Allah ke yahan iska martaba ye hai ke) agar kisi baat par Allah ki qism kha ley to Allah usey zaroor poori kar deta hai aur kya main tumhen dozakh walon ke mutaalliq na bata dun har bdkhoo, bhari jism wala aur takabbur karne wala."
4919,hamara rab qiyamat ke din apni pindlii kholega us waqt har momin mard aur har momina aurat uske liye sajde mein gir padengey. sirf wo baqi reh jaeinge jo duniya mein dikhawey aur naamwarii ke liye sajda kartey they. jab wo sajda karna chaahengey to unki peeth takhta ho jaeygi aur wo sajde ke liye na mud sakengey.
4920,jo but Musa (Alaihissalam) ki qaum mein poojey jatey they baad mein wahi Arab mein poojey janey lagey. wadd daumatul-Jandal mein bani kalab ka but tha. suwaa' banii-Huzail kaa. Yaghoos bani murad ka aur murad ki shaakh bani Ghutef ka jo wadi ajwaf mein qaume-sabaa ke paas rahtey they Yaooq bani hamdaan ka but tha. Nasr hameer ka but tha jo zul-kulaa' ki aal mein se they. ye panchon Nuh (Alaihissalam) ki qaum ke nek logon ke naam they jab unki maut ho gaee to shaitan ne unke dil mein daala ke apni majlison mein jahan wo baithey they unke but qaaim kar lein aur un buton ke naam apne nek logon ke naam par rakh lein chunanche un logon ne aisa hi kya us waqt un buton ki puja nahi hoti thi lekin jab wo log bhi mar gaey jinhoney but qaaim kiye they aur ilm logon mein na raha to unki puja honey lagi
4921,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sahaba ke sath bazar Ukaaz (Makka aur Taaif ke darmyan aik maidan jahan Arbon ka mashhoor mela lagta tha) ka irada kya us zamane mein shayatin tak aasman ki khabron ke churaa leney mein rukawat paida kar di gaee thi aur un par aasman se aag ke angaarey chhodey jatey they jab wo jin apni qaum ke paas lot kar aaey to unki qaum ne unse puchha ke kya baat hui. unhon-ne bataya ke aasman ki khabron main aur hamarey darmyan rukawat kar di gaee hai aur ham par aasman se aag ke angaarey barsaey gaey hain, unhon-ne kaha ke aasman ki khabron aur tumharey darmyan rukawat honey ki wjah ye hai ke koi khas baat pesh aai hai. isliye saari zameen par mashriq w maghrib mein phail jao aur talash karo ke kon si baat pesh aa gaee hai. chunanche shayatin mashriq w maghrib mein phail gaey taake is baat ka pata lagaaein ke aasman ki khabron ki un tak pahunchne mein rukawat paida ki gaee hai wo kis badey waaqie ki wjah se hai. bayan kya ke jo shayatin is khoj mein nikley they unka aik giroh wadi tahaama ki taraf bhi aa nikla (ye jagah Makka muazzama se aik din ke safar ki raah par hai) jahan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mandi Ukaaz ki taraf jatey huey khajoor ke aik baagh ke paas thahrey huey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt sahaba ke sath fajr ki Namaz padh rahe they. jab shayatin ne Quran Majeed suna to ye usko sunney lag gaey phir unhon-ne kaha ke yahi cheez hai wo jiski wjah se tumharey aur aasman ki khabron ke darmyan rukawat paida hui hai. iske baad wo apni qaum ki taraf lot aaey aur unse kaha ke) إنا سمعنا قرآنا عجبا ( ham ne aik ajeeb Quran suna hai jo neki ki raah dikhlaataa hai so ham to is par eman ley aaey aur ham ab apne parwardigar ko kisi ka saajhii na banaaengey Allah Taala ne apne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par ye aayat nazil ki قل أوحي إلى أنه استمع نفر من الجن‏ aap kahey ke mere paas wahi aai hai is baat ki ke Jinnon ki aik jamat ne Quran Majeed suna yahi Jinnon ka qaul Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par nazil hua."
4922,"Quran Majeed ki kon si aayat sabse pahley nazil hui thi. unhon-ne kaha ke) ya أيها المدثر‏ ( maine arz kya ke log to kehtey hain ke ( اقرأ باسم ربك الذي خلق‏ ) sabse pahley nazil hui. abu-Salma ne is par kaha ke maine Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha tha aur jo baat abhi tum ne mujh se kahi wahi maine bhi unse kahi thi lekin Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha tha ke main tum se wahi hadis bayan karta hun jo ham se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmai thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke main ghare-hira mein aik muddat ke liye khilwat (ekaant) mein tha. jab main wo din poorey karke pahaad se utra to mujhey awaz di gaee, maine us awaz par apne daain taraf dekha lekin koi cheez nahi dikhai di. phir baain taraf dekha udhar bhi koi cheez dikhai nahi di, samney dekha udhar bhi koi cheez nahi dikhai di. peechhey ki taraf dekha aur udhar bhi koi cheez nahi dikhai di. ab maine apna sar uper ki taraf uthaya to mujhey aik cheez dikhai di. phir main Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aaya aur unse kaha ke mujhey kapda odha 2 aur mujh par thanda pani daalo. farmaya ke phir unhon-ne mujhey kapda odha diya aur thanda pani mujh par bahaayaa. farmaya ke phir ye aayat nazil hui (ya أيها المدثر * قم فأنذر * وربك فكبر‏ ( yani ''aey kapdey mein lipatne waale! uthiye phir logon ko azabe-Ilahi se daraaiye aur apne parwardigar ki badaai bayan keejiye.''"
4923,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main ghare-hira main tanhai ikhtiyar kiye huey tha. ye riwayat bhi Usman bin umr ki hadis ki tarah hai jo unhon-ne Ali bin-Mubarak se bayan ki hai.
4924,maine abu-Salma se puchha ke Quran Majeed ki kon si aayat sabse pahley nazil hui thi? farmaya ke) ya أيها المدثر‏ ( maine kaha ke mujhey khabar mili hai ke ( اقرأ باسم ربك الذي خلق‏ ) sabse pahley nazil hui thi. abu-Salma ne bayan kya ke maine Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha tha ke Quran ki kon si aayat sabse pahley nazil hui thi? unhon-ne farmaya ke) ya أيها المدثر‏ ( ''aey kapdey mein lipatne waley ! '' maine unse yahi kaha tha ke mujhey khabar mili hai ke ( اقرأ باسم ربك الذي خلق‏ ) sabse pahley nazil hui thi to unhon-ne kaha ke main tumhen wahi khabar de raha hun jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine ghare-hira main tanhai ikhtiyar ki jab main wo muddat poori kar chuka aur nichey utar kar wadi ke beech mein pahuncha to mujhey pukara gaya. maine apne aagey peechhey daain baain dekha aur mujhey dikhai diya ke farishta aasman aur zameen ke darmyan kursi par betha hai. phir main Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aaya aur unse kaha ke mujhey kapda odha 2 aur mere uper thanda pani dalo aur mujh par ye aayat nazil hui (ya أيها المدثر * قم فأنذر * وربك فكبر‏ ( ''aey kapdey mein lipatne waley ! uthiye phir logon ko azab aakhirat se daraaiye aur apne parwardigar ki badaai keejiye.''
4925,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) darmyan mein wahi ka silsile ruk janey ka haal bayan farma rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main ro raha tha ke maine aasman ki taraf se awaz suni. maine apna sar uper uthaya to wahi farishta nazar aaya jo mere paas ghare-hira mein aaya tha. wo aasman w zameen ke darmyan kursi par betha hua tha. main iske dar se ghabraa gaya phir main ghar wapas aaya aur Khadija se kaha ke mujhey kapda odha do, mujhey kapda odha do. unhon-ne mujhey kapda odha diya phir Allah Taala ne aayat (ya أيها المدثر‏ ( se ( والرجز فاهجر‏ ( tak nazil ki. ye sura Namaz farz kiye janey se pahley nazil hui thi ( الرجز‏ ( se murad but hai."
4926,"maine Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) darmyan mein wahi ke silsiley ke ruk janey se mutaalliq bayan farma rahe they ke main chal raha tha ke maine aasman ki taraf se awaz suni. apni nazar aasman ki taraf utha kar dekha to wahi farishta nazar aaya jo mere paas ghare-hira mein aaya tha. wo kursi par aasman aur zameen ke darmyan mein betha hua tha. maine usey dekh kar itna dara ke zameen par gir padaa . phir main apni biwi ke paas aaya aur unse kaha ke mujhey kapda odha do, mujhey kapda odha do ! mujhey kapda odha do. phir Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki) ya أيها المدثر‏ ( se ( والرجز فاهجر‏ ( tak abu-Salma ne bayan kya ke) الرجز ( but ke mana mein hai. phir wahi garm ho gaee aur silsila nahi tootaa ."
4927,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi nazil hoti to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par apni zaban hilaayaa kartey they. Sufiyan ne kaha ke us hilaaney se aap ka maqsad wahi ko yad karna hota tha. is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki لا تحرك به لسانك لتعجل به ''aap jaldi jaldii leney ke liye is par zaban na hilaayaa karein, iska jama kar dena aur iska padhwaa denaa, ye donon kaam to hamarey zimme hain.''"
4928,"unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se Allah Taala ke irshaad لا تحرك به لسانك لتعجل به yaanii ''aap Quran ko leney ke liye zaban na hilaayaa karein'' ke mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne bayan kya ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi nazil hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne hont hilaayaa kartey they isliye aap se kaha gayaa لا تحرك به لسانك لتعجل به yaanii wahi par apni zaban na hilaayaa karein, iska tumharey dil mein jama dena aur iska padha dena hamara kaam hai. jab ham usko padh chukein yani Jibraeel tujh ko suna chukein to jaisa Jibraeel ne padh kar sunaya to bhi isi tarah padh. phir ye bhi hamara hi kaam hai ke ham teri zaban se usko padhwaa dengey."
4929,"Allah Taala ke irshaad لا تحرك به لسانك لتعجل به yaanii ''aap usko jaldi jaldii leney ke liye is par zaban na hilaayaa karein'' ke mutaalliq batlaya ke jab Jibraeel aap par wahi nazil kartey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni zaban aur hont hilaayaa kartey they aur aap par ye bahut sakht guzarta , ye aap ke chehrey se bhi zahir hota tha. isliye Allah Taala ne wo aayat nazil ki jo sura 'Qiyaama' mein hai yaanii لا تحرك به لسانك لتعجل به yaanii ''aap usko jaldi jaldii leney ke liye is par zaban na hilaayaa karein. ye to hamarey zimme hai iska jama kar dena aur iska padhwaanaa, phir jab ham usey padhney lagein to aap iske peechhey yad kartey jaya karein. yani jab ham wahi nazil karein to aap ghaur se sunein. phir iska bayan kara dena bhi hamarey zimme hai.'' yani ye bhi hamarey zimme hai ke ham usey aap ki zabani logon ke samney bayan kara dein. bayan kya ke chunanche iske baad jab Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) wahi lekar aatey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khamosh ho jatey aur jab chaley jatey to padhtey jaisa ke Allah Taala ne aap se wada kya tha. aayat ( أولى لك فأولى‏ ( main ( تهديد ( yani daraanaa dhamakaanaa murad hai."
4930,ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they aur aap par sura Mursalaat nazil hui thi aur ham usko aap ke munh se seekh rahe they ke itney mein aik sanp nikal aaya. ham log iske maarney ko badhey lekin wo bach nikla aur apne suraakh mein ghus gaya. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo tumharey shar se bach gaya aur tum uske shar se bach gaey.
4931,"aur Yahya bin Adam ke sath us hadis ko Aswad bin Aamir ne Israel se riwayat ki aur Hafs bin Ghiyas aur abu-Muawia aur Sulaiman-bin قرم ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Aswad se riwayat kya aur Yahya bin Hammad ( Shekh Bukhari ( ne kaha ham ko abu-Awana ne khabar di, unhon-ne Mughira bin Muqsim se, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Alqama se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Masood se aur Muhammad-bin-Is'haaq ne us hadis ko Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Aswad se riwayat kya, unhon-ne apne walid Aswad se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Masood se bayan kya."
4932,kaha maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aayat إنها ترمي بشرر كالقصر yaanii ''wo angaarey barsaaeygii jaisey badey mahal ''ke mutaalliq puchha aur unhon-ne kaha ke ham teen-teen hath ki lakdiyan utha kar rakhtey they. aisa ham jaadon ke liye kartey they (taake wo jalaaney ke kaam aaein) aur unka naam (qasar) rakhtey they.
4933,"aur unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, aayat (ترمي بشرر‏ كالقصر) ke mutaalliq. aap ne farmaya ke ham teen hath ya us se bhi lambi lakdiyan utha kar jaadon ke liye rakh letey they. aisi lakdiyon ko ham (qasar) kehtey they, كأنه جمالات صفر se murad kashtii ki rassiyaan hain jo jod kar rakhi jaaein, wo aadmi ki kamar barabar motii ho jaaein."
4934,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik ghaar mein they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par sura Mursalaat nazil hui, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski tilawat ki aur maine usey aap hi ke munh se yad kar liya. wahi se aap ki munh ki taazgi us waqt bhi baqi thi ke itney mein ghaar ki taraf aik sanp lapkaa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey mar daalo. ham uski taraf badhey lekin wo bhag gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke wo bhi tumharey shar se is tarah bach nikla jaisa ke tum uske shar se bach gaey. Umar-bin Hafs ne kaha mujhey ye hadis yad hai, maine apne walid se suni thi, unhon-ne itna aur badhaya tha ke wo ghaar Mina mein tha."
4935,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke 2 Saur phoonkey janey ke darmyan chalis (40) fasla hoga. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke shagirdon ne puchha kya chalis (40) din murad hain? unhon-ne kaha ke mujhey malum nahi phir shagirdon ne puchha kya chalis (40) mahiney murad hain? unhon-ne kaha ke mujhey malum nahi. shagirdon ne puchha kya chalis (40) saal murad hain? kaha ke mujhey malum nahi. kaha ke phir Allah Taala aasman se pani barsaaeyga. jiski wjah se tamam murdey ji uthengey jaisey sabziyaan pani se ug aati hain. us waqt insan ka har hissey gal chuka hoga. siwaay reedh ki haddi ke aur us se qiyamat ke din tamam makhlooq dobara banai jaeygi.
4936,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha kaha aap apni beech ki ungli aur angoothey ke qareeb wali ungli ke ishaarey se farma rahe they ke main aisey waqt mein Nabi banaakar bheja gaya hun ke mere aur qiyamat ke darmyan sirf un 2 ke barabar fasla hai.
4937,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us shakhs ki misal jo Quran padhta hai aur wo iska Hafiz bhi hai, mukarram aur nek likhney waley (farishton) jaisi hai aur jo shakhs Quran Majeed baar-baar padhta hai. phir bhi wo uske liye dushwar hai to usey 2 guna sawab milega."
4938,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jis din log donon jahan ke paalne waley ke samney hisab dene ke liye khadey hongey to kanon ki lo tak paseene mein doob jaengey.
4939,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna.
4940,Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kahaa لتركبن طبقا an (an) طبق yaanii ''tum ko zaroor aik haalat ke baad dusri haalat par pahunchnaa hai.'' bayan kya ke yahan murad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain ke aapko kamiyabi dheerey-dheerey hasil hogi.
4941,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke (muhaajir) sahaba mein sabse pahley hamarey paas Madina tashrif laney waley Mus'ab-bin-Umair aur ibn-Umme-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) they. Madina pahunch kar un buzurgon ne hamein Quran Majeed padhaanaa shuru kar diya. phir Ammaar, Bilal aur Sad (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bees sahaba ko sath lekar aaey iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey maine kabhi Madina walon ko itna khush honey wala nahi dekha tha, jitna wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aamad par khush huey they. bachchiyaan aur bachchey bhi kehney lagey they ke aap Allah ke rasool hain, hamarey yahan tashrif laey hain. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Madina mein tashrif aawrii se pahley hi ( سبح اسم ربك الأعلى‏ (aur us jaisi aur soortein padh li thin."
4942,"unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne aik khutbe mein Saleh (Alaihissalam) ki ontni ka zikr farmaya aur us shakhs ka bhi zikr farmaya jisne uski koonchein kaat dali thin phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya ( إذ انبعث أشقاها‏ ( yani us ontni ko mar dalney ke liye aik fasaadii bad-bakht ko apni qaum mein abu-Zama'a ki tarah ghalib aur taaqatwar tha uthaa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aurton ke huquq ka bhi zikr farmaya ke tum mein kuchh apni biwi ko ghulam ki tarah kode maartey hain halanke isi din ke khatm honey par wo us se ham-bistarii bhi kartey hain. phir aap ne unhein hawa khaarij honey par hansney se mana farmaya aur farmaya ke aik kaam jo tum mein har shakhs karta hai usi par tum dusron par kis tarah hanstey ho. abu-Muawia ne bayan kya ke ham se Hisham-bin-Urwa bin Zuber ne, unse Abdullah-bin Zam-aa ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (is hadis mein) yun farmaya abu-Zama'a ki tarah jo Zubair-bin-Awaam ka chacha tha."
4943,"Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke shagirdon ke sath mein mulk Sham (Syria) pahuncha hamarey mutaalliq abu Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ne suna to ham se milney khud tashrif laey aur malum farmaya tum mein koi Quran Majeed ka qaari bhi hai? ham se kaha ji haan hai. malum farmaya ke sabse achchha qaari kon hai? logon ne meri taraf ishara kya. aap ne farmaya ke phir koi aayat tilawat karo. maine ( والليل إذا يغشى * والنهار إذا تجلى * والذكر والأنثى‏ ( ki tilawat ki. abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha kya tum ne khud ye aayat apne ustad Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki zabani isi tarah suni hai? maine kaha ji haan. unhon-ne is par kaha ke maine bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zabani ye aayat isi tarah suni hai, lekin ye Sham (Syria) waley ham par inkar kartey hain."
4944,Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke kuchh shagird abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan ( Sham (Syria) ( aaey unhon-ne unhein talash kya aur pa liya. phir unse puchha ke tum mein kon Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki qirat ke mutabiq qirat kar sakta hai? shagirdon ne kaha ke ham sab kar saktey hain. phir puchha kisey unki qirat zyada mehfooz hai? sab ne Alqama ki taraf ishara kya. unhon-ne malum kya unhein sura ( والليل إذا يغشى‏ ( ki qirat kartey kis tarah suna hai? Alqama ne kaha ke) والذكر والأنثى‏ ( ) baghair khalq ke) kaha ke main gawahi deta hun ke maine bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko isi tarah qirat kartey huey suna hai. lekin ye log (yani Sham (Syria) waale) chahtey hain ke ( وما خلق الذكر والأنثى‏ ) padhun. Allah ki qism main unki pairwi nahi karunga.
4945,ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Baqee gharqad (Madina Munawra ke qabristaan) mein aik janaaze mein they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us mauqe par farmaya ke tum mein koi aisa nahi jiska thikana jannat ya jahannam mein likha na ja chuka ho. sahaba ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! phir kyon na ham apni taqdeer par bharosa kar lein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke amal kartey raho ke har shakhs ko usi amal ki taufeeq miltii rehti hai (jiske liye wo paida kya gaya hai) phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aayat ( فأما من أعطى واتقى * وصدق بالحسنى‏ ( aakhir tak padhi. yani ham uske liye nek kaam aasan kar dengey.
4946,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik janaaze mein they, aap ne aik lakdi uthai aur us se zameen kuredtey huey farmaya ke tum mein koi shakhs aisa nahi jiska jannat ya dozakh ka thikana likha na ja chuka ho. sahaba ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! kya phir ham usi par bharosa na kar lein? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke amal kartey raho ke har shakhs ko taufeeq di gaee hai (unhiin aamaal ki jinke liye wo paida kya gaya hai) ( فأما من أعطى واتقى * وصدق بالحسنى‏ ( ''so jisne diya aur Allah se dara aur achi baat ko sachcha samjhaa'' aakhir aayat tak. Shoba ne bayan kya ke mujh se ye hadis Mansoor bin Motamir ne bhi bayan ki aur unhon-ne bhi Sulaiman Aamash se usi ke muwafiq bayan ki, usmein koi khilaf nahi kya."
4947,ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas baithey huey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ham mein koi aisa nahi jiska jahannam ka thikana aur jannat ka thikana likha na ja chuka ho. ham ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! phir ham usi par bharosa kyon na kar lein? farmaya nahi amal kartey raho kyonke har shakhs ko aasani di gaee hai aur uske baad aap ne us aayat ki tilawat ki) فأما من أعطى واتقى * وصدق بالحسنى * فسنيسره لليسرى‏ ( yani ''so jisne diya aur Allah se dara aur achi baat ko sachcha samjha uske liye raahat ki cheez aasan kar dengey. '' ( فسنيسره للعسرى‏ ( tak.
4948,"ham Baqee gharqad mein aik janaaze ke sath they. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi tashrif laey. aap baith gaey aur ham bhi aap ke charon taraf baith gaey. aap ke hath mein chhadi thi. aap ne sar jhukaa liya phir chhadi se zameen ko kuredney lagey. phir farmaya ke tum mein koi shakhs aisa nahi, koi paida honey wali jaan aisi nahi jiska jannat aur jahannam ka thikana likha na ja chuka ho. ye likha ja chuka hai ke kon nek hai aur kon bura hai. aik sahib ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! phir kya harj hai agar ham apni usi taqdeer par bharosa kar lein aur nek amal karna chhod dein jo ham mein nek hoga, wo nekiyon ke sath ja milega aur jo bura hoga us se buron ke se aamaal ho jaengey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo log nek hotey hain unhein nekon hi ke amal ki taufeeq hasil hoti hai aur jo burey hotey hain unhein buron hi jaisey amal karne ki taufeeq hoti hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is aayat ki tilawat ki) فأما من أعطى واتقى * وصدق بالحسنى‏ ( yani '' so jisne diya aur Allah se dara aur achi baat ko sachcha samjha so ham uske liye nek kaamon ko aasan kar dengey.''"
4949,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik janazey mein tashrif rakhtey they. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik cheez li aur us se zameen kuredney lagey aur farmaya, tum mein koi aisa shakhs nahi jiska jahannam ka thikana ya jannat ka thikana likha na ja chuka ho. sahaba ne arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! to phir ham kyon apni taqdeer par bharosa na kar lein aur nek amal karna chhod dein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nek amal karo, har shakhs ko un aamaal ki taufeeq di jati hai jinke liye wo paida kya gaya hai jo shakhs nek hoga usey nekon ke amal ki taufeeq mili hoti hai aur jo bad-bakht hota hai usey bad-bakhton ke amal ki taufeeq miltii hai phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aayat ( فأما من أعطى واتقى * وصدق بالحسنى‏ ( aakhir tak padhi yani ''so jisne diya aur Allah se dara aur achi baat ko sachcha samjhaa, so ham uske liye nek amalon ko aasan kar dengey.''"
4950,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bimar pad gaey aur 2 ya teen raaton ko (tahajjud ke liye) nahi uth sakey. phir aik aurat (abu-Lahab ki aurat Auraa) aai aur kehney lagi aey Muhammad! mera khayal hai ke tumharey shaitan ne tumhen chhod diya hai. 2 ya teen raaton se dekh rahi hun ke tumharey paas wo nahi aaya. is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki) والضحى * والليل إذا سجى * ما ودعك ربك وما قلى‏ ( aakhir tak yani '' qism hai din ki roshni ki aur raat ki jab wo qarar pakdey ke aap ke parwardigar ne na aapko chhoda hai aur na aap se bezaar hua hai.''
4951,aik aurat Ummul-Momenin Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah! main dekhti hun ke aap ke dost (Jibraaiil (al)) aap ke paas aaney mein der kartey hain. is par aayat nazil hui ( ما ودعك ربك وما قلى‏ ( yani '' aap ke parwardigar ne na aapko chhoda hai aur na aap se wo bezaar hua hai.''
4952,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik safar mein they aur isha ki aik rakaat mein aap ne sura والتین ki tilawat farmai thi. ( تقويم‏ (ke mana paidaaish, banawat ke hain."
4953,"unhein Urwa-bin-Zubair ne khabar di aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak biwi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko nabwooat se pahley sachey khuwab dikhaaey jatey they chunanche us daur mein aap jo khuwab bhi dekh letey wo subah ki roshni ki tarah bedaarii mein namudaar hota. phir aapko tanhai bhalii lagney lagi us daur mein aap ghare-hira tanha tashrif ley jatey aur aap wahan (tahannus) kya kartey they. Urwa ne kaha ke (tahannus) se ibadat murad hai. aap wahan kai-kai raatein jaagtey , ghar mein na aatey aur uske liye apne ghar se khane-pine ka saman ley jaya kartey they. phir jab khane-pine ka saman khatm ho jata phir Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan lot kar tashrif latey aur itna hi khane-pine ka saman phir ley jatey. usi haal mein aap ghare-hira mein they ke achcha aap par wahi nazil hui chunanche farishta aap ke paas aaya aur kaha padhiye! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main padha hua nahi hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bayan kya ke mujhey farishte ne pakad liya aur itna bheencha ke main be-taaqat ho gaya phir unhon-ne mujhey chhod diya aur kaha ke padhiye! maine kaha ke main padha hua nahi hun. unhon-ne phir dusri martaba mujhey pakad kar is tarah bheencha ke main be-taaqat ho gaya aur chhodney ke baad kaha ke padhiye! maine is martaba bhi yahi kaha ke main padha hua nahi hun. unhon-ne teesri martaba phir isi tarah mujhey pakad kar bheencha ke main be-taaqat ho gaya aur kaha ke padhiye! padhiye! اقرأ باسم ربك الذي خلق * خلق الإنسان من علق * اقرأ وربك الأكرم * الذي علم بالقلم''apne parwardigar ke naam ke sath jisne sab ko paida kya, jisne insan ko khoon ke lothdey se paida kya hai, aap padhiye aur aap ka rab Karim hai, jisne qalam ke zariey taleem di hai'' se aayat ( علم الإنسان ما لم يعلم‏ ) tak. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un panch aayatein ko lekar wapas ghar tashrif laey aur ghabraahat se aap ke mundhey aur gardan ka gosht phadak (harkat kar) raha tha. aap ne Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ke paas pahunch kar farmaya ke mujhey chadar udha do ! mujhey chadar udha do! chunanche unhon-ne aapko chadar udha di. jab ghabraahat aap se door hui to aap ne Khadija (Raziallahu anha) se kaha ab kya hoga mujhey to apni jaan ka dar ho gaya hai phir aap ne Sara waqia unhein sunaya. Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha aisa hargiz na hoga, aapko khushkhabri ho, Allah ki qism ! Allah aapko kabhi ruswa nahi karega . Allah ki qism ! aap to sila rehmii karne waley hain, aap hamesha sach boltey hain, aap kamzor w kamzor ka bojh khud utha letey hain, jinhein kahin se kuchh nahi milta wo aap ke yahan se pa letey hain. aap mehman nawaaz hain aur haq ke rastey mein pesh aaney wali museebaton par logon ki madad kartey hain. phir Khadija (Raziallahu anha) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko lekar Warqa-bin Nofal ke paas aaein wo Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ke chacha aur aap ke walid ke bhai they wo zamana jahiliyat mein nasrani ho gaey they aur arabii likh letey they jis tarah Allah ne chaha unhon-ne Injeel bhi arabii mein likhi thi. wo bahut boodhey they aur naa-beenaa ho gaey they. Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ne unse kaha chacha apne bhatijey ka haal suniye. Warqa-ne kaha betey! tum ne kya dekha hai? aap ne Sara haal sunaya jo kuchh aap ne dekha tha. is par Warqa-ne kaha yahi wo namus (Jibraaiil (al)) hain jo Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aatey they. kash! mein tumhari nabwooat ke zamane mein jawan aur taaqatwar hota. kash! mein us waqt tak zinda reh jata, phir Warqa ne kuchh aur kaha ke jab aap ki qaum aapko Makka se nikaalegii. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya waqei ye log mujhey Makka se nikal dengey? Warqa-ne kaha haan, jo dawat aap lekar aaey hain usey jo bhi lekar aaya to us se adaawat zaroor ki gaee. agar main aap ki nabwooat ke zamane mein zinda reh gaya to main zaroor bharpur tariqa par aap ka sath doonga. iske baad Warqa ka intiqal ho gaya aur kuchh dinon ke liye wahi ka aana bhi band ho gaya. aap wahi ke band ho janey ki wjah se ghamgeen rehney lagey."
4954,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahi ke kuchh dinon ke liye ruk janey ka zikr farma rahe they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main chal raha tha ke maine achcha aasman ki taraf se aik awaz suni. maine nazar utha kar dekha to wahi farishta (Jibraaiil (al)) jo mere paas ghare-hira mein aaya tha, aasman aur zameen ke darmyan kursi par betha hua nazar aaya. mein unse bahut dara aur ghar wapas aa kar maine kaha ke mujhey chadar udha do chunanche ghar walon ne mujhey chadar udha di, phir Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki) ya أيها المدثر * قم فأنذر * وربك فكبر * وثيابك فطهر * والرجز فاهجر‏ ( ''aey kapdey mein lipatne waley ! uthiye phir logon ko daraaiye aur apne parwardigar ki badaai bayan kijiye aur apne kapdon ko paak rakhiye.'' abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke) الرجز ( jahiliyat ke but they jinki wo parastish kya kartey they. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir wahi barabar aaney lagi"
4955,"shuru main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko sachey khuwab dikhaaey janey lagey. phir aap ke paas farishta aaya aur kahaa اقرأ باسم ربك الذي خلق * خلق الإنسان من علق * اقرأ وربك الأكرم ke ''aap padhiye, apne parwardigar ke naam ke sath jisne (sab ko paida kya hai) jisne insan ko khoon ke lothdey se paida kya hai. aap padha kijiye aur aap ka parwardigar bada Karim hai.''"
4956,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nabwooat ki shuruaat sachey khuwabon se ki gaee aur kahaa اقرأ باسم ربك الذي خلق * خلق الإنسان من علق * اقرأ وربك الأكرم ke ''aap padhiye, apne parwardigar ke naam ki madad se jisne sab ko paida kya hai, jisne insan ko khoon ke lothdey se banaya. aap padha kijiye aur aap ka parwardigar bada Karim hai, jisne qalam ko zariey taleem banaayaa.''"
4957,"phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ke paas wapas tashrif laey aur farmaya ( زملوني زملوني (ke mujhey chadar udha do, mujhey chadar udha do. phir aap ne Sara waqia bayan farmaya,"
4958,"abu-Jahal ne kaha tha ke agar maine Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Kaba ke paas Namaz padhtey dekh liya to uski gardan mein kuchal doonga . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jab ye baat pahunchi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar us ne aisa kya hota to usey Farishtey pakad letey. Abdur-Razzaq ke sath us hadis ko Amr bin Khalid ne riwayat kya hai, unse Ubaidullah ne, unse Abdul-Karim ne bayan kya."
4959,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ubai-bin-Kab se farmaya ke Allah Taala ne mujhey hukm diya hai ke tumhen sura ( لم يكن الذين كفروا‏ ( padh kar sunaun. Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, kya Allah Taala ne mera naam bhi liya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, is par wo roney lagey."
4960,"Allah Taala ne mujhey hukm diya hai ke tumhen Quran (sura لم یکن ( padh kar sunaun. Ubai-bin-Kab ne arz kya : kya aap se Allah Taala mera naam bhi liya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, Allah Taala ne tumhara naam bhi mujh se liya hai. Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ye sun kar roney lagey. Qatada ne bayan kya ke mujhey khabar di gaee hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein sura ( لم يكن الذين كفروا من أهل الكتاب‏ ( padh kar sunai thi."
4961,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ubai-bin-Kab se farmaya ke Allah Taala ne mujhey hukm diya hai ke tumhen Quran ki) sura لم یکن ( padh kar sunaun . unhon-ne puchha kya Allah ne aap se mera naam bhi liya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan. Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) boley tamam jahaanon ke paalne waley ke yahan mera zikr hua? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, is par unki aankhon se aansu nikal padey ."
4962,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ghoda teen tarah ke log teen qism ke paaltey hain. aik shakhs ke liye wo ajr hota hai doosrey ke liye wo maafi hai, teesrey ke liye azab hai. jiske liye wo ajr w sawab hai wo shakhs hai jo usey Allah ke raaste mein jihad ki niyat se paaltaa hai. charaagaah ya iske bajaey rawi ne ye kaha baagh mein uski rassii ko daraaz kar deta hai aur wo ghoda charaagaah ya baagh main apni rassii tudaa ley aur eik-do kode (phainkney ki doorii) tak apni had se aagey badh gaya to uske nishaanaate-qadam aur uski leed bhi Malik ke liye sawab bin jati hai aur agar kisi nehar se guzartey huey usmein Malik ke irade ke baghair khud hi us ne pani pi liya to ye bhi Malik ke liye baaise-sawaab bin jata hai. doosra shakhs jiske liye iska ghoda baais muaafii, parda banta hai. ye wo shakhs hai jisne logon se be-parwaah rehney aur logon (ke samney sawal karne se) bchney ke liye usey paalaa aur us ghodey ki gardan par jo Allah Taala ka haq hai aur uski peeth ko jo haq hai usey bhi wo ada karta rehta hai. to ghoda uske liye baais muaafii, parda bin jata hai aur jo shakhs ghoda apne darwazey par fakhr aur dikhawey aur Islam dushmanii ki gharaz se baandhtaa hai, wo uske liye wabaal hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se gadhon ke mutaalliq puchha gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ne iske mutaalliq mujh par khas aayat siwa us akelii aam aur jaame aayat ke nazil nahi ki) فمن يعمل مثقال ذرة خيرا يره * ومن يعمل مثقال ذرة شرا يره‏ ( yani ''jo koi zarra bhar neki karega wo usey bhi dekh lega aur jo koi zarra bhar burai karega wo usey bhi dekh lega.''"
4963,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se gadhon ke mutaalliq puchha gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is akelii aam aayat ke siwa mujh par iske barey mein aur koi khas hukm nazil nahi hua hai) فمن يعمل مثقال ذرة خيرا يره * ومن يعمل مثقال ذرة شرا يره‏ ( yani ''so jo koi zarra barabar neki karega usey dekh lega aur jo koi zarra barabar burai karega wo usey bhi dekh lega.''
4964,jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko meraaj hui Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main aik nehar par pahuncha jiske donon kinaron par khauldaar motiyon ke derey lagey huey they. maine puchha aey Jibraaiil! ye nehar kaisi hai? unhon-ne bataya ke ye hauze-kausar hai (jo Allah ne aapko diya hai).
4965,"maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se Allah Taala ke irshad ( إنا أعطيناك الكوثر‏ ( yani ''ham ne aapko kausar ata kya hai'' ke mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne batlaya ke ye (kausar) aik nehar hai jo tumharey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bakhshii gaee hai, iske 2 kinarey hain jin par khauldaar motiyon ke derey hain. iske aab-khorey sitaron ki tarah unginat hain. is hadis ki riwayat Zakariya aur Abul-Ehwas aur Mutarrif ne Abu-Ishaq se ki hai."
4966,"aur unse Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kausar ke mutaalliq ke wo khaire-kaseer hai jo Allah Taala ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko di hai. abu-Bashar ne bayan kya ke maine Saeed-bin-Jubair se arz ki, logon ka khayal hai ke us se jannat ki aik nehar murad hai? Saeed ne kaha ke jannat ki nehar bhi us khaire-kaseer mein se aik hai jo Allah Taala ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko di hai."
4967,"aayat إذا جاء نصر الله والفتح yaanii ''jab Allah ki madad aur fateh aa pahunchii'' jab se nazil hui thi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne koi Namaz aisi nahi padhi jis mein aap ye dua na kartey hon سبحانك ربنا وبحمدك ، Mina اللهم اغفر لي yaanii '' paak hai teri zaat , aey Allah ! aey hamarey rab! aur terey hi liye tareef hai. aey Allah meri maghfirat farma de.''"
4968,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( sura fateh nazil honey ke baad) apne rukoo aur sajdon mein kasrat se ye dua padhtey they  سبحانك اللهم ربنا وبحمدك ، Mina اللهم اغفر لي yaanii ''paak hai teri zaat, aey Allah ! aey hamarey rab! aur terey hi liye tareef hai, aey Allaah! meri maghfirat farma de. '' Quran Majeed ke hukm mazkoor par is tarah aap amal kartey they."
4969,umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne boodhey Badri sahaba se Allah Taala ke irshaad إذا جاء نصر الله والفتح yaanii ''jab Allah ki madad aur fateh aa pahunchii'' ke mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne jawab diya ke us se ishara bahut se shehron aur mulkon ke fateh honey ki taraf hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Ibne-Abbas tumhara kya khayal hai? Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya ke usmein aap ki wafat ki khabar ya aik misal hai maano aap ki maut ki aapko khabar di gaee hai.
4970,"umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) mujhey boodhey Badri sahaba ke sath majlis mein bithatey they. kuchh ( Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ( ko is par aetraz hua, unhon-ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke usey aap majlis mein hamarey sath bithatey hain, iske jaisey to hamarey bhi bachchey hain? umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke uski wjah tumhen malum hai. phir unhon-ne aik din Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya aur unhein boodhey Badri sahaba ke sath bithaya (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke) mein samajh gaya ke aap ne mujhey unhein dikhaaney ke liye bulaya hai, phir unse puchha Allah Taala ke us irshad ke mutaalliq tumhara kya khayal hai إذا جاء نصر الله والفتح yaanii '' jab Allah ki madad aur fateh aa pahunchi '' kuchh logon ne kaha ke jab hamein madad aur fateh hasil hui to Allah ki hamd aur us se istighfar ka hamein aayat mein hukm diya gaya hai. kuchh log khamosh rahe aur koi jawab nahi diya. phir aap ne mujh se puchha : Ibne-Abbas ! kya tumhara bhi yahi khayal hai? maine arz kya ke nahi. puchha phir tumhari kya raey hai? maine kaha ke usmein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ki taraf ishara hai. Allah Taala ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko yahi cheez batai hai aur farmaayaa إذا جاء نصر الله والفتح ke '' jab Allah ki madad aur fateh aa pahunchi '' yani phir ye aap ki wafat ki alamat hai. isliye aap apne parwardigar ki paakii w tareef bayan kijiye aur us se bakhshish maanga kijiye . beshak wo bada tauba qabool karne wala hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par kaha, main bhi wahi janta hun jo tum ne kahaa."
4971,"jab ye aayat nazil hui ( وأنذر عشيرتك الأقربين‏ ( '' aap apne qaribi rishte-daaron ko daraaiye aur apne giroh ke un logon ko daraaiye jo mukhleseen hain.'' to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Safa pahaadii par chadh gaey aur pukara : yaa-sabaahaahu! Quraish ne kaha ye kon hai, phir wahan sab aa kar jama ho gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke tumhara kya khayal hai, agar main tumhen bataaun ke aik lashkar us pahaad ke peechhey se aaney wala hai, to kya tum mujh ko sachcha nahi samjhogey? unhon-ne kaha ke hamein jhoot ka aap se tajriba kabhi bhi nahi hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir main tumhen us sakht azab se daraataa hun jo tumharey samney aa raha hai. ye sun kar abu-Lahab bola, to tabah ho, kya tu ney hamein usi liye jama kya tha? phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan se chaley aaey aur aap par ye sura nazil huii ( تبت يدا أبي لهب وتب‏) yaanii ''donon hath toot gaey abu-Lahab ke aur wo barbad ho gayaa.''"
4972,"yani wo halaak hua, na uska maal uske kaam aaya aur na jo kuchh usne kamaayaa wo kaam aaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Batha ki taraf tashrif le gaey aur pahaadii par chadh kar pukara . ya sabaahaa ! Quraish us awaz par aap ke paas jama ho gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse puchha : tumhara kya khayal hai agar main tumhen bataaun ke dushman tum par subah ke waqt ya Sham ke waqt hamla karne wala hai to kya tum meri tasdeeq nahi karogey? unhon-ne kaha ke haan, zaroor aap ki tasdeeq karengey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke to main tumhen sakht azab se daraataa hun jo tumharey samney aa raha hai. abu-Lahab bola tum tabah ho jao. kya tum ne hamein isi liye jama kya tha? is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki ( تبت يدا أبي لهب وتب‏) aakhir tak."
4973,abu-Lahab ne kaha tha ke to tabah ho. kya tu ney hamein usi liye jama kya tha? is par ye aayat ( تبت يدا أبي لهب وتب‏) naazil hui.
4974,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala farmata hai ke mujhey ibne-Aadam ne jhutlaayaa halanke uske liye ye bhi munasib nahi tha. mujhey jhutlana ye hai ke) ibne-Aadam ( kehta hai ke main usko dobara nahi paida karunga halanke mere liye dobara paida karna uske pehli martaba paida karne se zyada mushkil nahi. uska mujhey gali dena ye hai ke kehta hai ke Allah ne apna betaa banaya hai halanke main aik hun. be-niyaaz hun na mere liye koi aulad hai aur na main kisi ki aulad hun aur na koi mere barabar hai.
4975,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke (Allah paak ne farmaya hai ke) ibne-Aadam ne mujhey jhutlaayaa halanke uske liye ye munasib na tha. usne mujhey gali di halanke ye uska haq nahi tha. mujhey jhutlana ye hai ke (ibne-Aadam) kehta hai ke main usey dobara zinda nahi kar sakta jaisa ke maine usey pehli baar paida kya tha. uska gali dena ye hai ke kehta hai Allah ne betaa bana liya hai halanke main be-niyaaz hun, mere yahan na koi aulad hai aur na main kisi ki aulad aur na koi mere barabar ka hai. ( كفؤا (aur ( كفيئا (aur ( كفاء ( ham mana hain."
4976,unhon-ne Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se muawwizatain ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne bayan kya ke ye masla maine bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey ( Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ( ki zabani kaha gaya hai ke yun kahey ke) اعوذ برب Falaq ( maine isi tarah kaha chunanche ham bhi wahi kehtey hain jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kahaa.
4977,"ya abul-Munzir! aap ke bhai Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) to ye kehtey hain ke sura muawwizatain Quran mein dakhil nahi hain. Ubai-bin-Kab ne kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se is baat ko puchha tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya ke (Jibraaiil (Alaihissalam) ki zabaanii) mujh se yun kaha gaya ke aisa kahey aur maine kaha, Uabaii-bin-Ka'b (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ham bhi wahi kehtey hain jaisa ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha."
